(155, 13, 'Life as an end is qualitatively different from life as a means.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:14:50'),
(156, 13, 'To test if you are worrying too much about looking good, observe how you feel when you find out you\'ve made a mistake or don\'t know something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:15:37'),
(157, 13, 'Make personal growth a daily priority.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:15:51'),
(158, 13, 'I define success by personal growth; if you don’t continue to grow, you can’t continue to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:16:09'),
(159, 13, 'In general, if a couple cannot expand their original rules and boundaries to accommodate personal growth, the relationship disintegrates.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:16:49'),
(160, 13, 'All the great spiritual traditions have placed major emphasis upon meditation as a path to personal growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:17:13'),
(161, 13, 'Dare to be what your best self knows you ought to be; dare to be a bigger human being than you have ever been.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:17:29'),
(162, 13, 'Be humble, be big in mind and soul, be kindly; you will like yourself that way and so will other people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:17:43'),
(163, 13, 'Something of defeat, something of tragedy, can be a sacrament because it stops us and causes us to look deeper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:17:59'),
(164, 13, 'There might be some credit in being jolly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:18:57'),
(165, 13, 'You ain\'t gonna learn what you don\'t wanna know.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:19:13'),
(166, 13, 'Life consists not simply in what heredity and environment do to us, but in what we make out of what they do to us', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:19:26'),
(167, 13, 'If somebody offers you an amazing opportunity but you are not sure you can do it, say yes-then learn how to do it later!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:19:39'),
(168, 13, 'Change comes more from managing the journey than from announcing the destination', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:19:49'),
(169, 13, 'We can cross the rivers of doubt and discouragement on the bridge of faith even before we get to them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:20:04'),
(170, 13, 'It is the capacity to develop and improve their skills that distinguishes leaders from followers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:20:19'),
(171, 13, 'Living on purpose requires us to find what we love fiercely, give it all we\'ve got and then pass it on, as if it were a torch, to those who follow', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:20:33'),
(172, 13, 'Hard work keeps the wrinkles out of the mind and spirit', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:21:29'),
(173, 13, 'If you see yourself as prosperous, you will be. If you see yourself as continually hard up, that is exactly what you will be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:21:45'),
(174, 13, 'We have to do the best we are capable of. This is our sacred human responsibility.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:21:59'),
(175, 13, 'Enthusiasm is the steam that drives the engine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:22:12'),
(176, 13, 'A man has to live with himself, and he should see to it that he always has good company.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:22:37'),
(177, 13, 'By thought, the thing you want is brought to you. By action, you receive it', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:23:02'),
(178, 13, 'Be wary of the arrogant intellectual who comments from the stands without having played on the field.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:23:22'),
(179, 13, 'Watch out for people who think it\'s embarrassing not to know.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:23:38'),
(180, 13, 'I find myself, at this time in my life, no less challenged, no less plagued, no less intrigued by what I still don\'t know.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:24:29'),
(181, 13, 'Be interesting, be enthusiastic... and don\'t talk too much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:25:03'),
(182, 13, 'Purpose is when you know and understand what you were born to accomplish. Vision is when you see it in your mind and begin to imagine it', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:25:16'),
(183, 13, 'When you go through difficult times...recognize that God is refining you, knocking off some of your rough edges', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:25:44'),
(184, 13, 'Do things for people not because of who they are or what they do in return, but because of who you are', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:25:59'),
(185, 13, 'Remind yourself. Nobody built like you, you design yourself', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:26:12'),
(186, 13, 'The truth can set us free, but only if we\'re always in the process of discovering it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:26:50'),
(187, 13, 'The quest for truth must be carried out by each person individually. It is like breathing, something which no one else can do for us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:27:18'),
(188, 13, 'Acceptance is such an important commodity, some have called it \"the first law of personal growth', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:27:40'),
(189, 13, 'A gentleman is one who puts more into the world than he takes out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:30:59'),
(190, 13, 'The world is full of magical things patiently waiting for our wits to grow sharper', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:34:39'),
(191, 13, 'Not knowing you can\'t do something, is sometimes all it takes to do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:35:01'),
(192, 13, 'Prosperity is a great teacher; adversity a greater.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:35:15'),
(193, 13, 'The whole secret of a successful life is to find out what is one\'s destiny to do, and then do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:35:34'),
(194, 13, 'Being open to correction means making ourselves vulnerable, and many people are not willing to do that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:40:21'),
(195, 13, 'It\'s a simple solution. You change one thing, and suddenly you\'ve changed everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:41:26'),
(196, 13, 'If you are on an honest journey to find yourself, you\'ll find God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:41:43'),
(197, 13, 'Surrender comes when you no longer ask, \'Why is this happening to me?\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:42:18'),
(198, 13, 'Who does not grow, declines.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:42:31'),
(199, 13, 'Change is inevitable but personal growth is a choice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:42:46'),
(200, 13, 'Lack and limitation can only exist when we make room for them in our mind', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:43:03'),
(201, 13, 'The older you get, the more you realize that kindness is synonymous with happiness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:43:28'),
(202, 13, 'Fear not for the future, weep not for the past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:43:58'),
(203, 13, 'The main cause of failure is the inability to deal with self-doubt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:44:26'),
(204, 13, 'Take your victories, whatever they may be, cherish them, use them, but don\'t settle for them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:44:39'),
(205, 13, 'There are no new ideas. There are only new ways of making them felt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:45:03'),
(206, 13, 'The greatest tragedy in life is not death, but a life without a purpose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:45:37'),
(207, 13, 'Solid character will reflect itself in consistent behavior, while poor character will seek to hide behind deceptive words and actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:46:12'),
(208, 13, 'Hoping for the best, prepared for the worst, and unsurprised by anything in between.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:46:30'),
(209, 13, 'It takes true strength of character to redefine your limits by pushing past them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:47:13'),
(210, 13, 'You alone are the judge of your worth and your goal is to discover infinite worth in yourself, no matter what anyone else thinks.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:47:26'),
(211, 13, 'If you change the way you look at things, the things you look at change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:47:47'),
(212, 13, 'Keep away from people who try to belittle your ambition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:48:23'),
(213, 13, 'Make sure the outside of you is a good reflection of the inside of you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:48:50'),
(214, 13, 'To conquer oneself is the best and noblest victory; to be vanquished by one\'s own nature is the worst and most ignoble defeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:49:57'),
(215, 13, 'The happiest life is that which constantly exercises and educates what is best in us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:50:14'),
(216, 13, 'The searching-out and thorough investigation of truth ought to be the primary study of man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 17:51:36'),
(217, 13, 'All change is not growth, as all movement is not forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:04:27'),
(218, 13, 'Life is growth. If we stop growing, technically and spiritually, we are as good as dead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:04:50'),
(219, 13, 'Strength and growth come only through continuous effort and struggle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:05:04'),
(220, 13, 'Growth begins when we start to accept our own weakness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:05:19'),
(221, 13, 'If we\'re growing, we\'re always going to be out of our comfort zone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:05:34'),
(222, 13, 'Never look back unless you are planning to go that way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:05:51'),
(223, 13, 'We know what we are, but know not what we may be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:06:13'),
(224, 13, 'The strongest principle of growth lies in the human choice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:06:29'),
(225, 13, 'It takes courage to grow up and become who you really are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:06:43'),
(226, 13, 'A feeling of continuous growth is a wonderful source of motivation and self confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:06:56'),
(227, 13, 'Life isn\'t about finding yourself. Life is about creating yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:07:12'),
(228, 13, 'Good timber does not grow with ease; the stronger the wind, the stronger the trees', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:07:23'),
(229, 13, 'There are no great limits to growth because there are no limits of human intelligence, imagination, and wonder.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:07:38'),
(230, 13, 'Conformity is the jailer of freedom and the enemy of growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:07:50'),
(231, 13, 'Growth is an erratic forward movement: two steps forward, one step back. Remember that and be very gentle with yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:08:27'),
(232, 13, 'All growth depends upon activity. There is no development physically or intellectually without effort, and effort means work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:08:47'),
(233, 13, 'Knowledge is a plant of slow growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:08:58'),
(234, 13, 'Truth, like gold, is to be obtained not by its growth, but by washing away from it all that is not gold.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:09:46'),
(235, 13, 'When we blindly adopt a religion, a political system, a literary dogma, we become automatons. We cease to grow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:10:10'),
(236, 13, 'Develop what you lack.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:10:41'),
(237, 13, 'Without continual growth and progress, such words as improvement, achievement, and success have no meaning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:11:01'),
(238, 13, 'All growth depends upon activity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:11:15'),
(239, 13, 'Keep away from people who try to belittle your ambition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:11:31'),
(240, 13, 'Seeds of faith are always within us; sometimes it takes a crisis to nourish and encourage their growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:11:47'),
(241, 13, 'A good marriage is one which allows for change and growth in the individuals and in the way they express their love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:12:33'),
(242, 13, 'Growth has failed on its own terms. You can\'t have infinite growth in a world of finite resources.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:12:52'),
(243, 13, 'If the facts don\'t fit the theory, change the facts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:13:08'),
(244, 13, 'Growth itself contains the germ of happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:13:20'),
(245, 13, 'Growth is a spiral process, doubling back on itself, reassessing and regrouping.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:13:49'),
(246, 13, 'The big will get bigger; the small will get wiped out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:14:26'),
(247, 13, 'Where there is age there is evolution, where there is life there is growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:14:44'),
(248, 13, 'And so all growth that is not towards God Is growing to decay.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:14:58'),
(249, 13, 'If one is constantly challenged, one grows. If one becomes complacent, one stultifies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:15:36'),
(250, 13, 'Growth for the sake of growth is the ideology of the cancer cell.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:17:19'),
(251, 13, 'Don’t join an easy crowd; you won’t grow. Go where the expectations and the demands to perform are high.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:17:58'),
(252, 13, 'True growth is a process which one allows to happen rather than causes to happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:19:03'),
(253, 13, 'Change is inevitable. Growth is optional.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:19:19'),
(254, 13, 'In the end, it is the person you become, not the things you have achieved, that is the most important.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:19:39'),
(255, 13, 'There are no limits to growth and human progress when men and women are free to follow their dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:19:58'),
(256, 13, 'A man\'s growth is seen in the successive choirs of his friends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:20:11'),
(257, 13, 'The minute a man ceases to grow, no matter what his years, that minute he begins to be old.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:21:04'),
(258, 13, 'The greatest thing in this world is not so much where we stand as in what direction we are moving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:22:06'),
(259, 13, 'Thinking is growth; we cannot think without growing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:22:37'),
(260, 13, 'There is only one day left, always starting over: it is given to us at dawn and taken away from us at dusk.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:25:48'),
(261, 13, 'Out of your vulnerabilities will come your strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:27:31'),
(262, 13, 'The body grows slowly and steadily but the soul grows by leaps and bounds. It may come to its full stature in an hour.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:28:47'),
(263, 13, 'Personal growth has its price, and she was paying it without complaint.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:29:18'),
(264, 13, 'Change is not always growth, but growth is often rooted in change. Drizzt Do\'Urden', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:29:32'),
(265, 13, 'Aging is not just decay, you know, its growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:30:31'),
(266, 13, 'The way to real growth is not to become more powerful or more famous, but to become more human and more tolerant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:31:06'),
(267, 13, 'Every beginning is a consequence - every beginning ends some thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:32:12'),
(268, 13, 'The wind of change is blowing through the continent. Whether we like it or not, this growth of national consciousness is a political fact.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:33:07'),
(269, 13, 'A scholar who cherishes the love of comfort is not fit to be deemed a scholar.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:33:38'),
(270, 13, 'Everything is in a process of change, nothing endures; we do not seek permanence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:33:56'),
(271, 13, 'We grow because we struggle, we learn and overcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:34:46'),
(272, 13, 'Everything that happens in life is there to aid our spiritual growth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPersonal Growth', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-15 18:34:58'),
(273, 18, 'Clarity affords focus.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:02:48'),
(274, 18, 'Good leadership consists of showing average people how to do the work of superior people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:03:24'),
(275, 18, 'Excellence is to do a common thing in an uncommon way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:03:39'),
(276, 18, 'It is not the mountain we conquer, but ourselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:04:01'),
(277, 18, 'The goal of an effective leader is to recondition your team to be solution focused rather than problem focused.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:04:26'),
(278, 18, 'The price of excellence is discipline. The cost of mediocrity is disappointment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:04:44'),
(279, 18, 'All that is valuable in human society depends upon the opportunity for development accorded the individual.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:05:03'),
(280, 18, 'The most important single ingredient in the formula of success is knowing how to get along with people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:05:27'),
(281, 18, 'Pull the string, and it will follow wherever you wish. Push it, and it will go nowhere at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:05:41'),
(282, 18, 'The enemy is fear. We think it is hate; but, it is fear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:05:54'),
(283, 18, 'Leadership is based on a spiritual quality; the power to inspire, the power to inspire others to follow', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:06:05'),
(284, 18, 'Your most unhappy customers are your greatest source of learning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:06:18'),
(285, 18, 'Good leaders make people feel that they\'re at the very heart of things, not at the periphery.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:06:28'),
(286, 18, 'Every person has a longing to be significant; to make a contribution; to be a part of something noble and purposeful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:06:38'),
(287, 18, 'There are no office hours for leaders.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:06:49'),
(288, 18, 'Leaders don\'t create followers, they create more leaders.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:07:32'),
(289, 18, 'Leaders think and talk about the solutions. Followers think and talk about the problems.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:07:47'),
(290, 18, 'If your actions inspire others to dream more, learn more, do more and become more, you are a leader.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:08:02'),
(291, 18, 'Leadership is the capacity to translate vision into reality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:08:35'),
(292, 18, 'The growth and development of people is the highest calling of leadership.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:08:50'),
(293, 18, 'Don\'t find fault, find a remedy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:09:15'),
(294, 18, 'The greatest good you can do for another is not just to share your riches but to reveal to him his own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:09:30'),
(295, 18, 'Management is doing things right; leadership is doing the right things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:09:53'),
(296, 18, 'The four Cs of making dreams come true: Curiosity, Courage, Consistency, Confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:10:08'),
(297, 18, 'People may hear your words, but they feel your attitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:10:19'),
(298, 18, 'Courage is what it takes to stand up and speak; courage is also what it takes to sit down and listen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:10:37'),
(299, 18, 'A genuine leader is not a searcher for consensus but a molder of consensus.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:10:59'),
(300, 18, 'If you can\'t swallow your pride, you can\'t lead. Even the highest mountain had animals that step on it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:11:21'),
(301, 18, 'Our greatest glory is not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:11:41'),
(302, 18, 'He who has never learned to obey cannot be a good commander.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:11:53'),
(303, 18, 'It is amazing what you can accomplish if you do not care who gets the credit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:12:03'),
(304, 18, 'Leadership is a way of thinking, a way of acting and, most importantly, a way of communicating.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:12:17'),
(305, 18, 'People ask the difference between a leader and a boss. The leader leads, and the boss drives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:12:30'),
(306, 18, 'When the solution is simple, God is answering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:12:41'),
(307, 18, 'The leader is a teacher who succeeds without taking credit. And, because credit is not taken, credit is received.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:12:52'),
(308, 18, 'Remember the difference between a boss and a leader. A boss says, Go! A leader says, Let\'s go!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:13:06'),
(309, 18, 'Give me six hours to chop down a tree and I will spend the first four sharpening the axe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:13:20'),
(310, 18, 'Leadership is the ability to get extraordinary achievement from ordinary people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:13:35'),
(311, 18, 'Leadership is unlocking people\'s potential to become better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:13:49'),
(312, 18, 'Never tell people how to do things. Tell them what to do and they will surprise you with their ingenuity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:14:13'),
(313, 18, 'The older I get the less I listen to what people say and the more I look at what they do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:14:24'),
(314, 18, 'Leaders must be close enough to relate to others, but far enough ahead to motivate them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:15:04'),
(315, 18, 'You fail all the time, but you aren\'t a failure until you start blaming someone else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:15:22'),
(316, 18, 'Good leaders don\'t tell people what to do, they give teams capability and inspiration.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:15:32'),
(317, 18, 'No person can be a great leader unless he takes genuine joy in the successes of those under him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:15:43'),
(318, 18, 'The only prerequisites to leadership are that you remain positive, calm, and open-minded.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:15:56'),
(319, 18, 'Whoever is careless with the truth in small matters cannot be trusted in important affairs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:16:06'),
(320, 18, 'A leader is a dealer in hope.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:16:15'),
(321, 18, 'A leader is a dealer in hope.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:17:16'),
(322, 18, 'To keep the wrong leader in the wrong place prevents the right leader from being in the right place.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:17:26'),
(323, 18, 'Leadership has a harder job to do than just choose sides. It must bring sides together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:17:39'),
(324, 18, 'He that cannot obey, cannot command.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:17:52'),
(325, 18, 'The key to successful leadership today is influence, not authority.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:18:10'),
(326, 18, 'There is no higher religion than human service. To work for the common good is the greatest creed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:18:23'),
(327, 18, 'Leaders grow; they are not made.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:18:37'),
(328, 18, 'You don\'t lead by hitting people over the head - that\'s assault, not leadership.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:18:50'),
(329, 18, 'The final test of a leader is that he leaves behind him in other men the conviction and the will to carry on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:19:05'),
(330, 18, 'Management is about arranging and telling. Leadership is about nurturing and enhancing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:19:26'),
(331, 18, 'Nobody cares how much you know, until they know how much you care.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:19:51'),
(332, 18, 'It is the responsibility of intellectuals to speak the truth and expose lies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:20:06'),
(333, 18, 'Lead me, follow me, or get out of my way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:20:21');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(334, 18, 'Leadership is the art of giving people a platform for spreading ideas that work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:21:30'),
(335, 18, 'Life is like a ten speed bicycle. Most of us have gears we never use.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:21:44'),
(336, 18, 'Go as far as you can see; when you get there you\'ll be able to see farther.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:21:57'),
(337, 18, 'If you do not look at things on a large scale, it will be difficult to master strategy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:22:20'),
(338, 18, 'Strive not to be a success, but rather to be of value.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:22:37'),
(339, 18, 'Start by doing what\'s necessary; then do what\'s possible; and suddenly you are doing the impossible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:22:49'),
(340, 18, 'Power is like being a lady... if you have to tell people you are, you aren\'t.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:23:02'),
(341, 18, 'You\'re only as good as the people you hire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:23:17'),
(342, 18, 'Education is the mother of leadership.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:23:26'),
(343, 18, 'Leadership cannot really be taught. It can only be learned.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:23:37'),
(344, 18, 'Leadership is the challenge to be something more than average.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:23:48'),
(345, 18, 'To do great things is difficult; but to command great things is more difficult.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:24:01'),
(346, 18, 'Treat people as if they were what they ought to be and you help them to become what they are capable of being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:24:12'),
(347, 18, 'If you care enough for a result, you will most certainly attain it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:24:24'),
(348, 18, 'A man is but the product of his thoughts what he thinks, he becomes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:24:36'),
(349, 18, 'Leaders don’t complain about what’s not working. Leaders celebrate what is working and work to amplify it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:25:03'),
(350, 18, 'Ability may get you to the top, but it takes character to keep you there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:25:13'),
(351, 18, 'The task of leadership is not to put greatness into people, but to elicit it, for the greatness is there already.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:25:26'),
(352, 18, 'You have to think anyway, so why not think big?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:25:44'),
(353, 18, 'When you\'re finished changing, you\'re finished.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:25:55'),
(354, 18, 'To govern was to serve, not to rule.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:26:28'),
(355, 18, 'Example is not the main thing in influencing others. It is the only thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:26:41'),
(356, 18, 'People who enjoy meetings should not be in charge of anything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:26:53'),
(357, 18, 'Force always attracts men of low morality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:27:08'),
(358, 18, 'There is no worse mistake in public leadership than to hold out false hope soon to be swept away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:27:20'),
(359, 18, 'Excellence is not an accomplishment. It is a spirit, a never-ending process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:27:36'),
(360, 18, 'A great leader\'s courage to fulfill his vision comes from passion, not position.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:27:50'),
(361, 18, 'The better you are at surrounding yourself with people of high potential, the greater your chance for success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:28:02'),
(362, 18, 'Leadership is action, not position', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:28:27'),
(363, 18, 'A general is just as good or just as bad as the troops under his command make him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:28:37'),
(364, 18, 'A good plan violently executed now is better than a perfect plan executed next week.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:28:46'),
(365, 18, 'Leadership should be born out of the understanding of the needs of those who would be affected by it', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:29:02'),
(366, 18, 'The manager asks how and when; the leader asks what and why.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:29:15'),
(367, 18, 'To add value to others, one must first value others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:29:27'),
(368, 18, 'Leadership and learning are indispensable to each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:29:36'),
(369, 18, 'To be able to lead others, a man must be willing to go forward alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:29:46'),
(370, 18, 'Nothing so conclusively proves a man\'s ability to lead others as what he does from day to day to lead himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:30:05'),
(371, 18, 'Leadership cannot just go along to get along. Leadership must meet the moral challenge of the day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:30:17'),
(372, 18, 'The very essence of leadership is that you have to have vision. You can\'t blow an uncertain trumpet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:30:30'),
(373, 18, 'No one can make you feel inferior without your consent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:30:42'),
(374, 18, 'People often say that motivation doesn\'t last. Well, neither does bathing - that\'s why we recommend it daily.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:30:54'),
(375, 18, 'Leaders are those who empower others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:31:05'),
(376, 18, 'Consensus is the negation of leadership.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:31:17'),
(377, 18, 'To acquire knowledge, one must study; but to acquire wisdom, one must observe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:06'),
(378, 18, 'Great leaders are not defined by the absence of weakness, but rather by the presence of clear strengths.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:16'),
(379, 18, 'Leaders are people who do the right thing; managers are people who do things right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:28'),
(380, 18, 'Things may come to those who wait, but only the things left by those who hustle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:37'),
(381, 18, 'Become the kind of leader that people would follow voluntarily; even if you had no title or position.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:47'),
(382, 18, 'There\'s only one way to succeed in anything, and that is to give it everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:32:58'),
(383, 18, 'The function of leadership is to produce more leaders, not more followers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:33:19'),
(384, 18, 'People buy into the leader before they buy into the vision.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:33:32'),
(385, 18, 'It is common sense to take a method and try it. If it fails, admit it frankly and try another. But above all, try something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:33:42'),
(386, 18, 'A person who never made a mistake never tried anything new.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:33:52'),
(387, 18, 'Do the right thing. It will gratify some people and astonish the rest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:34:07'),
(388, 18, 'It\'s not the size of the dog in the fight, it\'s the size of the fight in the dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:34:25'),
(389, 18, 'Leadership is the special quality which enables people to stand up and pull the rest of us over the horizon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:34:38'),
(390, 18, 'Innovation distinguishes between a leader and a follower.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:34:48'),
(391, 18, 'If you want to make peace with your enemy, you have to work with your enemy. Then he becomes your partner.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:34:59'),
(392, 18, 'Character matters; leadership descends from character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:35:13'),
(393, 18, 'Great leadership usually starts with a willing heart, a positive attitude, and a desire to make a difference.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:35:23'),
(394, 18, 'Effective leaders are made, not born. They learn from trial and error, and from experience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:35:35'),
(395, 18, 'The greatness of a leader is measured by the achievements of the led. This is the ultimate test of his effectiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:36:13'),
(396, 18, 'The power is detested, and miserable the life, of him who wishes to be feared rather than to be loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:36:53'),
(397, 18, 'Intelligence is the ability to adapt to change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:37:22'),
(398, 18, 'We live in a society obsessed with public opinion. But leadership has never been about popularity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:37:32'),
(399, 18, 'Leadership is found in the action to defeat that which would defeat you… You are made by the struggles you choose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:37:42'),
(400, 18, 'What you allow you encourage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:38:03'),
(401, 18, 'Change from the top down happens at the will and whim of those below.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:38:45'),
(402, 18, 'The art of leadership is saying no, not saying yes. It is very easy to say yes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:38:59'),
(403, 18, 'The most important thing in coaching is communication. It\'s not what you say as much as what they absorb.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:39:10'),
(404, 18, 'And the trouble is, if you don\'t risk anything, you risk even more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:39:22'),
(405, 18, 'The speed of the leader is the speed of the gang.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:39:34'),
(406, 18, 'Difficulties mastered are opportunities won.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:39:56'),
(407, 18, 'When Jesus Christ forgives you of sin, He never brings it back up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:40:08'),
(408, 18, 'When I give a minister an order, I leave it to him to find the means to carry it out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:40:17'),
(409, 18, 'It is better to have a lion at the head of an army of sheep, than a sheep at the head of an army of lions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:40:27'),
(410, 18, 'It is better to have a lion at the head of an army of sheep, than a sheep at the head of an army of lions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:40:51'),
(411, 18, 'It is the nature of man to rise to greatness if greatness is expected of him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:41:01'),
(412, 18, 'It is not fair to ask of others what you are not willing to do yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:41:12'),
(413, 18, 'Leadership consists not in degrees of technique but in traits of character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:41:22'),
(414, 18, 'There is nothing like returning to a place that remains unchanged to find the ways in which you yourself have altered.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:41:37'),
(415, 18, 'The price of greatness is responsibility.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:41:48'),
(416, 18, 'The best form of saying is doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:42:18'),
(417, 18, 'The supreme quality of leadership is integrity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:42:29'),
(418, 18, 'Winners never quit and quitters never win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:42:39'),
(419, 18, 'It\'s important to be innovative when times are prosperous. It\'s essential to be innovative when they are not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:42:58'),
(420, 18, 'To handle yourself, use your head; to handle others, use your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:43:24'),
(421, 18, 'Leaders are more powerful role models when they learn than when they teach.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:43:34'),
(422, 18, 'The task of the leader is to get his people from where they are to where they have not been.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:44:26'),
(423, 18, 'I never wear a watch, because I always know it\'s now - and now is when you should do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:44:46'),
(424, 18, 'The ear of the leader must ring with the voices of the people', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:45:15'),
(425, 18, 'Hold yourself responsible for a higher standard than anybody expects of you. Never excuse yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:45:26'),
(426, 18, 'If you treat staff as your equal, they\'ll roll their sleeves up to get the job done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:45:36'),
(427, 18, 'Few men have virtue to withstand the highest bidder.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:46:01'),
(428, 18, 'The leader has to be practical and a realist, yet must talk the language of the visionary and the idealist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:46:21'),
(429, 18, 'Leadership is getting someone to do what they don\'t want to do but to achieve what they want to achieve.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:47:34'),
(430, 18, 'Nurture your mind with great thoughts, for you will never go any higher than you think.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:47:45'),
(431, 18, 'Vision is the Art of seeing Things invisible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:48:04'),
(432, 18, 'Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:48:14'),
(433, 18, 'To educate a man in mind and not in morals is to educate a menace to society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:49:08'),
(434, 18, 'Logic will get you from A to B. Imagination will take you everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:49:42'),
(435, 18, 'Give whatever you are doing and whoever you are with the gift of your attention.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:49:53'),
(436, 18, 'The only safe ship in a storm is leadership.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:50:04'),
(437, 18, 'The cautious seldom err.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:50:16'),
(438, 18, 'Dream as if you\'ll live forever. Live as if you\'ll die today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:50:30'),
(439, 18, 'You can\'t get much done in life if you only work on the days when you feel good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:50:40'),
(440, 18, 'As we look ahead into the next century, leaders will be those who empower others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:50:54'),
(441, 18, 'If one is lucky, a solitary fantasy can totally transform one million realities.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:51:24'),
(442, 18, 'Never give an order that can\'t be obeyed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:51:38'),
(443, 18, 'No man is good enough to govern another man without the other\'s consent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:51:55'),
(444, 18, 'People will never forget how you made them feel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:52:48'),
(445, 18, 'Love your Enemies, for they tell you your Faults.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:53:03'),
(446, 18, 'Confidence is contagious. So is lack of confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:53:13'),
(447, 18, 'Your true value is determined by how much more you give in value than you take in payment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:53:25'),
(448, 18, 'Leaders do not avoid, repress, or deny conflict, but rather see it as an opportunity', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:53:39'),
(449, 18, 'Never forget that only dead fish swim with the stream.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:54:14'),
(450, 18, 'Leadership does not always wear the harness of compromise.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:54:26'),
(451, 18, 'It is the mark of an educated mind to be able to entertain a thought without accepting it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:54:36'),
(452, 18, 'There is no power on earth that can neutralize the influence of a high, simple and useful life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:54:48'),
(453, 18, 'He who has learned how to obey will know how to command.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:55:02'),
(454, 18, 'A prime function of a leader is to keep hope alive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:55:44'),
(455, 18, 'Our chief want is someone who will inspire us to be what we know we could be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:55:58'),
(456, 18, 'Leadership - leadership is about taking responsibility, not making excuses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:56:17'),
(457, 18, 'Alone we can do so little; together we can do so much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:56:40'),
(458, 18, 'Speak softly and carry a big stick; you will go far.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:56:50'),
(459, 18, 'I am a leader by default, only because nature does not allow a vacuum.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:01'),
(460, 18, 'Good leaders must first become good servants.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:13'),
(461, 18, 'It\'s hard to lead a cavalry charge if you think you look funny on a horse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:28'),
(462, 18, 'To lead people, walk behind them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:39'),
(463, 18, 'Kind words can be short and easy to speak, but their echoes are truly endless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:48'),
(464, 18, 'Imagination is more important than knowledge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:57:58'),
(465, 18, 'A leader must have the courage to act against an expert\'s advice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:58:08'),
(466, 18, 'When angry count to ten before you speak. If very angry, count to one hundred.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:58:17'),
(467, 18, 'Learning is not compulsory; it\'s voluntary... But to survive, we must learn.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:59:06'),
(468, 18, 'In this world a man must either be anvil or hammer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:59:20'),
(469, 18, 'Authority without wisdom is like a heavy ax without an edge -- fitter to bruise than polish.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:59:32'),
(470, 18, 'It is impossible to imagine anything which better becomes a ruler than mercy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:59:44'),
(471, 18, 'Successful people willingly do what unsuccessful people are unwilling to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 15:59:57'),
(472, 18, 'Leadership is the key to 99 percent of all successful efforts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAALeadership', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-17 16:00:07'),
(473, 28, 'Success is not the key to happiness. Happiness is the key to success. If you love what you are doing, you will be successful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:58:20'),
(474, 28, 'There are no secrets to success. It is the result of preparation, hard work, and learning from failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:58:31'),
(475, 28, 'Doing the best at this moment puts you in the best place for the next moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:58:41'),
(476, 28, 'Everything you\'ve ever wanted is on the other side of fear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:58:51'),
(477, 28, 'People don\'t have to believe in you for you to succeed. Just work hard, when you succeed, they will believe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:59:01'),
(478, 28, 'Success is a state of mind. If you want success, start thinking of yourself as a success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:59:10'),
(479, 28, 'When obstacles arise, you change your direction to reach your goal; you do not change your decision to get there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:59:19'),
(480, 28, 'I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can\'t accept not trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:59:34'),
(481, 28, 'Coming together is a beginning; keeping together is progress; working together is success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 14:59:50'),
(482, 28, 'I don\'t measure a man\'s success by how high he climbs but how high he bounces when he hits bottom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:00'),
(483, 28, 'Beginners are many; finishers are few.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:09'),
(484, 28, 'The greatest danger for most of us is not that our aim is too high and we miss it, but that it is too low and we reach it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:24'),
(485, 28, 'Remember, success is a journey not a destination. Have faith in your ability. You will do just fine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:32'),
(486, 28, 'Action is the foundational key to all success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:43'),
(487, 28, 'Your attitude, not your aptitude, will determine your altitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:00:55'),
(488, 28, 'If you can imagine it, you can achieve it. If you can dream it, you can become it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:01:07'),
(489, 28, 'A person who never made a mistake never tried anything new.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:01:20'),
(490, 28, 'If you really want to do something, you\'ll find a way. If you don\'t, you\'ll find an excuse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:01:29'),
(491, 28, 'The man who starts out simply with the idea of getting rich won\'t succeed, you must have a larger ambition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:01:38'),
(492, 28, 'Success is where preparation and opportunity meet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:01:59'),
(493, 28, 'A failure is like fertilizer; it stinks to be sure, but it makes things grow faster in the future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:02:09'),
(494, 28, 'Never was anything great achieved without danger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:02:19'),
(495, 28, 'Your life does not get better by chance, it gets better by change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:02:30'),
(496, 28, 'Your goal should be out of reach but not out of sight.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:02:42'),
(497, 28, 'The secret of achievement is to hold a picture of a successful outcome in mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:02:51'),
(498, 28, 'A lot of people notice when you succeed, but they don\'t see what it takes to get there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:01'),
(499, 28, 'Six essential qualities that are the key to success: Sincerity, personal integrity, humility, courtesy, wisdom, charity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:12'),
(500, 28, 'Things turn out best for the people who make the best of the way things turn out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:22'),
(501, 28, 'One important key to success is self-confidence. An important key to self-confidence is preparation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:33'),
(502, 28, 'If you want to succeed you should strike out on new paths, rather than travel the worn paths of accepted success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:43'),
(503, 28, 'The only thing that separates successful people from the ones who aren\'t is the willingness to work very, very hard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:03:53'),
(504, 28, 'Do what you have to do, to do what you want to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:03'),
(505, 28, 'Two roads diverged in a wood and I - I took the one less traveled by, and that has made all the difference.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:15'),
(506, 28, 'Never give up on something that you can\'t go a day without thinking about.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:25'),
(507, 28, 'The trees that are slow to grow bear the best fruit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:36'),
(508, 28, 'People rarely succeed unless they have fun in what they are doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:47'),
(509, 28, 'Most people who succeed in the face of seemingly impossible conditions are people who simply don\'t know how to quit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:04:59'),
(510, 28, 'A successful man is one who makes more money than his wife can spend. A successful woman is one who can find such a man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:05:19'),
(511, 28, 'Failure will never overtake me if my determination to succeed is strong enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:05:31'),
(512, 28, 'Victory belongs to the most persevering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:06:29'),
(513, 28, 'The indispensable first step to getting the things you want out of life is this: decide what you want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:06:43'),
(514, 28, 'Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day-in and day-out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:06:56'),
(515, 28, 'It is literally true that you can succeed best and quickest by helping others to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:07:10'),
(516, 28, 'It\'s not whether you get knocked down, it\'s whether you get up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:07:22'),
(517, 28, 'Self-belief and hard work will always earn you success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:07:33'),
(518, 28, 'Never mind what others do; do better than yourself, beat your own record from day to day, and you are a success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:07:49'),
(519, 28, 'If opportunity doesn\'t knock, build a door.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:07:59'),
(520, 28, 'Successful and unsuccessful people do not vary greatly in their abilities. They vary in their desires to reach their potential.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:09'),
(521, 28, 'The ladder of success is never crowded at the top.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:19'),
(522, 28, 'FOCUS - Follow One Course Until Successful', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:29'),
(523, 28, 'Sometimes life hits you in the head with a brick. Don\'t lose faith.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:39'),
(524, 28, 'Four things for success: work and pray, think and believe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:48'),
(525, 28, 'Most of the successful people I\'ve known are the ones who do more listening than talking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:08:59'),
(526, 28, 'Impossible is just an opinion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:09:08'),
(527, 28, 'The function of leadership is to produce more leaders, not more followers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:09:17'),
(528, 28, 'Successful people are simply those with successful habits.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:09:30'),
(529, 28, 'Success demands singleness of purpose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:09:38'),
(530, 28, 'One of the most important principles of success is developing the habit of going the extra mile.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:09:54'),
(531, 28, 'Successful people ask better questions, and as a result, they get better answers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:10:14'),
(532, 28, 'One of the rewards of success is freedom. the ability to do whatever you like.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:10:23'),
(533, 28, 'Success does not consist in never making mistakes but in never making the same one a second time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:10:33'),
(534, 28, 'He who is not courageous enough to take risks will accomplish nothing in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:10:42'),
(535, 28, 'One secret of success in life is for a man to be ready for his opportunity when it comes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:10:51'),
(536, 28, 'The secret of success is making your vocation your vacation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:11:00'),
(537, 28, 'Don’t read success stories, you will only get a message. Read failure stories, you will get some ideas to get success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:11:09'),
(538, 28, 'Success is the progressive realization of a worthy goal or ideal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:11:18'),
(539, 28, 'Men are born to succeed, not to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:11:29'),
(540, 28, 'I attribute my success to this - I never gave or took any excuse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:11:41'),
(541, 28, 'I feel that luck is preparation meeting opportunity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:12:03'),
(542, 28, 'Most great people have attained their greatest success just one step beyond their greatest failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:12:13'),
(543, 28, 'Identify your problems but give your power and energy to solutions', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:12:29'),
(544, 28, 'That some achieve great success, is proof to all that others can achieve it as well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:12:39'),
(545, 28, 'Our greatest glory is not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:12:52'),
(546, 28, 'The secret of success is constancy to purpose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:13:03'),
(547, 28, 'Patience, persistence and perspiration make an unbeatable combination for success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:13:12'),
(548, 28, 'The price of greatness is responsibility.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:13:22'),
(549, 28, 'All problems become smaller if you don\'t dodge them but confront them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:13:32'),
(550, 28, ' Success is the good fortune that comes from aspiration, desperation, perspiration,and inspiration.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:09'),
(551, 28, 'The guy who takes a chance, who walks the line between the known and unknown, who is unafraid of failure, will succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:19'),
(552, 28, 'Success follows doing what you want to do. There is no other way to be successful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:30'),
(553, 28, 'The road to success is always under construction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:40'),
(554, 28, 'Failure is the key to success; each mistake teaches us something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:49'),
(555, 28, 'Ability may get you to the top, but it takes character to keep you there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:14:58'),
(556, 28, 'If you fall behind, run faster. Never give up, never surrender, and rise up against the odds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:08'),
(557, 28, 'If you\'re going to be thinking anyway, think big!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:17'),
(558, 28, 'Self-trust is the first secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:27'),
(559, 28, 'Failure is success in progress', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:36'),
(560, 28, 'In order to succeed, we must first believe that we can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:46'),
(561, 28, 'Without self-discipline, success is impossible, period.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:15:58'),
(562, 28, 'Develop success from failures. Discouragement and failure are two of the surest stepping stones to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:09'),
(563, 28, 'People begin to become successful the minute they decide to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:20'),
(564, 28, 'Talent is a gift, but you can only succeed with hard work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:30'),
(565, 28, 'Men who try to do something and fail are infinitely better than those who try to do nothing and succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:39'),
(566, 28, 'The successful man will profit from his mistakes and try again in a different way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:49'),
(567, 28, 'Success is more permanent when you achieve it without destroying your principles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:16:58'),
(568, 28, 'The real secret of success is enthusiasm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:17:07'),
(569, 28, 'Any day that we don\'t give up puts us one day closer to success!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:17:16'),
(570, 28, 'Don\'t flaunt your success, but don\'t apologize for it either.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:17:25'),
(571, 28, 'Work hard at your job and you can make a living. Work hard on yourself and you can make a fortune.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:17:34'),
(572, 28, 'Good, Better, Best. Never let it rest. Until your Good is Better, and your Better is your Best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:17:43'),
(573, 28, 'Success is falling nine times and getting up ten.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:18:02'),
(574, 28, 'If you don\'t build your dream, someone else will hire you to help them build theirs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:19:26'),
(575, 28, 'If you want to succeed, you must make your own opportunities as you go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:19:59'),
(576, 28, 'No man can succeed in a line of endeavor which he does not like.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:20:09'),
(577, 28, 'A successful man is one who can lay a firm foundation with the bricks others have thrown at him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:20:20'),
(578, 28, 'Some succeed because they are destined to, but most succeed because they are determined to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:20:32'),
(579, 28, 'The starting point of all achievement is desire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:20:43'),
(580, 28, 'We can\'t be in survival mode. We have to be in growth mode.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:20:52'),
(581, 28, 'Poor people have big TV\'s. Rich people have big libraries.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:21:10'),
(582, 28, 'Winners never quit and quitters never win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:21:21'),
(583, 28, 'If you don\'t care about what people think, you already passed the first step of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:21:30'),
(584, 28, 'If you are not willing to risk the unusual, you will have to settle for the ordinary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:21:38'),
(585, 28, 'To succeed, you need to find something to hold on to, something to motivate you, something to inspire you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:21:48'),
(586, 28, 'Don\'t wait for your ship to come in, swim out and meet the bloody thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:22:01'),
(587, 28, 'Defeat is a state of mind; no one is ever defeated until defeat has been accepted as a reality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:22:13'),
(588, 28, 'Belief in oneself is one of the most important bricks in building any successful venture.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:22:23'),
(589, 28, 'Believe you can and you\'re halfway there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:22:35'),
(590, 28, 'Every day I get up and look through the Forbes list of the richest people in America. If I\'m not there, I go to work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:22:47'),
(591, 28, 'If you want to conquer fear, don\'t sit home and think about it. Go out and get busy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:23:14'),
(592, 28, 'The person interested in success has to learn to view failure as a healthy, inevitable part of the process of getting to the top.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:23:25'),
(593, 28, 'Just because you made a mistake doesn\'t mean you are a mistake.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:23:34'),
(594, 28, 'Be ready when opportunity comes...Luck is the time when preparation and opportunity meet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:23:47'),
(595, 28, 'You have to learn the rules of the game. And then you have to play better than anyone else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:23:56'),
(596, 28, 'To succeed in life, you need two things: ignorance and confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:24:07'),
(597, 28, 'We are all self-made, but only the successful will admit it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:24:35'),
(598, 28, 'Always bear in mind that your own resolution to succeed is more important than any other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:24:48'),
(599, 28, 'For true success ask yourself these four questions: Why? Why not? Why not me? Why not now?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:24:58'),
(600, 28, 'Victory is sweetest when you\'ve known defeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:25:08'),
(601, 28, 'Courage is resistance to fear, mastery of fear, not absence of fear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:25:26'),
(602, 28, 'The path to success is to take massive, determined action.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:25:35'),
(603, 28, 'There are no speed limits on the road to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:26:01'),
(604, 28, 'A good head and a good heart are always a formidable combination.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:26:18'),
(605, 28, 'You must either modify your dreams or magnify your skills', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:26:29'),
(606, 28, 'Things may come to those who wait, but only the things left by those who hustle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:26:39'),
(607, 28, 'Success doesn\'t come to you, you go to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:26:51'),
(608, 28, 'Success is never so interesting as struggle', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:01'),
(609, 28, 'Let no feeling of discouragement prey upon you, and in the end you are sure to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:10'),
(610, 28, 'All great achievements have one thing in common - people with a passion to succeed', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:18'),
(611, 28, 'Success is not built on success. It\'s built on failure. It\'s built on frustration. Sometimes its built on catastrophe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:31'),
(612, 28, 'If at first you don\'t succeed, try, try, try again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:44');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(613, 28, 'Capital isn\'t scarce; vision is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:27:53'),
(614, 28, 'The middle of every successful project looks like a disaster.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:28:02'),
(615, 28, 'A failure isn\'t a failure if it prepares you for success tomorrow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:28:12'),
(616, 28, 'If you try and lose then it isn\'t your fault. But if you don\'t try and we lose, then it\'s all your fault.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:28:22'),
(617, 28, 'To accomplish great things, we must not only act, but also dream; not only plan, but also believe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:28:30'),
(618, 28, 'Not every successful man is a good father. But every good father is a successful man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:28:42'),
(619, 28, 'People can do whatever they want if they just set their heart to it, and just never give up, and just go out there and do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:29:07'),
(620, 28, 'Success is achieved by developing our strengths, not by eliminating our weaknesses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:29:17'),
(621, 28, 'People often say that motivation doesn\'t last. Well, neither does bathing - that\'s why we recommend it daily.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:29:26'),
(622, 28, 'There is no success without hardship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:29:37'),
(623, 28, 'A hero is an ordinary individual who finds the strength to persevere and endure in spite of overwhelming obstacles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:30:17'),
(624, 28, 'Success is a lousy teacher. It seduces smart people into thinking they can\'t lose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:30:27'),
(625, 28, 'Success is liking yourself, liking what you do, and liking how you do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:30:43'),
(626, 28, 'If A is a success in life, then A equals x plus y plus z. Work is x; y is play; and z is keeping your mouth shut', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:30:51'),
(627, 28, 'Talent is cheaper than table salt. What separates the talented individual from the successful one is a lot of hard work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:31:03'),
(628, 28, 'What comes out of you when you are squeezed is what is inside of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:34:23'),
(629, 28, 'Dreams come true; without that possibility, nature would not incite us to have them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:34:33'),
(630, 28, 'I honestly think it is better to be a failure at something you love than to be a success at something you hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:34:45'),
(631, 28, 'You don\'t pay the price for success, you enjoy the benefits of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:34:57'),
(632, 28, 'Help others achieve their dreams and you will achieve yours.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:35:07'),
(633, 28, 'To climb steep hills requires a slow pace at first.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:35:24'),
(634, 28, 'The best way out is always through.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:35:47'),
(635, 28, 'To be successful in life what you need is education, not literacy and degrees.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:35:56'),
(636, 28, 'Your present circumstances don\'t determine where you can go; they merely determine where you start.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:36:06'),
(637, 28, 'If you wish to be a success in the world, promise everything, deliver nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:36:20'),
(638, 28, 'Success is focusing the full power of all you are on what you have a burning desire to achieve.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:36:34'),
(639, 28, 'There is little success where there is little laughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:36:47'),
(640, 28, 'Obstacles are those frightful things you see when you take your eyes off your goal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:37:00'),
(641, 28, 'Success is not to be pursued; it is to be attracted by the person you become.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:37:16'),
(642, 28, 'If you try to do too much, you will not achieve anything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:37:28'),
(643, 28, 'Success is often the result of taking a misstep in the right direction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:37:38'),
(644, 28, 'One sound idea is all that you need to achieve success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:37:49'),
(645, 28, 'Nobody who ever gave his best regretted it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:38:00'),
(646, 28, 'Whatever you can do, or dream you can, begin it. Boldness has genius, power and magic in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:38:15'),
(647, 28, 'Success is the progressive realization of predetermined, worthwhile, personal goals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:38:53'),
(648, 28, 'When it is obvious that the goals cannot be reached, don\'t adjust the goals, adjust the action steps.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:04'),
(649, 28, 'Without an open-minded mind, you can never be a great success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:15'),
(650, 28, 'Any coward can fight a battle when he\'s sure of winning; but give me the man who has the pluck to fight when he\'s sure of losing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:27'),
(651, 28, 'The secret to success: find out where people are going and get there first', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:37'),
(652, 28, 'Do what you can, with what you have, where you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:47'),
(653, 28, 'Success is often achieved by those who don\'t know that failure is inevitable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:39:57'),
(654, 28, 'I think you can accomplish anything if you\'re willing to pay the price.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:40:08'),
(655, 28, 'The more you lose yourself in something bigger than yourself, the more energy you will have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:40:21'),
(656, 28, 'The quality of your work, in the long run, is the deciding factor on how much your services are valued by the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:40:30'),
(657, 28, 'The secret of success is… to be fully awake to everything about you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:40:39'),
(658, 28, 'Failure is success if we learn from it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:41:09'),
(659, 28, 'Nobody talks of entrepreneurship as survival, but that\'s exactly what it is and what nurtures creative thinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:41:20'),
(660, 28, 'It is better to know some of the questions than all of the answers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:41:39'),
(661, 28, 'Most people fail in life because they major in minor things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:41:58'),
(662, 28, 'Success usually comes to those who are too busy to be looking for it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:42:08'),
(663, 28, 'It is no use saying, \'We are doing our best.\' You have got to succeed in doing what is necessary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:42:19'),
(664, 28, 'It is hard to fail, but it is worse never to have tried to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:42:29'),
(665, 28, 'There is no point at which you can say, \"Well, I\'m successful now. I might as well take a nap.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:42:42'),
(666, 28, 'We are what we repeatedly do. Excellence, then, is not an act, but a habit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:42:57'),
(667, 28, 'A weak man has doubts before a decision; a strong man has them afterwards.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:43:07'),
(668, 28, 'You will find the key to success under the alarm clock.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:43:19'),
(669, 28, 'If you do not know where you are going, every road will get you nowhere', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:43:29'),
(670, 28, 'The only limit to our realization of tomorrow will be our doubts of today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:43:40'),
(671, 28, 'If everyone is moving forward together, then success takes care of itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:43:53'),
(672, 28, 'Remember: Rewards come in action, not in discussion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:44:05'),
(673, 28, 'Every setback means you\'re one step closer to seeing the dream come to pass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:44:15'),
(674, 28, 'You may have a fresh start any moment you choose, for this thing that we call \'failure\' is not the falling down, but the staying down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:44:27'),
(675, 28, 'No one can make you feel inferior without your consent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:44:43'),
(676, 28, 'It is difficult to say what is impossible, for the dream of yesterday is the hope of today and the reality of tomorrow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:44:53'),
(677, 28, 'I think I have learned that the best way to lift one\'s self up is to help someone else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:45:02'),
(678, 28, 'If you aren\'t making any mistakes, it\'s a sure sign you\'re playing it too safe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:45:12'),
(679, 32, 'Being a mother means that your heart is no longer yours; it wanders wherever your children do', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:48:55'),
(680, 32, 'A mother is she who can take the place of all others but whose place no one else can take.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:49:10'),
(681, 32, 'God could not be everywhere, and therefore he made mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:49:20'),
(682, 32, 'It doesn\'t matter how old you are, or what you do in your life, you never stop needing your mom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:49:35'),
(683, 32, 'The most important thing a father can do for his children is to love their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:49:48'),
(684, 32, 'No language can express the power and beauty and heroism of a mother\'s love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:49:57'),
(685, 32, 'My mother had a great deal of trouble with me, but I think she enjoyed it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:50:07'),
(686, 32, 'What is a mom but the sunshine of our days and the north star of our nights.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:50:18'),
(687, 32, 'To describe my mother would be to write about a hurricane in its perfect power. Or the climbing, falling colors of a rainbow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:50:33'),
(688, 32, 'Every mother is like Moses. She does not enter the promised land. She prepares a world she will not see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:51:45'),
(689, 32, 'All that I am my mother made me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:51:56'),
(690, 32, 'We are born of love. Love is our mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:52:06'),
(691, 32, 'My mother made a brilliant impression upon my childhood life. She shone for me like the evening star.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:52:19'),
(692, 32, 'No man is poor who has a Godly mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:52:29'),
(693, 32, 'Each day of our lives we make deposits in the memory banks of our children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:52:41'),
(694, 32, 'A mother is the truest friend we have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:02'),
(695, 32, 'All that I am, or hope to be, I owe to my angel mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:13'),
(696, 32, 'Successful Mothers are not the ones that have never struggled. They are the ones that never give up, despite the struggles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:23'),
(697, 32, 'Youth fades, love droops, the leaves of friendship fall; A mother\'s secret hope outlives them all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:33'),
(698, 32, 'Mother is a verb, not a noun.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:44'),
(699, 32, 'It is not until you become a mother that your judgment slowly turns to compassion and understanding.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:53:57'),
(700, 32, 'No man succeeds without a good woman behind him. Wife or mother, if it is both, he is twice blessed indeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:54:06'),
(701, 32, 'Motherhood: All love begins and ends there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:54:15'),
(702, 32, 'The memory of my mother will always be a blessing to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:54:27'),
(703, 32, 'My mother was the making of me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:54:40'),
(704, 32, 'A mother\'s arms are made of tenderness and children sleep soundly in them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:54:51'),
(705, 32, 'Only God Himself fully appreciates the influence of a Christian mother in the molding of character in her children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:05'),
(706, 32, 'The moment a child is born, the mother is also born.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:14'),
(707, 32, 'Mothers have as powerful an influence over the welfare of future generations as all other earthly causes combined.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:24'),
(708, 32, 'Be the living expression of God\'s kindness; kindness in your face, kindness in your eyes, kindness in your smile.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:34'),
(709, 32, 'In search of my mother\'s garden, I found my own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:45'),
(710, 32, 'If you judge people, you have no time to love them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:55:55'),
(711, 32, 'I remember my mother\'s prayers and they have always followed me. They have clung to me all my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:56:03'),
(712, 32, 'If you have a mom, there is nowhere you are likely to go where a prayer has not already been.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:56:31'),
(713, 32, 'Mother\'s love is peace. It need not be acquired, it need not be deserved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:56:44'),
(714, 32, 'Mother\'s love is peace. It need not be acquired, it need not be deserved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:56:53'),
(715, 32, 'If evolution really works, how come mothers only have two hands?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:57:06'),
(716, 32, 'Whatever our religion, we know that if we really want to love, we must first learn to forgive before anything else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:57:20'),
(717, 32, 'Only mothers can think of the future - because they give birth to it in their children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:57:29'),
(718, 32, 'Before you speak, it is necessary for you to listen, for God speaks in the silence of the heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:57:41'),
(719, 32, 'The mother\'s heart is the child\'s schoolroom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:57:52'),
(720, 32, 'An ounce of mother is worth a pound of clergy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:02'),
(721, 32, 'Whatever else is unsure in this stinking dunghill of a world a mother\'s love is not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:11'),
(722, 32, 'Mothers are the most instinctive philosophers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:20'),
(723, 32, 'Joy is a net of love by which you can catch souls.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:32'),
(724, 32, 'Mama exhorted her children at every opportunity to \'jump at the sun.\' We might not land on the sun, but at least we would get off the ground.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:47'),
(725, 32, 'Mom - the person most likely to write an autobiography and never mention herself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:58:58'),
(726, 32, 'Mother is the name for God in the lips and hearts of little children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:59:09'),
(727, 32, 'Of all the rights of women, the greatest is to be a mother', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:59:43'),
(728, 32, 'Men are what their mothers made them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 15:59:52'),
(729, 32, 'There is no way to be a perfect mother, and a million ways to be a good one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:00'),
(730, 32, 'Mothers are all slightly insane.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:10'),
(731, 32, 'I am sure that if the mothers of various nations could meet, there would be no more wars.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:22'),
(732, 32, 'My mother... she is beautiful, softened at the edges and tempered with a spine of steel. I want to grow old and be like her.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:33'),
(733, 32, 'Happy is the son whose faith in his mother remains unchallenged.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:43'),
(734, 32, 'If you\'ve never been hated by your child, you\'ve never been a parent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:00:53'),
(735, 32, 'Being a mom has made me so tired. And so happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:03'),
(736, 32, 'That best academy, a mother\'s knee.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:13'),
(737, 32, 'Biology is the least of what makes someone a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:24'),
(738, 32, 'Sometimes the strength of motherhood is greater than natural laws.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:34'),
(739, 32, 'The kind of power mothers have is enormous.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:48'),
(740, 32, 'A mother\'s love for her child is like nothing else in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:01:59'),
(741, 32, 'God pardons like a mother, who kisses the offense into everlasting forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:02:17'),
(742, 32, 'That strong mother doesn\'t tell her cub, Son, stay weak so the wolves can get you. She says, Toughen up, this is reality we are living in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:02:29'),
(743, 32, 'You were my home, Mother. I had no home but you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:02:39'),
(744, 32, 'A mother\'s happiness is like a beacon, lighting up the future but reflected also on the past in the guise of fond memories.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:03:06'),
(745, 32, 'The tie which links mother and child is of such pure and immaculate strength as to be never violated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:03:31'),
(746, 32, 'The tie which links mother and child is of such pure and immaculate strength as to be never violated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:04:16'),
(747, 32, 'MOTHER (a word that means the world to me)', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:04:23'),
(748, 32, 'A mother never realizes that her children are no longer children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:04:36'),
(749, 32, 'If we pray, we will believe; If we believe, we will love; If we love, we will serve.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:04:47'),
(750, 32, 'Mother\'s love grows by giving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:02'),
(751, 32, 'Our mothers always remain the strangest, craziest people we\'ve ever met.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:14'),
(752, 32, 'Peace begins with a smile.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:23'),
(753, 32, 'Mothers all want their sons to grow up to be president, but they don\'t want them to become politicians in the process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:36'),
(754, 32, 'No matter how old a mother is, she watches her middle-aged children for signs of improvement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:46'),
(755, 32, 'The babe at first feeds upon the mother\'s bosom, but it is always on her heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:05:57'),
(756, 32, 'I was so ugly my mother used to feed me with a sling shot', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:06:16'),
(757, 32, 'Setting a good example for your children takes all the fun out of middle age.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:06:36'),
(758, 32, 'The best place to cry is on a mother\'s arms.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:06:45'),
(759, 32, 'With what price we pay for the glory of motherhood.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:07:05'),
(760, 32, 'A good mother is worth hundreds of schoolmasters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:07:19'),
(761, 32, 'Insanity is hereditary; you get it from your children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:07:32'),
(762, 32, 'The hand that rocks the cradle is the hand that rules the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:07:46'),
(763, 32, 'My mother played piano so we always had music around the house', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:08:00'),
(764, 32, 'A mother is the truest friend we have when trials, heavy and sudden, fall upon us; when adversity takes the place of prosperity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:08:18'),
(765, 32, 'He is a poor son whose sonship does not make him desire to serve all men\'s mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:08:32'),
(766, 32, 'My mother loved children - she would have given anything if I had been one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:08:42'),
(767, 32, 'Motherhood is priced Of God, at price no man may dare To lessen or misunderstand.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:09:14'),
(768, 32, 'A father may turn his back on his child, … . but a mother\'s love endures through all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:09:25'),
(769, 32, 'His mother should have thrown him away and kept the stork.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:09:36'),
(770, 32, 'Whenever I\'m with my mother, I feel as though I have to spend the whole time avoiding land mines.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:09:47'),
(771, 32, 'Do not wait for leaders; do it alone, person to person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:10:01'),
(772, 32, 'The only love that I really believe in is a mother’s love for her children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:10:15'),
(773, 32, 'There was never a great man who had not a great mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:10:27'),
(774, 32, 'The greatest destroyer of peace is abortion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:10:41'),
(775, 32, 'Be faithful in small things because it is in them that your strength lies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:10:51'),
(776, 32, 'Mothers are the people who love us for no good reason, and those of us who are mothers know it\'s the most exquisite love of all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:11:04'),
(777, 32, 'Mothers are fonder than fathers of their children because they are more certain they are their own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:11:31'),
(778, 32, 'The heart of a mother is a deep abyss at the bottom of which you will always find forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:11:40'),
(779, 32, 'A mother has to think twice, once for herself and once for her child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:11:51'),
(780, 32, 'All women become like their mothers. That is their tragedy. No man does. That\'s his.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:00'),
(781, 32, 'Richer than I you can never be, I had a mother who read to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:08'),
(782, 32, 'There are few things more powerful than the faithful prayers of a righteous mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:24'),
(783, 32, 'I cannot forget my mother, She is my bridge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:36'),
(784, 32, 'The precursor of the mirror is the mother\'s face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:46'),
(785, 32, 'A mother takes twenty years to make a man of her boy, and another woman makes a fool of him in twenty minutes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:12:56'),
(786, 32, 'There is nothing in the world of art like the songs mother used to sing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:13:05'),
(787, 32, 'Blaming mother is just a negative way of clinging to her still.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:13:16'),
(788, 32, 'What a mother sings to the cradle goes all the way down to the coffin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:13:25'),
(789, 32, 'A mother is a mother still, The holiest thing alive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:13:35'),
(790, 32, 'Every time you smile at someone, it is an action of love, a gift to that person, a beautiful thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:13:48'),
(791, 32, 'God doesn\'t require us to succeed, he only requires that you try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:14:00'),
(792, 32, 'A mighty power and stronger Man from his throne has hurled,For the hand that rocks the cradle Is the hand that rules the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:14:10'),
(793, 32, 'For mother\'s sake the child was dear, and dearer was the mother for the child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:14:21'),
(794, 32, 'The earth is the mother of all people, and all people should have equal rights upon it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:03'),
(795, 32, 'He didn\'t realize that love as powerful as your mother\'s for you leaves its own mark.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:13'),
(796, 32, 'My mother is a walking miracle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:22'),
(797, 32, 'It is only in the act of nursing that a woman realizes her motherhood in visible and tangible fashion; it is a joy of every moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:34'),
(798, 32, 'My mother taught me about the power of inspiration and courage, and she did it with a strength and a passion that I wish could be bottled.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:46'),
(799, 32, 'If I were dammed of body and soul, I know whose prayers would make me whole, mother o\' mine o mother o\' mine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:15:55'),
(800, 32, 'I got to grow up with a mother who taught me to believe in me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:06'),
(801, 32, 'There\'s a lot more to being a woman than being a mother, but there\'s a hell of a lot more to being a mother than most people suspect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:17'),
(802, 32, 'Spread love everywhere you go. Let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:27'),
(803, 32, 'She never quite leaves her children at home, even when she doesn\'t take them along.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:38'),
(804, 32, 'Life began with waking up and loving my mother\'s face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:47'),
(805, 32, 'The lullaby is the spell whereby the mother attempts to transform herself back from an ogre to a saint.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:16:56'),
(806, 32, 'A suburban mother\'s role is to deliver children obstetrically once, and by car forever after.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:17:06'),
(807, 32, 'Kind words can be short and easy to speak, but their echoes are truly endless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:17:14'),
(808, 32, 'Yesterday is gone. Tomorrow has not yet come. We have only today. Let us begin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:17:29'),
(809, 32, 'A mother\'s arms are more comforting than anyone else\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:17:39'),
(810, 32, 'Life is a song, sing it. Life is a struggle, accept it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:01'),
(811, 32, 'My job as the mother of daughters is to make sure my children see that every opportunity is available to them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:11'),
(812, 32, 'A mother who is really a mother is never free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:21'),
(813, 32, 'Never marry a man who hates his mother because he\'ll end up hating you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:31'),
(814, 32, 'It kills you to see them grow up. But I guess it would kill you quicker if they didn\'t.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:43'),
(815, 32, 'The only mothers it is safe to forget on Mother\'s Day are the good ones.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:18:56'),
(816, 32, 'I want my children to have all the things I couldn\'t afford. Then I want to move in with them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:19:06'),
(817, 32, 'Any mother could perform the jobs of several air-traffic controllers with ease.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:19:19'),
(818, 32, 'Don\'t worry that children never listen to you; worry that they are always watching you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:19:32'),
(819, 32, 'If we have no peace, it is because we have forgotten that we belong to each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:19:43'),
(820, 32, 'I was always at peace because of the way my mom treated me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:19:52'),
(821, 32, 'I was always at peace because of the way my mom treated me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:20:19'),
(822, 32, 'If you can dream it, you can do it. Always remember that this whole thing was started with a dream and a mouse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:20:34'),
(823, 32, 'If nature had arranged that husbands and wives should have children alternatively, there would never be more than three in a family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:21:13'),
(824, 32, 'Children are the anchors of a mother\'s life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:21:23'),
(825, 32, 'God intended motherhood to be a relay race. Each generation would pass the baton on to the next.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:21:43'),
(826, 32, 'Life is a game, play it... Life is too precious, do not destroy it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:21:52'),
(827, 32, 'My mother said I must always be intolerant of ignorance but understanding of illiteracy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:22:13'),
(828, 32, 'No influence is so powerful as that of the mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:22:24'),
(829, 32, 'I really learned it all from mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:22:35'),
(830, 32, 'The love of a mother is the veil of a softer light between the heart and the heavenly Father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:22:47'),
(831, 32, 'Every man must define his identity against his mother. If he does not, he just falls back into her and is swallowed up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:22:57'),
(832, 32, 'Time is the only comforter for the loss of a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:23:18'),
(833, 32, 'How beautifully everything is arranged by Nature; as soon as a child enters the world, it finds a mother ready to take care of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:23:32'),
(834, 32, 'Where there is a mother in the home, matters go well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:23:58'),
(835, 32, 'Everything my mother and father did was designed to put me where I am.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:28:08'),
(836, 32, 'My mother never breast fed me, she told me she only liked me as a friend.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:28:21'),
(837, 32, 'There was never a child so lovely but his mother was glad to get him to sleep.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:28:34'),
(838, 32, 'Neurotics build castles in the air, psychotics live in them. My mother cleans them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:28:51'),
(839, 32, 'Motherhood is the strangest thing, it can be like being one\'s own Trojan horse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:29:05'),
(840, 32, 'We are all pencils in the hand of God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:29:17'),
(841, 32, 'Of course mothers and daughters with strong personalities might see the world from very different points of view.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:29:28'),
(842, 32, 'My mother used to say, \'He who angers you, conquers you!\' But my mother was a saint.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:29:40'),
(843, 32, 'Women who miscalculate are called mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:29:50'),
(844, 32, 'It is a poverty to decide that a child must die so that you may live as you wish.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:30:02'),
(845, 32, 'My mother was the source from which I derived the guiding principles of my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:30:51'),
(846, 32, 'Most mothers are instinctive philosophers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:31:01'),
(847, 32, 'We have to be women we want our daughters to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:31:10'),
(848, 32, 'I guess I was a mom so late in life, my daughter was the greatest thing since sliced bread.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:31:56'),
(849, 32, 'Marriage is the mother of the world. It preserves kingdoms, and fills cities and churches, and heaven itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:32:07'),
(850, 32, 'Instruct the mothers of the French people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:32:18'),
(851, 32, 'I learned more about Christianity from my mother than from all the theologians in England.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:32:37'),
(852, 32, 'Poverty, the mother of manhood. Also, the mother of prostitution. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:33:26'),
(853, 32, 'My mother enjoyed few things more than investing in the underdogs and showing them that they were special and could achieve their dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:35:01'),
(854, 32, 'My mother was very family-oriented. And I do love being with my children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:35:17'),
(855, 32, 'Religion brought forth riches, and the daughter devoured the mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:35:32'),
(856, 32, 'My mother is extraordinary; she\'s a superwoman, like so many other single mothers who are out there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:36:08'),
(857, 32, 'My mother and father have also raised five boys so they know there\'s only so much that can be controlled.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:37:07'),
(858, 32, 'All mothers go through the exact same things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:37:17'),
(859, 32, 'Who can ever measure the benefit of a mother\'s inspiration?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:37:28'),
(860, 32, 'Catholics have guilt and Jews have guilt, fine. But mothers can trump them all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:37:41'),
(861, 32, 'My mother\'s side of the family is from the Bahamas, and I spent time there on and off when I was growing up. It\'s the place where I feel at peace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:38:17'),
(862, 32, 'I take every opportunity to tell people how happy my mother is to be dead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:38:50'),
(863, 32, 'Do I believe in God? I did until Mother\'s accident. She fell on some meat loaf and it penetrated her spleen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:39:50'),
(864, 32, 'When your mother dies, it really hurts. But with time, you get used to it. That\'s nature\'s way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:40:03'),
(865, 32, 'All we have to do is listen. The Good Lord gave us two ears and only one mouth, my dear white-headed mother used to say.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:40:14'),
(866, 32, 'Ignorance and fear are twins whose mother is slavery and whose father is oppression, and the mentality of the whole family is that of slaves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:41:07'),
(867, 32, 'The future of a nation lies in the hands of mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:41:18'),
(868, 32, 'Limitation of aims is the mother of wisdom and the secret of achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:41:38'),
(869, 32, 'In order to get meat, we have to kill. And we are certainly not entitled to any other milk except the mother\'s milk in our infancy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:42:09'),
(870, 32, 'When he is sick, every man wants his mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:42:31'),
(871, 32, 'If you can look in your mother\'s eyes and she\'s proud of you, then you\'re a champion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:42:42'),
(872, 32, 'My mother taught me to walk proud and tall \'as if the world was mine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-18 16:43:06'),
(873, 31, 'The most important thing a father can do for his children is to love their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:18:58'),
(874, 31, 'A good father is one of the most unsung, unpraised, unnoticed, and yet one of the most valuable assets in our society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:19:10'),
(875, 31, 'Any man can be a father. It takes someone special to be a dad.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:19:20'),
(876, 31, 'I cannot think of any need in childhood as strong as the need for a father\'s protection.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:19:32'),
(877, 31, 'Nothing I\'ve ever done has given me more joys and rewards than being a father to my children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:19:44'),
(878, 31, 'When a father gives to his son, both laugh; when a son gives to his father, both cry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:19:54'),
(879, 31, 'My father didn\'t tell me how to live; he lived, and let me watch him do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:20:05'),
(880, 31, 'Blessed indeed is the man who hears many gentle voices call him father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:20:14'),
(881, 31, 'The righteous man walks in his integrity; His children are blessed after him. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:20:31'),
(882, 31, 'No love is greater than that of a father for His son.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:20:42'),
(883, 31, 'It doesn\'t matter who my father was; it matters who I remember he was.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:20:52'),
(884, 31, 'A man knows when he is growing old because he begins to look like his father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:21:03'),
(885, 31, 'One father is more than a hundred schoolmasters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:21:12'),
(886, 31, 'It is not flesh and blood, but heart which makes us fathers and sons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:21:22'),
(887, 31, 'Fathering is the most masculine thing a man can do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:21:39'),
(888, 31, 'No matter how old we become, we can still call them \'Holy Mother\' and \'Father\' and put a child-like trust in them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:22:11'),
(889, 31, 'There is nothing that moves a loving father\'s soul quite like his child\'s cry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:22:41');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(890, 31, 'What do I owe my father? Everything!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:22:54'),
(891, 31, 'To a father growing old nothing is dearer than a daughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:23:03'),
(892, 31, 'It is a wise father that knows his own child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:23:14'),
(893, 31, 'I may neither choose who I would, nor refuse who I dislike; so is the will of a living daughter curbed by the will of a dead father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:23:32'),
(894, 31, 'The older I get, the smarter my father seems to get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:23:42'),
(895, 31, 'A father carries pictures where his money used to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:23:56'),
(896, 31, 'I\'m so proud of you that it makes me proud of me. I hope you know that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:24:07'),
(897, 31, 'My father said there were two kinds of people in the world: givers and takers. The takers may eat better, but the givers sleep better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:24:20'),
(898, 31, 'As my father used to tell me, the only true sign of success in life is being able to do for a living that which makes you happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:24:30'),
(899, 31, 'By the time a man realizes that his father was right, he has a son who thinks he\'s wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:24:39'),
(900, 31, 'I love the comic opportunities that come up in the context of a father-son relationship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:25:39'),
(901, 31, 'A wise son makes a glad father, But a foolish son is the grief of his mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:25:51'),
(902, 31, 'A father is a man who expects his son to be as good a man as he meant to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:00'),
(903, 31, 'The great man is he who does not lose his child\'s heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:19'),
(904, 31, 'It is easier for a father to have children than for children to have a real father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:28'),
(905, 31, 'My father, he was like the rock, the guy you went to with every problem.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:38'),
(906, 31, 'My father used to sing to me in my mother\'s womb. I think I can name about any tune in two beats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:47'),
(907, 31, 'The father who does not teach his son his duties is equally guilty with the son who neglects them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:26:57'),
(908, 31, 'A father is always making his baby into a little woman. And when she is a woman he turns her back again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:27:06'),
(909, 31, 'Love and fear. Everything the father of a family says must inspire one or the other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:27:15'),
(910, 31, 'Children learn to smile from their parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:27:25'),
(911, 31, 'Fatherhood is pretending the present you love most is soap-on-a-rope.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:27:35'),
(912, 31, 'It kills you to see them grow up. But I guess it would kill you quicker if they didn\'t.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:27:48'),
(913, 31, 'That was when the world wasn\'t so big and I could see everywhere. It was when my father was a hero and not a human.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:28:06'),
(914, 31, 'I know that I will never find my father in any other man who comes into my life, because it is a void in my life that can only be filled by him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:28:28'),
(915, 31, 'My father confused me. From the ages of one to seven, I thought my name was Jesus Christ!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:28:37'),
(916, 31, 'My father taught me to work; he did not teach me to love it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:28:55'),
(917, 31, 'My father loved people, children and pets.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:29:06'),
(918, 31, 'I am not ashamed to say that no man I ever met was my father\'s equal, and I never loved any other man as much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:29:20'),
(919, 31, 'Whoever does not have a good father should procure one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:29:31'),
(920, 31, 'The father is always a Republican toward his son, and his mother\'s always a Democrat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:29:52'),
(921, 31, 'What was silent in the father speaks in the son, and often I found in the son the unveiled secret of the father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:03'),
(922, 31, 'I talk and talk and talk, and I haven\'t taught people in 50 years what my father taught by example in one week.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:13'),
(923, 31, 'You don\'t have to deserve your mother\'s love. You have to deserve your father\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:22'),
(924, 31, 'To her, the name of father was another name for love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:32'),
(925, 31, 'Old as she was, she still missed her daddy sometimes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:43'),
(926, 31, 'There are fathers who do not love their children; there is no grandfather who does not adore his grandson.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:30:54'),
(927, 31, 'My father, when he went, made my childhood a gift of a half a century.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:31:03'),
(928, 31, 'My father invented a cure for which there was no disease and unfortunately my mother caught it and died of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:31:15'),
(929, 31, 'I grew up not liking my father very much. I never saw him cry. But he must have. Everybody cries.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:31:25'),
(930, 31, 'I owe my father everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:31:39'),
(931, 31, 'Life was a lot simpler when what we honored was father and mother rather than all major credit cards.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:32:00'),
(932, 31, 'I just wish I could understand my father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:32:12'),
(933, 31, 'The place of the father in the modern suburban family is a very small one, particularly if he plays golf.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:32:21'),
(934, 31, 'What a father says to his children is not heard by the world, but it will be heard by posterity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:32:43'),
(935, 31, 'I am indebted to my father for living, but to my teacher for living well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:32:57'),
(936, 31, 'The surprising thing about fatherhood was finding my inner mush. Now I want to share it with the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:33:14'),
(937, 31, 'I stopped loving my father a long time ago. What remained was the slavery to a pattern.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:33:23'),
(938, 31, 'We think our fathers fools, so wise we grow. Our wiser sons, no doubt will think us so.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:33:44'),
(939, 31, 'Being a father to my family and a husband is to me much more important than what I did in the business.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:33:55'),
(940, 31, 'Being a father, being a friend, those are the things that make me feel successful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:34:06'),
(941, 31, 'When I was a kid, my father told me every day, \'You\'re the most wonderful boy in the world, and you can do anything you want to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:34:27'),
(942, 31, 'I was raised Catholic, but my father\'s people were Methodist, so we went to both churches.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:36:03'),
(943, 31, 'My father was the guy on the block who said hi to everyone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:36:16'),
(944, 31, 'The fundamental defect of fathers, in our competitive society, is that they want their children to be a credit to them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:36:29'),
(945, 31, 'My mother protected me from the world and my father threatened me with it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:36:43'),
(946, 31, 'Fathers, like mothers, are not born. Men grow into fathers and fathering is a very important stage in their development.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:36:55'),
(947, 31, 'Scratch any father, you find / Someone chock-full of qualms and romantic terrors, / Believing change is a threat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:38:03'),
(948, 31, 'Be brave as your fathers before you. Have faith and go forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:38:13'),
(949, 31, 'You know, fathers just have a way of putting everything together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:38:49'),
(950, 31, 'You know, fathers just have a way of putting everything together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:39:35'),
(951, 31, 'The love of a mother is the veil of a softer light between the heart and the heavenly Father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:39:46'),
(952, 31, 'I thought I would be more inspired to have all these new feelings to talk about, but I really just want to hang out with my daughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:40:05'),
(953, 31, 'You will find that if you really try to be a father, your child will meet you halfway.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:40:15'),
(954, 31, 'When a father, absent during the day, returns home at six, his children receive only his temperament, not his teaching.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:40:32'),
(955, 31, 'When you have a good mother and no father, God kind of sits in. It\'s not enough, but it helps.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:40:47'),
(956, 31, 'I have never been a material girl. My father always told me never to love anything that cannot love you back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:41:33'),
(957, 31, 'Being a father helps me be more responsible... you see more things than you\'ve ever seen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:41:42'),
(958, 31, 'I would want my legacy to be that I was a great son, father and friend.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:41:52'),
(959, 31, 'My father considered a walk among the mountains as the equivalent of churchgoing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:42:02'),
(960, 31, 'My father always used to say that when you die, if you\'ve got five real friends, then you\'ve had a great life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:42:15'),
(961, 31, 'That is the thankless position of the father in the family-the provider for all, and the enemy of all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:42:46'),
(962, 31, 'My father was a proctologist and my mother was an abstract artist, so that\'s how I view the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:42:55'),
(963, 31, 'I pressed my father\'s hand and told him I would protect his grave with my life. My father smiled and passed away to the spirit land.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:43:07'),
(964, 31, 'Feels good to try, but playing a father, I\'m getting a little older. I see now that I\'m taking it more serious and I do want that lifestyle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:43:24'),
(965, 31, 'My father carries around the picture of the kid who came with his wallet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:43:36'),
(966, 31, 'I\'m a father. It isn\'t just my life any more. I don\'t want my kid finding bottles in the house or seeing his father completely smashed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:43:50'),
(967, 31, 'It is impossible to please all the world and one\'s father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:43:58'),
(968, 31, 'A son can bear with equanimity the loss of his father, but the loss of his inheritance may drive him to despair.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:44:35'),
(969, 31, 'Love matches, so called, have illusion for their father and need for their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:44:44'),
(970, 31, 'As Daddy said, life is 95 percent anticipation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:44:56'),
(971, 31, 'There will always be a few people who have the courage to love what is untamed inside us. One of those men is my father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:45:30'),
(972, 31, 'A father is a fellow who has replaced the currency in his wallet with snapshots of his kids.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:46:55'),
(973, 31, 'My mother gave me my drive but my father gave me my dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:47:05'),
(974, 31, 'It was my father who taught me to value myself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:47:32'),
(975, 31, 'There\'s really no point in having children if you\'re not going to be home enough to father them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:47:56'),
(976, 31, 'Those who have never had a father can at any rate never know the sweets of losing one. To most men the death of his father is a new lease of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:48:16'),
(977, 31, 'To gather with God\'s people in united adoration of the Father is as necessary to the Christian life as prayer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:48:30'),
(978, 31, 'I don\'t care what they say about me when I\'m through with sports. I don\'t want to be known as anything else in life but a great father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:49:19'),
(979, 31, 'If we expect to inherit the blessings of our Fathers, we should return a little more to their primitive Simplicity of Manners.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:50:01'),
(980, 31, 'My father was always talking about God, and I idolized my father, so I\'d spend hours trying to have mental telepathy with God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:50:28'),
(981, 31, 'I always admire writers. My father was a writer, a poet. I always admire people who can clearly state their mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:51:28'),
(982, 31, 'Everything we have - every blessing, every talent - is a gift from our Father. The only thing that\'s all ours is our sin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:52:13'),
(983, 31, 'The commandments are a gift, not a curse. Sin is less about breaking the rules and more about breaking the Father\'s heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:52:30'),
(984, 31, 'If our founding fathers were alive today, they\'d roll over in their graves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:52:47'),
(985, 31, 'My father believed in me many times more than I believed in myself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:53:40'),
(986, 31, 'I\'ve never made an excuse of not knowing my father, because I\'ve had great people in my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:54:01'),
(987, 31, 'The love of a father is one of nature\'s greatest masterpieces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:55:23'),
(988, 31, 'Father, look upon us in Your goodness and kindness, we pray as a church. Help us to love each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:56:39'),
(989, 31, 'My father always said, \'Bet on yourself.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:57:04'),
(990, 31, 'My father always said: \'If you want to know someone, live together on a boat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:57:34'),
(991, 31, 'The biggest impact my father had on my life was teaching the importance of literacy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:57:53'),
(992, 31, 'My father and I used to watch movies all the time. That was our bonding time, so thats when I kind of fell in love with acting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 15:59:01'),
(993, 31, 'My father told me I should marry the woman that loves me, not the woman I loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:06:22'),
(994, 31, 'If more husbands and fathers would put as much energy into their marriages and families as they do their jobs, the world would change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:06:35'),
(995, 31, 'Remember that our Heavenly Father and our Savior, Jesus Christ, know you best and love you the most.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:06:53'),
(996, 31, 'The Father doesn\'t give life directions in one big bundle because the goal is knowing Him, not the plan.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:07:41'),
(997, 31, 'God is the mother and father of the world. Our parents are the mother and father of this body.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:08:12'),
(998, 31, 'They call our language the mother tongue because the father seldom gets to speak.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:08:57'),
(999, 31, 'My father was the only man I ever knew who really loved me unselfishly, who never used me for personal gain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:27:19'),
(1000, 31, 'Tonight, the daughter of an immigrant from Italy has been chosen to run for vice president in the new land my father came to love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:27:28'),
(1001, 31, 'Father and son are natural enemies and each is happier and more secure in keeping it that way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:27:36'),
(1002, 31, 'My friends and I were all deathly afraid of our fathers, which was right and proper and even biblically ordained. Fathers were angry; it was their job.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:27:51'),
(1003, 31, 'My father said about money: \'You have to have some. But you don\'t have to have all of it. Just be honest with yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:28:25'),
(1004, 31, 'All we have to do is to go onward and upward, and keep the commandments of our Father and God; and he will confound our enemies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:28:36'),
(1005, 31, 'My father instilled in me a love for racing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:28:51'),
(1006, 31, 'My father knows me better than anyone. He can tell me over the phone what I\'m doing wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:29:02'),
(1007, 31, 'I want to follow in my father\'s footsteps, but do it better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:29:13'),
(1008, 31, 'I hated farm work. I always got stuck with the jobs my father and brother didn\'t want to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:29:27'),
(1009, 31, 'A good father is one of the most unsung, unpraised, unnoticed, and yet one of the most valuable assets in our society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:30:18'),
(1010, 31, 'Good fathers not only tell us how to live, they show us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:30:28'),
(1011, 31, 'A good father does these basic things: provides for his family, protects his family, and gives spiritual and moral guidance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:30:39'),
(1012, 31, 'Parents can only give good advice or put them on the right paths, but the final forming of a person\'s character lies in their own hands.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:30:49'),
(1013, 31, 'A dad stands tallest when he kneels to pray with his children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:30:59'),
(1014, 31, 'Dad taught me everything I know. Unfortunately, he didn\'t teach me everything he knows.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:31:08'),
(1015, 31, 'When one has not had a good father, one must create one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:31:19'),
(1016, 31, 'It is easier for a father to have children than for children to have a real father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:31:28'),
(1017, 31, 'I hope I am remembered by my children as a good father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:31:40'),
(1018, 31, 'Whoever does not have a good father should procure one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:31:50'),
(1019, 31, 'He who can be a good son will be a good father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:32:00'),
(1020, 31, 'One thing that prevents a man from being a good father is he hasn\'t completed being a boy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:32:10'),
(1021, 31, 'The best way to be a good father to your children is to be a good husband to their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:32:26'),
(1022, 31, 'The most important thing a father can do for his children is to love their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-19 16:32:59'),
