(1111, 30, 'Live in such a way that you would not be ashamed to sell your parrot to the town gossip.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:06:09'),
(1112, 30, 'If you cannot get rid of the family skeleton, you may as well make it dance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:06:19'),
(1113, 30, 'Fathers should be neither seen nor heard. That is the only proper basis for family life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:06:29'),
(1114, 30, 'If the family were a fruit, it would be an orange, a circle of sections, held together but separable - each segment distinct.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:06:45'),
(1115, 30, 'Give a little love to a child, and you get a great deal back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:06:55'),
(1116, 30, 'The love of family and the admiration of friends is much more important than wealth and privilege.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:04'),
(1117, 30, 'The only rock I know that stays steady, the only institution I know that works, is the family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:14'),
(1118, 30, 'When everything goes to hell, the people who stand by you without flinching - they are your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:23'),
(1119, 30, 'You go through life wondering what is it all about but at the end of the day it\'s all about family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:38'),
(1120, 30, 'One of the things that binds us as a family is a shared sense of humor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:48'),
(1121, 30, 'Remember that children, marriages, and flower gardens reflect the kind of care they get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:07:59'),
(1122, 30, 'The God who existed before any religion counts on you to make the oneness of the human family known and celebrated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:08:13'),
(1123, 30, 'Each day of our lives we make deposits in the memory banks of our children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:08:22'),
(1124, 30, 'Sticking with your family is what makes it a family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:08:43'),
(1125, 30, 'Happiness is having a large, loving, caring, close-knit family in another city.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:09:08'),
(1126, 30, 'The strength of a family, like the strength of an army, lies in its loyalty to each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:09:18'),
(1127, 30, 'We must restore the sacredness of the family as a bedrock of humane values everywhere, in peace as well as in war.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:09:31'),
(1128, 30, 'I believe the world is one big family, and we need to help each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:09:41'),
(1129, 30, 'One day you will do things for me that you hate. That is what it means to be family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:09:55'),
(1130, 30, 'Let parents bequeath to their children not riches, but the spirit of reverence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:06'),
(1131, 30, 'We believed in our idea - a family park where parents and children could have fun- together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:16'),
(1132, 30, 'Nothing I\'ve ever done has given me more joys and rewards than being a father to my children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:27'),
(1133, 30, 'A family is a place where principles are hammered and honed on the anvil of everyday living.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:36'),
(1134, 30, 'Home is people. Not a place. If you go back there after the people are gone, then all you can see is what is not there any more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:47'),
(1135, 30, 'Children begin by loving their parents; after a time they judge them; rarely, if ever, do they forgive them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:10:58'),
(1136, 30, 'The reason grandparents and grandchildren get along so well is that they have a common enemy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:11:07'),
(1137, 30, 'If the family goes, so goes our civilization.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:11:16'),
(1138, 30, 'I think togetherness is a very important ingredient to family life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:11:36'),
(1139, 30, 'That\'s what people do who love you. They put their arms around you and love you when you\'re not so lovable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:11:47'),
(1140, 30, 'A family stitched together with love seldom unravels.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:11:57'),
(1141, 30, 'The best of all gifts around any Christmas tree: the presence of a happy family all wrapped up in each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:10'),
(1142, 30, 'If the family were a boat, it would be a canoe that makes no progress unless everyone paddles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:19'),
(1143, 30, 'Cherish your human connections: your relationships with friends and family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:28'),
(1144, 30, 'No man has ever lived that had enough of children\'s gratitude or woman\'s love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:37'),
(1145, 30, 'A family can develop only with a loving woman as its center.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:47'),
(1146, 30, 'Some of the most important conversations I\'ve ever had occurred at my family\'s dinner table.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:12:58'),
(1147, 30, 'Family is everything. Family comes first. It\'s not what I expected it to be, but nothing ever is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:13:07'),
(1148, 30, 'Your children need your presence more than your presents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:13:17'),
(1149, 30, 'Family connexions were always worth preserving, good company always worth seeking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:13:27'),
(1150, 30, 'There is nothing more important than a good, safe, secure home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:13:41'),
(1151, 30, 'Family, nature and health all go together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:14:00'),
(1152, 30, 'The only people that you really have, that I learned, are your family, because they love you no matter what.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:14:09'),
(1153, 30, 'The family is more sacred than the state.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:14:20'),
(1154, 30, 'A happy marriage is the union of two good forgivers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:14:33');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(1155, 30, 'No one\'s family is normal. Normalcy is a lie invented by advertising agencies to make the rest of us feel inferior.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:14:42'),
(1156, 30, 'To us, family means putting your arms around each other and being there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:15:01'),
(1157, 30, 'A sense of concern for others gives our lives meaning; it is the root of all human happiness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:15:10'),
(1158, 30, 'It takes a lot of work to put together a marriage, to put together a family and a home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:15:19'),
(1159, 30, 'My father chose my name , and my last name was chosen by my ancestors . That’s enough, I myself choose my way', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:15:31'),
(1160, 30, 'At the end of the day, a loving family should find everything forgivable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:15:41'),
(1161, 30, 'No other success [in life] can compensate for failure in the home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:16:06'),
(1162, 30, 'The happiest moments of my life have been the few which I have passed at home in the bosom of my family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:16:54'),
(1163, 30, 'It is not possible for one to teach others who cannot teach his own family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:07'),
(1164, 30, 'If we abandon marriage, we abandon the family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:17'),
(1165, 30, 'Never help a child with a task at which he feels he can succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:27'),
(1166, 30, 'There\'s nothing I value more than the closeness of friends and family, a smile as I pass someone on the street.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:37'),
(1167, 30, 'Without a family, man, alone in the world, trembles with the cold.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:48'),
(1168, 30, 'Perhaps the greatest social service that can be rendered by anybody to the country and to mankind is to bring up a family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:17:57'),
(1169, 30, 'My kids give me the balance to live right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:18:08'),
(1170, 30, 'The whole world is my family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:18:18'),
(1171, 30, 'The whole world is my family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:20:00'),
(1172, 30, 'The heart of a mother is a deep abyss at the bottom of which you will always find forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:20:15'),
(1173, 30, 'I know if mama ain\'t happy, ain\'t nobody happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:20:35'),
(1174, 30, 'The family is the test of freedom; because the family is the only thing that the free man makes for himself and by himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:20:57'),
(1175, 30, 'The family is the school of duties - founded on love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:21:10'),
(1176, 30, 'Siblings: children of the same parents, each of whom is perfectly normal until they get together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:21:38'),
(1177, 30, 'The less you talk, the more you\'re listened to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:21:49'),
(1178, 30, 'It is not a bad thing that children should occasionally, and politely, put parents in their place.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:21:59'),
(1179, 30, 'It is not flesh and blood, but heart which makes us fathers and sons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:22:15'),
(1180, 30, 'The children despise their parents until the age of when they suddenly become just like them - thus preserving the system.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:22:28'),
(1181, 30, 'It is a wise father that knows his own child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:22:53'),
(1182, 30, 'I have a family to support. And I\'m not always going to be doing exactly what I want to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:04'),
(1183, 30, 'A dysfunctional family is any family with more than one person in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:14'),
(1184, 30, 'To bring up a child in the way he should go, travel that way yourself once in a while.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:23'),
(1185, 30, 'Making the family a top priority will invariably bring success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:33'),
(1186, 30, 'Let your children go if you want to keep them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:47'),
(1187, 30, 'As a child my family\'s menu consisted of two choices: take it or leave it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:23:58'),
(1188, 30, 'we must take care of our families wherever we find them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:24:08'),
(1189, 30, 'Manners will become important to children only if they are important to their parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:24:17'),
(1190, 30, 'I think, at a child\'s birth, if a mother could ask a fairy godmother to endow it with the most useful gift, that gift should be curiosity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:24:28'),
(1191, 30, 'You leave home to seek your fortune and, when you get it, you go home and share it with your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:24:55'),
(1192, 30, 'You know your children are growing up when they stop asking you where they came from and refuse to tell you where they\'re going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:05'),
(1193, 30, 'I consider my mom and all my sisters my friends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:14'),
(1194, 30, 'Family life is too intimate to be preserved by the spirit of justice. It can be sustained by a spirit of love which goes beyond justice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:24'),
(1195, 30, 'You are born into your family and your family is born into you. No returns. No exchanges.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:35'),
(1196, 30, 'When trouble comes, it\'s your family that supports you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:44'),
(1197, 30, 'I grew up with six brothers. That\'s how I learned to dance - waiting for the bathroom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:25:53'),
(1198, 30, 'Chance makes our parents, but choice makes our friends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:04'),
(1199, 30, 'Mother is the name for God in the lips and hearts of little children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:14'),
(1200, 30, 'Let us all reaffirm our commitment to improving the well- being of families throughout the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:23'),
(1201, 30, 'In family life, love is the oil that eases friction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:32'),
(1202, 30, 'Being popular is the most important thing in the world!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:41'),
(1203, 30, 'I have these visions of myself being thirty, thirty-five, forty having a family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:26:51'),
(1204, 30, 'The family unit plays a critical role in our society and in the training of the generation to come.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:27:00'),
(1205, 30, 'I am the family face; flesh perishes, I live on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:27:09'),
(1206, 30, 'Spend some time this weekend on home improvement; improve your attitude toward your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:27:31'),
(1207, 30, 'Having children is like having a bowling alley installed in your brain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:27:40'),
(1208, 30, 'If you don\'t believe in ghosts, you\'ve never been to a family reunion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:27:51'),
(1209, 30, 'The bond that links your true family is not one of blood, but of respect and joy in each other\'s life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:28:07'),
(1210, 30, 'Some family trees bear an enormous crop of nuts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:28:17'),
(1211, 30, 'Family is the most important thing in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:28:27'),
(1212, 30, 'My family\'s the most important thing in my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:28:38'),
(1213, 30, 'To nourish children and raise them against odds is in any time, any place, more valuable than to fix bolts in cars or design nuclear weapons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:28:51'),
(1214, 30, 'The mother\'s heart is the child\'s schoolroom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:01'),
(1215, 30, 'When you look at your life the greatest happinesses are family happinesses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:10'),
(1216, 30, 'I would rather start a family than finish one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:19'),
(1217, 30, 'Human beings are the only creatures on earth that allow their children to come back home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:28'),
(1218, 30, 'I have learned that to be with those I like is enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:36'),
(1219, 30, 'One laugh of a child will make the holiest day more sacred still.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:47'),
(1220, 30, 'I realized my family was funny, because nobody ever wanted to leave our house.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:29:58'),
(1221, 30, 'Home is the place where, when you have to go there, they have to take you in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:30:06'),
(1222, 30, 'The great advantage of living in a large family is that early lesson of life\'s essential unfairness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:30:15'),
(1223, 30, 'As the family goes, so goes society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:30:45'),
(1224, 30, 'I like to see a home like this, a home connected with people\'s thoughts and work, things they love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:30:53'),
(1225, 30, 'When I remember my family, I always remember their backs. They were always indignantly leaving places.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:31:03'),
(1226, 30, 'Family is what grounds you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:31:14'),
(1227, 30, 'Those who love the young best stay young longer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:31:26'),
(1228, 30, 'Adults are just children who earn money.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:31:59'),
(1229, 30, 'A loving family provides the foundation children need to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:32:10'),
(1230, 30, 'To be a good friend remember that we are human magnets: that like attracts like and that as we give we get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:32:21'),
(1231, 30, 'When I\'m ready, I plan to adopt. I still believe in family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:32:33'),
(1232, 30, 'Insanity runs in my family. It practically gallops.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:32:46'),
(1233, 30, 'The foundation of family - that\'s where it all begins for me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:33:23'),
(1234, 30, 'I don\'t have to look up my family tree, because I know that I\'m the sap.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:33:35'),
(1235, 30, 'When our relatives are at home, we have to think of all their good points or it would be impossible to endure them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:33:45'),
(1236, 30, 'Friends are the family we choose for ourselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:00'),
(1237, 30, 'Tennis just a game, family is forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:10'),
(1238, 30, 'The hatred of relatives is the most violent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:18'),
(1239, 30, 'There is nothing like staying at home for real comfort.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:27'),
(1240, 30, 'My family is more important than my party.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:36'),
(1241, 30, 'I stay in tune with my family and God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:48'),
(1242, 30, 'Writers will happen in the best of families.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:34:59'),
(1243, 30, 'The family is the first essential cell of human society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:09'),
(1244, 30, 'My family was my guide to my reality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:20'),
(1245, 30, 'Love is the chain whereby to bind a child to its parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:29'),
(1246, 30, 'Love is the chain whereby to bind a child to its parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:37'),
(1247, 30, 'Family likeness has often a deep sadness in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:45'),
(1248, 30, 'Treat people as if they were what they ought to be and you help them to become what they are capable of being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:35:57'),
(1249, 30, 'I can get up in the morning and look myself in the mirror and my family can look at me too and that\'s all that matters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:36:08'),
(1250, 30, 'The greatest thing in family life is to take a hint when a hint is intended-and not to take a hint when a hint isn\'t intended.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:36:36'),
(1251, 30, 'A woman can take care of the family. It takes a man to provide structure, to provide stability.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:36:45'),
(1252, 30, 'Acting is just a way of making a living, the family is life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:36:57'),
(1253, 30, 'Families are the compass that guide us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:37:06'),
(1254, 30, 'The family - that dear octopus from whose tentacles we never quite escape, nor, in our inmost hearts, ever quite wish to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:37:16'),
(1255, 30, 'Trust yourself, you know more than you think you do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:37:33'),
(1256, 30, 'No amount of law enforcement can solve a problem that goes back to the family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:37:44'),
(1257, 30, 'As a general thing, when a woman wears the pants in a family, she has a good right to them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:37:52'),
(1258, 30, 'In general my children refuse to eat anything that hasn\'t danced in television.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:38:02'),
(1259, 30, 'The place is very well and quiet and the children only scream in a low voice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:38:11'),
(1260, 30, 'I don\'t know if I believe in marriage. I believe in family, love and children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:38:23'),
(1261, 30, 'Whatever else is unsure in this stinking dunghill of a world a mother\'s love is not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:38:50'),
(1262, 30, 'Friends are God\'s apology for relations.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:39:30'),
(1263, 30, 'I grew up in a big family with a lot of kids around, and I definitely want to have children as well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:39:38'),
(1264, 30, 'She got her looks from her father. He\'s a plastic surgeon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:39:48'),
(1265, 30, 'I have Muslim members of my family. I have lived in Muslim countries.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:39:58'),
(1266, 30, 'Make a Goal Box, a chart of positive daily contact with a family when you are working with them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:40:07'),
(1267, 30, 'Dad kept us out of school, but school comes and goes. Family is forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:40:17'),
(1268, 30, 'At a certain point I\'m going to want to have a family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:40:26'),
(1269, 30, 'It is extraordinary that when you are acquainted with a whole family you can forget about them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:40:36'),
(1270, 30, 'You have to defend your honor. And your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:40:57'),
(1271, 30, 'A person starts to live when he can live outside himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:41:14'),
(1272, 30, 'This was the trouble with families. Like invidious doctors, they knew just where it hurt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:41:24'),
(1273, 30, 'Poverty devastates families, communities and nations. It causes instability and political unrest and fuels conflict.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:41:32'),
(1274, 30, 'The joke in our family is that we can cry reading the phone book.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:41:46'),
(1275, 30, 'When you start about family, about lineage and ancestry, you are talking about every person on earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:42:00'),
(1276, 30, 'The most difficult is the first family, to bring someone out of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFamily', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 06:42:09'),
(1277, 29, 'Failure is simply the opportunity to begin again, this time more intelligently.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:23:18'),
(1278, 29, 'Don\'t be so bitter about a bad experience from your past that you miss the opportunities in front of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:23:30'),
(1279, 29, 'Don\'t be so bitter about a bad experience from your past that you miss the opportunities in front of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:24:13'),
(1280, 29, 'Failure is not the opposite of success; it\'s part of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:24:25'),
(1281, 29, 'Many of life\'s failures are people who did not realize how close they were to success when they gave up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:24:33'),
(1282, 29, 'Do not be embarrassed by your failures, learn from them and start again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:24:53'),
(1283, 29, 'A person who never made a mistake never tried anything new.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:04'),
(1284, 29, 'Failure is unimportant. It takes courage to make a fool of yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:14'),
(1285, 29, 'You always pass failure on the way to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:24'),
(1286, 29, 'If you\'re not failing every now and again, it\'s a sign you\'re not doing anything very innovative.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:37'),
(1287, 29, 'There are two kinds of failures: those who thought and never did, and those who did and never thought', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:47'),
(1288, 29, 'There are no secrets to success. It is the result of preparation, hard work, and learning from failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:25:58'),
(1289, 29, 'Forget about the consequences of failure. Failure is only a temporary change in direction to set you straight for your next success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:26:09'),
(1290, 29, 'Develop success from failures. Discouragement and failure are two of the surest stepping stones to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:26:18'),
(1291, 29, 'Defeat is not the worst of failures. Not to have tried is the true failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:26:36'),
(1292, 29, 'Concern yourself not with what you tried and failed in, but with what it is still possible for you to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:26:45'),
(1293, 29, 'A failure is not always a mistake, it may simply be the best one can do under the circumstances. The real mistake is to stop trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:26:56'),
(1294, 29, 'Success consists of going from failure to failure without loss of enthusiasm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:05'),
(1295, 29, 'Failure is a detour, not a dead-end street.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:14'),
(1296, 29, 'It\'s fine to celebrate success but it is more important to heed the lessons of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:23'),
(1297, 29, 'I didn\'t fail the test, I just found 100 ways to do it wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:32'),
(1298, 29, 'I have not failed. I\'ve just found 10,000 ways that won\'t work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:46'),
(1299, 29, 'Success is not final, failure is not fatal: it is the courage to continue that counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:27:55'),
(1300, 29, 'If you fell down yesterday, stand up today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:28:13'),
(1301, 29, 'Those who dare to fail miserably can achieve greatly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:28:26'),
(1302, 29, 'Those who dare to fail miserably can achieve greatly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:28:36'),
(1303, 29, 'A life spent making mistakes is not only more honorable, but more useful than a life spent doing nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:32:42'),
(1304, 29, 'In order to succeed, your desire for success should be greater than your fear of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:32:54'),
(1305, 29, 'For every failure, there\'s an alternative course of action. You just have to find it. When you come to a roadblock, take a detour.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:33:05'),
(1306, 29, 'If you want to succeed, double your failure rate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:33:14'),
(1307, 29, 'Success depends upon previous preparation, and without such preparation there is sure to be failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:33:26'),
(1308, 29, 'I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can\'t accept not trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:33:39'),
(1309, 29, 'Failure is merely feedback that there is something blocking the path of the emergence and expansion of the greatest version of yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:33:53'),
(1310, 29, 'Each time you fail, you have eliminated another wrong option.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:34:04'),
(1311, 29, 'Our greatest weakness lies in giving up. The most certain way to succeed is always to try just one more time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:34:26'),
(1312, 29, 'We need to discover the root causes of success rather than the root causes of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:34:45'),
(1313, 29, 'If you learn from defeat, you haven\'t really lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:34:55'),
(1314, 29, 'Remember that failure is an event, not a person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:35:12'),
(1315, 29, 'We are not a failure just because we fail at something. Nobody is a failure unless they quit trying!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:35:25'),
(1316, 29, 'It is hard to fail, but it is worse never to have tried to succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:35:35'),
(1317, 29, 'If at first you don\'t succeed, failure may be your style.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:35:44'),
(1318, 29, 'Failure after long perseverance is much grander than never to have a striving good enough to be called a failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:35:56'),
(1319, 29, 'Failure is not fatal, but failure to change might be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:36:06'),
(1320, 29, 'The awesome thing about failure is that it is only temporary. Embrace it, learn the lesson and come back blazing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:36:16'),
(1321, 29, 'Experience teaches slowly, and at the cost of mistakes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:36:28'),
(1322, 29, 'You may have a fresh start any moment you choose, for this thing that we call \'failure\' is not the falling down, but the staying down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:36:39'),
(1323, 29, 'An inventor fails 999 times, and if he succeeds once, he\'s in. He treats his failures simply as practice shots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:38:19'),
(1324, 29, 'Success represents the 1% of your work which results from the 99% that is called failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:38:29'),
(1325, 29, 'I don\'t know the key to success, but the key to failure is trying to please everybody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:38:40'),
(1326, 29, 'Experience is simply the name we give our mistakes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:38:52'),
(1327, 29, 'Fear is the main source of superstition, and one of the main sources of cruelty. To conquer fear is the beginning of wisdom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:39:04'),
(1328, 29, 'Do not fear mistakes. You will know failure. Continue to reach out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:39:14'),
(1329, 29, 'Even though the ship may go down, the journey goes on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:39:28'),
(1330, 29, 'In all science, error precedes the truth, and it is better it should go first than last.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:39:38'),
(1331, 29, 'The greatest failure is the failure to try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:39:48'),
(1332, 29, 'Congealed thinking is the forerunner of failure... make sure you are always receptive to new ideas.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:00'),
(1333, 29, 'Recovering from failure is often easier than building from success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:09'),
(1334, 29, 'He only is exempt from failures who makes no efforts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:21'),
(1335, 29, 'Failure is authentic, and because it\'s authentic, it\'s real and genuine, and because of that, it\'s a pure state of being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:29'),
(1336, 29, 'The loss which is unknown is no loss at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:39'),
(1337, 29, 'It is foolish to fear what you cannot avoid.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:40:48'),
(1338, 29, 'The better a man is the more mistakes will he make – for the more new things he will try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:41:01'),
(1339, 29, 'He\'s no failure. He\'s not dead yet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:41:15'),
(1340, 29, 'The success or failure of a life, as far as posterity goes, seems to lie in the more or less luck of seizing the right moment of escape', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:41:30'),
(1341, 29, 'In this game that we\'re playing, we can\'t win. Some kinds of failure are better than other kinds, that\'s all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:41:44'),
(1342, 29, 'The man who fails because he aims astray or because he does not aim at all is to be found everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:41:55'),
(1343, 29, 'The man who fails because he aims astray or because he does not aim at all is to be found everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:43:25'),
(1344, 29, 'I was shipwrecked before I got aboard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:43:34'),
(1345, 29, 'An artist, a man, a failure, must proceed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:43:44'),
(1346, 29, 'Most of my conscious efforts have ended in embarrassing failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:43:57'),
(1347, 29, 'I had to come to terms with my failure as an artist... I had to find a way for myself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:44:07'),
(1348, 29, 'Artists know failure. It is not tragic that they know failure; it is only tragic if they know failure and little else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:44:27'),
(1349, 29, 'The only real failure is trying to second-guess the taste of an audience. Nothing comes out of that except a kind of inward humiliation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:44:42'),
(1350, 29, 'Success is seldom permanent, and failure is seldom fatal. The important thing is to keep trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:44:53'),
(1351, 29, 'Reconcile the loss of the painting - no matter how many times it may happen - with the joy of beginning again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:02'),
(1352, 29, 'Failure is the mechanism of learning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:11'),
(1353, 29, 'Defeat should never be a source of discouragement but rather a fresh stimulus.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:21'),
(1354, 29, 'No man is a failure who is enjoying life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:31'),
(1355, 29, 'The majority of men meet with failure because of their lack of persistence in creating new plans to take the place of those which fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:50'),
(1356, 29, 'A failure is a man who has blundered, but is not able to cash in the experience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:45:58'),
(1357, 29, 'The only time you mustn\'t fail is the last time you try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:46:08'),
(1358, 29, 'There is no failure except in no longer trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:46:19'),
(1359, 29, 'There is much to be said for failure. It is more interesting than success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:46:30'),
(1360, 29, 'It\'s best to have failure happen early in life. It wakes up the Phoenix bird in you so you rise from the ashes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:46:51'),
(1361, 29, 'It\'s not necessary to fear the prospect of failure but to be determined not to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:46:59'),
(1362, 29, 'The only failure is not to try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:08'),
(1363, 29, 'Failure happens all the time. It happens every day in practice. What makes you better is how you react to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:17'),
(1364, 29, 'My fault, my failure, is not in the passions I have, but in my lack of control of them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:25'),
(1365, 29, 'It is not enough to succeed. Others must fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:36'),
(1366, 29, 'Failure is more frequently from want of energy than want of capital.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:47'),
(1367, 29, 'Giving up is the only sure way to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:47:57'),
(1368, 29, 'Half of the failures in life come from pulling one\'s horse when he is leaping.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:48:12'),
(1369, 29, 'If you\'re doing your best, you won\'t have any time to worry about failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:48:24'),
(1370, 29, 'If you\'re doing your best, you won\'t have any time to worry about failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:55:31'),
(1371, 29, 'Make failure your teacher, not your undertaker.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:55:43'),
(1372, 29, 'Failures are like skinned knees, painful but superficial.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:55:53'),
(1373, 29, 'No man is ever whipped until he quits - in his own mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:56:07'),
(1374, 29, 'The fearful are the failing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:56:20'),
(1375, 29, 'One fails forward toward success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:00'),
(1376, 29, 'Never confuse a single defeat with a final defeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:09'),
(1377, 29, 'Ninety-nine percent of the failures come from people who have the habit of making excuses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:19'),
(1378, 29, 'A minute\'s success pays the failure of years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:28'),
(1379, 29, 'A man\'s life is interesting primarily when he has failed - I well know. For it\'s a sign that he tried to surpass himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:37'),
(1380, 29, 'Failure is not a single, cataclysmic event. You don\'t fail overnight. Instead, failure is a few errors in judgement, repeated every day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:57:54'),
(1381, 29, 'There are no failures - just experiences and your reactions to them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:58:05'),
(1382, 29, 'It\'s not the failure that holds us back but the reluctance to begin over again that causes us to stagnate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:58:14'),
(1383, 29, 'You may be disappointed if you fail, but you are doomed if you don\'t try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:58:30'),
(1384, 29, 'It\'s not how far you fall, but how high you bounce that counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 16:58:46'),
(1385, 29, 'Only those who dare to fail greatly can ever achieve greatly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:00:39'),
(1386, 29, 'I wasn\'t afraid to fail. Something good always comes out of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:00:49'),
(1387, 29, 'There is the greatest practical benefit in making a few failures early in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:01:02'),
(1388, 29, 'Failure is the condiment that gives success its flavor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:01:20'),
(1389, 29, 'The season of failure is the best time for sowing the seeds of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:01:32'),
(1390, 29, 'You don\'t have to fear defeat if you believe it may reveal powers that you didn\'t know you possessed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:01:45'),
(1391, 29, 'Our most profitable lessons are learned from failure, not success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:02:14'),
(1392, 29, 'You don\'t learn to walk by following rules. You learn by doing, and by falling over.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:02:25'),
(1393, 29, 'I honestly think it is better to be a failure at something you love than to be a success at something you hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:02:36'),
(1394, 29, 'A failure establishes only this, that our determination to succeed was not strong enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:02:47'),
(1395, 29, 'There is only one failure in life possible, and that is not to be true to the best one knows.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:02:55'),
(1396, 29, 'However things may seem, no evil thing is success and no good thing is failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:03:04'),
(1397, 29, 'Ambition is the last refuge of the failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:03:13'),
(1398, 29, 'The most important of my discoveries have been suggested to me by failures.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:03:21'),
(1399, 29, 'He that is down needs fear no fall.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:03:32'),
(1400, 29, 'There is no impossibility to him who stands prepared to conquer every hazard. The fearful are the failing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:03:41'),
(1401, 29, 'Failure will never overtake me if my determination to succeed is strong enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:01'),
(1402, 29, 'Every great mistake has a halfway moment, a split second when it can be recalled and perhaps remedied.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:11'),
(1403, 29, 'Just because something doesn\'t do what you planned it to do doesn\'t mean it\'s useless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:20'),
(1404, 29, 'Little minds are tamed and subdued by misfortune; but great minds rise above them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:32'),
(1405, 29, 'The one phrase you can use is that success has a thousand fathers, and failure is an orphan.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:44'),
(1406, 29, 'Don\'t be afraid of missing opportunities. Behind every failure is an opportunity somebody wishes they had missed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:04:53'),
(1407, 29, 'Every failure is a step to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:05:05'),
(1408, 29, 'Men are failures, not because they are stupid, but because they are not sufficiently impassioned.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:05:27'),
(1409, 29, 'Indecision and delays are the parents of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:06:07'),
(1410, 29, 'Never give a man up until he has failed at something he likes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:06:16'),
(1411, 29, 'The only failure one should fear, is not hugging to the purpose they see as best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:06:25'),
(1412, 29, 'I would prefer even to fail with honor than win by cheating.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:06:35'),
(1413, 29, 'Just once it might be instructive to pretend you\'re accepting an award for failure, just to see who you would thank.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:06:49'),
(1414, 29, 'It is not a disgrace to fail. Failing is one of the greatest arts in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:00'),
(1415, 29, 'There is only one thing that makes a dream impossible to achieve: the fear of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:09'),
(1416, 29, 'There can be no real freedom without the freedom to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:18'),
(1417, 29, 'Your most unhappy customers are your greatest source of learning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:29'),
(1418, 29, 'If you want to conquer fear, don\'t sit home and think about it. Go out and get busy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:39'),
(1419, 29, 'Success is often achieved by those who don\'t know that failure is inevitable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:07:51'),
(1420, 29, 'Most great people have attained their greatest success just one step beyond their greatest failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:00'),
(1421, 29, 'Persistent people begin their success where others end in failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:09'),
(1422, 29, 'Try and fail,but don\'t fail to try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:18'),
(1423, 29, 'Failure is in a sense the highway to success, as each discovery of what is false leads us to seek earnestly after what is true.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:27'),
(1424, 29, 'If we achieve our sustainability targets and no one else follows, we will have failed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:36'),
(1425, 29, 'You win only if you aren\'t afraid to lose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:45'),
(1426, 29, 'My downfall raises me to infinite heights.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:08:54'),
(1427, 29, 'You\'re never a loser until you quit trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:09:03'),
(1428, 29, 'Failure seems to be nature\'s plan for preparing us for great responsibilities.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:09:13'),
(1429, 29, 'Excuses are the nails used to build a house of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:09:29'),
(1430, 29, 'I\'d rather be partly great than entirely useless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:09:41'),
(1431, 29, 'Every wrong attempt discarded is another step forward', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:09:50');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(1432, 29, 'Every negative event contains within it the seed of an equal or greater benefit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:01'),
(1433, 29, 'The politician who never made a mistake never made a decision.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:10'),
(1434, 29, 'Our doubts are traitors and make us lose the good we oft might win by fearing to attempt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:20'),
(1435, 29, 'A person who doubts himself is like a man who would enlist in the ranks of his enemies and bear arms against himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:32'),
(1436, 29, 'The only people who never tumble are those who never mount the high wire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:42'),
(1437, 29, 'If you think you can - you can!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:10:52'),
(1438, 29, 'Don\'t fear failure. Not failure, but low aim, is the crime. In great attempts it is glorious even to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:01'),
(1439, 29, 'The only real mistake is the one from which we learn nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:09'),
(1440, 29, 'I\'ve always believed that if you put in the work, the results will come.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:18'),
(1441, 29, 'Inaction breeds doubt and fear. Action breeds confidence and courage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:27'),
(1442, 29, 'My great concern is not whether you have failed, but whether you are content with your failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:37'),
(1443, 29, 'The challenge of education is not to prepare a person for success, but to prepare him for failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:47'),
(1444, 29, 'When life knocks you down you have two choices- stay down or get up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:11:56'),
(1445, 29, 'Show me a thoroughly satisfied man - and I will show you a failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:12:06'),
(1446, 29, 'Think like a queen. A queen is not afraid to fail. Failure is another steppingstone to greatness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:12:19'),
(1447, 29, 'Failures are finger posts on the road to achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:12:44'),
(1448, 29, 'Failure should be our teacher, not our undertaker', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:12:53'),
(1449, 29, 'Being defeated is often a temporary condition. Giving up is what makes it permanent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:03'),
(1450, 29, 'Failing organizations are usually over-managed and under-led.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:12'),
(1451, 29, 'Go on failing. Go on. Only next time, try to fail better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:20'),
(1452, 29, 'I don\'t believe in failure. It is not failure if you enjoyed the process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:29'),
(1453, 29, 'We have forty million reasons for failure, but not a single excuse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:41'),
(1454, 29, 'Not failure, but low aim, is crime.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:13:52'),
(1455, 29, 'Failure doesn\'t mean you are a failure it just means you haven\'t succeeded yet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:02'),
(1456, 29, 'Our business in life is not to succeed, but to continue to fail in good spirits.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:14'),
(1457, 29, '\"Failure\" is not the falling down, but the staying down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:23'),
(1458, 29, 'One must be a god to be able to tell successes from failures without making a mistake.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:32'),
(1459, 29, 'They say President Wilson has blundered. Perhaps he has, but I notice he usually blunders forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:43'),
(1460, 29, 'There is no loneliness greater than the loneliness of a failure. The failure is a stranger in his own house.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:14:52'),
(1461, 29, 'I would sooner fail than not be among the greatest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:15:03'),
(1462, 29, 'My reputation grows with every failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:15:11'),
(1463, 29, 'He who never made a mistake, never made a discovery.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:15:35'),
(1464, 29, 'You cannot climb the ladder of success dressed in the costume of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:15:47'),
(1465, 29, 'We are all failures - at least the best of us are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:15:59'),
(1466, 29, 'Formula for failure: Try to please everybody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:16:13'),
(1467, 29, 'Learn how to fail intelligently.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:16:22'),
(1468, 29, 'Success breeds complacency. Complacency breeds failure. Only the paranoid survive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:16:30'),
(1469, 29, 'Ever tried. Ever failed. No matter. Try Again. Fail again. Fail better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:16:50'),
(1470, 29, 'Failure is the key to success; each mistake teaches us something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:17:01'),
(1471, 29, 'Success isn\'t permanent and failure isn\'t fatal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFailure', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-20 17:17:10'),
(1472, 26, 'A happy marriage is the union of two good forgivers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:11:52'),
(1473, 26, 'What counts in making a happy marriage is not so much how compatible you are but how you deal with incompatibility.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:12:06'),
(1474, 26, 'Love is the master key that opens the gates of happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:12:38'),
(1475, 26, 'Come grow old with me. The best is yet to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:12:52'),
(1476, 26, 'Happy is the man who finds a true friend, and far happier is he who finds that true friend in his wife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:02'),
(1477, 26, 'A successful marriage requires falling in love many times, always with the same person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:14'),
(1478, 26, 'Marriage is not a noun; it\'s a verb. It isn\'t something you get. It\'s something you do. It\'s the way you love your partner every day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:26'),
(1479, 26, 'The best proof of love is trust.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:34'),
(1480, 26, 'Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:43'),
(1481, 26, 'I love you not only for what you are, but for what I am when I am with you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:13:52'),
(1482, 26, 'Coming together is a beginning; keeping together is progress; working together is success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:03'),
(1483, 26, 'Marriage is the triumph of imagination over intelligence. Second marriage is the triumph of hope over experience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:14'),
(1484, 26, 'The most important thing a father can do for his children is to love their mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:24'),
(1485, 26, 'The more time you invest in a marriage, the more valuable it becomes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:35'),
(1486, 26, 'Marriage is too interesting an experiment to be tried only once.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:49'),
(1487, 26, 'The man who says his wife can\'t take a joke, forgets that she took him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:14:59'),
(1488, 26, 'Whenever you\'re wrong, admit it; Whenever you\'re right, shut up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:15:20'),
(1489, 26, 'One thing you learn in a long marriage is how many sneezes to wait before saying, \"Bless you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:15:29'),
(1490, 26, 'Love is an ideal thing, marriage a real thing', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:15:38'),
(1491, 26, 'If you love somebody, let them go, for if they return, they were always yours. And if they don\'t, they never were.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:15:48'),
(1492, 26, 'When you make the sacrifice in marriage, you\'re sacrificing not to each other but to unity in a relationship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:15:57'),
(1493, 26, 'Nobody has ever measured, not even poets, how much the heart can hold.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:06'),
(1494, 26, 'When people tell me they\'ve learned from experience, I tell them the trick is to learn from other people\'s experience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:14'),
(1495, 26, 'You know you\'re in love when you can\'t fall asleep because reality is finally better than your dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:24'),
(1496, 26, 'Let there be spaces in your togetherness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:32'),
(1497, 26, 'It is not a lack of love, but a lack of friendship that makes unhappy marriages.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:41'),
(1498, 26, 'All men make mistakes, but married men find out about them sooner.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:51'),
(1499, 26, 'The first duty of love is to listen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:16:59'),
(1500, 26, 'Let us now set forth one of the fundamental truths about marriage: the wife is in charge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:08'),
(1501, 26, 'We come to love not by finding the perfect person, but by learning to see an imperfect person perfectly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:16'),
(1502, 26, 'Many marriages would be better if the husband and the wife clearly understood that they are on the same side.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:24'),
(1503, 26, 'The husband who wants a happy marriage should learn to keep his mouth shut and his checkbook open.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:33'),
(1504, 26, 'Live so that when your children think of fairness, caring, and integrity, they think of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:40'),
(1505, 26, 'Our greatest weakness lies in giving up. The most certain way to succeed is always to try just one more time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:17:54'),
(1506, 26, 'A good marriage is a contest of generosity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:04'),
(1507, 26, 'Love is that condition in which the happiness of another person is essential to your own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:15'),
(1508, 26, 'Marriage is an adventure, like going to war.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:23'),
(1509, 26, 'When I have learned to love God better than my earthly dearest, I shall love my earthly dearest better than I do now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:33'),
(1510, 26, 'Where there is love there is life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:48'),
(1511, 26, 'As for his secret to staying married: \"My wife tells me that if I ever decide to leave, she is coming with me.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:18:58'),
(1512, 26, 'Chains do not hold a marriage together. It is threads, hundreds of tiny threads, which sew people together through the years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:07'),
(1513, 26, 'How can a woman be expected to be happy with a man who insists on treating her as if she were a perfectly normal human being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:17'),
(1514, 26, 'When a man marries a woman, they become one-the trouble starts when they try to decide which one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:27'),
(1515, 26, 'Marriage has no guarantees. If that\'s what you\'re looking for, go live with a car battery.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:35'),
(1516, 26, 'Before marriage, a man will lie awake thinking about something you said; after marriage , he\'ll fall asleep before you finish saying it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:44'),
(1517, 26, 'Let the wife make the husband glad to come home, and let him make her sorry to see him leave.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:19:52'),
(1518, 26, 'Love does not consist in gazing at each other, but in looking outward together in the same direction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:02'),
(1519, 26, 'The difficulty with marriage is that we fall in love with a personality, but must live with a character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:10'),
(1520, 26, 'All young women begin by believing they can change and reform the men they marry. They can\'t.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:19'),
(1521, 26, 'There is no more lovely, friendly and charming relationship, communion or company than a good marriage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:31'),
(1522, 26, 'Grief can take care if itself, but to get the full value of a joy you must have somebody to divide it with.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:40'),
(1523, 26, 'Don\'t smother each other. No one can grow in the shade.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:20:50'),
(1524, 26, 'The secret of a happy marriage is finding the right person. You know they\'re right if you love to be with them all the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:00'),
(1525, 26, 'A good marriage would be between a blind wife and a deaf husband.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:09'),
(1526, 26, 'When you realize you want to spend the rest of your life with somebody, you want the rest of your life to start as soon as possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:18'),
(1527, 26, 'The secret of a happy marriage remains a secret.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:27'),
(1528, 26, 'The minute I heard my first love story, I started looking for you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:37'),
(1529, 26, 'More marriages might survive if the partners realized that sometimes the better comes after the worse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:47'),
(1530, 26, 'Life is the flower for which love is the honey.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:21:55'),
(1531, 26, 'A good marriage is one which allows for change and growth in the individuals and in the way they express their love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:22:04'),
(1532, 26, 'Before marriage, a girl has to make love to a man to hold him. After marriage, she has to hold him to make love to him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:22:14'),
(1533, 26, 'To avoid mistakes and regrets, always consult your wife before engaging in a flirtation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:22:35'),
(1534, 26, 'Marriage is a wonderful invention: then again, so is a bicycle repair kit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:22:43'),
(1535, 26, 'The hardest-learned lesson: that people have only their kind of love to give, not our kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:22:51'),
(1536, 26, 'Love is the triumph of imagination over intelligence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:01'),
(1537, 26, 'All too often people concentrate on finding the right spouse, little realizing that half of any marriage is being the right spouse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:14'),
(1538, 26, 'Marriage is an attempt to solve problems together which you didn\'t even have when you were on your own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:24'),
(1539, 26, 'There is no remedy for love but to love more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:34'),
(1540, 26, 'A good wife always forgives her husband when she\'s wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:46'),
(1541, 26, 'Marriage is not about age; it\'s about finding the right person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:23:54'),
(1542, 26, 'I am a very committed wife. And I should be committed too - for being married so many times.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:04'),
(1543, 26, 'Never get married in the morning, because you never know who you\'ll meet that night.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:13'),
(1544, 26, 'After marriage, husband and wife become two sides of a coin; they just can\'t face each other, but still they stay together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:22'),
(1545, 26, 'The greatest weakness of most humans is their hesitancy to tell others how much they love them while they\'re alive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:30'),
(1546, 26, 'Marriage should be a duet - when one sings, the other claps.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:39'),
(1547, 26, 'In my house I\'m the boss, my wife is just the decision maker.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:49'),
(1548, 26, 'A good marriage is that in which each appoints the other guardian of his solitude', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:24:59'),
(1549, 26, 'In the end, the love you take is equal to the love you make.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:25:21'),
(1550, 26, 'I love being married. It\'s so great to find that one special person you want to annoy for the rest of your life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:25:30'),
(1551, 26, 'Don\'t marry the person you think you can live with; marry only the individual you think you can\'t live without.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:25:41'),
(1552, 26, 'Love is everything it\'s cracked up to be. It really is worth fighting for, being brave for, risking everything for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:25:57'),
(1553, 26, 'We waste time looking for the perfect lover, instead of creating the perfect love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:05'),
(1554, 26, 'Love is like the wind, you can\'t see it but you can feel it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:14'),
(1555, 26, 'Never go to bed mad. Stay up and fight.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:26'),
(1556, 26, 'Love like there\'s no tomorrow, and if tomorrow comes, love again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:35'),
(1557, 26, 'Marriage is our last, best chance to grow up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:47'),
(1558, 26, 'Keep your eyes wide open before marriage, half shut afterwards.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:26:56'),
(1559, 26, 'Only choose in marriage a man whom you would choose as a friend if he were a woman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:05'),
(1560, 26, 'A journey is like marriage. The certain way to be wrong is to think you control it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:14'),
(1561, 26, 'No married man is genuinely happy if he has to drink worse whisky than he used to drink when he was single.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:23'),
(1562, 26, 'There is only one happiness in this life, to love and be loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:31'),
(1563, 26, 'It is sometimes essential for a husband and a wife to quarrel - they get to know each other better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:41'),
(1564, 26, 'The way to love anything is to realize that it may be lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:27:50'),
(1565, 26, 'Take it from me, marriage isn\'t a word - it\'s a sentence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:28:02'),
(1566, 26, 'All weddings are similar, but every marriage is different.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:28:11'),
(1567, 26, 'Don\'t worry that children never listen to you; worry that they are always watching you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:28:23'),
(1568, 26, 'The great secret of a successful marriage is to treat all disasters as incidents and none of the incidents as disasters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:28:32'),
(1569, 26, 'It is not your love that sustains the marriage, but from now on, the marriage that sustains your love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:28:41'),
(1570, 26, 'Wives are young men\'s mistresses, companions for middle age, and old men\'s nurses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:29:18'),
(1571, 26, 'Dear young people, don\'t be afraid to marry. A faithful and fruitful marriage will bring you happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:29:36'),
(1572, 26, 'Dear young people, don\'t be afraid to marry. A faithful and fruitful marriage will bring you happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:30:53'),
(1573, 26, 'A happy marriage is a long conversation which always seems too short.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:31:17'),
(1574, 26, 'Love is like Pi: natural, irrational, and very important.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:31:35'),
(1575, 26, 'I\'d marry again if I found a man who had fifteen million dollars, would sign over half to me, and guarantee that he\'d be dead within a year.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:31:45'),
(1576, 26, 'An ideal wife is any woman who has an ideal husband.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:31:53'),
(1577, 26, 'Marriage is the only adventure open to the cowardly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:06'),
(1578, 26, 'To love and be loved is to feel the sun from both sides.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:17'),
(1579, 26, 'A dog is much like a married man, obeying his master\'s voice for the sake of his master\'s touch.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:25'),
(1580, 26, 'Marriage is like a golden ring in a chain, whose beginning is a glance and whose ending is eternity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:34'),
(1581, 26, 'My wife has a slight impediment in her speech. Every now and then she stops to breathe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:42'),
(1582, 26, 'A man doesn\'t know what happiness is until he\'s married. By then it\'s too late.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:32:58'),
(1583, 26, 'Never go in a place that you wouldn\'t take your wife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:09'),
(1584, 26, 'grow old with me. the best is yet to be. the last of life for which the first was made.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:17'),
(1585, 26, 'To find someone who will love you for no reason, and to shower that person with reasons, that is the ultimate happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:27'),
(1586, 26, 'The fastest way to improve your relationships is to make others feel important in every way possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:36'),
(1587, 26, 'Where there\'s marriage without love, there will be love without marriage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:45'),
(1588, 26, 'Marriage is the most natural state of man, and therefore the state in which one is most likely to find solid happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:33:56'),
(1589, 26, 'I have yet to hear a man ask for advice on how to combine marriage and a career.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:34:05'),
(1590, 26, 'Bigamy is having one wife too many. Monogamy is the same.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:34:16'),
(1591, 26, 'The secret to having a good marriage is to understand that marriage must be total, it must be permanent, and it must be equal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:34:38'),
(1592, 26, 'We accept the love we think we deserve.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:34:48'),
(1593, 26, 'Often the difference between a successful marriage and a mediocre one consists of leaving about three or four things a day unsaid.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:35:10'),
(1594, 26, 'A man in love is incomplete until he has married. Then he\'s finished.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:35:19'),
(1595, 26, 'I married the first man I ever kissed. When I tell this to my children, they just about throw up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:35:31'),
(1596, 26, 'Marriage is popular because it combines the maximum of temptation with the maximum of opportunity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:35:43'),
(1597, 26, 'More belongs to marriage than four legs in a bed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:35:51'),
(1598, 26, 'I don\'t worry about terrorism. I was married for two years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:01'),
(1599, 26, 'It\'s true what they say - all the good men are married. But it\'s marriage that makes them good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:10'),
(1600, 26, 'Marriage is like twirling a baton, turning hand springs or eating with chopsticks. It looks easy until you try it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:19'),
(1601, 26, 'I have great hopes that we shall love each other all our lives as much as if we had never married at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:29'),
(1602, 26, 'Once a woman has forgiven her man, she must not reheat his sins for breakfast.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:37'),
(1603, 26, 'The most happy marriage I can picture or imagine to myself would be the union of a deaf man to a blind woman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:46'),
(1604, 26, 'Women hope men will change after marriage but they don\'t; men hope women won\'t change but they do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:36:58'),
(1605, 26, 'A man\'s wife has more power over him than the state has.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:05'),
(1606, 26, 'The most happy marriage I can picture or imagine to myself would be the union of a deaf man to a blind woman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:23'),
(1607, 26, 'Women hope men will change after marriage but they don\'t; men hope women won\'t change but they do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:31'),
(1608, 26, 'A man\'s wife has more power over him than the state has.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:40'),
(1609, 26, 'Never get married in college; it\'s hard to get a start if a prospective employer finds you\'ve already made one mistake.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:50'),
(1610, 26, 'All marriages are happy, it\'s living together afterward that\'s tough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:37:58'),
(1611, 26, 'Whatever our souls are made of, his and mine are the same.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:38:11'),
(1612, 26, 'When a man opens a car door for his wife, it\'s either a new car or a new wife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:38:23'),
(1613, 26, 'Marriage, like money, is still with us; and, like money, progressively devalued.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:38:32'),
(1614, 26, 'The man who puts into the marriage only half of what he owns will get that out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:38:43'),
(1615, 26, 'That married couples can live together day after day is a miracle that the Vatican has overlooked.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:38:58'),
(1616, 26, 'A man may be a fool and not know it, but not if he is married.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:39:19'),
(1617, 26, 'Bad marriages don\'t cause infidelity; infidelity causes bad marriages.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:39:39'),
(1618, 26, 'Men who have a pierced ear are better prepared for marriage - they\'ve experienced pain and bought jewelry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:39:58'),
(1619, 26, 'Men who have a pierced ear are better prepared for marriage - they\'ve experienced pain and bought jewelry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:40:20'),
(1620, 26, 'Marriage is give and take. You\'d better give it to her or she\'ll take it anyway.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:40:36'),
(1621, 26, 'A woman seldom asks advice before she has bought her wedding clothes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:40:46'),
(1622, 26, 'Basically my wife was immature. I\'d be at home in the bath and she\'d come in and sink my boats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:40:59'),
(1623, 26, 'To marry unequally is to suffer equally.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:41:11'),
(1624, 26, 'Husbands are like fires - they go out when unattended.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:41:32'),
(1625, 26, 'Where we love is home - home that our feet may leave, but not our hearts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:41:43'),
(1626, 26, 'It is love, not reason, that is stronger than death.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:41:57'),
(1627, 26, 'In the arithmetic of love, one plus one equals everything, and two minus one equals nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:42:20'),
(1628, 26, 'Marriage is like a cage; one sees the birds outside desperate to get in, and those inside equally desperate to get out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:42:29'),
(1629, 26, 'Marriage is like a cage; one sees the birds outside desperate to get in, and those inside equally desperate to get out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:42:43'),
(1630, 26, 'If thou wouldst marry wisely, marry thine equal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:42:52'),
(1631, 26, 'He that said it was not good for man to be alone, placed the celibate amongst the inferior states of perfection.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:43:02'),
(1632, 26, 'Every one who marries goes it blind, more or less.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:43:12'),
(1633, 26, 'Even cohabitation has been corrupted - by marriage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:43:21'),
(1634, 26, 'Young men not ought to marry yet, and old men never ought to marry at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:43:30'),
(1635, 26, 'Marrying for love may be a bit risky, but it is so honest that God can\'t help but smile on it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:44:32'),
(1636, 26, 'How marriage ruins a man! It is as demoralizing as cigarettes, and far more expensive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:44:43'),
(1637, 26, 'Being married is like having somebody permanently in your corner. It feels limitless, not limited.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:44:58'),
(1638, 26, 'Married life teaches one invaluable lesson: to think of things far enough ahead not to say them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:45:11'),
(1639, 26, 'Married life teaches one invaluable lesson: to think of things far enough ahead not to say them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:45:20'),
(1640, 26, 'The majority of husbands remind me of an orangutan trying to play the violin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:45:31'),
(1641, 26, 'Sometimes I wonder if men and women really suit each other. Perhaps they should live next door and just visit now and then.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:45:44'),
(1642, 26, 'A husband is what is left of a lover, after the nerve has been extracted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:45:54'),
(1643, 26, 'My husband and I have never considered divorce... murder sometimes, but never divorce.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:04'),
(1644, 26, 'Love requires a willingness to die; marriage, a willingness to live.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:15'),
(1645, 26, 'The concept of two people living together for 25 years without a serious dispute suggests a lack of spirit only to be admired in sheep.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:25'),
(1646, 26, 'Getting married is a lot like getting into a tub of hot water. After you get used to it, it ain\'t so hot.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:37'),
(1647, 26, 'We always hold hands. If I let go, she shops.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:46'),
(1648, 26, 'Marriage is a book of which the first chapter is written in poetry and the remaining chapters in prose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:46:55'),
(1649, 26, 'If you want to read about love and marriage, you\'ve got to buy two separate books.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:47:04'),
(1650, 26, 'Love is not something people feel, but something people try to express no matter how they feel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:47:18'),
(1651, 26, 'Love one another, but make not a bond of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:03'),
(1652, 26, 'This is a way to kill a wife with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:13'),
(1653, 26, 'An object in possession seldom retains the same charm that it had in pursuit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:21'),
(1654, 26, 'If you live to be a hundred, I want to live to be a hundred minus one day so I never have to live without you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:31'),
(1655, 26, 'Bachelors have consciences, married men have wives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:40'),
(1656, 26, 'A bad marriage is like an electrical thrilling machine: it makes you dance, but you can\'t let go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:48:52'),
(1657, 26, 'Marriage is neither heaven nor hell, it is simply purgatory.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:49:19'),
(1658, 26, 'No man should marry until he has studied anatomy and dissected at least one woman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:49:32'),
(1659, 26, 'When a wife has a good husband, it is easily seen on her face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:49:41'),
(1660, 26, 'Marriage, like a submarine, is only safe if you get all the way inside.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:49:54'),
(1661, 26, 'It\'s not beauty but fine qualities, my girl, that keep a husband.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:50:10'),
(1662, 26, 'Men have a much better time of it than women. For one thing, they marry later; for another thing, they die earlier.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:50:24'),
(1663, 26, 'I\'ve had bad luck with both my wives. The first one left me and the second one didn\'t.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:50:34'),
(1664, 26, 'Even with all its problems, I will support marriage as an institution until something better comes along.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:51:12'),
(1665, 26, 'I\'ve sometimes thought of marrying - and then I\'ve thought again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:52:06'),
(1666, 26, 'Keep your eyes wide open before marriage, and halfway closed there after.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:52:16'),
(1667, 26, 'Love is an act of endless forgiveness, a tender look which becomes a habit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:52:31'),
(1668, 26, 'Those Marriages generally abound most with Love and Constancy, that are preceded by a long Courtship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:52:44'),
(1669, 26, 'Marriage is a bribe to make a housekeeper think she\'s a householder.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:52:53'),
(1670, 26, 'Politics doesn\'t make strange bedfellows - marriage does.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:02'),
(1671, 26, 'There is no substitute for the comfort supplied by the utterly taken-for-granted relationship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:11'),
(1672, 26, 'Marriage is about the most expensive way for the average man to get laundry done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:20'),
(1673, 26, 'Love is an ideal thing, marriage a real thing; a confusion of the real with the ideal never goes unpunished.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:30'),
(1674, 26, 'What a happy and holy fashion it is that those who love one another should rest on the same pillow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:39'),
(1675, 26, 'Love is often the fruit of marriage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:50'),
(1676, 26, 'Hanging and wiving goes by destiny.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMarriage', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-21 16:53:59'),
