(2165, 25, 'When your mind is besieged by some inauspicious thoughts, you can bring the sunshine into your life by staying calm!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:21:35'),
(2166, 25, 'Sunshine, it’s the Celt wanting a little reassurance that I haven’t eaten you or anything. (Vane)', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:21:48'),
(2167, 25, 'He needed fresh air and sunshine. A walk in the woods and afterward a good book to read by the fire. Yeah, that was the life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:22:10'),
(2168, 25, 'I was born and raised on a Carolina sea island and I carried the sunshine of the low-country, inked in dark gold, on my back and shoulders.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:22:23'),
(2169, 25, 'Prosperity suits some people, and they blossom best in a glow of sunshine; others need the shade, and are the sweeter for a touch of frost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:22:32'),
(2170, 25, 'Some people are so much sunshine to the square inch.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:22:43'),
(2171, 25, 'Face your fears, Halt had always thought him, and more often than not they fade like mist in the sunshine', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:22:53'),
(2172, 25, 'His words are nothing more than mist and sunshine, impossible to hold down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:23:01'),
(2173, 25, 'Look. Let’s just say he’s in Tabitha’s line of work. Okay? (Selena) Ladies’ lingerie? He hardly looks the type to sell that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:23:13'),
(2174, 25, 'Go into the sunshine and be happy with what you see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:23:22'),
(2175, 25, 'I think it might honestly be time for the Sunshine State to officially change its motto to the Worst State.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:23:31'),
(2176, 25, 'Play is as necessary to the perfect development of a child as sunshine is to the perfect development of a plant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:23:46'),
(2177, 25, 'Ah, love, - you are my unutterable blessing.....I am in full sunshine now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:24:00'),
(2178, 25, 'When I filter the sunshine in my life, I bask in the light of a transforming and inspiring reality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:24:08'),
(2179, 25, 'I\'m Little Miss Sunshine, I sprinkle it around.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:24:20'),
(2180, 25, 'You are the only warmth in my heart. The only sunshine my winter has ever known', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:24:39'),
(2181, 25, 'A joyful heart is like the sunshine of God\'s love, the hope of eternal happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:24:56'),
(2182, 25, 'Death is the chillness that precedes the dawn; We shudder for a moment, then awake In the broad sunshine of the other life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:10'),
(2183, 25, 'Love is like sunshine.  Sometimes you have to get burned to know you were there.  I want to know that I\'m here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:19'),
(2184, 25, 'Let us open up our natures, throw wide the doors of our hearts and let in the sunshine of good will and kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:29'),
(2185, 25, 'This not my talent to conceal my thoughts, Or carry smiles and sunshine in my face, When discontent sits heavy at my heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:40'),
(2186, 25, 'Call me Sunshine, pussy spread like the rainbow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:49'),
(2187, 25, 'O yellow eye, let me be sick with your heat, let me be feverish and frowning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:25:58'),
(2188, 25, 'Make all good men your well-wishers, and then, in the years\' steady sifting, Some of them turn into friends. Friends are the sunshine of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:26:07'),
(2189, 25, 'If the Lord should once more give us sunshine and I do not give you enough fighting, I will never ask you to come out again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:26:15'),
(2190, 25, 'Let there be sunshine, let there be rain, let the broken hearted love again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:26:40'),
(2191, 25, 'I beg your pardon, I never promised you a rose garden. Along with sunshine, there\'s got to be a little rain sometime.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:27:13'),
(2192, 25, 'What are you doing son, you\'re gonna drive yourself insane. You\'ll never find the sunshine, when you\'re following the rain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:27:23'),
(2193, 25, 'Every man\'s the same, he wants the sunshine in his name.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:27:31'),
(2194, 25, 'Take my hand and we\'ll go riding through the sunshine from above. We\'ll find happiness together in the summer skies of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:27:49'),
(2195, 25, 'Do not allow obligation or immediacy to bind you to physical things or specific actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:27:57'),
(2196, 25, 'Sometimes the things you really want sneak in the back door. Notice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:08'),
(2197, 25, 'Sunshine on the water looks so lovely', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:17'),
(2198, 25, 'Instead of living in the sunshine of God\'s forgiveness through Christ, we tend to live under an overcast sky of guilt most of the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:29'),
(2199, 25, 'Pleasantly, between the pelting showers, the sunshine gushes down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:39'),
(2200, 25, 'You are the sunshine of my life! Thanks for brightening my world with the warmth of your Love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:47'),
(2201, 25, 'Intelligence is the shadow of objective truth. How can the shadow vie with sunshine?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:28:56'),
(2202, 25, 'I\'ll spend my mornings at the sunshine café.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:05'),
(2203, 25, 'Art is as natural as sunshine and as vital as nourishment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:13'),
(2204, 25, 'Thunderstorms are as much our friends as the sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:22'),
(2205, 25, 'We\'ll let the sunshine in and shine on us, because today we\'re happy and tomorrow we\'ll be even happier.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:31'),
(2206, 25, 'For the recuperation of body and mind, there is nothing better than natural therapy - sand, sunshine and surf.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:43'),
(2207, 25, 'If I saw \'Virgin Suicides\' or \'Eternal Sunshine,\' I\'m so proud to be in those movies. They are such great movies. I felt so free on those sets.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:29:55'),
(2208, 25, 'When you do not know what to do or which way to turn, smile. This will relax your mind and let the sunshine of happiness into your soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:30:32'),
(2209, 25, 'I feel like I\'ve been split open and stuffed with sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:30:46'),
(2210, 25, 'Pure air, good water, sunshine, the beautiful surroundings of nature...these are God\'s means for restoring the sick to health.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:30:54'),
(2211, 25, 'I built with my own hands ... a large swimming-pool which was filtered to limpidity and could be heated to supplement our fickle sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:31:04'),
(2212, 25, 'A Christian never falls asleep in the fire or in the water, but grows drowsy in the sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:31:16'),
(2213, 25, 'By all means never fail to get all the sunshine and fresh air you can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:31:53'),
(2214, 25, 'The harvest of the Lord’s field is seldom ripened by sunshine only. It must go through its days of wind, rain and storm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:01'),
(2215, 25, 'The shadow proves the sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:09'),
(2216, 25, 'Around us, life bursts with miracles, a glass of water, a ray of sunshine, a leaf, a caterpillar, a flower, laughter, raindrops.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:22'),
(2217, 25, 'The sunshine is a glorious birth; But yet I know, where\'er I go, That there hath passed away a glory from the earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:32'),
(2218, 25, 'Good humor is the sunshine of the mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:42');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(2219, 25, 'It is never difficult to distinguish between a Scotsman with a grievance and a ray of sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:32:54'),
(2220, 25, 'Character is blazing sunshine in the soul\'s abode, the body.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:33:03'),
(2221, 25, 'Sunshine, lollipops and rainbows, everything that\'s wonderful, Is sure to come your way', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 04:33:12'),
(2222, 25, 'I have sunshine in my heart regardless of conditions around me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:06:41'),
(2223, 25, 'Oh, sunshine, I whisper and smile gently. Haven\'t you figured out that I\'m completely in love with you?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:06:50'),
(2224, 25, 'Buttercups, bright eyed and bold, hold their chalices of gold to catch the sunshine and the dew.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:06:59'),
(2225, 25, 'The weather varies between heavy fog and pale sunshine; My thoughts follow the exact same process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:07:09'),
(2226, 25, 'On bravely through the sunshine and the showers! Time hath his work to do, and we have ours.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:07:22'),
(2227, 25, 'Working in the tea fields under a beautiful sunshine is the dream of all the miners.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:07:37'),
(2228, 25, 'Radio, books, sports-so many means to spend time, but what I like most is the leafy sunshine amidst the Debdaru.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:07:53'),
(2229, 25, 'I stay out of the sunshine and away from people as much as possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:08:09'),
(2230, 25, 'I\'m a foot soldier in the war on Christmas. And the war on puppies and sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:08:18'),
(2231, 25, 'If there were no valleys of sadness and death, we could never really appreciate the sunshine of happiness on the mountain top.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:08:34'),
(2232, 25, 'Sunshine can burn you, food can poison you, words can condemn you, pictures can insult you; music cannot punish - only bless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:08:58'),
(2233, 25, 'The dinner-hour is the summer of the day: full of sunshine, I grant; but not like the mellow autumn of supper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:09:11'),
(2234, 25, 'Lives that flash in sunshine, and lives that are born in tears, receive their hue from circumstances.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:09:23'),
(2235, 25, 'But the sunshine aye shall light the sky, As round and round we run; And the truth shall ever come uppermost, And justice shall be done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:09:39'),
(2236, 25, 'You can\'t always be like \'sunshine and roses\'. I like a little bit of darkness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:09:51'),
(2237, 25, 'If you\'re spreading light, you don\'t care where the sunshine goes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:10:13'),
(2238, 25, 'When you are happy, you feel the sunshine even inside the fog; when you are unhappy, you feel the fog even in the sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:10:32'),
(2239, 25, 'You can be a flower in somebody\'s garden or a pig or the sunshine or a crow or a nightingale! Be something nice in someone else\'s garden.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:10:43'),
(2240, 25, 'I\'ve got sunshine on a cloudy day', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:10:53'),
(2241, 25, 'When we cannot see the sunshine of God\'s face, it is blessed to cower down beneath the shadow of his wings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:11:01'),
(2242, 25, 'If you look toward the sunshine, you will never see the shadows.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:11:13'),
(2243, 25, 'Mama says that, happiness is from magic rays of sunshine that come down when you\'re feeling blue.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:11:33'),
(2244, 25, 'I\'m a massive fan of Sunshine. Oh my God, I love that film.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:11:44'),
(2245, 25, 'Let us then blend everything: love, religion, genius, with sunshine, perfume, music, and poetry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:12:03'),
(2246, 25, 'Much too oft we make life gloomy-- When happy we might be, If we gathered more of sunshine, And not dark shadows see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:12:13'),
(2247, 25, 'If our love were but more simple, We should take Him at His word; And our lives would be all sunshine In the sweetness of the Lord.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:12:24'),
(2248, 25, 'The current fad in art, is to shock people or appear \'different\'... My goal is to help people find the rays of sunshine in an often dark world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:12:38'),
(2249, 25, 'On dreary night let lusty sunshine fall.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:12:45'),
(2250, 25, 'Portraits are to daily faces As an evening west To a fine, pedantic sunshine In a satin vest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:02'),
(2251, 25, 'I work even in the middle of the day, in the full sunshine, and I enjoy it like a cicada.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:13'),
(2252, 25, 'There will be plenty of blame to go around but if you take credit for the sunshine, you also get blamed for the rain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:26'),
(2253, 25, 'Life is a blend of laughter and tears, a combination of rain and sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:35'),
(2254, 25, 'Thine to work as well as pray, Clearing thorny wrongs away; Plucking up the weeds of sin, Letting heaven\'s warm sunshine in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:46'),
(2255, 25, 'Without haste! without rest! Bind the motto to thy breast! Bear it with thee as a spell; Storm or sunshine , guard it well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:13:55'),
(2256, 25, 'I want to paint sunshine and burning golden leaves and blue waters, and laughing faces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:14:11'),
(2257, 25, 'Merciful Father, I will not complain. I know that the sunshine shall follow the rain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:14:19'),
(2258, 25, 'I usually just wear black so my shoes and my socks are my rays of sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:15:30'),
(2259, 25, 'Strive to have sunshine in our hearts each day. It will greatly improve our outlook.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:15:39'),
(2260, 25, 'The tempests of youth are mingled with days of brilliant sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:15:57'),
(2261, 25, 'It\'s a perfect day here in Australia, glorious blue sunshine', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:16:11'),
(2262, 25, 'When every brake hath found its note, and sunshine smiles in every flower.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:16:30'),
(2263, 25, 'Eyes that displace the neighbor diamond, and outface that sunshine by their own sweet grace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:16:39'),
(2264, 25, 'Memories were like sunshine. They warmed you up and left a pleasant glow, but you couldn\'t hold them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:16:55'),
(2265, 25, 'Some people seemed to get all sunshine, and some all shadow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:17:05'),
(2266, 25, 'If he was winter, I was summer. If I was sunshine, he was night. A dark and stormy one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:17:16'),
(2267, 25, 'If he was winter, I was summer. If I was sunshine, he was night. A dark and stormy one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:17:42'),
(2268, 25, 'And I am in love with light. Lock me in the sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:18:12'),
(2269, 25, 'You stink like a faerie, all flowers and sunshine and evil manipulation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:18:35'),
(2270, 25, 'In the dark beside me, she smelled of sweat and sunshine and vanilla.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:19:02'),
(2271, 25, 'The Seeker needed a nice long lifetime eating sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:19:11'),
(2272, 25, 'I always knew that someday I would once again feel the grass under my feet and walk in the sunshine as a free man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:19:22'),
(2273, 25, 'It was June, and the world smelled of roses. The sunshine was like powdered gold over the grassy hillside.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:19:37'),
(2274, 25, 'When you\'ve only got one little shimmer of sunshine, you capture it best you can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-24 15:19:59'),
