(2499, 24, 'Two minds with but a single thought, two hearts that beat as one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:54:18'),
(2500, 24, 'You know you\'re in love when you can\'t fall asleep because reality is finally better than your dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:54:27'),
(2501, 24, 'If I had a flower for every time I thought of you...I could walk through my garden forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:54:37'),
(2502, 24, 'I love you not only for what you are, but for what I am when I am with you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:54:47'),
(2503, 24, 'Don\'t be surprised if I love you for all that you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:55:05'),
(2504, 24, 'But you\'ve slipped under my skin, invaded my blood and seized my heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:55:29'),
(2505, 24, 'Love grows by giving. The love we give away is the only love we keep. The only way to retain love is to give it away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:55:43'),
(2506, 24, 'If I know what love is, it is because of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:56:01'),
(2507, 24, 'No one can deny, this love I have inside, and I\'ll give it all to you, my endless love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:56:17'),
(2508, 24, 'You don\'t love someone for their looks, or their clothes, or for their fancy car, but because they sing a song only you can hear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:56:31'),
(2509, 24, 'To look into that persons eyes and find yourself so completely lost in another world, a world full of absolute comfort and happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:56:42'),
(2510, 24, 'True love will triumph in the end—which may or may not be a lie, but if it is a lie, it\'s the most beautiful lie we have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:56:52'),
(2511, 24, 'We don\'t need to explain our love. We only need to show it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:01'),
(2512, 24, 'Love recognizes no barriers. It jumps hurdles, leaps fences, penetrates walls to arrive at its destination full of hope.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:10'),
(2513, 24, 'Forever is not a word...rather a place where two lovers go when true love takes them there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:18'),
(2514, 24, 'For it was not into my ear you whispered, but into my heart. It was not my lips you kissed, but my soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:28'),
(2515, 24, 'When the world outside my arms is pulling us apart, press your lips to mine and hold me with your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:37'),
(2516, 24, 'Meet me where the sky touches the sea. Wait for me where the world begins.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:46'),
(2517, 24, 'Love is not a business. It\'s not a transaction. It\'s not an exchange or something you get for doing something it\'s not a trade. It\'s a gift!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:57:56'),
(2518, 24, 'I see you everywhere, in the stars, in the river, to me you\'re everything that exists; the reality of everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:06'),
(2519, 24, 'There is never a time or place for true love. It happens accidentally, in a heartbeat, in a single flashing, throbbing moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:15'),
(2520, 24, 'I ask you to pass through life at my side—to be my second self, and best earthly companion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:23'),
(2521, 24, 'When I saw you I fell in love. And you smiled because you knew.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:32'),
(2522, 24, 'I\'ve looked around enough to know that you\'re the one I want to go through time with.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:49'),
(2523, 24, 'Morning without you is a dwindled dawn.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:58:57'),
(2524, 24, 'There may be a brighter star. But through my eyes the light of you is all I see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:05'),
(2525, 24, 'It is love alone that gives worth to all things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:15'),
(2526, 24, 'I needed to see you. And touch you. And just... know', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:24'),
(2527, 24, 'Suddenly I found you and the spirit in me sings, Don\'t have to look no further, You\'re the soul of many things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:32'),
(2528, 24, 'Sunsets are so beautiful that they almost seem as if we were looking through the gates of Heaven.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:43'),
(2529, 24, 'One day, in your search for happiness, you discover a partner by your side, and you realize that your happiness has come to help you search.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 05:59:54'),
(2530, 24, 'And I’d choose you; in a hundred lifetimes, in a hundred worlds, in any version of reality, I’d find you and I’d choose you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:03'),
(2531, 24, 'You are my glue. Without you, I\'d be nothing but broken pieces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:11'),
(2532, 24, 'Love, and you shall be loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:20'),
(2533, 24, 'Unforgettable in every way, and forever more, that\'s how you\'ll stay.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:30'),
(2534, 24, 'The only regret I will have in dying is if it is not for love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:40'),
(2535, 24, 'With every breath, I\'m deeper in you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:49'),
(2536, 24, 'You were made perfectly to be loved - and surely I have loved you, in the idea of you, my whole life long.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:00:58'),
(2537, 24, 'Once upon a time there was a boy who loved a girl, and her laughter was a question he wanted to spend his whole life answering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:01:07'),
(2538, 24, 'Holding you, I held everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:01:29'),
(2539, 24, 'Have a heart that never hardens, and a temper that never tires, and a touch that never hurts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:01:38'),
(2540, 24, 'Whatever our souls are made of, his and mine are the same.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:01:47'),
(2541, 24, 'Your lips are my persuasion, your love will be my cure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:01:56'),
(2542, 24, 'Romance is the glamour which turns the dust of everyday life into a golden haze.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:04'),
(2543, 24, 'All I\'ve ever wanted was to be near you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:16'),
(2544, 24, 'Love him and let him love you. Do you think anything else under heaven really matters?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:23'),
(2545, 24, 'Be thou the rainbow in the storms of life. The evening beam that smiles the clouds away, and tints tomorrow with prophetic ray.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:32'),
(2546, 24, 'If you were a star you\'d be the one I\'m searching for', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:42'),
(2547, 24, 'Love is the beauty of the soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:02:51'),
(2548, 24, 'Only passions, great passions, can elevate the soul to great things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:00'),
(2549, 24, 'I loved you like a man loves a woman he never touches, only writes to, keeps little photographs of.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:08'),
(2550, 24, 'When someone loves you, the way they say your name is different. You know that your name is safe in their mouth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:16'),
(2551, 24, 'My nightmares are usually about losing you. I\'m okay once I realize you\'re here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:26'),
(2552, 24, 'Even in winter it shall be green in my heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:45'),
(2553, 24, 'How bold one gets when one is sure of being loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:03:54'),
(2554, 24, 'Soul meets soul on lovers\' lips.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:04:03'),
(2555, 24, 'When you look at me, when you think of me, I am in paradise.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:04:13'),
(2556, 24, 'I will love you unconditionally .', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:04:24'),
(2557, 24, 'Every atom of your flesh is as dear to me as my own: in pain and sickness it would still be dear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:04:35'),
(2558, 24, 'Then I realize what it is. It\'s him. Something about him makes me feel like I am about to fall. Or turn to liquid. Or burst into flames.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:05:11'),
(2559, 24, 'Now join your hands, and with your hands your hearts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:05:21'),
(2560, 24, 'So, I love you because the entire universe conspired to help me find you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:05:46'),
(2561, 24, 'I love thee, I love thee with a love that shall not die. Till the sun grows cold and the stars grow old.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:05:55'),
(2562, 24, 'Not one word, not one gesture of yours shall I, could I, ever forget.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:08'),
(2563, 24, 'Love is always open arms. If you close your arms about love you will find that you are left holding only yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:22'),
(2564, 24, 'Love is a promise, love is a souvenir, once given never forgotten, never let it disappear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:31'),
(2565, 24, 'Remember tonight... for it is the beginning of always.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:40'),
(2566, 24, 'He stepped down, trying not to look long at her, as if she were the sun, yet he saw her, like the sun, even without looking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:49'),
(2567, 24, 'Did my heart love till now? forswear it, sight! For I ne\'er saw true beauty till this night.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:06:59'),
(2568, 24, 'Find me now. Before someone else does.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:09'),
(2569, 24, 'Eventually soulmates meet, for they have the same hiding place.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:17'),
(2570, 24, 'Where there is love there is life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:27'),
(2571, 24, 'We are each of us angels with only one wing, and we can only fly by embracing one another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:37'),
(2572, 24, 'I wanted someone to love who would stay: stay and be there, always.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:46'),
(2573, 24, 'Sometimes love blinds us, other times it let\'s us see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:07:55'),
(2574, 24, 'Nobody has ever measured, not even poets, how much the heart can hold.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:04'),
(2575, 24, 'ever thine, ever mine, ever ours', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:12'),
(2576, 24, 'In order to love simply, it is necessary to know how to show love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:21'),
(2577, 24, 'Love is a canvas furnished by Nature and embroidered by imagination.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:39'),
(2578, 24, 'Some find it in their lovers eyes, who can deny the joy it brings. When you\'ve found that special thing, you\'re flying without wings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:48'),
(2579, 24, 'My thoughts and wishes are all that surrounds, mysteries hold you then fly you away. You know you are my life, my lady of dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:08:58'),
(2580, 24, 'Love doesn\'t just sit there, like a stone; it has to be made, like bread, remade all the time, made new.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:10'),
(2581, 24, 'There is no remedy for love but to love more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:20'),
(2582, 24, 'The real lover is the man who can thrill you by kissing your forehead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:30'),
(2583, 24, 'What the world really needs is more love and less paper work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:39'),
(2584, 24, 'If you say my eyes are beautiful, it\'s because they are looking at you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:49'),
(2585, 24, 'What will survive of us is love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:09:57'),
(2586, 24, 'You pierce my soul. I am half agony, half hope...I have loved none but you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:10:06'),
(2587, 24, 'My creed is love and you are its only tenet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:10:16'),
(2588, 24, 'Life is the flower for which love is the honey.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:10:26'),
(2589, 24, 'This is my dream, It is my own dream, I dreamt it. I dreamt that my hair was kempt. Then I dreamt that my true love unkempt it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:10:35'),
(2590, 24, 'Plant your love and let it grow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:10:45'),
(2591, 24, 'I like the feel of your name on my lips.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:12:05'),
(2592, 24, 'Kisses are a better fate than wisdom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:12:15'),
(2593, 24, 'Immature love says: \'I love you because I need you.\' Mature love says \'I need you because I love you.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:12:28'),
(2594, 24, 'With you, I would walk anywhere', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:12:39'),
(2595, 24, 'Don\'t pursue a heart that you\'re not ready to be loyal to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:12:49'),
(2596, 24, 'A kiss is a lovely trick designed by nature to stop speech when words become superfluous.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:08'),
(2597, 24, 'I am a romantic, but I do put up a barrier around myself, so it is hard for people to get in and to know the real me', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:21'),
(2598, 24, 'Lovers don\'t finally meet somewhere. They\'re in each other all along.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:30'),
(2599, 24, 'Wise men say only fools rush in. But I can\'t help falling in love with you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:40'),
(2600, 24, 'If I eat a huge meal and I can get the girl to rub my belly, I think that\'s about as romantic as I can think of.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:49'),
(2601, 24, 'I want to do to you what spring does with the cherry trees.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:13:58'),
(2602, 24, 'Love does not consist in gazing at each other, but in looking outward together in the same direction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:14:08'),
(2603, 24, 'Love must be as much a light as it is a flame.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:14:16'),
(2604, 24, 'The arms of love encompass you with your present, your past, your future, the arms of love gather you together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:14:32'),
(2605, 24, 'I took a chance with my heart and I feel it taking over', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:14:42'),
(2606, 24, 'We loved with a love that was more than love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:14:55'),
(2607, 24, 'But in the garden of simple, where all of us are nameless, you were never anything but beautiful to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:15:04'),
(2608, 24, 'I\'d cut up my heart for you to wear if you wanted it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:15:14'),
(2609, 24, 'Sometimes people don\'t understand the promises they\'re making when they make them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:15:22'),
(2610, 24, 'Where love is concerned, too much is not even enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:15:30'),
(2611, 24, 'You\'re a marshmallow. Soft and sweet and when you get heated up you go all gooey and delicious.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:15:44'),
(2612, 24, 'Just stay alive, no matter what occurs! I will find you. No matter how long it takes, no matter how far. I will find you!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:01'),
(2613, 24, 'I never loved you any more than I do, right this second. And I\'ll never love you any less than I do, right this second.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:09'),
(2614, 24, 'Grace was in all her steps, heaven in her eye, in every gesture dignity and love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:17'),
(2615, 24, 'Men always want to be a woman\'s first love - women like to be a man\'s last romance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:25'),
(2616, 24, 'Love is being stupid together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:34'),
(2617, 24, 'But true love is a durable fire, In the mind ever burning, Never sick, never old, never dead, From itself never turning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:43'),
(2618, 24, 'I have enjoyed the happiness of the world; I have loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:16:52'),
(2619, 24, 'When you realize you want to spend the rest of your life with somebody, you want the rest of your life to start as soon as possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:03'),
(2620, 24, 'We were together. I forget the rest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:11'),
(2621, 24, 'As he read, I fell in love the way you fall asleep: slowly, and then all at once.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:21'),
(2622, 24, 'The more I think about it, the more I realize there is nothing more artistic than to love others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:31'),
(2623, 24, 'Tell me who admires and loves you, and I will tell you who you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:40'),
(2624, 24, 'Nothing prepared me for your smile', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:49'),
(2625, 24, 'Love is an act of faith.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:17:57'),
(2626, 24, 'Love Is Stronger Than Pride', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:18:07'),
(2627, 24, 'Each time you happen to me all over again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:18:15'),
(2628, 24, 'My life has been awaiting you. Your footfall was my own heart\'s beat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:18:24'),
(2629, 24, 'What I feel for you seems less of earth and more of a cloudless heaven.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:18:35'),
(2630, 24, 'In vain have I struggled. It will not do. My feelings will not be repressed. You must allow me to tell you how ardently I admire and love you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:18:57'),
(2631, 24, 'Journeys end in lovers meeting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:19:10'),
(2632, 24, 'Love to me has meant different things at different junctures of my life. I\'m not a hopeless romantic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:19:19'),
(2633, 24, 'Love of my life, I love you so. Love of my life, don\'t ever go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:19:28'),
(2634, 24, 'If music be the food of love, play on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:20:03'),
(2635, 24, 'Surely the stars are images of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:20:14'),
(2636, 24, 'My heart is broke, but I have some glue, help me inhale and mend it with you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:20:22'),
(2637, 24, 'When you know my love, my love will warm you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:20:49'),
(2638, 24, 'Sometimes I can\'t see myself when I\'m with you. I can only just see you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:02'),
(2639, 24, 'Love makes the greatest pleasures and most sensitive misfortunes of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:11'),
(2640, 24, 'Love is like a friendship caught on fire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:21'),
(2641, 24, 'There is always something left to love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:29'),
(2642, 24, 'You\'re my special angel, sent from up above. The Lord smiled down on me, and sent an angel to love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:38'),
(2643, 24, 'Love is a smoke made with the fume of sighs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:46'),
(2644, 24, 'I\'m not a smart man, but I know what love is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:21:56'),
(2645, 24, 'It had to teach her to think of love as a state of grace: not the means to anything but the alpha and omega, an end it itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:22:36'),
(2646, 24, 'There is a garden in her eyes, where roses and white lilies flow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:22:44'),
(2647, 24, 'You don\'t even have to ask twice, you could have my heart or we could share it like the last slice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:22:53'),
(2648, 24, 'Love does not begin and end the way we seem to think it does. Love is a battle, love is a war; love is a growing up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:04'),
(2649, 24, 'Love and you shall be loved. All love is mathematically just, as much as two sides of an algebraic equation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:13'),
(2650, 24, 'Honor the ocean of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:22'),
(2651, 24, 'A successful marriage requires falling in love many times, always with the same person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:33'),
(2652, 24, 'I love thee to the depth and breadth and height my soul can reach.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:43'),
(2653, 24, 'The real lover is the man who can thrill you just by touching your head or smiling into your eyes - or just by staring into space.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:23:52'),
(2654, 24, 'What light through yonder window breaks?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:02'),
(2655, 24, 'Sometimes two people stay together for the sake of the kids - two kids who sat under a full moon and pledged to be forever true.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:10'),
(2656, 24, 'There is no greater glory than to die for love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:21'),
(2657, 24, 'You\'re nothing short of my everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:30'),
(2658, 24, 'Gravitation is not responsible for people falling in love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:39'),
(2659, 24, 'You\'re the kiss that puts my soul at ease.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:24:48'),
(2660, 24, 'we would be together and have our books and at night be warm in bed together with the windows open and the stars bright.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:25:18'),
(2661, 24, 'When I look at you girl, I see a true work of art. So many beautiful things coming in one little heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:25:30'),
(2662, 24, 'To love abundantly is to live abundantly, and to love forever is to live forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:25:40'),
(2663, 24, 'I will always be the hopeless romantic, more often pathetic than heroic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:25:49'),
(2664, 24, 'I stare to memorize your face, to kiss you in my mind, love you all the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:25:58'),
(2665, 24, 'It\'s one thing to fall in love. It\'s another to feel someone else fall in love with you, and to feel a responsibility toward that love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:07'),
(2666, 24, 'If I love you, is that a fact or a weapon?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:16'),
(2667, 24, 'I\'ll always thank the Lord when my working day is through, I get my sweet reward to be alone with you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:25'),
(2668, 24, 'A tragedy, when a mature mind and a romantic heart are in the same body.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:34'),
(2669, 24, 'This better to have loved and lost than never to have loved at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:50'),
(2670, 24, 'You don\'t get to choose if you get hurt in this world...but you do have some say in who hurts you. I like my choices.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:26:59'),
(2671, 24, 'I want everyone to meet you. You\'re my favorite person of all time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:27:10'),
(2672, 24, 'I\'ll be a poet, and you\'ll be poetry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:27:20'),
(2673, 24, 'She was ready to deny the existence of space and time rather than admit that love might not be eternal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:27:29'),
(2674, 24, 'I\'ve spent a life time waiting for the right time, now that you\'re near, the time is here at last.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:27:37'),
(2675, 24, 'You say you\'re not special because the world doesn\'t know about you, but that\'s an insult to me. I know about you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 06:27:46'),
(2676, 23, 'Good teams become great ones when the members trust each other enough to surrender the Me for the We.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:21:57'),
(2677, 23, 'Coming together is a beginning; keeping together is progress; working together is success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:22:08'),
(2678, 23, 'The strength of the team is each individual member. The strength of each member is the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:22:21'),
(2679, 23, 'Talent wins games, but teamwork and intelligence wins championships.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:22:30'),
(2680, 23, 'Basketball is a beautiful game when the five players on the court play with one heartbeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:22:40'),
(2681, 23, 'I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can\'t accept not trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:22:53'),
(2682, 23, 'The best teams have chemistry. They communicate with each other and they sacrifice personal glory for a common goal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:03'),
(2683, 23, 'Alone we can do so little; together we can do so much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:12'),
(2684, 23, 'Some people want it to happen, some wish it would happen, others make it happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:22'),
(2685, 23, 'Just play. Have fun. Enjoy the game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:31'),
(2686, 23, 'The secret of winning is working more as a team, less as individuals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:46'),
(2687, 23, 'One man can be a crucial ingredient on a team, but one man cannot make a team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:23:56'),
(2688, 23, 'To me, teamwork is the beauty of our sport, where you have five acting as one. You become selfless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:04'),
(2689, 23, 'Individual commitment to a group effort - that is what makes a team work, a company work, a society work, a civilization work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:13'),
(2690, 23, 'If you run into a wall, don\'t turn around and give up. Figure out how to climb it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:24'),
(2691, 23, 'My attitude is that if you push me towards something that you think is a weakness, then I will turn that perceived weakness into a strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:39'),
(2692, 23, 'The way a team plays as a whole determines its success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:49'),
(2693, 23, 'Always turn a negative situation into a positive situation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:24:59'),
(2694, 23, 'I\'ve always believed that if you put in the work, the results will come.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:25:08'),
(2695, 23, 'Teamwork doesn\'t come naturally. It must be taught.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:25:18'),
(2696, 23, 'Teamwork is the ability to work together toward a common vision.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:25:36'),
(2697, 23, 'If a team is to reach its potential, each player must be willing to subordinate his personal goals to the good of the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:25:45'),
(2698, 23, 'One man cannot make a team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:25:55'),
(2699, 23, 'Teams that play together beat those with superior players who play more as individuals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:04'),
(2700, 23, 'Finding good players is easy. Getting them to play as a team is another story.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:15'),
(2701, 23, 'You have to expect things of yourself before you can do them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:26'),
(2702, 23, 'Figure out how to climb it, go through it, or work around it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:35'),
(2703, 23, 'Create unselfishness as the most important team attribute.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:44'),
(2704, 23, 'People have been known to achieve more as a result of working with others than against them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:26:53'),
(2705, 23, 'Great teamwork is the only way we create the breakthroughs that define our careers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:02'),
(2706, 23, 'When a team outgrows individual performance and learns team confidence, excellence becomes a reality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:11'),
(2707, 23, 'If you quit ONCE it becomes a habit.Never quit!!!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:21'),
(2708, 23, 'If you accept the expectations of others, especially negative ones, then you never will change the outcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:29'),
(2709, 23, 'My heroes are and were my parents. I can\'t see having anyone else as my heroes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:38'),
(2710, 23, 'If you\'re trying to achieve, there will be roadblocks. I\'ve had them; everybody has had them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:46'),
(2711, 23, 'I\'ve failed over and over and over again in my life and that is why I succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:27:55'),
(2712, 23, 'What is love? Love is playing every game as if it\'s your last!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:06'),
(2713, 23, 'What you are as a person is far more important than what you are as a basketball player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:15'),
(2714, 23, 'The game is my wife. It demands loyalty and responsibility, and it gives me back fulfillment and peace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:23'),
(2715, 23, 'No one can whistle a symphony. It takes a whole orchestra to play it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:32'),
(2716, 23, 'For the strength of the Pack is the Wolf, and the strength of the Wolf is the Pack.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:41'),
(2717, 23, 'When a gifted team dedicates itself to unselfish trust and combines instinct with boldness and effort, its ready to climb.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:28:51'),
(2718, 23, 'The speed of the boss is the speed of the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:08'),
(2719, 23, 'A list is only as strong as its weakest link.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:20'),
(2720, 23, 'Once I made a decision, I never thought about it again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:30'),
(2721, 23, 'It takes two flints to make a fire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:39'),
(2722, 23, 'May your adventures bring you closer together, even as they take you far away from home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:47'),
(2723, 23, 'Being a part of success is more important than being personally indispensable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:29:56'),
(2724, 23, 'The achievements of an organization are the results of the combined effort of each individual.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:30:07'),
(2725, 23, 'When I lose the sense of motivation and the sense to prove something as a basketball player, it\'s time for me to move away from the game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:30:15'),
(2726, 23, 'Always turn a negative situation into a positive situation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:35:50'),
(2727, 23, 'I know fear is an obstacle for some people, but it is an illusion to me . . . Failure always made me try harder next time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:02'),
(2728, 23, 'Not only is there more to life than basketball, there\'s a lot more to basketball than basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:12'),
(2729, 23, 'The game is my wife. It demands loyalty and responsibility, and it gives me back fulfillment and peace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:21'),
(2730, 23, 'Talent wins games, but teamwork and intelligence wins championships.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:38'),
(2731, 23, 'You have to expect things of yourself before you can do them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:46'),
(2732, 23, 'I never looked at the consequences of missing a big shot... when you think about the consequences you always think of a negative result.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:36:56'),
(2733, 23, 'Get the fundamentals down and the level of everything you do will rise', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:37:07'),
(2734, 23, 'You can\'t get much done in life if you only work on the days when you feel good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:38:16'),
(2735, 23, 'If you make every game a life and death proposition, you\'re going to have problems. For one thing, you\'ll be dead a lot.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:38:27'),
(2736, 23, 'My heroes are and were my parents. I can\'t see having anyone else as my heroes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:38:35'),
(2737, 23, 'I\'ve failed over and over and over again in my life and that is why I succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:38:48'),
(2738, 23, 'I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can\'t accept not trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:38:58'),
(2739, 23, 'Some people want it to happen, some wish it would happen, others make it happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:08'),
(2740, 23, 'I don\'t need too much. Glamour and all that stuff don\'t excite me. I am just glad I have the game of basketball in my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:20'),
(2741, 23, 'In basketball - as in life - true joy comes from being fully present in each and every moment, not just when things are going your way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:31'),
(2742, 23, 'There is no such thing as life in-between.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:40'),
(2743, 23, 'Heart is what separates the good from the great.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:49'),
(2744, 23, 'I always mean what I say, but I don\'t always say what I\'m thinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:39:58'),
(2745, 23, 'There is a lot of pressure put on me, but I don\'t put a lot of pressure on myself. I feel if I play my game, it will take care of itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:40:08');
