(2746, 23, 'You can\'t be afraid to fail. It\'s the only way you succeed - you\'re not gonna succeed all the time, and I know that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:40:24'),
(2747, 23, 'The only way you\'re going to get through life, happily, is being yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:40:33'),
(2748, 23, 'Just play. Have fun. Enjoy the game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:40:43'),
(2749, 23, 'Basketball is a team game. But that doesn\'t mean all five players should have the same amount of shots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:40:54'),
(2750, 23, 'A great pleasure in life is doing what people say you cannot do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:41:03'),
(2751, 23, 'Winning takes talent; to repeat takes character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:42:19'),
(2752, 23, 'Failure is not fatal, but failure to change might be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:42:29'),
(2753, 23, 'Do not let what you cannot do interfere with what you can do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:42:38'),
(2754, 23, 'Some people want it to happen, some wish it would happen, others make it happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:42:50'),
(2755, 23, 'There are only two options regarding commitment; you’re either in or you’re out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:01'),
(2756, 23, 'The best teams have chemistry. They communicate with each other and they sacrifice personal glory for a common goal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:09'),
(2757, 23, 'It\'s what you learn after you know it all that counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:18'),
(2758, 23, 'I can accept failure, everyone fails at something. But I can\'t accept not trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:27'),
(2759, 23, 'Individual commitment to a group effort - that is what makes a team work, a company work, a society work, a civilization work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:38'),
(2760, 23, 'A player who makes a team great is better than a great player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:47'),
(2761, 23, 'The most important thing in coaching is communication. It\'s not what you say as much as what they absorb.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:43:57'),
(2762, 23, 'If you run into a wall, don\'t turn around and give up. Figure out how to climb it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:44:07'),
(2763, 23, 'A leader has to be positive about all things that happen to his team. Look at nothing in the past as failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:44:16'),
(2764, 23, 'A leader\'s job is to develop committed followers. Bad leaders destroy their followers\' sense of commitment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:44:32'),
(2765, 23, 'Things turn out best for the people who make the best of the way things turn out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:44:42'),
(2766, 23, 'One man can be a crucial ingredient on a team, but one man cannot make a team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:44:51'),
(2767, 23, 'I didn\'t get into teaching and coaching for the number of wins or the money. It was a passion for trying to help young people', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:45:02'),
(2768, 23, 'Talent wins games, but teamwork and intelligence wins championships.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:45:17'),
(2769, 23, 'A coach is someone who can give correction without causing resentment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:47:05'),
(2770, 23, 'I don\'t look at myself as a basketball coach. I look at myself as a leader who happens to coach basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:47:35'),
(2771, 23, 'Talent is God given. Be humble. Fame is man-given. Be grateful. Conceit is self-given. Be careful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:47:45'),
(2772, 23, 'The most important thing in good leadership is truly caring.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:47:54'),
(2773, 23, 'Never mistake activity for achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:03'),
(2774, 23, 'If you make every game a life and death proposition, you\'re going to have problems. For one thing, you\'ll be dead a lot.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:12'),
(2775, 23, 'It\'s not so important who starts the game but who finishes it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:20'),
(2776, 23, 'I would spend almost as much time planning a practice as conducting it. Everything was planned out each day', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:31'),
(2777, 23, 'You can\'t live a perfect day without doing something for someone who will never be able to repay you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:39'),
(2778, 23, 'Figure out how to climb it, go through it, or work around it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:48'),
(2779, 23, 'Whatever a leader does now sets up what he does later. And there\'s always a later.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:48:56'),
(2780, 23, 'People want to be part of something bigger than they are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:06'),
(2781, 23, 'If you don\'t feel you have something to prove every day, you\'ll never improve', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:16'),
(2782, 23, 'To have long term success as a coach or in any position of leadership, you have to be obsessed in some way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:24'),
(2783, 23, 'Be more concerned with your character than your reputation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:32'),
(2784, 23, 'What to do with a mistake: recognize it, admit it, learn from it, forget it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:43'),
(2785, 23, 'If Kyle Korver blocks your shot there should be a penalty box you should go to!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:49:53'),
