(2795, 23, 'The truth is that many people set rules to keep from making decisions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:51:36'),
(2796, 23, 'I always mean what I say, but I don\'t always say what I\'m thinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:51:45'),
(2797, 23, 'Don\'t measure yourself by what you have accomplished, but by what you should have accomplished with your ability.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:51:54'),
(2798, 23, 'It isn\'t about what you do, but how you do it', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:52:04'),
(2799, 23, 'It\'s the little details that are vital. Little things make big things happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:52:13'),
(2800, 23, 'My goal is to win the next game one possession at a time. That\'s it. I don\'t have any other goals', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:52:21'),
(2801, 23, 'When you have a problem, if you tell the truth, the problem becomes part of your past. If you lie, it becomes part of your future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:52:30'),
(2802, 23, 'Ability may get you to the top, but it takes character to keep you there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:52:44'),
