(2823, 23, 'A basketball team is like the five fingers on your hand. If you can get them all together, you have a fist. That\'s how I want you to play.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 15:58:49'),
