(2968, 22, 'Pro football is like nuclear warfare. There are no winners, only survivors.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:49:51'),
(2969, 22, 'A football team is a like a beautiful woman, when you do not tell her, she forgets she is beautiful', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:00'),
(2970, 22, 'In life, as in football, the principle to follow is to hit the line hard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:10'),
(2971, 22, 'No one has ever drowned in sweat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:19'),
(2972, 22, 'The lad got over-excited when he saw the whites of the goalpost\'s eyes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:28'),
(2973, 22, 'Setting a goal is not the main thing. It is deciding how you will go about achieving it and staying with that plan.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:37'),
(2974, 22, 'If you don\'t play well, you have a bad game or a nightmare you know that the amount of coverage is worldwide.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:50:55'),
(2975, 22, 'Who will win the League? It\'s a toss of a coin between three of them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:04'),
(2976, 22, 'I feel like football players are overworked and underpaid compared to any other sports.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:18'),
(2977, 22, 'We didn\'t lose the game; we just ran out of time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:29'),
(2978, 22, 'Both sides have scored a couple of goals, and both sides have conceded a couple of goals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:38'),
(2979, 22, 'Pressue is something you feel when you don\'t know what the hell you\'re doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:47'),
(2980, 22, 'It\'s not the size of the dog in the fight, it\'s the size of the fight in the dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:51:56'),
(2981, 22, 'The Rose Bowl is the only bowl I\'ve ever seen that I didn\'t have to clean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:10'),
(2982, 22, 'It was an ideal day for football - too cold for the spectators and too cold for the players.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:19'),
(2983, 22, 'Soccer is simple, but it is difficult to play simple.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:27'),
(2984, 22, 'Everyone in my high school was a bit nerdy. We didn\'t even have a football team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:36'),
(2985, 22, 'Football (soccer) is a matter of life and death, except more important.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:46'),
(2986, 22, 'We are inclined to think that if we watch a football game or a baseball game, we have taken part in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:52:56'),
(2987, 22, 'Football is the ballet of the masses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:05'),
(2988, 22, 'Whoever invented soccer should be worshipped as God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:14'),
(2989, 22, 'Football\'s not just about scoring goals - it\'s about winning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:23'),
(2990, 22, 'They cut us up like boarding house pie. And that\'s real small pieces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:32'),
(2991, 22, 'You only stop learning when you quit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:41'),
(2992, 22, 'To play this game (football) you must have fire in you, and there is nothing that strokes fire like hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:53:49'),
(2993, 22, 'I am constantly being asked about individuals. The only way to win is as a team. Football is not about one or two or three star players.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:54:00'),
(2994, 22, 'I\'m going to make a prediction - it could go either way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:54:29'),
(2995, 22, 'He can\'t kick with his left foot, he can\'t head a ball, he can\'t tackle and he doesn\'t score many goals. Apart from that he\'s all right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:54:40'),
(2996, 22, 'They were numerically outnumbered.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:54:49'),
(2997, 22, 'Not to win is guttering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:54:58'),
(2998, 22, 'If you can\'t stand the heat in the dressing-room, get out of the kitchen', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:07'),
(2999, 22, 'In terms of the Richter scale this defeat was a force 8 gale.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:17'),
(3000, 22, 'A game is not won until it is lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:26'),
(3001, 22, 'I\'ve been consistent in patches this season.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:34'),
(3002, 22, 'The thing about goalscorers is that they score goals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:47'),
(3003, 22, 'Maybe a good rule in life is never become too important to do your own laundry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:55:56'),
(3004, 22, 'In this case, I realize that, unlike when I was 22 years old, I realize now that football will not go on forever, it is a small part of your life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:56:08'),
(3005, 22, 'Football, bloody hell!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:56:19'),
(3006, 22, 'Sure, luck means a lot in football. Not having a good quarterback is bad luck.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:56:30'),
(3007, 22, 'Only true champions come out and show their worth after defeat- and I expect us to do that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:56:42'),
(3008, 22, 'Losing is not in my vocabulary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:56:53'),
(3009, 22, 'Football is a game played with arms, legs and shoulders but mostly from the neck up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:57:03'),
(3010, 22, 'Nobody in football should be called a genius. A genius is a guy like Norman Einstein.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:57:27'),
(3011, 22, 'If you can accept losing, you can\'t win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:57:34'),
(3012, 22, 'My parents have been there for me, ever since I was about 7.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:57:45'),
(3013, 22, 'All that I know most surely about morality and obligations I owe to football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:57:55');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(3014, 22, 'Men kick friendship around like a football, but it doesn\'t seem to crack. Women treat it like glass and it goes to pieces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:05'),
(3015, 22, 'Everything about morality and obligations I owe to football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:16'),
(3016, 22, 'I also played two years of high school football but I wasn\'t very, how shall I say it, talented.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:26'),
(3017, 22, 'My advice to defensive players: Take the shortest route to the ball and arrive in a bad humor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:35'),
(3018, 22, 'If you never concede a goal, you\'re going to win more games than you lose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:46'),
(3019, 22, 'If a man watches three football games in a row, he should be declared legally dead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:58:55'),
(3020, 22, 'Football isn\'t a contact sport; it\'s a collision sport. Dancing is a contact sport.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:04'),
(3021, 22, 'Football isn\'t a contact sport, it\'s a collision sport.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:13'),
(3022, 22, 'In my time at Anfield we always said we had the best two teams on Merseyside - Liverpool and Liverpool reserves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:23'),
(3023, 22, 'Football is a game of skill, we kicked them a bit and they kicked us a bit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:33'),
(3024, 22, 'It was six of a half and one dozen of the other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:42'),
(3025, 22, 'In real football, I wouldn\'t want Terrell Owens anywhere near my team. But you\'re nuts if you don\'t take him in fantasy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 16:59:51'),
(3026, 22, 'Actually, I wanted to act even when I was still playing football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:00:01'),
(3027, 22, 'A lot of football success is in the mind. You must believe you are the best and then make sure that you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:00:12'),
(3028, 22, 'I make my practices real hard because if a player is a quitter, I want him to quit in practice, not in a game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:00:21'),
(3029, 22, 'When you win, say nothing. When you lose, say less.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:00:36'),
(3030, 22, 'The football season is like pain. You forget how terrible it is until it seizes you again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:00:45'),
(3031, 22, 'American football makes rugby look like a Tupperware party.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:00'),
(3032, 22, 'One man practicing sportsmanship is far better than a hundred teaching it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:10'),
(3033, 22, 'Failure happens all the time. It happens every day in practice. What makes you better is how you react to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:18'),
(3034, 22, 'I always think about what I missed, and I think that was my driving force - never be satisfied with what I\'ve done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:28'),
(3035, 22, 'It\'s kind of hard to rally around a math class.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:37'),
(3036, 22, 'If football taught me anything about business, it is that you win the game one play at a time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:46'),
(3037, 22, 'Sometimes in football you have to hold your hand up and say, yeah, they\'re better than us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:01:54'),
(3038, 22, 'The person that said winning isn\'t everything, never won anything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:03'),
(3039, 22, 'There\'s nothing that cleanses your soul like getting the hell kicked out of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:11'),
(3040, 22, 'Motivation is simple. You eliminate those who are not motivated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:20'),
(3041, 22, 'You can learn more character on the two-yard line than anywhere else in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:31'),
(3042, 22, 'I\'ve found that prayers work best when you have big players.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:42'),
(3043, 22, 'I never make predictions and I never will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:02:50'),
(3044, 22, 'Most football players are temperamental. That\'s 90 percent temper and 10 percent mental.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:03:00'),
(3045, 22, 'In football you have an adversary; in cinema that adversary is yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:03:09'),
(3046, 22, 'When it\'s football season, I\'m all football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:03:18'),
(3047, 22, 'If what you did yesterday seems big, you haven\'t done anything today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:03:32'),
(3048, 22, 'Pro football gave me a good sense of perspective to enter politics: I\'d already been booed, cheered, cut, sold, traded and hung in effigy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:00'),
(3049, 22, 'I think the best place to work in football is England.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:15'),
(3050, 22, 'I started out as a football player. I liked to inflict pain. In basketball, it was the same thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:23'),
(3051, 22, 'God blessed me to play football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:31'),
(3052, 22, 'I\'m really normal. I play football, go to the beach, drive. We have dogs. I can imagine people calling me a character, but I\'m Joe Straight.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:40'),
(3053, 22, 'I\'m a rock star because I couldn\'t be a soccer star.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:04:51'),
(3054, 22, 'Good luck is a residue of preparation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:01'),
(3055, 22, 'All good athletes make mistakes; the great ones learn to make that mistake only once.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:12'),
(3056, 22, 'Other countries have their history. Uruguay has its football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:21'),
(3057, 22, 'Whenever I wasn\'t watching the planes, I was playing community baseball, football, or something like that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:30'),
(3058, 22, 'Football\'s a difficult business and aren\'t they prima donnas. But it\'s a wonderful game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:42'),
(3059, 22, 'Hawaii doesn\'t win many games in the United States.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:05:53'),
(3060, 22, 'When I get the ball, for some reason I see holes. I\'m not really sure how.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:06:03'),
(3061, 22, 'Son, you\'ve got a good engine, but your hands aren\'t on the steering wheel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:06:12'),
(3062, 22, 'After you retire, there\'s only one big event left....and I ain\'t ready for that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:06:22'),
(3063, 22, 'I\'m really happy for Coach Cooper and the guys who\'ve been around here for six or seven years, especially our seniors.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:06:30'),
(3064, 22, 'If lessons are learned in defeat, our team is getting a great education.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:01'),
(3065, 22, 'I don\'t hire anybody not brighter than I am. If they\'re not brighter than I am, I don\'t need them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:12'),
(3066, 22, 'They whipped us like a tied up goat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:20'),
(3067, 22, 'Oh, we played about like three tons of buzzard puke this afternoon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:29'),
(3068, 22, 'Three things can happen when you throw the ball, and two of them are bad.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:37'),
(3069, 22, 'I don\'t expect to win enough games to be put on NCAA probation. I just want to win enough to warrant an investigation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:46'),
(3070, 22, 'The only qualifications for a lineman are to be big and dumb. To be a back, you only have to be dumb.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:07:55'),
(3071, 22, 'No, but you can see it from here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:03'),
(3072, 22, 'I was the originator of smack. Some guys rattle with smack; with other guys it rolls right off their shoulders like nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:11'),
(3073, 22, 'A good back makes his own holes. Anybody can run where the holes are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:22'),
(3074, 22, 'That field goal attempt was so far to the left it nearly decapitated Lyndon LaRouche.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:32'),
(3075, 22, 'Its great grass at Anfield, professional grass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:43'),
(3076, 22, 'Football is a simple game made complicated by people who should know better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:08:57'),
(3077, 22, 'There\'s some people on the pitch... they think it\'s all over... it is now!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:09'),
(3078, 22, 'Thats the beauty of sport. Sometimes you laugh, sometimes you cry', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:18'),
(3079, 22, 'That was only a yard away from being an inch-perfect pass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:28'),
(3080, 22, 'Woodcock would have scored but his shot was too perfect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:37'),
(3081, 22, 'If it stays as it is I can\'t see it altering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:45'),
(3082, 22, 'Beckenbauer has really gambled all his eggs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:09:52'),
(3083, 22, 'What I said to them at half time would be unprintable on the radio.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:10:00'),
(3084, 22, 'Unfortunately, we keep kicking ourselves in the foot.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-25 17:10:12'),
(3085, 21, 'A cat has absolute emotional honesty: human beings, for one reason or another, may hide their feelings, but a cat does not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:23:09'),
(3086, 21, 'What greater gift than the love of a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:23:16'),
(3087, 21, 'Time spent with cats is never wasted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:23:25'),
(3088, 21, 'The cat does not offer services. The cat offers itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:23:35'),
(3089, 21, 'I simply can\'t resist a cat, particularly a purring one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:23:49'),
(3090, 21, 'Cats are intended to teach us that not everything in nature has a function.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:00'),
(3091, 21, 'Our perfect companions never have fewer than four feet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:09'),
(3092, 21, 'When a man loves cats, I am his friend and comrade, without further introduction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:16'),
(3093, 21, 'Cats have it all - admiration, an endless sleep, and company only when they want it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:24'),
(3094, 21, 'I love cats because I enjoy my home; and little by little, they become its visible soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:34'),
(3095, 21, 'Cat: a pygmy lion who loves mice, hates dogs, and patronizes human beings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:43'),
(3096, 21, 'The cat does not offer services. The cat offers itself. Of course he wants care and shelter. You don\'t buy love for nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:50'),
(3097, 21, 'As every cat owner knows, nobody owns a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:24:58'),
(3098, 21, 'If man could be crossed with the cat, it would improve man but deteriorate the cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:07'),
(3099, 21, 'I wish I could write as mysterious as a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:14'),
(3100, 21, 'There are two means of refuge from the miseries of life: music and cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:23'),
(3101, 21, 'Way down deep, we\'re all motivated by the same urges. Cats have the courage to live by them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:34'),
(3102, 21, 'Dogs come when they\'re called; cats take a message and get back to you later.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:42'),
(3103, 21, 'The dog is a gentleman; I hope to go to his heaven not man\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:50'),
(3104, 21, 'To respect the cat is the beginning of the aesthetic sense.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:25:58'),
(3105, 21, 'Cats are smarter than dogs. You can\'t get eight cats to pull a sled through snow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:26:06'),
(3106, 21, 'After scolding one\'s cat one looks into its face and is seized by the ugly suspicion that it understood every word. And has filed it for reference.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:26:15'),
(3107, 21, 'Cats know how to obtain food without labor, shelter without confinement, and love without penalties.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:26:23'),
(3108, 21, 'One cat just leads to another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:26:39'),
(3109, 21, 'You cannot look at a sleeping cat and feel tense.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:26:47'),
(3110, 21, 'If cats looked like frogs we\'d realize what nasty, cruel little bastards they are. Style. That\'s what people remember.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:03'),
(3111, 21, 'Dogs are not our whole life, but they make our lives whole.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:10'),
(3112, 21, 'A dog is the only thing on earth that loves you more than you love yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:23'),
(3113, 21, 'Authors like cats because they are such quiet, lovable, wise creatures, and cats like authors for the same reasons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:33'),
(3114, 21, 'The problem with cats is that they get the exact same look on their face whether they see a moth or an axe-murderer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:42'),
(3115, 21, 'If you pick up a starving dog and make him prosperous he will not bite you. This is the principal difference between a dog and man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:50'),
(3116, 21, 'If animals could speak, the dog would be a blundering outspoken fellow; but the cat would have the rare grace of never saying a word too much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:27:59'),
(3117, 21, 'Those who\'ll play with cats must expect to be scratched.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:10'),
(3118, 21, 'I am fond of pigs. Dogs look up to us. Cats look down on us. Pigs treat us as equals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:18'),
(3119, 21, 'Women and cats will do as they please, and men and dogs should relax and get used to the idea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:25'),
(3120, 21, 'I\'ve met many thinkers and many cats, but the wisdom of cats is infinitely superior.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:34'),
(3121, 21, 'Cats seem to go on the principle that it never does any harm to ask for what you want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:45'),
(3122, 21, 'I would like to see anyone, prophet, king or God, convince a thousand cats to do the same thing at the same time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:28:53'),
(3123, 21, 'In a cat\'s eye, all things belong to cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:29:00'),
(3124, 21, 'I love them, they are so nice and selfish. Dogs are TOO good and unselfish. They make me feel uncomfortable. But cats are gloriously human.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:29:09'),
(3125, 21, 'The greatness of a nation can be judged by the way its animals are treated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:29:18'),
(3126, 21, 'If I have any beliefs about immortality, it is that certain dogs I have known will go to heaven, and very, very few persons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:29:27'),
(3127, 21, 'While the cat\'s away, the mice will play.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:29:35'),
(3128, 21, 'Cats love one so much - more than they will allow. But they have so much wisdom they keep it to themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:30:19'),
(3129, 21, 'All cats love a cushioned couch.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:30:40'),
(3130, 21, 'I\'ve been married for 46 years, and I live in a nice house, my grass is always cut, I pay my bills, and my cat loves me!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:30:50'),
(3131, 21, 'Bach was a top harmonist geezer, which is why the jazz cats love him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:30:58'),
(3132, 21, 'God has made the cat to give man the pleasure of caressing the tiger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:31:53'),
(3133, 21, 'Cats know not how to pardon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:07'),
(3134, 21, 'Everything a cat is and does physically is to me beautiful, lovely, stimulating, soothing, attractive and an enchantment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:17'),
(3135, 21, 'You can keep a dog: but it is the cat who keeps people, because cats find humans useful domestic animals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:25'),
(3136, 21, 'Way down deep, we\'re all motivated by the same urges. Cats have the courage to live by them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:33'),
(3137, 21, 'A dog is like a liberal. He wants to please everybody. A cat really doesn\'t need to know that everybody loves him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:41'),
(3138, 21, 'A cat is only technically an animal, being divine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:49'),
(3139, 21, 'This is all you need in life: a computer, a camera, and a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:32:57'),
(3140, 21, 'The phrase \'domestic cat\' is an oxymoron', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:04'),
(3141, 21, 'Cats regard people as warm-blooded furniture.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:12'),
(3142, 21, 'A cat pours his body on the floor like water. It is restful just to see him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:29'),
(3143, 21, 'Dogs may have kept us company on the hunt, but it was the cats who insisted we invent houses and discover fire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:38'),
(3144, 21, 'Anyone who considers protocol unimportant has never dealt with a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:49'),
(3145, 21, 'One of the oldest human needs is having someone to wonder where you are when you don\'t come home at night.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:33:57'),
(3146, 21, 'It is a very inconvenient habit of kittens (Alice had once made the remark) that whatever you say to them, they always purr.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:34:06'),
(3147, 21, 'After scolding one\'s cat one looks into its face and is seized by the ugly suspicion that it understood every word. And has filed it for reference.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:34:14'),
(3148, 21, 'The cat does not offer services. The cat offers itself. Of course he wants care and shelter. You don\'t buy love for nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:34:22'),
(3149, 21, 'You call to a dog and a dog will break its neck to get to you. Dogs just want to please. Call to a cat and its attitude is, \'What\'s in it for me?\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:34:45'),
(3150, 21, 'It is difficult to obtain the friendship of a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:34:55'),
(3151, 21, 'Nothing makes a house cozier than cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:04'),
(3152, 21, 'Holding up my purring cat to the moon. I sighed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:12'),
(3153, 21, 'Lettin\' the cat outta the bag is a whole lot easier \'n puttin\' it back in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:21'),
(3154, 21, 'When they are among us cats are angels', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:28'),
(3155, 21, 'The cat is a dilettante in fur.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:36'),
(3156, 21, 'Cats sleep fat and walk thin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:44'),
(3157, 21, 'My husband said it was him or the cat. I miss him sometimes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:35:53'),
(3158, 21, 'Curiosity killed the cat, but where human beings are concerned, the only thing a healthy curiosity can kill is ignorance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:01'),
(3159, 21, 'Cats know everything there is to know about meditation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:13'),
(3160, 21, 'A man is like a cat; chase him and he will run - sit still and ignore him and he\'ll come purring at your feet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:20'),
(3161, 21, 'I have just been given a very engaging Persian kitten... and his opinion is that I have been given to him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:28'),
(3162, 21, 'Cats randomly refuse to follow orders to prove they can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:35'),
(3163, 21, 'The cat is domestic only as far as suits its own ends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:44'),
(3164, 21, 'If a cat does something, we call it instinct; if we do the same thing, for the same reason, we call it intelligence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:36:52'),
(3165, 21, 'While the rest of the species is descended from apes, redheads are descended from cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:00'),
(3166, 21, 'All I need to know I learned from my cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:12'),
(3167, 21, 'A dog\'s idea of personal grooming is to roll on a dead fish.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:20'),
(3168, 21, 'Cats are kindly masters, just so long as you remember your place.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:37'),
(3169, 21, 'A cat is better than you are, more honest, more graceful, smarter for her size, better coordinated, and infinitely more beautiful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:46'),
(3170, 21, 'A cat is witty, he has nerve, he knows how to do precisely the right thing at the right moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:37:55'),
(3171, 21, 'The cat in gloves catches no mice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:03'),
(3172, 21, 'All dogs look up to you. All cats look down on you. Only the pig looks at you as an equal', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:11'),
(3173, 21, 'Two things are aesthetically perfect in the world - the clock and the cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:20'),
(3174, 21, 'When I played in the sandbox, the cat kept covering me up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:29'),
(3175, 21, 'A pharaoh\'s profile, a Krishna\'s grace, tail like a question mark.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:39'),
(3176, 21, 'Books, Cats, Life is Good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:47'),
(3177, 21, '[A cat] will lie the whole evening on your knee, purring and happy in your society.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:38:55'),
(3178, 21, 'Of all animals, the cat alone attains to the comtemplative life. He regards the wheel of existence from without, like the Buddha.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:05'),
(3179, 21, 'Your cat just got cat hair on me.” “It’s only fair,” Min said. “Your suit just got expensive suit lint on him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:15'),
(3180, 21, 'Cats, no less liquid than their shadows, offer no angles to the wind. They slip, diminished, neat, through loopholes less than themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:25'),
(3181, 21, 'Time spent with a cat is never wasted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:32'),
(3182, 21, 'A novel must be exceptionally good to live as long as the average cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:41'),
(3183, 21, 'If cats looked like frogs we\'d realize what nasty, cruel little bastards they are. Style. That\'s what people remember.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:39:52'),
(3184, 21, 'A woman who takes her husband about with her everywhere is like a cat that goes on playing with a mouse long after she\'s killed it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:00'),
(3185, 21, 'Cats are inquisitive, but hate to admit it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:14'),
(3186, 21, 'Cats have no sense of humor, they have terribly inflated egos, and they are very touchy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:23'),
(3187, 21, 'With one of the most bewitching sounds in the world, its purr, the cat persuades us that it thinks we are wonderful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:33'),
(3188, 21, 'And let me touch those curving claws of yellow ivory; and grasp the tail that like a monstrous asp coils round your heavy velvet paws.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:41'),
(3189, 21, 'Authors like cats because they are such quiet, lovable, wise creatures, and cats like authors for the same reasons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:50'),
(3190, 21, 'All day long the door of the sub-conscious remains just ajar; we slip through to the other side, and return again, as easily and secretly as a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:40:59'),
(3191, 21, 'If you are worthy of its affection, a cat will be your friend but never your slave.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:07'),
(3192, 21, 'Once [a cat] has given its love, what absolute confidence, what fidelity of affection!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:16'),
(3193, 21, 'Cats have it all - admiration, an endless sleep, and company only when they want it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:24'),
(3194, 21, 'The cat is the only animal which accepts the comforts but rejects the bondage of domesticity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:32'),
(3195, 21, 'It doesn\'t matter if a cat is black or white, so long as it catches mice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:42'),
(3196, 21, 'Kittens can happen to anyone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:50'),
(3197, 21, 'Never ask a hungry cat whether he loves you for yourself alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:41:57'),
(3198, 21, 'Dogs serve people, but people serve cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:05'),
(3199, 21, 'A cat\'s got her own opinion of human beings. She don\'t say much, but you can tell enough to make you anxious not to hear the whole of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:16'),
(3200, 21, 'Cats will amusingly tolerate humans only until someone comes up with a tin opener that can be operated with a paw.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:30'),
(3201, 21, 'The cat is a character of being, the dog, a character of doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:39'),
(3202, 21, 'I am not a cat man, but a dog man, and all felines can tell this at a glance - a sharp, vindictive glance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:47'),
(3203, 21, 'Even overweight cats instinctively know the cardinal rule: when fat, arrange yourself in slim poses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:42:56'),
(3204, 21, 'A cat is nobody\'s fool.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:43:04'),
(3205, 21, 'Comets are like cats: they have tails, and they do precisely what they want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:00'),
(3206, 21, 'No matter how tired or wretched I am, a pussycat sitting in a doorway can divert my mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:10'),
(3207, 21, 'We cannot without becoming cats, perfectly understand the cat mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:19'),
(3208, 21, 'Cats are only human, they have their faults.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:28'),
(3209, 21, '[A cat] will make itself the companion of your hours of work, of loneliness, or of sadness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:38'),
(3210, 21, 'We have three cats. It\'s like having children, but there is no tuition involved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:48'),
(3211, 21, 'I think all cats are wild. They only act tame if there´s a saucer of milk in it for them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:45:57'),
(3212, 21, 'A cat sleeps fat, yet walks thin.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:46:05'),
(3213, 21, 'I write so much because my cat sits on my lap. She purrs so I don\'t want to get up. She\'s so much more calming than my husband.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:46:14'),
(3214, 21, 'Aren\'t they all heroes-our cats who train us, keep us and put up with us? For these accomplishments alone, they deserve medals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:46:26'),
(3215, 21, 'Cat hate reflects an ugly, stupid, loutish, bigoted spirit. There can be no compromise with this Ugly Spirit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:46:39'),
(3216, 21, 'The fog comes on little cat feet. It sits looking over the harbor and city on silent haunches and then moves on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:47:00'),
(3217, 21, 'Do not be like the cat who wanted a fish but was afraid to get his paws wet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:47:21'),
(3218, 21, 'Cities, like cats, will reveal themselves at night.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:00'),
(3219, 21, 'Cats are designated friends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:08'),
(3220, 21, 'Woman is essentially unpeaceful, like the cat, however well she may have trained herself to present an appearance of peace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:17'),
(3221, 21, 'In a burning building I would save a cat before a Rembrandt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:25'),
(3222, 21, 'No animal is a better judge of comfort than a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:33'),
(3223, 21, 'Meow” means “woof” in cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:42'),
(3224, 21, 'There are two means of refuge from the miseries of life: music and cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:51'),
(3225, 21, 'The cat, it is well to remember, remains the friend of man because it pleases him to do so and not because he must.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:49:59'),
(3226, 21, 'My relationship with cats has saved me from a deadly and pervasive ignorance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:07'),
(3227, 21, 'The cat sat on the mat is not a story. The cat sat on the other cat’s mat is a story.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:15'),
(3228, 21, 'I enjoy many silent moments with my cat, a conversation always resumed exactly where left off.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:25'),
(3229, 21, 'If you want to be a psychological novelist and write about human beings, the best thing you can do is keep a pair of cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:33'),
(3230, 21, 'Ignorance killed the cat; curiosity was framed!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:42'),
(3231, 21, 'When I play with my cat, who knows whether I do not make her more sport than she makes me?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:50:59'),
(3232, 21, 'I take care of my flowers and my cats. And enjoy food. And that\'s living.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:51:34'),
(3233, 21, 'When a cat flatters ... he is not insincere: you may safely take it for real kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:51:41'),
(3234, 21, 'Cats like men are flatterers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:51:49'),
(3235, 21, 'Those who\'ll play with cats must expect to be scratched.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:51:57'),
(3236, 21, 'I had been told that the training procedure with cats was difficult. It\'s not. Mine had me trained in two days.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:05'),
(3237, 21, 'Guys are like dogs. They keep comin\' back. Ladies are like cats. Yell at a cat one time, they\'re gone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:14'),
(3238, 21, 'Cats know how to obtain food without labor, shelter without confinement, and love without penalties.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:22'),
(3239, 21, 'One cat just leads to another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:30'),
(3240, 21, 'The way to keep a cat is to try to chase it away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:39'),
(3241, 21, 'Prowling his own quiet backyard or asleep by the fire, he is still only a whisker away from the wilds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:46'),
(3242, 21, 'No favor can win gratitude from a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:52:55'),
(3243, 21, 'In nine lifetimes, you\'ll never know as much about your cat as your cat knows about you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:04'),
(3244, 21, 'Any cat that misses a mouse pretends it was aiming for the dead leaf.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:12'),
(3245, 21, 'What is the victory of a cat on a hot tin roof? - I wish I knew... Just staying on it, I guess, as long as she can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:20'),
(3246, 21, 'No animal has more liberty than the cat, but it buries the mess it makes. The cat is the best anarchist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:28'),
(3247, 21, 'Dogs are high on life. Cats need catnip.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:37'),
(3248, 21, 'Cats can be cooperative when something feels good, which, to a cat, is the way everything is supposed to feel as much of the time as possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:47'),
(3249, 21, 'The hardest thing of all is to find a black cat in a dark room, especially if there is no cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:53:55'),
(3250, 21, 'Cats sleep Anywhere, Any table, Any chair, Top of piano, Window-ledge, In the middle, On the edge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:03'),
(3251, 21, 'The reason domestic pets are so lovable and so helpful to us is because they enjoy, quietly and placidly, the present moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:11'),
(3252, 21, 'Nobody keeps a cat. They condescend to live with you is all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:19'),
(3253, 21, 'It\'s funny how dogs and cats know the inside of folks better than other folks do, isn\'t it?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:34'),
(3254, 21, 'Cats are more interesting, let\'s face it. Dogs are loveable and a bit boring.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:47'),
(3255, 21, 'The last thing I would accuse a cat of is innocence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:54:56'),
(3256, 21, 'What sort of philosophers are we, who know absolutely nothing of the origin and destiny of cats?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:55:09'),
(3257, 21, 'If a fish is the movement of water embodied, given shape, then cat is a diagram and pattern of subtle air.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:55:34'),
(3258, 21, 'Where the hell are the singing cats?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:55:42'),
(3259, 21, 'The trouble with cats is that they\'ve got no tact.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:55:50'),
(3260, 21, 'The playful kitten, with its pretty little tigerish gambols, is infinitely more amusing than half the people one is obliged to live with in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:02'),
(3261, 21, 'Cats are a mysterious kind of folk.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:11'),
(3262, 21, 'Some animals are secretive; some are shy. A cat is private.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:21'),
(3263, 21, 'I believe cats to be spirits come to earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:33'),
(3264, 21, 'A cat may look at a king.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:42'),
(3265, 21, 'In the dictionary of Cat, mercy is missing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:56:51'),
(3266, 21, 'Dogs are not our whole life, but they make our lives whole.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:57:00'),
(3267, 21, 'A cat determined not to be found can fold itself up like a pocket handkerchief if it wants to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:57:09'),
(3268, 21, 'Purring would seem to be, in her case, an automatic safety-valve device for dealing with happiness overflow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:57:18'),
(3269, 21, 'People who hate cats, will come back as mice in their next life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:57:29'),
(3270, 21, 'The clever cat eats cheese and breathes down rat holes with baited breath.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:58:03'),
(3271, 21, 'Among human beings, a cat is merely a cat; among cats, a cat is a prowling shadow in a jungle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:58:12'),
(3272, 21, 'If you hold a cat by the tail you learn things you cannot learn any other way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 15:58:23'),
(3273, 20, 'The voice of the sea speaks to the soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:11:10'),
(3274, 20, 'At the beach, life is different. Time doesn\'t move hour to hour but mood to moment. We live by the currents, plan by the tides, and follow the sun.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:11:21'),
(3275, 20, 'The ocean stirs the heart, inspires the imagination and brings eternal joy to the soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:11:29'),
(3276, 20, 'The sea, once it casts its spell, holds one in its net of wonder forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:11:40'),
(3277, 20, 'Because there\'s nothing more beautiful than the way the ocean refuses to stop kissing the shoreline, no matter how many times it\'s sent away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:11:58'),
(3278, 20, 'Smell the sea and feel the sky.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:08'),
(3279, 20, 'On the ocean of life let your mind be the ship and your heart be the compass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:17'),
(3280, 20, 'My soul is full of longing for the secret of the sea, and the heart of the great ocean sends a thrilling pulse through me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:28'),
(3281, 20, 'One doesn\'t discover new lands without consenting to lose sight, for a very long time, of the shore.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:36'),
(3282, 20, 'A woman\'s heart is a deep ocean of secrets.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:46'),
(3283, 20, 'My altars are the mountains and the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:12:54');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(3284, 20, 'The cure for anything is salt water: sweat, tears or the sea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:02'),
(3285, 20, 'The voice of the sea speaks to the soul. The touch of the sea is sensuous, enfolding the body in its soft, close embrace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:13'),
(3286, 20, 'Just as the ocean has waves or the sun has rays, so the minds\'s own radiance is its thoughts and emotions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:21'),
(3287, 20, 'We ourselves feel that what we are doing is just a drop in the ocean. But the ocean would be less because of that missing drop.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:31'),
(3288, 20, 'We know that when we protect our oceans we\'re protecting our future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:40'),
(3289, 20, 'Limitless and immortal, the waters are the beginning and end of all things on earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:48'),
(3290, 20, 'Faith is knowing there is an ocean because you have seen a brook.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:13:57'),
(3291, 20, 'To go out with the setting sun on an empty beach is to truly embrace your solitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:14:06'),
(3292, 20, 'Why do we love the sea? It is because it has some potent power to make us think things we like to think.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:14:18'),
(3293, 20, 'You must not lose faith in humanity. Humanity is an ocean; if a few drops of the ocean are dirty, the ocean does not become dirty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:14:26'),
(3294, 20, 'My soul is full of longing for the secret of the sea', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:14:47'),
(3295, 20, 'Just as every drop of the ocean carries the taste of the ocean, so does every moment carry the taste of eternity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:14:55'),
(3296, 20, 'Either you decide to stay in the shallow end of the pool or you go out in the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:04'),
(3297, 20, 'You can\'t do anything about the length of your life, but you can do something about its width and depth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:12'),
(3298, 20, 'For whatever we lose (like a you or a me), It\'s always our self we find in the sea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:32'),
(3299, 20, 'We are tied to the ocean. And when we go back to the sea, whether it is to sail or to watch - we are going back from whence we came.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:40'),
(3300, 20, 'The sea lives in every one of us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:48'),
(3301, 20, 'The ocean is a mighty harmonist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:15:56'),
(3302, 20, 'Hark, now hear the sailors cry, smell the sea, and feel the sky let your soul & spirit fly, into the mystic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:04'),
(3303, 20, 'I could never stay long enough on the shore; the tang of the untainted, fresh, and free sea air was like a cool, quieting thought.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:16'),
(3304, 20, 'You don\'t understand. You\'re not a wave. You\'re part of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:30'),
(3305, 20, 'Asking is the beginning of receiving. Make sure you don\'t go to the ocean with a teaspoon. At least take a bucket so the kids won\'t laugh at you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:40'),
(3306, 20, 'How inappropriate to call this planet Earth when it is quite clearly Ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:48'),
(3307, 20, 'Don\'t try to describe the ocean if you\'ve never seen it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:16:57'),
(3308, 20, 'The more clearly we can focus our attention on the wonders and realities of the universe about us, the less taste we shall have for destruction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:06'),
(3309, 20, 'We never know the worth of water till the well is dry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:14'),
(3310, 20, 'Ocean is more ancient than the mountains, and freighted with the memories and the dreams of Time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:28'),
(3311, 20, 'Every drop in the ocean counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:37'),
(3312, 20, 'At night, when the sky is full of stars and the sea is still you get the wonderful sensation that you are floating in space.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:44'),
(3313, 20, 'The heart can think of no devotion Greater than being shore to the ocean- Holding the curve of one position, Counting an endless repetition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:17:53'),
(3314, 20, 'God\'s LOVE is Like an Ocean; You can See its Beginning, but not its end.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:01'),
(3315, 20, 'From birth, man carries the weight of gravity on his shoulders. He is bolted to earth. But man has only to sink beneath the surface and he is free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:10'),
(3316, 20, 'I\'ll love you till the ocean Is folded and hung up to dry And the seven stars go squawking Like geese about the sky.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:20'),
(3317, 20, 'The ocean has always been a salve to my soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:29'),
(3318, 20, 'But more wonderful than the lore of old men and the lore of books is the secret lore of ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:38'),
(3319, 20, 'I threw bitter tears at the ocean, but all that came back was the tide.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:46'),
(3320, 20, 'A frog in a well cannot conceive of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:18:56'),
(3321, 20, 'He that will learn to pray, let him go to sea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:05'),
(3322, 20, 'I am you; you are ME. You are the waves; I am the ocean. Know this and be free, be divine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:16'),
(3323, 20, 'Swelling in anger or sparkling in glee.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:25'),
(3324, 20, 'God moves in a mysterious way, His wonders to perform. He plants his footsteps in the sea, and rides upon the storm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:34'),
(3325, 20, 'A lot of people attack the sea, I make love to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:43'),
(3326, 20, 'I am the daughter of Earth and Water, And the nursling of the Sky; I pass through the pores of the ocean and shores; I change, but I cannot die.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:19:53'),
(3327, 20, 'Praise the sea; on shore remain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:02'),
(3328, 20, 'I pray to be like the ocean, with soft currents, maybe waves at times. More and more, I want the consistency rather than the highs and the lows.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:09'),
(3329, 20, 'The sea pronounces something, over and over, in a hoarse whisper; I cannot quite make it out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:18'),
(3330, 20, 'The sea! The sea! The open sea!, The blue, the fresh, the ever free!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:39'),
(3331, 20, 'With every drop of water you drink, every breath you take, you\'re connected to the sea. No matter where on Earth you live.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:47'),
(3332, 20, 'The sea appears all golden. Beneath the sun-lit sky.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:20:55'),
(3333, 20, 'Sponges grow in the ocean. That just kills me. I wonder how much deeper the ocean would be if that didn\'t happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:21:04'),
(3334, 20, 'The sea complains upon a thousand shores.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:21:18'),
(3335, 20, 'In every outthrust headland, in every curving beach, in every grain of sand there is the story of the earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:21:31'),
(3336, 20, 'Break, break, break, On thy cold gray stones, oh sea! And I would that my tongue could utter The thoughts that arise in me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:21:57'),
(3337, 20, 'Old ocean\'s gray and melancholy waste.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:06'),
(3338, 20, 'Your heart is like the ocean, mysterious and dark.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:14'),
(3339, 20, 'Whilst breezy waves toss up their silvery spray.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:23'),
(3340, 20, 'I\'m horrified of lobsters. And shrimp and lobsters are the cockroaches of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:32'),
(3341, 20, 'The virtues are lost in self-interest as rivers are lost in the sea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:41'),
(3342, 20, 'The true peace of God begins at any spot a thousand miles from the nearest land.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:49'),
(3343, 20, 'You\'re not a wave, you\'re a part of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:22:58'),
(3344, 20, 'The sea hath no king but God alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:23:10'),
(3345, 20, 'Man has only to sink beneath the surface and he is free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:23:19'),
(3346, 20, 'We may not be God, but we are of God, even as a little drop of water is of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:23:34'),
(3347, 20, 'Water and air, the two essential fluids on which all life depends, have become global garbage cans.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:23:50'),
(3348, 20, 'There is nothing so desperately monotonous as the sea, and I no longer wonder at the cruelty of pirates.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:24:07'),
(3349, 20, 'Fishes live in the sea, as men do a-land; the great ones eat up the little ones.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:24:18'),
(3350, 20, 'The great obstacle to discovering the shape of the earth, the continents, and the oceans was not ignorance, but the illusion of knowledge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:24:28'),
(3351, 20, 'What makes the desert beautiful is that somewhere it hides a well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:24:43'),
(3352, 20, 'A citizen of America will cross the ocean to fight for democracy, but won\'t cross the street to vote in a national election.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:24:53'),
(3353, 20, 'What would an ocean be without a monster lurking in the dark? It would be like sleep without dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:25:05'),
(3354, 20, 'The biggest sin in the world would be if I lost my love for the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:25:17'),
(3355, 20, 'Ocean: A body of water occupying about two-thirds of a world made for man - who has no gills.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:25:36'),
(3356, 20, 'I had fought on behalf of man against the sea, but I realized that it had become more urgent to fight on behalf of the sea against men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:25:46'),
(3357, 20, 'One cannot collect all the beautiful shells on the beach.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:25:55'),
(3358, 20, 'Cut down on your use of plastic shopping bags because many end up in the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:04'),
(3359, 20, 'Our knowledge is a little island in a great ocean of nonknowledge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:13'),
(3360, 20, 'Full many a gem of purest ray serene, The dark unfathomed caves of ocean bear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:23'),
(3361, 20, 'The sea has never been friendly to man. At most it has been the accomplice of human restlessness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:31'),
(3362, 20, 'I imagine a line, a white line, painted on the sand and on the ocean, from me to you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:40'),
(3363, 20, 'American public opinion is like an ocean, it cannot be stirred by a teaspoon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:49'),
(3364, 20, 'Without water, our planet would be one of the billions of lifeless rocks floating endlessly in the vastness of the inky-black void.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:26:58'),
(3365, 20, 'Neither earth nor ocean produces a creature as savage and monstrous as woman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:27:06'),
(3366, 20, 'Praise the Sea, but keep on land.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:27:16'),
(3367, 20, 'The land is dearer for the sea, The ocean for the shore.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:27:52'),
(3368, 20, 'Even the upper end of the river believes in the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:28:04'),
(3369, 20, 'The least movement is of importance to all nature. The entire ocean is affected by a pebble.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:28:27'),
(3370, 20, 'Many drops make a bucket, many buckets make a pond, many ponds make a lake, and many lakes make an ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:28:37'),
(3371, 20, 'Truth makes on the ocean of nature no one track of light; every eye, looking on, finds its own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:28:49'),
(3372, 20, 'Rich and various gems inlay The unadorned bosom of the deep.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:29:00'),
(3373, 20, 'Just remember; someone loves everything you hate about yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:29:12'),
(3374, 20, 'I do an awful lot of scuba diving. I love to be on the ocean, under the ocean. I live next to the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:29:22'),
(3375, 20, 'And Thou, vast Ocean! on whole awful face Time\'s iron feet can print no ruin trace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:29:32'),
(3376, 20, 'It was a lone voice in the middle of the ocean, but it was heard at great depth and great distance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:29:54'),
(3377, 20, 'It isn\'t the oceans which cut us off from the world - it\'s the American way of looking at things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:01'),
(3378, 20, 'The sea speaks a language polite people never repeat. It is a colossal scavenger slang and has no respect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:13'),
(3379, 20, 'Blue, green, grey, white, or black; smooth, ruffled, or mountainous; that ocean is not silent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:24'),
(3380, 20, 'My gratitude for good writing is unbounded; I’m grateful for it the way I’m grateful for the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:34'),
(3381, 20, 'You cannot speak of the ocean to a frog that lives in a well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:43'),
(3382, 20, 'Don\'t cross oceans for people who wouldn\'t cross a puddle for you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:30:51'),
(3383, 20, 'The ocean is worth writing about just as man is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:01'),
(3384, 20, 'Man marks the earth with ruin - his control stops with the shore', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:11'),
(3385, 20, 'We are all connected to the ocean. Without healthy oceans, no life, not even on land, can exist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:21'),
(3386, 20, 'What you have to get is a ocean of love within your heart and to seek that in others also.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:29'),
(3387, 20, 'Our past, our present, and whatever remains of our future, absolutely depend on what we do now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:41'),
(3388, 20, 'Waves are the voices of tides. Tides are life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:31:53'),
(3389, 20, 'The ocean is a supreme metaphor for change. I expect the unexpected but am never fully prepared.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:32:01'),
(3390, 20, 'No nation ever had two better friends that we have. You know who they are? The Atlantic and Pacific oceans.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:32:10'),
(3391, 20, 'You\'re an island of reality in an ocean of diarrhea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:32:18'),
(3392, 20, 'Don\'t leave my ocean for shallow waters then ask me about the moon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:32:29'),
(3393, 20, 'The smallest oceans still make big big waves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:32:48'),
(3394, 20, 'With care and protection, with safe havens in the ocean, there is still a good chance that we can turn things around.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:33:00'),
(3395, 20, 'it is all ash and dry leaves and grief gone like an ocean liner.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:33:09'),
(3396, 20, 'But it\'s a big ocean. It\'s an even bigger world. And maybe we\'ve gotten as close as we\'re supposed to get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:33:17'),
(3397, 20, 'My heart resembles the ocean; has storm, and ebb and flow; and many a beautiful pearl lies hid in its depths below.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:33:29'),
(3398, 20, 'I\'m concerned about the ocean and the environment. And I love whales.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:33:43'),
(3399, 20, 'The world is a navy in an empty ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:34:18'),
(3400, 20, 'A desert blessing, an ocean curse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:34:27'),
(3401, 20, 'As the oceans go, so do we.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:34:36'),
(3402, 20, 'We are a blue planet and an ocean world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:34:46'),
(3403, 20, 'For ocean, whale is a small fish; for wise man, small fish is an ocean! Sun, hides in the candle!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:34:57'),
(3404, 20, 'I love just how beautiful Vancouver is. I mean, everywhere you look it\'s just mountains and ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:35:39'),
(3405, 20, 'There are so many issues in our oceans - like the near extinction of blue fin tuna - that should be taken more seriously worldwide.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:35:51'),
(3406, 20, 'The history of American women is all about leaving home - crossing oceans and continents, or getting jobs and living on their own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:36:04'),
(3407, 20, 'Listening to soft music and the sound of the ocean is quite relaxing to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:36:18'),
(3408, 20, 'I really feel that my body craves to be in the mountains or by the ocean or in the countryside.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:36:26'),
(3409, 20, 'The positive heuristic of the programme saves the scientist from becoming confused by the ocean of anomalies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:36:35'),
(3410, 20, 'You know, I do speak the Queens English. It\'s just the wrong Queens that\'s all. It\'s over the 59th Street Bridge. It\'s not over the Atlantic Ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:41:11'),
(3411, 20, 'Towns oftener swamp one than carry one out onto the big ocean of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:41:20'),
(3412, 20, 'How many whales do we really need? I figure five. One for each ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:41:28'),
(3413, 20, 'In the ocean of baseness, the deeper we get, the easier the sinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:41:40'),
(3414, 20, 'I also derive a great deal of pleasure from horses and dogs... the ocean... and love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:41:58'),
(3415, 20, 'I love the woods even more than the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:42:13'),
(3416, 20, 'We need to do a better job of keeping oceans healthy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:42:30'),
(3417, 20, 'I do a lot of swimming, both in the ocean and in the pool.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:42:40'),
(3418, 20, 'In this ocean of hours I\'m all the time drinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:42:55'),
(3419, 20, 'Sometimes there aren\'t words. The silence between us is flung wide as an ocean. But I manage to reach across it, to wrap my arms around him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:43:09'),
(3420, 20, 'We\'re all water from different rivers, That\'s why it\'s so easy to meet, We\'re all water in this vast, vast ocean, Someday we\'ll evaporate together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:43:19'),
(3421, 20, 'Tears have a purpose. they are what we carry of the ocean, and perhaps we must become the sea, give ourselves to it, if we are to be transformed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:43:39'),
(3422, 20, 'The ocean has been singing to me, and the song is that of our life together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:43:48'),
(3423, 20, 'She would be half a planet away, floating in a turquoise sea, dancing by moonlight to flamenco guitar.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:43:57'),
(3424, 20, 'How much deeper would the ocean be if sponges didn’t live there?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:44:33'),
(3425, 20, 'Talking to Francis gave me the sensation of settling slowly to the bottom of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:44:42'),
(3426, 20, 'Writing history is like drinking an ocean and pissing a cupful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:44:53'),
(3427, 20, 'An ocean without unnamed monsters would be like sleep without dreams.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:45:05'),
(3428, 20, 'We have spilt an ocean of blood for the brotherhood and unity of our peoples and we shall not allow anyone to touch or destroy it from within.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:45:16'),
(3429, 20, 'Ocean, Ocean I\'ll beat you in the end.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:45:24'),
(3430, 20, 'Sorrow is like the ocean and sometimes I wish my heart would stop.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:45:45'),
(3431, 20, 'I can never drive my car over a bridge without thinking of suicide. I can never look at a lake or an ocean without thinking of suicide.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:46:02'),
(3432, 20, 'There exists no God. What exists is godliness, and that godliness surrounds you. We are all in the same ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:46:10'),
(3433, 20, 'To see the ocean once is to learn how to miss it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:46:41'),
(3434, 20, 'I drink from a small spring, / my thirst excedes the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:46:49'),
(3435, 20, 'Day after day, day after day, We stuck, nor breath nor motion; As idle as a painted ship Upon a painted ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:02'),
(3436, 20, 'Here we go mother on the shipless ocean. Pity us, pity the ocean, here we go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:20'),
(3437, 20, 'I didn\'t flee a dictator or swim an ocean to be an American like some do. I just thought long and hard about it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:31'),
(3438, 20, 'It\'s all like an ocean!\" cried Dostoevski. I say it\'s all like cellophane.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:40'),
(3439, 20, 'I think there are two different oceans - the one that plays with you in the summer, and the one that gets so mad in the winter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:50'),
(3440, 20, 'I thought that the light-house looked lovely as hope, That star on life\'s tremulous ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:47:58'),
(3441, 20, 'when we\'re married, can we go to the ocean? I\'ve never been', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:48:23'),
(3442, 20, 'Comparing what you see during an eclipse to the darkness at night is like comparing an ocean to a teardrop.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:48:50'),
(3443, 20, 'You wouldn\'t think you could kill an ocean, would you? But we\'ll do it one day. That\'s how negligent we are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:48:59'),
(3444, 20, 'Somewhere in the ocean, a shark was missing its cold eyes because this man had them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:06'),
(3445, 20, 'There is a gulf as wide as an ocean between should and want, and I am drowning in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:15'),
(3446, 20, 'Dive deep into the ocean, Sita, and you will find that the greatest treasures you find are the illusions you leave behind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:23'),
(3447, 20, 'I’m telling you, trouble is like the ocean. It covers two thirds of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:32'),
(3448, 20, 'Men really do need sea-monsters in their personal oceans', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:40'),
(3449, 20, 'A string of bright white buildinh, glistening like teeth over the slurping mouth of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:49:50'),
(3450, 20, 'An untold story has a weight that can submerge you, sure as a sunken ship at the bottom of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:50:01'),
(3451, 20, 'Asking me to describe my son is like asking me to hold the ocean in a paper cup', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:50:24'),
(3452, 20, 'The car emitted on last gasp and rolled to a stop, in the middle of the Altlantic Ocean. \"We\'re here,\" Leven tried to joke.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:50:35'),
(3453, 20, 'You can\'t stop your heart from loving, really -- it\'s like standing out there in the ocean yelling at the waves to stop.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:50:44'),
(3454, 20, 'For all is like an ocean, all flows and connects; touch it in one place and it echoes at the other end of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:50:52'),
(3455, 20, 'It\'s the silence I imagine in the rest of the world, the silence of an endless ocean and uninhabitable island, a silence that can be seen from space.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:51:01'),
(3456, 20, 'You may not see the ocean, but right now we are in the middle of the ocean, and we have to keep swimming.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:51:30'),
(3457, 20, 'Finally, he knew the kind of loving that made two one and understood Jane was his world. His ocean, his country, his sun, his rain, his very heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:51:45'),
(3458, 20, 'Like a mermaid rising from an ocean of paper, the girl emerged across the room.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:51:54'),
(3459, 20, 'Surrounded, detached, in measureless oceans of space.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:52:02'),
(3460, 20, 'I cried a river of tears but he was too heavy to float on them. So I dragged him with me these years across an ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:52:11'),
(3461, 20, 'I felt like I was staring out across an ocean that I was going to have to swim from shore to shore before I could rest again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:52:44'),
(3462, 20, 'Everybody needs a seashell in her bathroom to remind her the ocean is her home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:53:04'),
(3463, 20, 'We\'d been trying to touch the sky from the bottom of the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:53:15'),
(3464, 20, 'It was like trying to bail out an ocean of water with a teaspoon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:53:31'),
(3465, 20, 'Break your pitcher against a rock. We don\'t need any longer to haul pieces of the ocean around.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:53:46'),
(3466, 20, 'Don’t wait any longer. Dive in the ocean, Leave and let the sea be you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:53:56'),
(3467, 20, 'At midnight the wind in the tress can sound like the ocean. The moonlight can make a road appear as endless as the sea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:54:05'),
(3468, 20, 'Because time is a drop in the ocean, and you cannot measure off one drop against another to see which one is bigger, which one is smaller.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:54:16'),
(3469, 20, 'When you were alone in the rising ocean, you grabbed whatever raft passed by.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:54:25'),
(3470, 20, 'Whenever I look at the ocean, I always want to talk to people, but when I\'m talking to people, I always want to look at the ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:54:36'),
(3471, 20, 'We\'d been trying to touch the sky from the bottom of the ocean. I realized that if we boosted one another, maybe we\'d get a little closer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:08'),
(3472, 20, 'How do you expect to communicate with the ocean, when you can’t even understand one another?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:21'),
(3473, 20, 'For quiet times disappear listen to the ocean', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:29'),
(3474, 20, 'For my love, I will wade through an ocean of blood, even if it destroys me', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:36'),
(3475, 20, 'He gave Marcie a spare to the Jeep—I should park this thing in the ocean, twenty feet under.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:45'),
(3476, 20, 'I don\'t trust the ocean, either; it would kill me as soon as not. It doesn\'t mean I\'m afraid of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:55:54'),
(3477, 20, 'If you ever want to see how small you are in the plan of God, just stand at the edge of an ocean.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:56:05'),
(3478, 20, 'For in dreams we enter a world that is entirely our own. Let them swim in the deepest ocean or glide over the highest cloud.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAOcean', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 16:56:13'),
(3479, 19, 'A dog will teach you unconditional love. If you can have that in your life, things won\'t be too bad.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-27 17:03:06'),
(3480, 19, 'I think dogs are the most amazing creatures; they give unconditional love. For me they are the role model for being alive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:11:56'),
(3481, 19, 'I wonder if other dogs think poodles are members of a weird religious cult.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:12:34'),
(3482, 19, 'Know yourself. Don\'t accept your dog\'s admiration as conclusive evidence that you are wonderful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:12:45'),
(3483, 19, 'Dogs\' lives are too short. Their only fault, really.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:12:55'),
(3484, 19, 'Such short little lives our pets have to spend with us, and they spend most of it waiting for us to come home each day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:04'),
(3485, 19, 'Dogs are our link to paradise. They don\'t know evil or jealousy or discontent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:12'),
(3486, 19, 'The only creatures that are evolved enough to convey pure love are dogs and infants.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:27'),
(3487, 19, 'Dogs are not our whole life, but they make our lives whole.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:37'),
(3488, 19, 'If you pick up a starving dog and make him prosperous he will not bite you. This is the principal difference between a dog and man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:45'),
(3489, 19, 'The greatness of a nation can be judged by the way its animals are treated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:13:55'),
(3490, 19, 'It\'s just the most amazing thing to love a dog, isn\'t it? It makes our relationships with people seem as boring as a bowl of oatmeal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:03'),
(3491, 19, 'I think we are drawn to dogs because they are the uninhibited creatures we might be if we weren\'t certain we knew better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:12'),
(3492, 19, 'A dog teaches a boy fidelity, perseverance, and to turn around three times before lying down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:20'),
(3493, 19, 'Dogs love their friends and bite their enemies, quite unlike people, who are incapable of pure love and always have to mix love and hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:29'),
(3494, 19, 'Heaven goes by favor. If it went by merit, you would stay out and your dog would go in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:39'),
(3495, 19, 'All his life he tried to be a good person. Many times, however, he failed. For after all, he was only human. He wasn\'t a dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:48'),
(3496, 19, 'Women and cats will do as they please, and men and dogs should relax and get used to the idea.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:14:57'),
(3497, 19, 'To sit with a dog on a hillside on a glorious afternoon is to be back in Eden, where doing nothing was not boring - it was peace.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:15:06'),
(3498, 19, 'You think dogs will not be in heaven? I tell you, they will be there long before any of us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:15:21'),
(3499, 19, 'I love a dog. He does nothing for political reasons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:15:34'),
(3500, 19, 'The average dog is a nicer person than the average person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:15:50'),
(3501, 19, 'Until one has loved an animal a part of one\'s soul remains unawakened.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:00'),
(3502, 19, 'Even the tiniest poodle is lionhearted, ready to do anything to defend home, master, and mistress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:10'),
(3503, 19, 'Money can buy you a fine dog, but only love can make him wag his tail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:21'),
(3504, 19, 'Whoever said you can\'t buy Happiness forgot little puppies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:31'),
(3505, 19, 'I am fond of pigs. Dogs look up to us. Cats look down on us. Pigs treat us as equals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:39'),
(3506, 19, 'A dog is the only thing on earth that loves you more than you love yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:16:52'),
(3507, 19, 'Everything I know, I learned from dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:01'),
(3508, 19, 'If I have any beliefs about immortality, it is that certain dogs I have known will go to heaven, and very, very few persons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:13'),
(3509, 19, 'There is no psychiatrist in the world like a puppy licking your face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:22'),
(3510, 19, 'If there are no dogs in Heaven, then when I die I want to go where they went.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:31'),
(3511, 19, 'The dog is a gentleman; I hope to go to his heaven not man\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:44'),
(3512, 19, 'Dogs never bite me. Just humans.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:17:53'),
(3513, 19, 'The more boys I meet the more I love my dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:18:04'),
(3514, 19, 'Our perfect companions never have fewer than four feet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:18:15'),
(3515, 19, 'Buy a pup and your money will buy Love unflinching that cannot lie.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:18:26'),
(3516, 19, 'Did you know that there are over three hundred words for love in canine?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:18:35'),
(3517, 19, 'The misery of keeping a dog is his dying so soon. But, to be sure, if he lived for fifty years and then died, what would become of me?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:18:54'),
(3518, 19, 'Dogs just need you and love, that\'s all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:02'),
(3519, 19, 'Everybody loves dogs. They\'re the pizza of the animal kingdom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:12'),
(3520, 19, 'I used to love dogs until I discovered cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:22'),
(3521, 19, 'Dogs love us not only because we feed them, walk them, or groom them, or protect them, but because we are fun. How astonishing!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:31'),
(3522, 19, 'I love dogs, but dogs, you have to be in the country with dogs. I cannot walk a dog on the street.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:40'),
(3523, 19, 'I love dogs. Like, A LOT. They’re my favorite animal. Ever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:19:49'),
(3524, 19, 'Dogs are actually very smart, it\'s just that they\'re rather clumsy, but it\'s this trait that makes humans attracted to them and why I love dogs so much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:01'),
(3525, 19, 'I\'m an equestrian, so I like to ride. Ride horses, I love to hike with my dog, love to travel. Most recently I went to Costa Rica, which I loved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:11'),
(3526, 19, 'My dogs love me. Of course, by love I mean poop and by me I mean everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:22'),
(3527, 19, 'Just thinking that my dog loves me more than I love him, I feel shame.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:31'),
(3528, 19, 'Dogs love to go for rides. A dog will happily get into any vehicle going anywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:40'),
(3529, 19, 'I\'ve grown up with dogs and love dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:20:51'),
(3530, 19, 'Let us love dogs; let us love only dogs! Men and cats are unworthy creatures.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:21:02'),
(3531, 19, 'I petted the dogs who didn\'t argue with me ever. All dogs love God. They\'re wiser than their masters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:21:22'),
(3532, 19, 'I love dogs because they\'re so adaptable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:21:31'),
(3533, 19, 'I really love dogs. When I see a dog, I go crazy, it\'s like, “Oh my God, come here, come here!”', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:21:42'),
(3534, 19, 'Dogs love us unconditionally and cats are big on redemption. Our sins and shortcomings don\'t bother them as long as we delight in their presence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:22:04'),
(3535, 19, 'Just as the dog loves to chew bones, the human mind loves its problems.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:22:15'),
(3536, 19, 'I just love dogs, and there really is no better companion than an animal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:22:24'),
(3537, 19, 'Dogs love company. They place it first on their short list of needs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:22:34'),
(3538, 19, 'I think dogs are the most amazing creatures; they give unconditional love. For me they are the role model for being alive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:24:21'),
(3539, 19, 'Who loves me will love my dog also.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:24:30'),
(3540, 19, 'The more I learn about people, the more I like my dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:24:39'),
(3541, 19, 'Until one has loved an animal a part of one\'s soul remains unawakened.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2022-05-28 04:24:47'),
