(6899, 48, '(Cartoon caption:) I never really rallied after the birth of my first child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:40:44'),
(6900, 48, 'How pleasant it is for a father to sit at his child\'s board. It is like an aged man reclining under the shadow of an oak which he has planted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:40:52'),
(6901, 48, 'Listen to the desires of your children. Encourage them and then give them the autonomy to make their own decision.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:41:04'),
(6902, 48, 'When correcting a child, the goal is to apply light, not heat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:41:14'),
(6903, 48, 'The saddest things we fail at are fun things we never get to do, so in your busy day be sure to plan fun things too.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:41:23'),
(6904, 48, 'Family is a collective expression of individual perspective-a living work of art.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:41:54'),
(6905, 48, 'If there is any truth to my parenting the dreamwork movement, it comes from the power of the press.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:42:03'),
(6906, 48, 'OF COURSE I\'d like to be the ideal mother. But I\'m too busy raising children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:42:12'),
(6907, 48, 'The American Dream is not to own your own home, but to get your kids out of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:42:21'),
(6908, 48, 'Better a little chiding than a great deal of heartbreak.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:42:31'),
(6909, 48, 'The trick is to enjoy life. Don\'t wish away your days waiting for better ones ahead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:42:40'),
(6910, 48, 'The greatest treasure you can leave your children is a sense of modesty and the advice to follow virtuous persons.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:08'),
(6911, 48, 'Every happy home has a foundation of love and a framework of support', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:18'),
(6912, 48, 'Alas, regardless of their doom, the little victims play! No sense have they of ills to come nor care beyond today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:27'),
(6913, 48, 'The world\'s greatest changes are made at home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:36'),
(6914, 48, 'A family portrait is only complete with love to fill it\'s frame.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:44'),
(6915, 48, 'Was it Gorky who had said, \"If your children are no better than you are, you have fathered them in vain, indeed you have lived in vain\".', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:43:56'),
(6916, 48, '(About parenting:) ... all that tedium, broken up by little spurts of high drama.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:44:05'),
(6917, 48, 'Parents are key when it comes to keeping kids off drugs. Good parenting is the best anti-drug we have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:44:13'),
(6918, 48, 'Your typical Six-year-old is a paradoxical little person, and bipolarity is the name of his game', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:44:34'),
(6919, 48, 'Breasts are a scandal because they shatter the border between motherhood and sexuality', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:44:46'),
(6920, 48, 'My father wasn\'t really involved and my mom is the light in my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:45:25'),
(6921, 48, 'Parents, they\'re strict on you when you\'re little, and you don\'t understand why. But as you get older, you understand and you appreciate it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:45:39'),
(6922, 48, 'Education, like neurosis, begins at home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:45:47'),
(6923, 48, 'Kindness effects more than severity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:06'),
(6924, 48, 'Parents were invented to make children happy by giving them something to ignore.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:15'),
(6925, 48, 'Home life\'s great, man. The kids are great, happy and healthy. I\'ve reached this sort of wonderful precipice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:23'),
(6926, 48, 'The gain is not the having of children; it is the discovery of love and how to be loving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:32'),
(6927, 48, 'Conduct yourself towards your parents as you would have your children conduct themselves towards you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:42'),
(6928, 48, 'Don\'t quarrel with your parents even if you are on the right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:46:51'),
(6929, 48, 'Well, I just want him to grow up happy. That\'s the main thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:00'),
(6930, 48, 'Youth should stay away from all evil, especially things that produce wickedness and ill-will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:09'),
(6931, 48, 'I just sat all night looking at him, saying, \'Wow, it\'s incredible.\' When Yoko woke up, I told her, \'He\'s fine,\' and we cried.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:18'),
(6932, 48, 'Women are individuals in parenting, and why not?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:28'),
(6933, 48, 'My mom\'s a Catholic, and my dad\'s a Jew, and they didn\'t want anything to do with anything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:37'),
(6934, 48, 'No blade can puncture the human heart like the well-chosen words of a spiteful son.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:47:51'),
(6935, 48, 'I would have made a terrible parent. The first time my child didn\'t do what I wanted, I\'d kill him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:48:01'),
(6936, 48, 'Be The Peace You Wish To See In The World!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:48:22'),
(6937, 48, 'A lot of mothers will do anything for their children, except let them be themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:48:31'),
(6938, 48, 'Work at our responsibility as parents as if everything in life counted on it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:48:42'),
(6939, 48, 'Attachment parenting demands not just certain actions you take with your baby but also certain emotional states to accompany those actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:48:56'),
(6940, 48, 'There are only two things a child will share willingly; communicable diseases and its mother\'s age.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:49:34'),
(6941, 48, 'I thought that once we were out of the baby stage, parenting would be a breeze.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:49:45'),
(6942, 48, 'It is a wise father that knows his own child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:49:56'),
(6943, 48, 'Be sure to lie to your kids about the benevolent, all-seeing Santa Claus. It will prepare them for an adulthood of believing in God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:50:05'),
(6944, 48, 'Sometimes, kids want you to hurt the way they hurt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:50:17'),
(6945, 48, 'You are the reason why he exists on this earth. You don\'t have the right to abandon him just because he\'s inconvenient or has trouble in school.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:50:31'),
(6946, 48, 'In the home begins the disruption of the peace of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:50:43'),
(6947, 48, 'As someone very sagely said during the parricide trials of the Menendez Brothers: anytime your kids kill you, you are at least partly to blame.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:51:26'),
(6948, 48, 'I would have given anything to keep her little. They outgrow us so much faster than we outgrow them. Brian Fitzgerald, talking about his children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:51:36'),
(6949, 48, 'And my parents finally realize I\'m kidnapped and they snap into action immediately: They rent out my room.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:51:45'),
(6950, 48, 'There is no such thing as fun for the whole family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:51:54'),
(6951, 48, 'Children are our second chance to have a great parent-child relationship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:52:03'),
(6952, 48, 'What lingers from the parent\'s individual past, unresolved or incomplete, often becomes part of her or his irrational parenting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:52:11'),
(6953, 48, 'There\'s really no point in having children if you\'re not going to be home enough to father them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:52:21'),
(6954, 48, 'I want my children to have all the things I couldn\'t afford. Then I want to move in with them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:52:30'),
(6955, 48, 'The other night I ate at a real nice family restaurant. Every table had an argument going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:52:40'),
(6956, 48, 'Among my most prized possessions are words that I have never spoken.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:53:09'),
(6957, 48, 'If we had paid no more attention to our plants than we have to our children, we would now be living in a jungle of weed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:53:19'),
(6958, 48, 'The young do not know enough to be prudent, and therefore they attempt the impossible - and achieve it, generation after generation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:53:33'),
(6959, 48, 'Having a baby changes the way you view your in-laws. I love it when they come to visit now. They can hold the baby and I can go out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:53:43'),
(6960, 48, 'When a child is locked in the bathroom with water running and he says he\'s doing nothing but the dog is barking, call 911.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:53:55'),
(6961, 48, 'I know how to do anything, I\'m a mom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:54:06'),
(6962, 48, 'The heart of a mother is a deep abyss at the bottom of which you will always find forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:54:14'),
(6963, 48, 'A mother who is really a mother is never free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:59:36'),
(6964, 48, 'Don\'t try to make children grow up to be like you, or they may do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 17:59:55'),
(6965, 48, 'Of course, the ideal scenario for parenting is obviously two parents of a mature age.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:00:21'),
(6966, 48, 'In mere moments of togetherness, families forge their most indelibe memories.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:00:30'),
(6967, 48, 'Life began with waking up and loving my mother\'s face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:00:38'),
(6968, 48, 'Mothers are all slightly insane.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:00:47'),
(6969, 48, 'The trouble with the world is that the stupid are cocksure and the intelligent are full of doubt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:00:55');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(6970, 48, 'Neurotics build castles in the air, psychotics live in them. My mother cleans them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:03'),
(6971, 48, 'Both of my parents got to see me host Carson, thank God. That\'s all anyone wants: to have their parents see they\'re going to be all right in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:13'),
(6972, 48, 'Whatever happened to the good ole days, when children worked in factories?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:23'),
(6973, 48, 'Do your kids a favor - don\'t have any.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:32'),
(6974, 48, 'To me luxury is to be at home with my daughter, and the occasional massage doesn\'t hurt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:42'),
(6975, 48, 'If help and salvation are to come they can only come from the children, for the children are the makers of men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:01:51'),
(6977, 48, 'Always render more and better service than is expected of you, no matter what your task may be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:02:26'),
(6978, 48, 'I grew up with six brothers. That\'s how I learned to dance - waiting for the bathroom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:03:07'),
(6979, 48, 'Both my mother and father were very supportive of any career move any of us wanted to make.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:03:19'),
(6980, 48, 'Blessed is the man, who having nothing to say, abstains from giving wordy evidence of the fact.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:03:28'),
(6981, 48, 'Children\'s talent to endure stems from their ignorance of alternatives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:03:40'),
(6982, 48, 'A man can\'t be in the space where there is feminine rage and bitterness. He doesn\'t know how to navigate it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:03:51'),
(6983, 48, 'Relationships are complicated no matter what style of parenting you choose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:04:01'),
(6984, 48, 'All mothers think their children are oaks, but the world never lacks for cabbages.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:04:09'),
(6985, 48, 'When I stopped seeing my mother with the eyes of a child, I saw the woman who helped me give birth to myself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:04:36'),
(6986, 48, 'Mother: the most beautiful word on the lips of mankind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:04:44'),
(6987, 48, 'The love of a parent for a child is the love that should grow towards separation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:04:52'),
(6988, 48, 'Don\'t let the sun go down without saying thank you to someone, and without admitting to yourself that absolutely no one gets this far alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:04'),
(6989, 48, 'This is probably one of the most difficult challenges any parent could face - learning to love the other parent enough to make the children first.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:16'),
(6990, 48, 'Why are you measuring? This is how you block, delay, hinder, obstruct and deny his place in the life as a father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:25'),
(6991, 48, 'You never put her in your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:33'),
(6992, 48, 'There are going to be moments today you don\'t like me. You\'ll get over it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:43'),
(6993, 48, 'The true test of a person\'s character is how they treat the people in life that they don\'t need.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:05:55'),
(6994, 48, 'Nothing is more characteristically juvenile than contempt for juvenility. . . youth\'s characteristic chronological snobbery.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:06:03'),
(6995, 48, 'If someone feels that he has never made a mistake in his life, it only means that he has never tried anything new in his life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:06:12'),
(6996, 48, 'We have not passed that subtle line between childhood and adulthood until we have stopped saying \'It got lost,\' and say, \'I lost it.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:06:20'),
(6997, 48, 'The fact that someone says something doesn\'t mean it\'s true. Doesn\'t mean they\'re lying, but it doesn\'t mean it\'s true.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:06:29'),
(6998, 48, 'The problem with children is that you have to put up with their parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:07:03'),
(6999, 48, 'The fact that boys are allowed to exist at all is evidence of a remarkable Christian forebearance among men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:07:11'),
(7000, 48, 'Give a small boy a hammer and he will find that everything he encounters needs pounding.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:07:21'),
(7001, 48, 'Now, as always, the most automated appliance in a household is the mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:07:29'),
