(7004, 48, 'Many a man wishes he were strong enough to tear a telephone book in half - especially if he has a teenage daughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:07:41'),
(7005, 48, 'No animal is so inexhaustible as an excited infant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:09'),
(7006, 48, 'A baby is an inestimable blessing and bother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:17'),
(7007, 48, 'Always obey your parents - when they are present.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:26'),
(7008, 48, 'The worst fault of the working classes is telling their children they\'re not going to succeed, saying: There is life, but it\'s not for you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:35'),
(7009, 48, 'It is the function of parents to see that their children habitually experience the true consequences of their conduct.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:44'),
(7010, 48, 'Your children are not your children, they come through you, but they are life itself, wanting to express itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:08:52'),
(7011, 48, 'My parents taught me I could be anything in the world I wanted to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:09:01'),
(7012, 48, 'The greatest happiness is family happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:09:09'),
(7013, 48, 'I\'m not going to have a better day, a more magical moment than the first time I heard my daughter giggle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:09:17'),
(7014, 48, 'I\'ve always wanted to be a mom. Because I want to give a kid all of the magical gifts my mom gave me, such as love and friendship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:09:27'),
(7015, 48, 'I talk and talk and talk, and I haven\'t taught people in 50 years what my father taught by example in one week.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:09:41'),
(7016, 48, 'The mind is like the stomach. It is not how much you put into it that counts, but how much it digests...', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:05'),
(7017, 48, 'The way you help heal the world is you start with your own family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:14'),
(7018, 48, 'Ask the young. They know everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:24'),
(7019, 48, 'Minds are like parachutes, they only function when they are open.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:36'),
(7020, 48, 'When everything goes to hell, the people who stand by you without flinching - they are your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:45'),
(7021, 48, 'Love is the chain whereby to bind a child to its parents.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:10:55'),
(7022, 48, 'By the time a man realizes that his father was right, he has a son who thinks he\'s wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:04'),
(7023, 48, 'Be original. The world will try to fit you into a mold, but carve your own path.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:12'),
(7024, 48, 'Be original. The world will try to fit you into a mold, but carve your own path.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:20'),
(7025, 48, 'The surest way to a child\'s heart is to spend time with them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:30'),
(7026, 48, 'Love is giving your kids your undivided attention and time', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:38'),
(7027, 48, 'Biology makes us Mothers & Fathers, whats in the heart makes us Mom\'s and Dad\'s', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:46'),
(7028, 48, 'The best gift is giving from your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:11:57'),
(7029, 48, 'What I love about kids is there innate ability to love unconditionally - we can all learn from this.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:12:09'),
(7030, 48, 'Parents need to listen as much to their kids as they do to them: \"The first duty of love is to listen.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:12:19'),
(7031, 48, 'Communicating w/kids, its a 2 way street, sometimes they just need us to be there for them & listen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:12:27'),
(7032, 48, 'Without the support from religion--remember, we talked about it--no father, using only his own resources, would be able to bring up a child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:12:36'),
(7033, 48, 'The teacher who is indeed wise does not bid you to enter the house of his wisdom but rather leads you to the threshold of your mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:12:45'),
(7034, 48, 'Youth fades, love droops, the leaves of friendship fall; A mother\'s secret hope outlives them all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:13:00'),
(7035, 48, 'Any kid will run any errand for you, if you ask at bedtime.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:13:38'),
(7036, 48, 'Mother\'s love is peace. It need not be acquired, it need not be deserved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:13:47'),
(7037, 48, 'Being a mother is an attitude, not a biological relation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:13:56'),
(7038, 48, 'It is time for parents to teach young people early on that in diversity there is beauty and there is strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:05'),
(7039, 48, 'Happiness is having a large, loving, caring, close-knit family in another city.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:15'),
(7040, 48, 'Some people care too much. I think it\'s called love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:24'),
(7041, 48, 'I knew I was an unwanted baby when I saw that my bath toys were a toaster and a radio.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:33'),
(7042, 48, 'When I was a kid my parents moved a lot, but I always found them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:42'),
(7043, 48, 'Vulnerability sounds like truth and feels like courage. Truth and courage aren\'t always comfortable, but they\'re never weakness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:50'),
(7044, 48, 'A happy family is but an earlier heaven.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:14:59'),
(7045, 48, 'Our vision is more obstructed by what we think we know than by our lack of knowledge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:15:07'),
(7046, 48, 'When you can do the common things of life in an uncommon way, you will command the attention of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:15:19'),
(7047, 48, 'In the end, it\'s not the years in your life that count. It\'s the life in your years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:15:28'),
(7048, 48, 'The reason grandparents and grandchildren get along so well is that they have a common enemy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:15:37'),
(7049, 48, 'Common sense is the collection of prejudices acquired by age eighteen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:15:46'),
(7050, 48, 'The mind is not a vessel to be filled but a fire to be kindled.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:16:38'),
(7051, 48, 'You know the only people who are always sure about the proper way to raise children? Those who\'ve never had any.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:16:54'),
(7052, 48, 'There are obviously two educations. One should teach us how to make a living and the other how to live.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:17:02'),
(7053, 48, 'Learning without thought is labor lost; thought without learning is perilous.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:17:13'),
(7054, 48, 'I\'ve learned that you shouldn\'t go through life with a catcher\'s mitt on both hands; you need to be able to throw something back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAParenting', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-07-30 18:17:21'),
(7055, 28, 'Adversity has the effect of eliciting talents which, in prosperous circumstances, would have lain dormant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:01'),
(7056, 28, 'The person who makes a success of living is the one who sees his goal steadily and aims for it unswervingly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:11'),
(7057, 28, 'You can\'t expect to hit the jackpot if you don\'t put a few nickels in the machine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:19'),
(7058, 28, 'Courage is doing what you are afraid to do. There can be no courage unless you are scared.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:28'),
(7059, 28, 'Genius is one percent inspiration, ninety-nine percent perspiration.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:37'),
(7060, 28, 'If you don\'t like something, change it. If you can\'t change it, change your attitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:45'),
(7061, 28, 'The difference between average people and achieving people is their perception of and response to...failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:19:54'),
(7062, 28, 'You\'re not obligated to win. You\'re obligated to keep trying to do the best you can every day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:03'),
(7063, 28, 'Success seems to be largely a matter of hanging on after others have let go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:11'),
(7064, 28, 'No amount of reading or memorizing will make you successful in life. It is the understanding and application of wise thought which counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:23'),
(7065, 28, 'One of the secrets to success is ideas mixed with inspiration', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:31'),
(7066, 28, 'The greater danger for most of us lies not in setting our aim too high and falling short; but in setting our aim too low, and achieving our mark.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:40'),
(7067, 28, 'Success is that old ABC: ability, breaks and courage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:20:52'),
(7068, 28, 'That man is a success who has lived well, laughed often and loved much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:00'),
(7069, 28, 'The toughest thing about success is that you\'ve got to keep on being a success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:07'),
(7070, 28, 'A wise man will make more opportunities than he finds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:16'),
(7071, 28, 'The best way to have a good idea is to have a lot of ideas.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:26'),
(7072, 28, 'Your time is limited, so don\'t waste it living someone else\'s life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:35'),
(7073, 28, 'I\'ve failed over and over and over again in my life and that is why I succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:45'),
(7074, 28, 'The best revenge is massive success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:21:53'),
(7075, 28, 'Along with success comes a reputation for wisdom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:01'),
(7076, 28, 'Genius is seldom recognized for what it is: a great capacity for hard work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:09'),
(7077, 28, 'Every negative event contains within it the seed of an equal or greater benefit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:17'),
(7078, 28, 'Don\'t mistake activity with achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:35'),
(7079, 28, 'Do not seek dishonest gains: dishonest gains are losses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:43'),
(7080, 28, 'Success is never owned, it is rented, and the rent is due every day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:22:55'),
(7081, 28, 'Few men have the natural strength to honor a friend\'s success without envy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:02'),
(7082, 28, 'When it comes to success, there are no shortcuts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:11'),
(7083, 28, 'I believe if you follow your heart and do what you love, success will follow. If you enchant yourself, others will be too.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:20'),
(7084, 28, 'Success is like reaching an important birthday and finding you\'re exactly the same.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:27'),
(7085, 28, 'It is only as we develop others that we permanently succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:35'),
(7086, 28, 'The penalty for success is to be bored by the people who used to snub you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:43'),
(7087, 28, 'Whenever an individual or a business decides that success has been attained, progress stops.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:23:51'),
(7088, 28, 'I believe the greater the handicap, the greater the triumph.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:00'),
(7089, 28, 'Even if you\'re on the right track, you\'ll get run over if you just sit there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:08'),
(7090, 28, 'It\'s kind of fun to do the impossible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:15'),
(7091, 28, 'A great leader\'s courage to fulfill his vision comes from passion, not position.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:23'),
(7092, 28, 'The first requisite of success is the ability to apply your physical and mental energies to one problem without growing weary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:31'),
(7093, 28, 'Failure is simply a few errors in judgment, repeated every day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:39'),
(7094, 28, 'Failures are finger posts on the road to achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:47'),
(7095, 28, 'If you can be the best, then why not try to be the best?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:24:55'),
(7096, 28, 'Envy was just the tax you paid on success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:25:02'),
(7097, 28, 'To find someone who will love you through success and failure is to discover how little life has to do with either.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:25:10'),
(7098, 28, 'Definiteness of purpose is the starting point of all achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:25:37'),
(7099, 28, 'The hopeful man sees success where others see failure, sunshine where others see shadows and storm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:25:45'),
(7100, 28, 'Nothing ever comes to one, that is worth having, except as a result of hard work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:25:56'),
(7101, 28, 'Our greatest weakness lies in giving up. The most certain way to succeed is always to try just one more time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:26:15'),
(7102, 28, 'What we hope ever to do with ease, we must learn first to do with diligence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:26:24'),
(7103, 28, 'Don\'t let yesterday use up too much of today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:29:32'),
(7104, 28, 'The great secret of success is to go through life as a man who never gets used to failing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:29:40'),
(7105, 28, 'I don\'t believe in failure. It is not failure if you enjoyed the process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:29:48'),
(7106, 28, 'A business that makes nothing but money is a poor business.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:29:58'),
(7107, 28, 'The only time you mustn\'t fail is the last time you try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:30:06'),
(7109, 28, 'A leader has the vision and conviction that a dream can be achieved. He inspires the power and energy to get it done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:30:37'),
(7110, 28, 'Often we look so long at the closed door that we do not see the one that has been opened for us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:30:46'),
(7111, 28, 'You know you are on the road to success if you would do your job, and not be paid for it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:30:54'),
(7112, 28, 'Success is the doing, not the getting - in the trying, not the triumph.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:03'),
(7113, 28, 'A strenuous soul hates cheap success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:15'),
(7114, 28, 'One person with a belief is equal to ninety-nine who have only interests.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:23'),
(7115, 28, 'The bigger the dream, the more important to the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:31'),
(7116, 28, 'I know the price of success: dedication, hard work, and an unremitting devotion to the things you want to see happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:40'),
(7117, 28, 'Technology is just a tool. In terms of getting the kids working together and motivating them, the teacher is the most important.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:31:50'),
(7118, 28, 'The difficulties and struggles of today are but the price we must pay for the accomplishments and victories of tomorrow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:32:19'),
(7119, 28, 'Without hard work, nothing grows but weeds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:32:27'),
(7120, 28, 'Success is the necessary misfortune of life, but it is only to the very unfortunate that it comes early.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:32:37'),
(7121, 28, 'Big pay and little responsibility are circumstances seldom found together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:32:45'),
(7122, 28, 'A superior man is modest in his speech, but exceeds in his actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:33:03'),
(7123, 28, 'An entrepreneur assumes the risk and is dedicated and committed to the success of whatever he or she undertakes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:33:12'),
(7124, 28, 'We must never be afraid to go too far, for truth lies beyond.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:33:21'),
(7125, 28, 'Success is not the measure of a man but a triumph over those who choose to hold him back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:33:43'),
(7126, 28, 'Do the very best you can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:33:51'),
(7127, 28, 'Almost every successful person begins with two beliefs: the future can be better than the present, and I have the power to make it so.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:05'),
(7128, 28, 'Flaming enthusiasm, backed up by horse sense and persistence, is the quality that most frequently makes for success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:14'),
(7129, 28, 'If you can dream it, you can do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:22'),
(7130, 28, 'Impatience never commanded success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:30'),
(7131, 28, 'Nothing that is worth doing can be achieved in a lifetime; therefore we must be saved by hope.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:38'),
(7132, 28, 'It takes strength to be gentle and kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:46'),
(7133, 28, 'The most important single ingredient in the formula of success is knowing how to get along with people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:34:57'),
(7134, 28, 'Desire is the starting point of all achievement, not a hope, not a wish, but a keen pulsating desire which transcends everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:35:06'),
(7135, 28, 'Put your heart, mind, and soul into even your smallest acts. This is the secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:35:14'),
(7136, 28, 'Everything has a price, including both success and failure. Choose either one and be prepared to pay the price.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:35:32'),
(7137, 28, 'Success is relative. It is what we make of the mess we have made of things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:35:46'),
(7138, 28, 'Eighty percent of success is showing up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:35:56'),
(7139, 28, 'Unless you try to do something beyond what you have already mastered, you will never grow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:36:14'),
(7140, 28, 'I\'ve always believed that I could do whatever I set my mind to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:36:23'),
(7141, 28, 'In order to succeed, your desire for success should be greater than your fear of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:38:48'),
(7142, 28, 'If you are always trying to be normal you will never know how amazing you can be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:38:56'),
(7143, 28, 'If at first you don\'t succeed, lie, lie again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:39:10'),
(7144, 28, 'Visionaries see the \"impossible\" as the inevitable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:39:25'),
(7145, 28, 'If you care at all,you\'ll get some results. If you care enough, you\'ll get incredible results.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:39:33'),
(7146, 28, 'Fear of failure leads to failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:39:41'),
(7147, 28, 'Remember this: Anticipation is the ultimate power. Losers react; leaders anticipate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:39:49'),
(7148, 28, 'A rejection is nothing more than a necessary step in the pursuit of success', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:40:01'),
(7149, 28, 'People are not lazy. They simply have impotent goals - that is, goals that do not inspire them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:40:09'),
(7150, 28, 'Success is never final, but failure can be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:40:19'),
(7151, 28, 'The golden rule for every business man is this: \'Put yourself in your customer\'s place.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:40:33'),
(7152, 28, 'How can smart women be so stupid about men sometimes? Lack of knowledge. It\'s what men have kept secret for so long.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:40:57'),
(7153, 28, 'You never achieve success unless you like what you are doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:43:08'),
(7154, 28, 'If you\'re interested in \'balancing\' work and pleasure, stop trying to balance them. Instead make your work more pleasurable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:43:25'),
(7155, 28, 'Pray that success will not come any faster than you are able to endure it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:43:34'),
(7156, 28, 'Excellence is doing ordinary things extraordinarily well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:43:44'),
(7157, 28, 'The secret of our success is that we never, never give up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:43:54'),
(7158, 28, 'Defeat is not the worst of failures. Not to have tried is the true failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:11'),
(7159, 28, 'Why does a woman work ten years to change a man\'s habits and then complain that he\'s not the man she married?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:20'),
(7160, 28, 'If you cannot explain it simply, you do not understand it enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:29'),
(7161, 28, 'Achievement is talent plus preparation', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:37'),
(7162, 28, 'I think we\'re having fun. I think our customers really like our products. And we\'re always trying to do better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:45'),
(7163, 28, 'Only those who dare to fail greatly can ever achieve greatly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:44:54'),
(7164, 28, 'The most important thing is to not stop questioning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:03'),
(7165, 28, 'The freedom to do your best means nothing unless you are willing to do your best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:12'),
(7166, 28, 'The freedom to do your best means nothing unless you are willing to do your best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:13'),
(7167, 28, 'Great victory requires great risk. -Hera', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:21'),
(7168, 28, 'Who wanted to creep along in comfort when there was one chance in a thousand of flying?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:28'),
(7169, 28, 'A person with a new idea is a crank until the idea succeeds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:37'),
(7170, 28, 'The superior man makes the difficulty to be overcome his first interest; success only comes later.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:47'),
(7171, 28, 'We must learn to apply all that we know so that we can attract all that we want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:45:55'),
(7172, 28, 'Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:46:05'),
(7173, 28, 'To become an able and successful man in any profession, three things are necessary, nature, study and practice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:46:12'),
(7174, 28, 'Long-term success is never achieved on our own. The phrase \'a self-made man\' is a myth all along the way we need support.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:46:21'),
(7175, 28, 'Begin now what you will be hereafter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:46:45'),
(7176, 28, 'The road to success is dotted with many tempting parking spaces.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:46:53'),
(7178, 28, 'If you cannot do great things, do small things in a great way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:47:33'),
(7179, 28, 'To be an overachiever you have to be an over believer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:47:41'),
(7180, 28, 'I have not failed. I\'ve just found 10,000 ways that won\'t work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:47:50'),
(7181, 28, 'This, then, is the test we must set for ourselves; not to march alone but to march in such a way that others will wish to join us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:47:59'),
(7182, 28, 'Many of life\'s failures are people who did not realize how close they were to success when they gave up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:48:41'),
(7183, 28, 'Have a dream, make a plan, go for it. You\'ll get there, I promise.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:48:49'),
(7184, 28, 'What a pity human beings can\'t exchange problems. Everyone knows exactly how to solve the other fellow\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:48:58'),
(7185, 28, 'People seldom see the halting and painful steps by which the most insignificant success is achieved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:49:07'),
(7186, 28, 'All great achievements require time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:49:16'),
(7187, 28, 'Chop your own wood and it will warm you twice', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:49:30'),
(7188, 28, 'The most successful men in the end are those whose success is the result of steady accretion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:49:42'),
(7189, 28, 'A man to carry on a successful business must have imagination. He must see things in a vision, a dream of the whole thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:49:50'),
(7190, 28, 'Begin with the end in mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:04'),
(7191, 28, 'You may be disappointed if you fail, but you are doomed if you don\'t try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:14'),
(7192, 28, 'Failure I can live with. Not trying is what I can\'t handle!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:24'),
(7193, 28, 'Before everything else, getting ready is the secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:33'),
(7194, 28, 'Success is not about who never fails. It is about who can spring - or even stagger - back up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:43'),
(7195, 28, 'The great accomplishments of man have resulted from the transmission of ideas and enthusiasm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:51'),
(7196, 28, 'Don\'t aim for success if you want it; just do what you love and believe in, and it will come naturally.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:50:59'),
(7197, 28, 'When I was young, I observed that nine out of ten things I did were failures. So I did ten times more work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:51:08'),
(7198, 28, 'The ladder of success is best climbed by stepping on the rungs of opportunity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:51:16'),
(7199, 28, 'I couldn\'t wait for success, so I went ahead without it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:51:25'),
(7200, 28, 'Carry your most important goal in your wallet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:51:38'),
(7201, 28, 'The only guarantee for failure is to stop trying.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:51:48'),
(7202, 28, 'Thinking should become your capital asset, no matter whatever ups and downs you come across in your life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:55:58'),
(7203, 28, 'The only place success comes before work is in the dictionary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:57:12'),
(7204, 28, 'We got to keep on being a success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:57:20'),
(7205, 28, 'The road to success is wherever people need another road.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:57:29'),
(7206, 28, 'The noblest search is the search for excellence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:57:56'),
(7207, 28, 'Act the way you\'d like to be and soon you\'ll be the way you act.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:04'),
(7208, 28, 'There is only one success - to be able to spend your life in your own way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:16'),
(7209, 28, 'Do not wait until the conditions are perfect to begin. Beginning makes the conditions perfect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:28'),
(7210, 28, 'Success is the child of drudgery and perseverance. It cannot be coaxed or bribed; pay the price and it is yours.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:37'),
(7211, 28, 'There is always room at the top.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:45'),
(7212, 28, 'Success is a journey, not a destination. The doing is often more important than the outcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:58:53'),
(7213, 28, 'We are made for loving. If we don’t love, we will be like plants without water.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:59:13'),
(7214, 28, 'Motivation is a fire from within. If someone else tries to light that fire under you, chances are it will burn very briefly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 16:59:37'),
(7215, 28, 'Expect the best, Prepare for the worst.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:00:39'),
(7216, 28, 'If you find a path with no obstacles, it probably doesn\'t lead anywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:00:49'),
(7217, 28, 'I don\'t deserve this award, but I have arthritis and I don\'t deserve that either.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:00:57'),
(7218, 28, 'It is a rough road that leads to the heights of greatness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:01:11'),
(7220, 28, 'Success is getting what you want. Happiness is wanting what you get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:02:00'),
(7221, 28, 'I don\'t know the key to success, but the key to failure is trying to please everybody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:02:33'),
(7223, 28, 'Don\'t judge each day by the harvest you reap but by the seeds that you plant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:03:21'),
(7224, 28, 'Destiny is no matter of chance. It is a matter of choice. It is not a thing to be waited for, it is a thing to be achieved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:03:49'),
(7225, 28, 'Success consists of going from failure to failure without loss of enthusiasm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:03:58'),
(7226, 28, 'Learn from the negative as well as the positive, from the failures as well as the successes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:04:07'),
(7227, 28, 'Success is a personal standard, reaching for the highest that is in us, becoming all that we can be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:03'),
(7228, 28, 'Never doubt that a small group of thoughtful, committed citizens can change the world; indeed, it\'s the only thing that ever has.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:13'),
(7229, 28, 'To me success would be to be able to do your very best in everything you do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:21'),
(7230, 28, 'A minute\'s success pays the failure of years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:30'),
(7231, 28, 'When you\'re ready to quit, you are closer than you think', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:38'),
(7232, 28, 'Real success doesn\'t care how you get there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:47'),
(7233, 28, 'The thing always happens that you really believe in; and the belief in a thing makes it happen.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:05:58'),
(7234, 28, 'To succeed, it is necessary to accept the world as it is and rise above it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:06:07'),
(7235, 28, 'I\'m not afraid of dying I\'m afraid of not trying', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:06:35'),
(7236, 28, 'I owe my success to having listened respectfully to the very best advice, and then going away and doing the exact opposite.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:06:45'),
(7237, 28, 'You don\'t get character because you\'re successful; you build character because of the hardships you face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:06:55'),
(7238, 28, 'Nothing succeeds like the appearance of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:07:11'),
(7239, 28, 'Success means we go to sleep at night knowing that our talents and ablities were used in a way that served others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:07:20'),
(7240, 28, 'Success is how high you bounce when you hit bottom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:07:32'),
(7241, 28, 'As a rule, he or she who has the most information will have the greatest success in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:07:40'),
(7242, 28, 'A clash of doctrine is not a disaster, it is an opportunity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:07:50');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(7243, 28, 'Optimism is essential to achievement and it is also the foundation of courage and true progress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:08:13'),
(7244, 28, 'Don\'t confuse fame with success. Madonna is one; Helen Keller is the other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:08:21'),
(7245, 28, 'A man, as a general rule, owes very little to what he is born with - a man is what he makes of himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:08'),
(7246, 28, 'You must remain focused on your journey to greatness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:17'),
(7247, 28, 'No one can possibly achieve any real and lasting success or \'get rich\' in business by being a conformist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:27'),
(7248, 28, 'If you want to achieve things in life, you\'ve just got to do them, and if you\'re talented and smart, you\'ll succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:37'),
(7249, 28, 'If you put in the work, put in the time, put in the effort, you\'re going to reap the benefits.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:46'),
(7250, 28, 'Only buy something that you\'d be perfectly happy to hold if the market shut down for 10 years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:09:55'),
(7251, 28, 'The way of success is the way of continuous pursuit of knowledge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:10:33'),
(7252, 28, 'Well done is better than well said.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:10:44'),
(7254, 28, 'Greatness finds us by obstacles in front of us. I don’t look at hurdles as obstacles blocking my path but opportunities to overcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:11:15'),
(7256, 28, 'Failure is not our only punishment for laziness; there is also the success of others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:15:30'),
(7257, 28, 'If at first you don\'t succeed, try, try again. Then quit. There\'s no point in being a damn fool about it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:15:59'),
(7259, 28, 'Nothing will ever be attempted if all possible objections must first be overcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:16:38'),
(7261, 28, 'The secret of success is to do the common things uncommonly well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:18:02'),
(7262, 28, 'If you don\'t know where you are going, you might wind up someplace else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:18:21'),
(7263, 28, 'The two most important days in your life are the day you are born and the day you find out why.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:18:47'),
(7264, 28, 'We never know how far reaching something we may think, say or do today will affect the lives of millions tomorrow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:19:10'),
(7265, 28, 'We need to discover the root causes of success rather than the root causes of failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:19:38'),
(7266, 28, 'The successful always has a number of projects planned, to which he looks forward. Anyone of them could change the course of his life overnight.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:02'),
(7267, 28, 'You can\'t build a reputation on what you are going to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:17'),
(7268, 28, 'There\'s a word for a writer who never gives up: published.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:26'),
(7269, 28, 'We win half the battle when we make up our minds to take the world as we find it including the thorns.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:36'),
(7270, 28, 'A good listener is not only popular everywhere, but after a while, he knows something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:45'),
(7271, 28, 'Sometimes our best is simply not enough.... We have to do what is required.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:20:54'),
(7272, 28, 'What will matter is not your success but your significance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:21:04'),
(7273, 28, 'Success in almost any field depends more on energy and drive than it does on intelligence. This explains why we have so many stupid leaders.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:21:16'),
(7274, 28, 'As long as you are in the relative worlds, you should be realistic and know there is winning and losing here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:21:26'),
(7275, 28, 'Judge your success by what you had to give up in order to get it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:21:46'),
(7276, 28, 'Nothing is as obnoxious as other people\'s luck.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:21:54'),
(7277, 28, 'The secret of success is this: there is no secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:22:02'),
(7278, 28, 'The world can only be grasped by action, not by contemplation. The hand is the cutting edge of the mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:22:11'),
(7279, 28, 'You might well remember that nothing can bring you success but yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:22:21'),
(7280, 28, 'The chief factor in any man\'s success or failure must be his own character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:22:30'),
(7281, 28, 'The chief factor in any man\'s success or failure must be his own character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:23:17'),
(7282, 28, ' The will to win is important, but the will to prepare is vital.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:23:25'),
(7283, 28, 'Success isn\'t permanent and failure isn\'t fatal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:23:33'),
(7284, 28, 'If you want to be financially-free, you need to become a different person than you are today and let go of whatever has held you back in the past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:24:21'),
(7285, 28, 'Keep your head up in failure and your head down in success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:25:23'),
(7286, 28, 'Success without honor is an unseasoned dish; it will satisfy your hunger, but it won\'t taste good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:26:01'),
(7287, 28, 'Success is how you collect your minutes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:26:14'),
(7288, 28, 'Each success only buys an admission ticket to a more difficult problem.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:26:21'),
(7289, 28, 'Success means doing the best we can with what we have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:26:30'),
(7290, 28, 'If at first you don\'t succeed, failure may be your style.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:26:39'),
(7291, 28, 'I cannot give you the formula for success, but I can give you the formula for failure - which is: Try to please everybody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:27:23'),
(7292, 28, 'Nothing fails like success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:27:59'),
(7293, 28, 'Nothing is impossible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:29:04'),
(7294, 28, 'From success you get a lot of things, but not that great inside thing that love brings you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:29:11'),
(7296, 28, 'Have fun, work hard and money will come. Don\'t waste time - grab your chances. Have a positive outlook on life. When it\'s not fun, move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:31:11'),
(7297, 28, 'I choose a lazy person to do a hard job. Because a lazy person will find an easy way to do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:31:31'),
(7298, 28, 'A business has to be involving, it has to be fun, and it has to exercise your creative instincts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:31:40'),
(7299, 28, 'Do your work with your whole heart, and you will succeed - there\'s so little competition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:31:49'),
(7300, 28, 'Success, in my view, is the willingness to strive for something you really want', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:32:46'),
(7301, 28, 'There are three ingredients in the good life: learning, earning and yearning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:32:54'),
(7302, 28, 'You have reached the pinnacle of success as soon as you become uninterested in money, compliments, or publicity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:33:03'),
(7303, 28, 'Your attitude is either the lock on, or the key to the door of your success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:33:12'),
(7304, 28, 'Success takes communication, collaboration and, sometimes, failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:33:27'),
(7305, 28, 'You can make money two ways - make more, or spend less.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:33:44'),
(7306, 28, 'Success is the child of audacity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:34:07'),
(7307, 28, 'Success is dangerous. One begins to copy oneself, and to copy oneself is more dangerous than to copy others. It leads to sterility.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:34:16'),
(7308, 28, 'I am a great believer in luck, and I find the harder I work the more I have of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:34:25'),
(7309, 28, 'A friendship founded on business is better than a business founded on friendship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:34:33'),
(7310, 28, 'Success to me is having ten honeydew melons and eating only the top half of each slice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:34:50'),
(7311, 28, 'To follow, without halt, one aim: There\'s the secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:35:00'),
(7312, 28, 'Success is a process that never ends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:35:21'),
(7313, 28, 'Let me tell you the secret that has led me to my goal. My strength lies solely in my tenacity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:35:30'),
(7314, 28, 'Empowerment is all about letting go so that others can get going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:35:56'),
(7315, 28, 'Where there is a brave man, in the thickest of the fight, there is the post of honor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:36:04'),
(7316, 28, 'Happiness is not a goal; it is a by-product.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:36:13'),
(7317, 28, 'Keep your business affairs in your own hands. It\'s the only way to be happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:36:21'),
(7318, 28, 'The only way to define your limits is by going beyond them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:36:30'),
(7319, 28, 'The question isn\'t who is going to let me; it\'s who is going to stop me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:36:38'),
(7321, 28, 'Practice does not make perfect. Only perfect practice makes perfect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:37:32'),
(7322, 28, 'You cannot have a proud and chivalrous spirit if your conduct is mean and paltry; for whatever a man\'s actions are, such must be his spirit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:37:50'),
(7323, 28, 'Hard work spotlights the character of people: some turn up their sleeves, some turn up their noses, and some don\'t turn up at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:38:02'),
(7324, 28, 'Success is never final.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:38:11'),
(7325, 28, 'Success is doing what you want to do, when you want, where you want, with whom you want, as much as you want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:38:21'),
(7326, 28, 'The formula for success is simple: practice and concentration then more practice and more concentration.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:38:30'),
(7327, 28, 'The man who is successful is the man who is useful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:38:40'),
(7328, 28, 'Strive not to be a success, but rather to be of value.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:39:21'),
(7329, 28, 'Always wake up with a smile knowing that today you are going to have fun accomplishing what others are too afraid to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:39:33'),
(7330, 28, 'To make our way, we must have firm resolve, persistence, tenacity. We must gear ourselves to work hard all the way. We can never let up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:39:43'),
(7331, 28, 'Success is counted sweetest / By those who ne\'er succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:39:54'),
(7332, 28, 'You\'ve got to quit lowering your standards. Set your requirements up front so when a guy hooks you, he has to know this is business.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:40:03'),
(7333, 28, 'In the end, success is not about who you know, it\'s about you know who.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:40:14'),
(7334, 28, 'It\'s just as difficult to overcome success as it is to overcome failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:40:22'),
(7335, 28, 'We succeed in enterprises which demand the positive qualities we possess, but we excel in those which can also make use of our defects.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:40:31'),
(7336, 28, 'The test of success is not what you do when you are on top. Success is how high you bounce when you hit bottom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:40:40'),
(7337, 28, 'Those who dare to fail miserably can achieve greatly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:41:07'),
(7338, 28, 'Do not be embarrassed by your failures, learn from them and start again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:41:55'),
(7339, 28, 'Most successful men have not achieved their distinction by having some new talent or opportunity that was at hand.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:42:20'),
(7340, 28, 'To do a common thing uncommonly well brings success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:42:29'),
(7341, 28, 'The more I want to get something done, the less I call it work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:42:39'),
(7342, 28, 'The ability to convert ideas to things is the secret of outward success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:42:48'),
(7343, 28, 'The whole secret of a successful life is to find out what is one\'s destiny to do, and then do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:42:59'),
(7344, 28, 'Success comes from aspiration, desperation, perspiration, and inspiration!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:43:08'),
(7345, 28, 'Being defeated is often a temporary condition. Giving up is what makes it permanent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:43:17'),
(7346, 28, 'Ask yourself the secret of your success. Listen to your answer, and practice it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:43:39'),
(7347, 28, 'If a man will begin with certainties, he shall end in doubts, but if he will content to begin with doubts, he shall end in certainties.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:43:48'),
(7348, 28, 'In this world it is not what we take up, but what we give up, that makes us rich.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:43:56'),
(7349, 28, 'Success is following the pattern of life one enjoys most.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:05'),
(7350, 28, 'The first man gets the oyster, the second man gets the shell.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:14'),
(7351, 28, 'After my spectacular failures, I could not be satisfied with an ordinary success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:21'),
(7352, 28, 'In preparing for battle I have always found that plans are useless, but planning is indispensable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:29'),
(7353, 28, 'It is not length of life, but depth of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:37'),
(7354, 28, 'Satisfaction lies in the effort, not in the attainment, full effort is full victory.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:44:51'),
(7356, 28, 'Think twice before you speak, because your words and influence will plant the seed of either success or failure in the mind of another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:45:27'),
(7357, 28, 'When your work speaks for itself, don\'t interrupt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:45:38'),
(7358, 28, 'For success, attitude is equally as important as ability.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:45:46'),
(7359, 28, 'Our doubts are traitors and make us lose the good we oft might win by fearing to attempt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:45:54'),
(7361, 28, 'Few people think more than two or three times a year; I have made an international reputation for myself by thinking once or twice a week.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:46:12'),
(7362, 28, 'She\'s the kind of girl who climbed the ladder of success wrong by wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:47:27'),
(7363, 28, 'There are victories of the soul and spirit. Sometimes, even if you lose, you win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:47:36'),
(7364, 28, 'Sometimes it takes a good fall to really know where you stand.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:47:45'),
(7365, 28, 'Success is blocked by concentrating on it and planning for it... Success is shy - it won\'t come out while you\'re watching.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:47:53'),
(7366, 28, 'Excellence is the best deterrent to racism or sexism.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:48:03'),
(7367, 28, 'We should never permit ourselves to do anything that we are not willing to see our children do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:48:11'),
(7368, 28, 'A thinker sees his own actions as experiments and questions--as attempts to find out something. Success and failure are for him answers above all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:49:20'),
(7369, 28, 'Happiness simply cannot be relied upon as a measure of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:49:28'),
(7370, 28, 'Take risks and you\'ll get the payoffs. Learn from your mistakes until you succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:49:47'),
(7371, 28, 'Initiative is to success what a lighted match is to a candle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:49:57'),
(7372, 28, 'The way to rise is to obey and please.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:50:13'),
(7373, 28, 'All you\'ve got to do is decide to go and the hardest part is over.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:50:30'),
(7374, 28, 'Success depends upon previous preparation, and without such preparation there is sure to be failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:50:39'),
(7375, 28, 'How can they say my life is not a success? Have I not for more than sixty years got enough to eat and escaped being eaten?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:50:49'),
(7376, 28, 'I\'m a success today because I had a friend who believed in me and I didn\'t have the heart to let him down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:51:02'),
(7377, 28, 'If you have the will to win, you have achieved half your success; if you don\'t, you have achieved half your failure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:51:15'),
(7378, 28, 'Honesty is the cornerstone of all success, without which confidence and ability to perform shall cease to exist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:51:24'),
(7379, 28, 'It is wise to keep in mind that neither success nor failure is ever final.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:51:33'),
(7380, 28, 'You\'ve got to be very careful if you don\'t know where you are going, because you might not get there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:52:20'),
(7381, 28, 'Why be a man when you can be a success?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:52:29'),
(7382, 28, 'The secret of joy in work is contained in one word - excellence. To know how to do something well is to enjoy it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:52:37'),
(7383, 28, 'You only have to do a very few things right in your life so long as you don\'t do too many things wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:52:45'),
(7384, 28, 'All your dreams can come true if you have the courage to pursue them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:53:23'),
(7385, 28, 'Use what talents you possess; the woods would be very silent if no birds sang there except those that sang best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASuccess', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:54:01'),
(7386, 32, 'I think the best thing that could happen is that I\'ll live to be a lot older than my mother lived.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:59:34'),
(7387, 32, 'When you\'re a mother hen, you sometimes coddle your children. But there are different ways of coddling. Some coddle with luxury, others with love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 17:59:49'),
(7388, 32, 'My mother had to justify the fact that she had heart pills.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:00:00'),
(7389, 32, 'In a sense the physical connectedness that you feel with your children as a mother changes as they become independent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:00:24'),
(7390, 32, 'Necessity is literally the mother of invention.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:00:45'),
(7391, 32, 'A wise mother knows: It is her state of consciousness that matters. Her gentleness and clarity command respect. Her love creates security.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:00:55'),
(7392, 32, 'We wondered why when a child laughed, he belonged to Daddy, and when he had a sagging diaper that smelled like a landfill, \'He wants his mother.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:01:08'),
(7393, 32, 'Gutenberg\'s invention of printing is the greatest event-the mother of revolution', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:01:17'),
(7394, 32, 'The only monster here is the gambling monster that has enslaved your mother, and I call him Gamblor!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:01:27'),
(7395, 32, 'Mother is the best and the first teacher to the child .', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:01:55'),
(7396, 32, 'I adore acting; it\'s in my blood - quite literally - but I can honestly say the most creative thing in the world for me is being a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:02:06'),
(7397, 32, 'I would get parts and not be able to take them because my mother didn\'t have a car.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:02:16'),
(7398, 32, 'I was very sensitive. I liked everything that touched fantasy and beauty. I dreamed of being a ballerina, but Mother said I was too big, too long.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:02:25'),
(7401, 32, 'Have you ever closed your eyes and listened to the sound of your own mother\'s voice?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:03:10'),
(7402, 32, 'To my mother, I was everything. To my father, nothing at all. To my grandmother, I was a daily reminder of loves long lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:03:39'),
(7403, 32, 'If you aren\'t nurturing your self, what kind of mother can you be, anyway?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:03:50'),
(7405, 32, 'For every hour a mother gets to herself, a father will demand five times that amount for drinking with friends and acting like an immature dipshit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:04:09'),
(7406, 32, 'Satan is not going to leave. The only way to get him out is to invite God in, and God is not welcome in my mother\'s house.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:06:14'),
(7407, 32, 'A good mother loves fiercely but ultimately brings up her children to thrive without her.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:06:36'),
(7408, 32, 'Right, except I\'m not going to lie to my mom, because what kind of (man) lies to his own mother?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:06:45'),
(7409, 32, 'My mother says I\'m crazy, I\'m not crazy, I just have a different way of looking at things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:06:55'),
(7410, 32, 'One thing my and mother and dad shared completely was their approach to money - they just didn\'t spend it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:07:03'),
(7411, 32, 'A moss which leaves its ocean becomes pale and dries up and a man which leaves his mother country is a moss which leaves it ocean!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:07:16'),
(7412, 32, 'Flowers are the beautiful hairs of the Mother Spring! Don\'t pluck them!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:07:28'),
(7413, 32, 'Time is the mother and mugger of us all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:07:47'),
(7414, 32, 'Story is the mother of us all, for we become who we say we are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:07:57'),
(7415, 32, 'Story is the mother of us all, for we become who we say we are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:09:10'),
(7416, 32, 'I think my gift expressed itself in every way possible. When I was a little child, my mother said I used to draw on the walls.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:09:26'),
(7417, 32, 'My mother\'s white, and she didn\'t know how to do my hair, so I had something that I always call white-mama hair.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:09:43'),
(7418, 32, 'We had to be our own mothers of invention, in many senses of the word.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:10:03'),
(7419, 32, 'I like movies like \'Mother\'s Day\', where you watch it, and you\'ve liked it for years as a horror movie.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:10:11'),
(7420, 32, 'Get to work because Mother Earth needs you right now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:10:38'),
(7421, 32, 'God is the mother and father of the world. Our parents are the mother and father of this body.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:10:48'),
(7422, 32, 'I fully intend to make amends and get back to being a good mother, wife, daughter, and friend.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:10:57'),
(7423, 32, 'If you don\'t love your mother you go straight to hell.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:11:07'),
(7424, 32, 'Leisure can be one of the Mothers of Philosophy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:11:22'),
(7425, 32, 'All mothers are working mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:12:02'),
(7426, 32, 'No one ever outgrows the need for a mother\'s love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:12:14'),
(7427, 32, 'My mother didn\'t teach me lessons about being Chinese as strongly as she did the notion of who I was as a female.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:12:25'),
(7428, 32, 'Do you expect, forsooth, that a mother will hand down to her children principles which differ from her own?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:12:39'),
(7429, 32, 'With my poems, I finally won even my mother. The longest wooing of my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:13:42'),
(7430, 32, 'In a perfect world, mothers would remind their daughters each morning of how beautiful their strong noses are, or how special their curly red hair is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:14:19'),
(7431, 32, 'The trouble with marriage is that, while every woman is at heart a mother, every man is at heart a bachelor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:14:38'),
(7432, 32, 'As bad as I was, as much trouble and worry as I caused my mother, I loved her.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:14:47'),
(7433, 32, 'I am often asked which picture is my favorite. This is like asking a mother which child she likes the most.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:15:18'),
(7434, 32, 'They call our language the mother tongue because the father seldom gets to speak.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:15:26'),
(7435, 32, 'I should have suspected my husband was lazy. On our wedding day, his mother told me: \"I\'m not losing a son; I\'m gaining a couch.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:15:35'),
(7436, 32, 'Our minds were circumscribed within narrow limits by an habitual belief that it was our duty to be subordinate to the mother country.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:15:44'),
(7437, 32, 'Prayer is the root, the fountain, the mother of a thousand blessings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:15:53'),
(7438, 32, 'Philosophy is the true mother of science.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:16:01'),
(7439, 32, 'Englishmen are not usually softened by appeals to the memory of their mothers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:16:12'),
(7440, 32, 'A mother is the portal by which you enter the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:16:22'),
(7441, 32, 'I guess I define myself as a mother, a wife, kind of a nutty person. A good person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:16:32'),
(7442, 32, 'I\'m a person who likes to give 100 percent to everything I do. I want to be the best at my job and as a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:02'),
(7443, 32, 'The mother-in-laws themselves weren\'t natural jokes but most comedians used to use that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:08'),
(7444, 32, 'People seem to trust you more when you\'re pregnant. I think they see you as some kind of Mother Earth figure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:20'),
(7445, 32, 'One hour with Mother is more than Without her, an age.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:29'),
(7446, 32, 'I\'m a mother, so I instantly identified with what that would be like and the horror of that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:40'),
(7447, 32, 'There is no slave out of heaven like a loving woman; and of all loving women, there is no such slave as a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:49'),
(7448, 32, 'A widow, the mother of a family, and from her heart she produces chords to which my whole being responds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:17:58'),
(7449, 32, 'I am lucky. I had a very beautiful mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:18:07'),
(7450, 32, 'You know which title I like best? I like to be called mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:18:16'),
(7451, 32, 'Mother Russia is on the move, she can\'t stand still, she\'s restless and can\'t find rest, she\'s talking and she can\'t stop.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:18:25'),
(7452, 32, 'Sometimes I spit on my mother\'s portrait for pleasure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:20:30'),
(7453, 32, 'I really doubt whether evolution ever works, how then come Mothers have only two hands.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:20:39'),
(7454, 32, 'The menu of my mother consisted of only two choices: Leave it or take it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:00'),
(7455, 32, 'A mother always thinks twice: for herself and for the child', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:21'),
(7456, 32, 'A mother is a bank where I deposit all my worries and hurts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:32'),
(7457, 32, 'Mother\'s love outlives everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:44'),
(7458, 32, 'What least makes a mother is biology.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:54'),
(7459, 32, 'What least makes a mother is biology.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:21:54'),
(7460, 32, 'The mother\'s kiss is the sweetest thing ever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:22:05'),
(7461, 32, 'If fathers were to be mothers, then there will never have a family of more than three.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:22:14'),
(7462, 32, 'Your responsibility as a parent is never great as the case is with the mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:22:24'),
(7463, 32, 'Mother\'s love always peace as it not to be acquired nor deserved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:22:33'),
(7464, 32, 'Kids are anchors of mothers\' life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:22:48'),
(7465, 32, 'I always remember the prayers of my mother as they always forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:23:00'),
(7466, 32, 'My mother\'s the most special person in my life ... I consider her my MVP: Most Valuable Parent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:24:54'),
(7467, 32, 'I have not met one living being that has not been the mother of all the rest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:05'),
(7468, 32, 'Money is not an issue to me. My mother always tells me, money, it comes and it goes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:13'),
(7469, 32, 'My mother was the biggest influence on me, without question.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:23'),
(7470, 32, 'I\'ve always been taught to care what other people think. My grandmother and mother taught me to project a positive image of myself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:34'),
(7471, 32, 'My biological mother made my clothes or bought my clothes from Salvation Army or Goodwill.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:43'),
(7472, 32, 'It\'s pretty hard being a tennis player and Mother Theresa at the same time and that\'s just the way it is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:25:56'),
(7473, 32, 'To me when a mother puts food in a microwave for her children, it is an act of hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:26:09'),
(7474, 32, 'I like changing my hairstyle, much to my mother\'s annoyance. It depends on my state of mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:26:18'),
(7475, 32, 'My father came back one day and forced my mother to submit to him. He raped her, holding a knife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:26:27'),
(7476, 32, 'My mother was a high school arts teacher, so I was always surrounded by the arts', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:27:28'),
(7477, 32, 'My mother is fine. For me it perfection.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:27:37'),
(7478, 32, 'Necessity, they say, is mother of invention, but fear, too, is not barren of ingenious suggestions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:27:53'),
(7479, 32, 'Have I got a mother-in-law. She\'s so neat she puts paper under the cuckoo clock.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:28:02'),
(7480, 32, 'Like the mother of the world, touch each being as your beloved child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:28:14'),
(7481, 32, 'The only way that a mother would go after her own children is if she\'s just completely gone and has no humanity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:28:40'),
(7482, 32, 'There is not substantial data that AZT stops the transmission of HIV from mother to child. There is too much conflicting data to make concrete policy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:28:54'),
(7483, 32, 'My mother implanted in me as a young girl...you can either be an actor in your own life, or a reactor in somebody else\'s.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:04'),
(7484, 32, 'Father\'s Day is like Mother\'s Day except the gift is cheaper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:14'),
(7485, 32, 'I am a child of Nature, and take after my mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:23'),
(7486, 32, 'I am a child of Nature, and take after my mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:35'),
(7487, 32, 'India was the motherland of our race and Samskrit the mother of Europe \'s languages...Mother India is in many ways the mother of us all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:47'),
(7488, 32, 'My mother tried to abort me herself with a coathanger, hence my wobbly eye.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:29:55'),
(7489, 32, 'The best mother is the mother who adapts, and the best children are the children who adapt as well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:30:16'),
(7490, 32, 'I\'m a fighter as a mother. I\'m fighting to be a mother, but I cannot say no to my passion because it\'s me, as well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:30:34'),
(7491, 32, 'When I was born, my mother didn\'t know what to name me. Eventually she named me after Thom Yorke.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:32:30'),
(7492, 32, 'No one who shall invoke this Mother of Grace with devotion and perseverance can possibly perish forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:32:41'),
(7493, 32, 'Godliness is the child of truth, and it must be nursed by its own mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:32:55'),
(7494, 32, 'My mother always texts me saying \'Fighting! Do well, my handsome son!\'.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:33:07'),
(7495, 32, 'Repetition is the mother of education.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:33:29'),
(7496, 32, 'A sick child is always the mother\'s property; her own feelings generally make it so.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:33:42'),
(7497, 32, 'My mother always said, \'When you\'re eating pretzels, chew before you swallow\'. Always listen to your mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:33:52'),
(7498, 32, 'To all fathers and mothers of the Church, tell your children that you love them and that you are so happy to have them in your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:01'),
(7499, 32, 'For a long time, I let my mother say what she wanted about me, and what was worse, for a long time I believed her.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:23'),
(7500, 32, 'As to my political faith- I have never voted. My father was a Democrat, my mother a Republican, and I am an Episcopalian.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:33'),
(7501, 32, 'Almost everyone who has gone to the bad early in life has had a deceitful mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:41'),
(7502, 32, 'Being a king, emperor, or president is mighty small potatoes compared to being a mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:50'),
(7503, 32, 'Don\'t worry about what your mother thinks of your language.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:34:58'),
(7504, 32, 'Never trust a journalist unless she\'s your mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:35:17'),
(7505, 32, 'One of the great logical puzzles is how a woman is always like her mother but never like her sister.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:35:27'),
(7506, 32, 'Sometimes you need a B-2 bomber and sometimes you need your mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:35:36'),
(7507, 32, 'The key to living a moral life is this: Do nothing in private that you would be ashamed to discuss openly with your mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:35:45'),
(7508, 32, 'The mother- poor invaded soul- finds even the bathroom door no bar to hammering little hands.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:35:54'),
(7509, 32, 'Belief is the mother of reality. Excellence is a state of mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:36:06'),
(7510, 32, 'I\'m very inspired by nature - you could say Mother Nature. I look at things around me and get all kinds of inspiration daily.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:36:20'),
(7511, 32, 'A light-heel\'d mother makes a heavy-heel\'d daughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:36:33'),
(7512, 32, 'My mother, grandmother and I all have different styles, but we share the same taste.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:36:52'),
(7513, 32, 'My mother always told me that inaction is not an option. And neither is going it alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:01'),
(7514, 32, 'I am prouder of my years as a single mother than of any other part of my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:09'),
(7515, 32, 'I had a mother who taught me there is no such thing as failure. It is just a temporary postponement of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:22'),
(7516, 32, 'The first gathering of salads, radishes and herbs made me feel like a mother about her baby - how could anything so beautiful be mine?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:32'),
(7517, 32, 'Progress is the mother of all problems.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:42');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(7518, 32, 'Ignorance is the Mother not of Devotion, but of Heresy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:37:52'),
(7519, 32, 'It\'s nearly impossible for a criminal to come from a good mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:38:03'),
(7520, 32, 'No role in life is more important than to be a good mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:38:12'),
(7521, 32, 'I\'m a little bit more of a relaxed, lazy mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:39:01'),
(7522, 32, 'When we were growing up, our mother taught us never to have your belly button exposed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:39:12'),
(7523, 32, 'They say the definition of ambivalence is watching your mother-in-law drive over a cliff in your new Cadillac.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:39:32'),
(7524, 32, 'I was the last girl in Larchmont, NY to get married. My mother had a sign up: \"Last Girl Before Freeway.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:40:05'),
(7525, 32, 'A father who is a chronic debtor, an adulterous mother, a beautiful wife, and an unlearned son are enemies in one\'s own home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:40:16'),
(7526, 32, 'Elvis Presley is my spiritual father, and as you may know Maria Callas is my spiritual mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:40:28'),
(7527, 32, 'God is our father, but even more is God our mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:40:52'),
(7528, 32, 'One race there is of men, one of gods, but from one mother we both draw our breath.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:00'),
(7529, 32, 'My father! The sun is my father, and the earth is my mother, and on her bosom I will recline.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:09'),
(7530, 32, 'Before my mother died, she made me promise to do everything that could be done to make sure my father was not left alone after she was gone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:22'),
(7531, 32, 'Women can be strong, be smart, be sexy, be mothers, be wives, and be powerful. We don\'t need to compromise.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:31'),
(7532, 32, 'My mother will never leave me. We\'re together. She will always stay in my heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:42'),
(7533, 32, 'A mother is only as happy as her saddest child.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:41:57'),
(7534, 32, 'I read once that water is a symbol for emotions. And for a while now I\'ve thought maybe my mother drowned in both.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:42:19'),
(7535, 32, 'My mother has a very chic sense of style, but she also has high expectations for her clothes to be functional and practical.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:42:37'),
(7536, 32, 'No mother in the world wants her daughter to have fewer rights than she did.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:42:50'),
(7537, 32, 'He who is devout to the Virgin Mother will certainly never be lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:43:05'),
(7538, 32, 'Dance was always part of my life because I was a dancer and my mother was a dancer, and I love the theater.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:43:14'),
(7539, 32, 'Whatever past you had, when you become a mother, it [life] is a whole different thing. You can\'t even predict it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:43:39'),
(7540, 32, 'Out of everything - out of the money and the gift bags - the most important thing to me is just my mother and father being happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:43:51'),
(7541, 32, 'My father and mother split and I never saw my father until I was 20, nor did I see much more of my mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:44:07'),
(7542, 32, 'I often wish my mother had died so that at least I could get some people\'s sympathy. But there she was, a perfectly beautiful mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:44:17'),
(7543, 32, 'A mother\'s love is supposed to be unconditional. That you could give your child up, over their sexuality, is unthinkable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:44:27'),
(7544, 32, 'The earth is not just our environment. The earth is our mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:44:49'),
(7545, 32, 'My mother passed at the end of the Circus tour. After that I really needed to take some time and just chill out and get my head together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:45:18'),
(7546, 32, 'My mum died when I was 14. That is a kind of strange age to lose a mother. John lost his mum when he was 17.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:45:27'),
(7547, 32, 'I\'m not a good mother at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:45:36'),
(7548, 32, 'There\'s two things I gotta do. One is, I gotta update my resume. And then, I have to call my mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:45:49'),
(7549, 32, 'In our society, any man who doesn\'t cry at his mother\'s funeral is liable to be condemned to death.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:46:01'),
(7550, 32, 'We\'re blessed on \'How I Met Your Mother\' to feel like we\'re doing a bit of a funny playlet everyday.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:46:11'),
(7551, 32, 'I think my mother, more than anyone, knew the importance of inspiration. If it was occurring, you had to use it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:46:26'),
(7552, 32, 'My mother and father could not handle even me being gay. We never talked about it really.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:46:37'),
(7553, 32, 'In crowds it is stupidity and not mother wit that is accumulated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:46:47'),
(7554, 32, 'I need the reality of other people, work, to fulfill myself. Must never become a mere mother and housewife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:47:02'),
(7555, 32, 'Scrum is like your mother-in-law, it points out ALL your faults.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:47:12'),
(7556, 32, 'Early in my career I began receiving letters from a woman in the Midwest who claimed to be my mother.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMother', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-08 18:47:30'),
(7557, 31, 'It means everything. Making my father happy, that\'s my biggest joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:08:34'),
(7558, 31, 'My father-he pretty much taught me everything I know. He still pushes me to be the best I can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:08:43'),
(7559, 31, 'For Father\'s Day, my kids always give me a bottle of cologne called English Leather. It\'s appropriate! To them I always smell like a wallet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:08:56'),
(7560, 31, 'A father, finding time for what is most important is the true marker of a successful person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:04'),
(7561, 31, 'A child identifies his parents with God, whether or not the adults want that role. Most children \'see\' God the way they perceive their earthly fathers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:13'),
(7562, 31, 'My father was in the Army and we moved around a lot, and one of my favorite places was the library.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:24'),
(7563, 31, 'My father came back one day and forced my mother to submit to him. He raped her, holding a knife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:35'),
(7564, 31, 'I only went to the third grade because my father only went to the fourth and I didn\'t want to pass him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:44'),
(7565, 31, 'I used to think my father was an idiot, until I turned twenty-one... Then I thought he was a genus.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:09:52'),
(7566, 31, 'My father was my god. His approval was so valuable to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:10:00'),
(7567, 31, 'When I was a boy I was my father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:10:08'),
(7568, 31, 'My father was a miner and he worked down a mine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:10:18'),
(7569, 31, 'Necessity is not merely the father of invention; it is the father of courage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:10:25'),
(7570, 31, 'I would like to understand my father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:10:33'),
(7571, 31, 'I was raised in the \'50s. I was taught by my father that how I looked was all that mattered.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:00'),
(7572, 31, 'The Heavenly Father does not ask for golden vessels. He does not ask for silver vessels. God asks for yielded vessels.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:08'),
(7573, 31, 'It breaks my heart that my father never knew my children. He should have been around for another 25 years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:20'),
(7574, 31, 'Faith dare the soul to go further than it can see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:28'),
(7575, 31, 'My father was a great fan of the horses. His only regret was that I never ran in the Grand National.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:38'),
(7576, 31, 'Andy Kaufman\'s mom wanted a girl, his father wanted a boy, and they were both satisfied!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:46'),
(7577, 31, 'I didn\'t do too much. I came here (to The Magic Castle) and learned about magic. I read a book, but not his father\'s book. Sorry about that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:11:56'),
(7578, 31, 'I took no money to make art, but my woman backed me up on it and I want my children to see their father happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:12:21'),
(7579, 31, 'Father Jude Nnorom says he hopes the pope\'s travels in Africa will help end all the wars ravaging the continent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:12:30'),
(7580, 31, 'The devil is the father of lies, but he neglected to patent the idea, and the business now suffers from competition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:12:43'),
(7581, 31, 'Every kid I knew had a father with a little stash of men\'s magazines which the father thought was secret and which the kid knew all about.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:12:53'),
(7582, 31, 'Father\'s Day is like Mother\'s Day except the gift is cheaper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:13:01'),
(7583, 31, 'Every divine action begins from the Father, proceeds through the Son, and is completed in the Holy Spirit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:13:19'),
(7584, 31, 'I mean my father was killed when I was six. And I only have tiny, tiny flashes of memory.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:13:27'),
(7585, 31, 'Prayer in secret is life finding expression in the realized Presence of God our Father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:13:38'),
(7586, 31, 'One of the greatest gifts my father gave me - unintentionally - was witnessing the courage with which he bore adversity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:13:48'),
(7587, 31, 'Our Father expects you to learn how to obtain that divine help by exercising faith in Him and His Holy Son, Jesus Christ.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:14:00'),
(7588, 31, 'Sometimes we forget that our Heavenly Father desires that each of us have this joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:14:26'),
(7589, 31, 'We must never, in any age or circumstance, let fear and the father of fear (Satan himself) divert us from our faith and faithful living.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:14:37'),
(7590, 31, 'To all fathers and mothers of the Church, tell your children that you love them and that you are so happy to have them in your family.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:14:47'),
(7591, 31, 'As to my political faith- I have never voted. My father was a Democrat, my mother a Republican, and I am an Episcopalian.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:14:58'),
(7592, 31, 'Fathers have a unique and irreplaceable role in the lives of children.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:15:06'),
(7593, 31, 'For years I thought my father was a hunchback. Turns out he didn\'t know suspenders were adjustable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:15:13'),
(7594, 31, 'It is almost nicer being a godfather than a father, like having white mice but making your nanny feed them for you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:15:21'),
(7595, 31, 'Men are all right for friends, but as soon as you marry them they turn into cranky old fathers, even the wild ones.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:15:29'),
(7596, 31, 'The wisest man may be a blind father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:15:37'),
(7597, 31, 'Let\'s start off with my father being a mailman.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:16:04'),
(7598, 31, 'I\'m not a truthiness fanatic, I\'m truthiness\'s father.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:16:15'),
(7599, 31, 'My father was a saint. I\'m not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:16:27'),
(7600, 31, 'Sons or fathers, poor men or rich men, sacred or secular: all are homosexual in their worship of everything phallic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFather', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-09 04:16:37'),
