(10317, 25, 'Today, give a stranger one of your smiles. It might be the only sunshine he sees all day. Source unknown A spark of kindness starts a fire of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAASunshine', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-25 16:51:45'),
