(10339, 33, 'When your ex says ‘You’ll never find anyone like me’. Say ‘that’s the point’.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABoyfriend', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-25 17:16:09'),
