(10739, 24, 'Kiss me as if you made believe You were not sure this eve, How my face, your flower, had pursed It\'s petals up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:32:16'),
(10740, 24, 'You live by the light of the moon, and I live by desire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:32:38'),
(10741, 24, 'The best smell in the world is that man that you love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:32:49'),
(10742, 24, 'I was cold and you were fire, and I never knew how the pyre could be burning on the edge of an ice field.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:32:56'),
(10743, 24, 'If you love someone, you say it, right then, out loud. Otherwise, the moment just passes you by.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:04'),
(10744, 24, 'Losing the future is the best thing that ever happened to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:12'),
(10745, 24, 'Your love made it all worth waiting for some like you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:19'),
(10746, 24, 'I think romance is anything honest. As long as it\'s honest, it\'s so disarming.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:27'),
(10747, 24, 'Don\'t forget I\'m just a girl, standing in front of a boy, asking him to love her.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:34'),
(10748, 24, 'In all the world, there is no heart for me like yours. In all the world, there is no love for you like mine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:47'),
(10749, 24, 'Love is an irresistible desire to be irresistibly desired.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:33:54'),
(10750, 24, 'Absence diminishes mediocre passions and increases great ones, as the wind extinguishes candles and fans fires.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:34:02'),
(10751, 24, 'Absence is to love as wind is to fire: it extinguishes the little flame, it fans the big.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:34:10'),
(10752, 24, 'I need you because I love you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:34:17'),
(10753, 24, 'Love is most nearly itself When here and now cease to matter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:34:46'),
(10754, 24, 'You can transmute love, ignore it, muddle it, but you can never pull it out of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:34:53'),
(10755, 24, 'Love me when I least deserve it, because that’s when I really need it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:01'),
(10756, 24, 'For love is immortality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:08'),
(10757, 24, 'A guy knows he\'s in love when he loses interest in his car for a couple of days.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:15'),
(10758, 24, 'Justice is the loveliest and health is the best. but the sweetest to obtain is the heart\'s desire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:22'),
(10759, 24, 'When love is not madness, it is not love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:32'),
(10760, 24, 'Take my hand and we\'ll go riding through the sunshine from above. We\'ll find happiness together in the summer skies of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:35:59'),
(10761, 24, 'The etiquette of romantic love is as elaborate as that surrounding the Emperor of China.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:36:07'),
(10762, 24, 'Said I loved you but I lied, cause this is more than love I feel inside.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:36:21'),
(10763, 24, 'Romance lasts forever, love don\'t fade away. They may take away our future, but they can\'t stop yesterday.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:36:35'),
(10764, 24, 'Well my biggest dream is to be in a romantic comedy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:36:44'),
(10765, 24, 'Is that romantic fantasy real? Um, after kids, no. Take the kids away, I don\'t know. Depends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:36:52'),
(10766, 24, 'I am a hopeless romantic. And I won\'t stop till I get it right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:02'),
(10767, 24, 'It was the most romantic plane ever made.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:12'),
(10768, 24, 'If you look at romantic comedies as pieces of commerce, the audience is looking for wish fulfillment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:20'),
(10769, 24, 'The Enlightenment needs more shadow; the Romantic Movement less.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:28'),
(10770, 24, 'Wine comes in at the mouth And love comes in at the eye; That\'s all we shall know for truth Before we grow old and die.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:36'),
(10771, 24, 'I am a hopeless romantic and so is my wife.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:37:56'),
(10772, 24, 'I used to be a hopeless romantic - I fell in love with everyone I went out with.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:38:04'),
(10773, 24, 'I\'ll paint you moments of gold, I\'ll spin you Valentine evenings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:38:25'),
(10774, 24, 'Adieu! \'tis love\'s last greeting, The parting hour is come! And fast thy soul is fleeting To seek its starry home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:38:32'),
(10775, 24, 'The heights charm us, but the steps do not; with the mountain in our view we love to walk the plains.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:38:39'),
(10776, 24, 'Love me sweet With all thou art Feeling, thinking, seeing; Love me in the Lightest part, Love me in full Being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:38:49'),
(10777, 24, 'Don\'t be afraid,\" I said, \"We belong together.\" I was immediatly overcome by the truth of my own words.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:39:23'),
(10778, 24, 'Classical, Romantic, and Baroque music, that\'s what I really like.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:39:32'),
(10779, 24, 'Theres nothing more romantic than Italian food.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:39:41'),
(10780, 24, 'It\'s a very romantic sentiment, but to think that you would die if you didn\'t write, well, I would definitely choose to not write and live', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:39:51'),
(10781, 24, 'In the movies, Bette Davis lights two cigarettes and hands the second one to James Cagney. It was just so glamorous and romantic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:40:06'),
(10782, 24, 'Clearly romantic comedy is my franchise genre, I don\'t mind saying that, it\'s true. I love doing them and hopefully always will do them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:40:16'),
(10783, 24, 'I vowed after that day that I would be your hero too, no matter how long it took', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:45:04'),
(10784, 24, 'In Romanticism, the main determinant is the mood, the atmosphere. And in that regard, you could also describe Schubert as a Romantic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:45:12'),
(10785, 24, 'Absence makes the heart grow fonder', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:45:29'),
(10786, 24, 'In mainstream romantic comedies, I\'m usually tearing my hair out. It\'s just a devastatingly difficult genre for me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:45:38'),
(10787, 24, 'Marriage is a book of which the first chapter is written in poetry and the remaining chapters in prose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:45:49'),
(10788, 24, 'Death was like love, a romantic escape.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:46:18'),
(10789, 24, 'She had never imagined that curiosty was one of the many masks of love .', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:46:27'),
(10790, 24, 'You realize that trying to keep your distance from me will not lessen my affection for you. All efforts to save me from you will fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:46:36'),
(10791, 24, 'Being in the studio is a really romantic time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:46:48'),
(10792, 24, 'Lady love, your love is peaceful like the summers breeze.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:46:56'),
(10793, 24, 'Like mercy from heaven\'s gate, there\'s a freedom in your arms that carries me through. I need you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:47:08'),
(10794, 24, 'My desire is to stand by the fire that burns inside of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:47:18'),
(10795, 24, 'Satan, really, is the romantic youth of Jesus re-appearing for a moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:47:30'),
(10796, 24, 'Acting is not about anything romantic, not even fantasy, although you do create fantasy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:47:44'),
(10797, 24, 'Love breaks your heart, love takes no less than everything. Love makes it hard, and it fades away so easily.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:47:54'),
(10798, 24, 'In her beauty rests (both) my death and my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:48:05'),
(10799, 24, 'A handful of older, romantic leading men, like Sean Connery, Jack Nicholson, and Robert Redford are still landing parts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:49:09'),
(10800, 24, 'Brighter than fireflies upon the Uji River are your words in the dark, Beloved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:49:19'),
(10801, 24, 'If we perform the romantic repertoire we need more musicians.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:49:39'),
(10802, 24, 'I\'m like the kid in kindergarten; I really do send valentines to everyone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:49:48'),
(10803, 24, 'The only thing I would unequivocally say is that I have never had any interest in romantic comedy I just couldn\'t do it. I think I\'d be terrible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:49:56'),
(10804, 24, 'Within my heart is carved a sculpture of your love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:04'),
(10805, 24, 'Your lips and mine, two sips of wine, memories are made of this.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:13'),
(10806, 24, 'Usually comedy is only available to us ladies in the romantic comedy. That\'s why I hate romantic comedies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:20'),
(10807, 24, 'You begin saving the world by saving one man at a time; all else is grandiose romanticism or politics.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:27'),
(10808, 24, 'On \'The Office,\' so much of the show is about disguising your true feelings and your romantic feelings because it was a mock documentary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:41');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(10809, 24, 'Everyone who knows me knows that I\'m a hopeless romantic who listens to love ballads and doo-wop songs all the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:50:50'),
(10810, 24, 'For one kiss, darling, I swear everything I would give. Cause you\'re a walking, talking reason to live.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:51:05'),
(10811, 24, 'When men attempt bold gestures, generally it\'s considered romantic. When women do it, it\'s often considered desperate or psycho.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:51:58'),
(10812, 24, 'Between now and then, \'til I see you again, I\'ll be loving you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:52:09'),
(10813, 24, 'May you be in love every day for the next 20,000 days. And out of that love, remake a world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:53:05'),
(10814, 24, 'I love you baby goodnight. There goes my life', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:53:21'),
(10815, 24, 'Suddenly I\'ve got an overwhelming desire to surround myself with the aura of classical and Romantic art.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:53:31'),
(10816, 24, '\"And what would humans be without love?\" Rare, said Death.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:53:47'),
(10817, 24, 'Anyone can say the love someone....It\'s loving someone enough to let them go that will prove that love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:53:55'),
(10818, 24, 'Loving a person is loving everything but the person. Being in love with that person is loving everything and that person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:54:05'),
(10819, 24, 'Then I abandoned comics for fine art because I had some romantic vision of being like Vincent Van Gogh Jr.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:54:16'),
(10820, 24, 'A romantic comedy has to be funny and make you think about life; but the obstacle that has to be overcome is key.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:54:24'),
(10821, 24, 'In the time it takes us to look beyond the lies, we could be sailing in each other\'s eyes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 16:54:37'),
(10822, 24, 'Any romantic feelings for a 12-year-old are like entering into a fantasy world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:15:34'),
(10823, 24, 'Deep in the darkness of passions insanity, I felt taken by lust\'s strange inhumanity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:15:43'),
(10824, 24, 'The most aggressive artists often hide their romantic side.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:15:51'),
(10825, 24, 'Good night, Westley. Good work. Sleep well. I\'ll most likely kill you in the morning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:05'),
(10826, 24, 'Their lips were four red roses on a stalk.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:13'),
(10827, 24, 'But romantic vision can also lead one away from certain very hard, ugly truths about life that are important to know.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:24'),
(10828, 24, 'Return to me, for my heart wants you only. Hurry home, hurry home, won\'t you please hurry home to my heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:34'),
(10829, 24, 'Am I a romantic? I\'ve seen \'Wuthering Heights\' ten times. I\'m a romantic.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:42'),
(10830, 24, 'A lady\'s imagination is very rapid; it jumps from admiration to love, from love to matrimony in a moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:16:51'),
(10831, 24, 'Tell me how you read and I\'ll tell you who you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:01'),
(10832, 24, 'For the taxable investor, indexing means never having to say you\'re sorry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:11'),
(10833, 24, 'O, thou art fairer than the evening air clad in the beauty of a thousand stars.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:20'),
(10834, 24, 'Marriage, n: the state or condition of a community consisting of a master, a mistress, and two slaves, making in all, two.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:38'),
(10835, 24, 'Marriage, n: the state or condition of a community consisting of a master, a mistress, and two slaves, making in all, two.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:45'),
(10836, 24, 'Knots Landing is the best thing that ever happened to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:17:53'),
(10837, 24, 'Death cannot stop true love. All it can do is delay it for a while.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:18:01'),
(10838, 24, 'Being sectioned was the best thing that ever happened to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:13'),
(10839, 24, 'They were so close to each other that they preferred death to separation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:21'),
(10840, 24, 'Other men it is said have seen angels, but I have seen thee and thou art enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:29'),
(10841, 24, 'Don\'t leave my embrace for here in my arms is your place.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:37'),
(10842, 24, 'French is the language that turns dirt into romance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:48'),
(10843, 24, 'As soon go kindle fire with snow, as seek to quench the fire of love with words.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:20:56'),
(10844, 24, 'All the stars will tell the story, of our love and all its glory. Let us make this night of magic, and make it a night of love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:07'),
(10845, 24, 'I may not be a smart man, but I know what love is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:17'),
(10846, 24, 'Love is composed of a single soul inhabiting two bodies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:26'),
(10847, 24, 'True love stories never have endings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:33'),
(10848, 24, 'The best thing you can do is follow your dreams', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:40'),
(10849, 24, 'Tell me with whom you associate, and I will tell you who you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:21:49'),
(10850, 24, 'Who ever loved that loved not at first sight?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:22:00'),
(10851, 24, 'Tell me who your enemy is, and I will tell you who you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:22:08'),
(10852, 24, 'Till I loved I never lived.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAARomantic', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 17:22:18'),
