(10970, 23, 'I play every game like it\'s my last game. All that matters is that you go out there and play every game as if it was your last.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:03:08'),
(10971, 23, 'Hockey is a sport for white men. Basketball is a sport for black men. Golf is a sport for white men dressed like black pimps.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:03:16'),
(10972, 23, 'The Big Cactus... because if you come too close, you\'re gonna get stuck.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:03:43'),
(10973, 23, 'I always believe I can beat the best, achieve the best. I always see myself in the top position.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:03:53'),
(10974, 23, '\'Play the right way\' means play unselfishly, respect each other\'s achievements, play hard, fulfill your role', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:04:03'),
(10975, 23, 'I\'m not the guy who\'s afraid of failure. I like to take risks, take the big shot and all that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:04:15'),
(10976, 23, 'Commitment separates those who live their dreams from those who live their lives regretting the opportunities they have squandered.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:04:24'),
(10977, 23, 'We believe in people executing their role and caring about the team more than anything individually', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:04:34'),
(10978, 23, 'If what you have done yesterday still looks big to you. You haven\'t done much today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:04:54'),
(10979, 23, 'I\'m never satisfied. I\'m always trying to get better and learn from my mistakes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:04'),
(10980, 23, 'It\'s not just about working hard, it\'s about working together. You have to care more about the team than you do about yourself', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:12'),
(10981, 23, 'If you run into a wall, don\'t turn around and give up. Figure out how to climb it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:20'),
(10982, 23, 'In life, winning and losing will both happen. What is never acceptable is quitting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:28'),
(10983, 23, 'I can\'t make every decision for you. I don\'t have 14 timeouts. You guys got to get together and talk', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:35'),
(10984, 23, 'Don\'t believe everything you hear - even in your own mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:43'),
(10985, 23, 'There are only two options regarding commitment; you’re either in or you’re out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:05:53'),
(10986, 23, 'Pressure is something you feel when you do not know what you are doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:01'),
(10987, 23, 'Handball, swimming, running, jumping, basketball, and boxing were as much a part of me as breathing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:09'),
(10988, 23, 'Basketball really had its origin in Indiana, which remains the center of the sport.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:18'),
(10989, 23, 'Education is of no value and talent is worthless - unless you have an unwavering aim. Never find yourself without a compass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:26'),
(10990, 23, 'It\'s not about the number of hours you practice, it\'s about the number of hours your mind is present during the practice', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:34'),
(10991, 23, 'My goal is to win the next game one possession at a time. That\'s it. I don\'t have any other goals', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:45'),
(10992, 23, 'The idea is not to block every shot. The idea is to make your opponent believe that you might block every shot.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:06:53'),
(10993, 23, 'Basketball is a pretty simple game. What wins is consistency and competitiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:07:01'),
(10994, 23, 'Asthma research is a lot better and new medicines are always coming out to help young people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:07:12'),
(10995, 23, 'Get the fundamentals down and the level of everything you do will rise', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:07:20'),
(10996, 23, 'I\'m like Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer. If I\'m not ready, the sled isn\'t going to go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:07:30'),
(10997, 23, 'How good can we expect to be if our best player is not our best teammate', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:09:21'),
(10998, 23, 'As long as they are medicated the right way with the asthma medicine they won\'t have any problems.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:09:29'),
(10999, 23, 'Talent is never enough. With few exceptions the best players are the hardest workers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:09:37'),
(11000, 23, 'A good coach will make his players see what they can be rather than what they are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:09:45'),
(11001, 23, 'A basketball team is like the five fingers on your hand. If you can get them all together, you have a fist. That\'s how I want you to play.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:09:54'),
(11002, 23, 'A team divided against itself can break down at any moment. The least bit of pressure or adversity will crack it apart', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:10:03'),
(11003, 23, 'Work hard, stay focused and surround yourself with good people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:10:13'),
(11004, 23, 'The most important thing in coaching is communication. It\'s not what you say as much as what they absorb.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:11:11'),
(11005, 23, 'To do the right thing at the right season is a great art.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:18:16'),
(11006, 23, 'Basketball doesn\'t build character it reveals it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:18:23'),
(11007, 23, 'In order to achieve to achieve positive results, one must work for them, not hope for them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:18:33'),
(11008, 23, 'Wisdom is always an overmatch for strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:18:43'),
(11009, 23, 'What to do with a mistake: recognize it, admit it, learn from it, forget it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:18:53'),
(11010, 23, 'Basketball is a beautiful game when the five players on the court play with one heartbeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:03'),
(11011, 23, 'The invention of basketball was not an accident. It was developed to meet a need.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:14'),
(11012, 23, 'Hard work is not punishment. Hard work is the price of admission for the opportunity to reach sustained excellence', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:26'),
(11013, 23, 'In the game of basketball, I play first off because I love it. I love to have fun. I love to run up and down the court.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:34'),
(11014, 23, 'True grit is making a decision and standing by it, doing what must be done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:46'),
(11015, 23, 'They shot the ball well early. What comes out of the microwave hot doesn\'t always stay hot. I know, because I eat bagels in the morning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:19:57'),
(11016, 23, 'Winning is important to me, but what brings me real joy is the experience of being fully engaged in whatever I\'m doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:04'),
(11017, 23, 'I believe that the measure of a person\'s life is the affect they have on others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:15'),
(11018, 23, 'It always amazes me that spectators want to coach, coaches want to officiate, and officials just want to watch the game', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:22'),
(11019, 23, 'What distinguishes a great player is his presence. When he goes on to the court, his presence dominates the atmosphere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:34'),
(11020, 23, 'You must have respect, which is a part of love, for those under your supervision. Then they will do what you ask and more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:42'),
(11021, 23, 'One of the hardest things for a ball player to do is to accept his role', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:20:57'),
(11022, 23, 'They said you have to use your five best players but I found you win with the five who fit together the best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:21:05'),
(11023, 23, 'On good teams coaches hold players accountable, on great teams players hold players accountable', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:21:15'),
(11024, 23, 'I haven\'t been able to slam-dunk the basketball for the past five years. Or, for the thirty-eight years before that, either.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:21:22'),
(11025, 23, 'Champions play as they practice. Create a consistency of excellence in all your habits.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:21:32'),
(11026, 23, 'My whole thing is, if you love me, then love me. If you don\'t, then believe what you hear and run with that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:21:43'),
(11027, 23, 'You\'re the only one who can make the difference. Whatever your dream is, go for it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:22:13'),
(11028, 23, 'The more honor and self-respect among players, the greater the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:22:22'),
(11029, 23, 'If I walk in a home and a kid disrespects a woman, his mother or grandmother, then I am out... I wont recruit them', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:22:32'),
(11030, 23, 'Sometimes a player\'s greatest challenge is coming to grips with his role on the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:22:43'),
(11031, 23, 'Greatness is not found in possessions, power, position, or prestige. It is discovered in goodness, humility, service, and character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:22:52'),
(11032, 23, 'The grass is not always greener on the other side. You learn to appreciate these people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:01'),
(11033, 23, 'Most people have a harder time letting themselves love than finding someone to love them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:12'),
(11034, 23, 'A leader\'s job is to develop committed followers. Bad leaders destroy their followers\' sense of commitment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:22'),
(11035, 23, 'There is no doubt in my mind and I know in my time, there will be a Canadian basketball player playing for Toronto Raptors, 100%', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:30'),
(11036, 23, 'Meadowlark was the most sensational, awesome, incredible basketball player I\'ve ever seen', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:42'),
(11037, 23, 'If you quit ONCE it becomes a habit.Never quit!!!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:50'),
(11038, 23, 'Effort is only effort when it begins to hurt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:23:58'),
(11039, 23, 'The big time is not a place; it\'s the state of your heart. It\'s not something you get; it\'s something you become.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:06'),
(11040, 23, 'You don\'t just be a team. You become a team. Through tough games you find that you need each other', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:13'),
(11041, 23, 'Nate Robinson has a lot of jumping ability, but I don\'t see Josh losing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:22'),
(11042, 23, 'Basketball is one of those rare opportunities where you can make a difference, not only for yourself, but for other people as well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:33'),
(11043, 23, 'Don\'t let what other people think decide who you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:40'),
(11044, 23, 'The secret is to have eight great players and four others who will cheer like crazy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:24:49'),
(11045, 23, 'Successful programs consist of people working hard, working together, while never worrying about who gets the credit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:25:00'),
(11046, 23, 'If we magnified blessings as much as we magnify disappointments, we would all be much happier.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:25:08'),
(11047, 23, 'Your limits are somewhere up there, waiting for you to reach beyond infinity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:25:18'),
(11048, 23, 'Success is that place in the road where preparation meets opportunity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-26 18:25:27'),
(11049, 23, 'If Shakespeare can compare all of life to a stage, maybe it\'s not odd to believe that part of the play can take place on a basketball court.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:12:40'),
(11050, 23, 'Winners are losers who got up and gave it one more try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:13:00'),
(11051, 23, 'You don\'t have to live anybody else\'s story.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:13:13'),
(11052, 23, 'If Kyle Korver blocks your shot there should be a penalty box you should go to!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:13:23'),
(11053, 23, 'Long term success is a direct result of what you achieve everyday. Goals provide your daily routine', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:13:46'),
(11054, 23, 'I play basketball on Sundays and I\'m a very spiritual guy; I read a lot of Eastern philosophy and I meditate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:01'),
(11055, 23, 'When I dunk, I put something on it. I want the ball to hit the floor before I do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:09'),
(11056, 23, 'I\'m ready to accept the challenge. I\'m coming home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:18'),
(11057, 23, 'I continually stress to my players that all I expect from them at practice and in the games is their maximum effort.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:27'),
(11058, 23, 'Winning is about having the whole team on the same page.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:37'),
(11059, 23, 'If you\'re going to hire an assassin, let him go out and kill someone. I can\'t be Shaq taking six or seven shots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:47'),
(11060, 23, 'I\'m going back to the old Shaq. I was normal last year - I was an earthling last summer. I had to go back to my alien roots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:14:54'),
(11061, 23, 'Desire outweighs footwork when it comes to crashing the glass', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:03'),
(11062, 23, 'You have to earn your right to win the game with effort and togetherness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:12'),
(11063, 23, 'The number one problem that keeps people from winning in the United States today is lack of belief in themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:19'),
(11064, 23, 'We would have two less championships here if it was not for Manu Ginobili. In my eyes, he\'s the stud of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:27'),
(11065, 23, 'A lot of guys go through their whole careers and don\'t win a championship, but are still great coaches.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:35'),
(11066, 23, 'If you do the work you get rewarded. There are no shortcuts in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:44'),
(11067, 23, 'If you\'ve got a Corvette that runs into a brick wall, you know what\'s going to happen. He\'s a Corvette. I\'m a brick wall.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:15:59'),
(11068, 23, 'I didn\'t get into teaching and coaching for the number of wins or the money. It was a passion for trying to help young people', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:07'),
(11069, 23, 'The best teams have chemistry. They communicate with each other and they sacrifice personal glory for a common goal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:14'),
(11070, 23, 'You build your program from the ideas of great coaches.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:26');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(11071, 23, 'Never underestimate the heart of a champion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:37'),
(11072, 23, 'The Spurs are a great WNBA team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:44'),
(11073, 23, 'He could be dominant - if he played in the WNBA.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:16:52'),
(11074, 23, 'I\'m not going to try to go out there and outdo him. I don\'t have to try to outdo him, I\'m Shaq.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:04'),
(11075, 23, 'Stop by stop by stop. Play aggressively. Sprint back on \'D\' and pay attention to how we\'re supposed to guard as a team', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:12'),
(11076, 23, 'He knew I enjoyed the relationships of college basketball. All along, he was the wise one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:20'),
(11077, 23, 'A person really doesn\'t become whole, until he becomes a part of something that\'s bigger than himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:29'),
(11078, 23, 'First master the fundamentals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:36'),
(11079, 23, 'Good people are happy when something good happens to someone else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:43'),
(11080, 23, 'If I can\'t expect someone to be accountable off the floor, how can I expect them to guard a pick and roll? Or get a rebound?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:51'),
(11081, 23, 'Your best players have to unite and inspire the group... otherwise, they\'ll divide the group', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:17:58'),
(11082, 23, 'Recognize and reward players who put the team first, not just the gifted ones.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:16'),
(11083, 23, 'Leadership is action, not position', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:24'),
(11084, 23, 'Champions are made from something they have deep inside of them-a desire, a dream, a vison.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:32'),
(11085, 23, 'Blacks can get into medical school with a lower grade . .. If that\'s true, a Jew should be able to play basketball with a lower net.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:40'),
(11086, 23, 'There is no substitution for hustle, and if you don\'t hustle there will be substitution', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:47'),
(11087, 23, 'The guys who take shortcuts, who aren\'t ready, they fail when their opportunity comes', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:18:56'),
(11088, 23, 'Discipline is the greatest form of love you can show someone. Great players crave discipline', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:04'),
(11089, 23, 'Criticize on defense and encourage on offense.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:14'),
(11090, 23, 'Character never quits; and with patience and persistence; Dreams do come true!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:19'),
(11091, 23, 'Pressure can burst a pipe, or pressure can make a diamond.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:27'),
(11092, 23, 'A lion never roars after a kill.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:34'),
(11093, 23, 'Working hard is one thing, but working hard with purpose is what separates the good from the great', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:45'),
(11094, 23, 'We are in the trophy generation.Give them a trophy for 23rd place.That makes the parents happy', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:52'),
(11095, 23, 'Because there are no fours.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:19:59'),
(11096, 23, 'Excellence is the unlimited ability to improve the quality of what you have to offer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:20:06'),
(11097, 23, 'Know how to win and how to lose and be able to handle adversity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:20:14'),
(11098, 23, 'Success is a matter of understanding and religiously practicing specific, simple habits that always lead to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:20:38'),
(11099, 23, 'When you are not practicing, remember, someone somewhere is practicing, and when you meet him he will win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:20:47'),
(11100, 23, 'I played basketball to try to get my parents from working so hard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:20:55'),
(11101, 23, 'Teams that play together beat those with superior players who play more as individuals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:21:23'),
(11102, 23, 'You never make any of the shots you never take. 87% of the ones you do take, you\'ll miss too. I make 110% of my shots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:21:30'),
(11103, 23, 'I learned early that if I wanted to achieve anything in life, I\'d have to do it myself. I learned that I had to be accountable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:21:39'),
(11104, 23, 'I don\'t hire good coaches, I hire good people. If they turn out to be good coaches, too, that\'s a plus.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:21:46'),
(11105, 23, 'I\'m looking for players who make their teammates better. You do that with enthusiasm and passion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:21:54'),
(11106, 23, 'I\'d rather be a non-All-Star playing in the Western Conference finals than an All-Star who\'s sitting at home in May.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:02'),
(11107, 23, 'You must have your player\'s heads and hearts before they will do anything for you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:10'),
(11108, 23, 'You don\'t win games as a coach during games. You win games as a coach before games. Players win during games, not coaches', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:19'),
(11109, 23, 'You have to make shots to win basketball games and we didn\'t do that. You also have to get back on defense, so it was a double-whammy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:27'),
(11110, 23, 'Fans never fall asleep at our games, because they\'re afraid they might get hit by a pass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:42'),
(11111, 23, 'Help your players to control their emotions - do this through example.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:22:53'),
(11112, 23, 'Prepare for every game like you just lost your last game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:02'),
(11113, 23, 'Your ability to communicate to your young people will determine your success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:10'),
(11114, 23, 'Champions never complain, they are too busy getting better', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:20'),
(11115, 23, 'The Boston Celtics are not a basketball team, they are a way of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:39'),
(11116, 23, 'Always acknowledge hustle plays in practice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:46'),
(11117, 23, 'Fatherhood will put a man through a lot, but it\'s a tremendous job, the best in the world - even better than playing basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:23:56'),
(11118, 23, 'Players know how to dribble, shoot and pass. The challenge is to teach them why they should do it a certain way, and when they should do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:24:08'),
(11119, 23, 'Blending the talents of your team members is crucial to basketball success', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:24:21'),
(11120, 23, 'Play the game with a smile.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:24:31'),
(11121, 23, 'The secret of winning is working more as a team, less as individuals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:24:38'),
(11122, 23, 'The more things we can get kids to do correctly off the court, the more they will do correctly on the court.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:24:47'),
(11123, 23, 'Every time you compete, try harder to improve on your last performance. Give nothing short of your very best effort.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:00'),
(11124, 23, 'Michael Jordon may have been the best basketball player in history, but he couldn\'t have won six NBA titles without a team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:08'),
(11125, 23, 'In basketball - as in life - true joy comes from being fully present in each and every moment, not just when things are going your way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:15'),
(11126, 23, 'Championship teams are built on being prepared, playing unselfishly and being held accountable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:22'),
(11127, 23, 'If you don\'t feel you have something to prove every day, you\'ll never improve', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:30'),
(11128, 23, 'Set higher standards for your own performance than anyone else around you, and your only competition will be with yourself', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:25:40'),
(11130, 23, 'The price of excellence is discipline. The cost of mediocrity is disappointment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:26:12'),
(11131, 23, 'Basketball is a team game. But that doesn\'t mean all five players should have the same amount of shots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:26:20'),
(11132, 23, 'The Big Cactus. I will stick you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:26:29'),
(11133, 23, 'The greatest compliment to any player is he is a great teammate. We can\'t all be great players, but we can all be great teammates.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:26:46'),
(11134, 23, 'Coaches win practices, players win games', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:26:55'),
(11135, 23, 'I always laugh when people ask me about rebounding techniques. I\'ve got a technique. It\'s called just go get the damn ball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:04'),
(11136, 23, 'You don\'t stop running because you get old, you get old because you stop running.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:13'),
(11137, 23, 'Footwork is one of the primary prerequisites to becoming a great player', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:23'),
(11138, 23, 'False Hustle = cheap fouls, lunging, reaching, etc.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:32'),
(11139, 23, 'I really get motivated when I have doubters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:40'),
(11140, 23, 'I don\'t believe in statistics. There are too many factors that can\'t be measured. You can\'t measure a ballplayer\'s heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:49'),
(11141, 23, 'Being a professional is doing the things you love to do, on the days you don\'t feel like doing them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:27:57'),
(11142, 23, 'Your best player has to set a tone of intolerance for anything that gets in the way of winning', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:28:07'),
(11143, 23, 'If you get tough mentally, you can get tough physically and overcome fatigue.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:11'),
(11144, 23, 'When you watch the game, be a student of the game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:20'),
(11145, 23, 'Michael Jordan is God disguised as a basketball player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:28'),
(11146, 23, 'We\'re focusing on the whole pie, not a slice. A slice is good, but it\'s not good enough to get you fat. We\'re trying to get fat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:35'),
(11147, 23, 'Winning coaches look for opportunities to praise. Anything that reflects a commitment to the team is praiseworthy', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:47'),
(11148, 23, 'What type of teammates do you want to play with? Be that teammate yourself', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:29:56'),
(11149, 23, 'It is not the critic who counts...The credit belongs to the man who is actually in the arena.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:08'),
(11150, 23, 'Positioning, anticipation and technique create quickness. Therefore, you can always get quicker', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:18'),
(11151, 23, 'If you\'re not talking, you\'re not playing defense', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:26'),
(11152, 23, 'The game honors toughness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:34'),
(11153, 23, 'They run like deer, jump like deer and think like deer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:44'),
(11154, 23, 'Insist upon yourself. Be original.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:31:55'),
(11155, 23, 'They say that nobody is perfect. Then they tell you practice makes perfect. I wish they\'d make up their minds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:03'),
(11156, 23, 'One player\'s selfish attitude can poison a locker room and make it hard, if not impossible, to establish team work', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:11'),
(11157, 23, 'This is a team game and one man doesn\'t win and one man doesn\'t lose. In the end, the best team usually wins.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:21'),
(11158, 23, 'Give your dreams all you\'ve got, and you\'ll be amazed at the energy that comes out of you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:30'),
(11159, 23, 'Happiness is a habit—cultivate it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:38'),
(11160, 23, 'I only use statistics to reinforce what I already think, or if it\'s something unusual.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:50'),
(11161, 23, 'I never comment on referees and I\'m not going to break the habit of a lifetime for that prat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:32:58'),
(11162, 23, 'Not only is there more to life than basketball, there\'s a lot more to basketball than basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:33:08'),
(11163, 23, 'Nothing is stronger than habit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:33:17'),
(11164, 23, 'Basketball is like war in that offensive weapons are developed first, and it always takes a while for the defense to catch up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:33:25'),
(11165, 23, 'Yeah, I like cars and basketball. But you know what I like more? Bananas.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:33:34'),
(11166, 23, 'I always mean what I say, but I don\'t always say what I\'m thinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:33:42'),
(11167, 23, 'My rule was I wouldn\'t recruit a kid if he had grass in front of his house. That\'s not my world. My world has a cracked sidewalk.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:35:37'),
(11168, 23, 'I don\'t believe professional athletes should be role models. I believe parents should be role models.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:35:54'),
(11169, 23, 'Have a spiritual basis which guides you in life. Have a philosophy of life to live by.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:36:04'),
(11170, 23, 'You should always want your coach to be critical. It gives you an opportunity to learn and to overcome adversity', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:36:13'),
(11171, 23, 'I never thought I\'d lead the NBA in rebounding, but I got a lot of help from my team-mates - they did a lot of missing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:36:57'),
(11172, 23, 'Good defensive play is as much a matter of hustle, desire and pride as it is anything else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:37:18'),
(11173, 23, 'To win the big games you must get to the Free Throw line, and then you must make them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:37:33'),
(11174, 23, 'Our self image and our habits tend to go together. Change one and you will automatically change the other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:37:42'),
(11175, 23, 'Great teamwork is the only way we create the breakthroughs that define our careers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:37:51'),
(11176, 23, '1. Be on time. 2. Never criticize a teammate. 3. Never use profanity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:03'),
(11177, 23, 'I\'m in favour of drug tests, just so long as they are multiple choice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:10'),
(11178, 23, 'The more your players have to think on the basketball court, the slower their feet get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:20'),
(11179, 23, 'I play to win, whether during practice or a real game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:28'),
(11180, 23, 'I\'m not comfortable being preachy, but more people need to start spending as much time in the library as they do on the basketball court.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:36'),
(11181, 23, 'Over coaching is the worst thing you can do to a player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:47'),
(11182, 23, 'If you are confident you have done everything possible to prepare yourself, then there is nothing to fear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:38:54'),
(11183, 23, 'Perfection is impossibility but striving for perfection is not. Do the best you can. That is what counts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:39:02'),
(11184, 23, 'We have the mentality of the hunter. We want to be the most enthusiastic team in the country. That\'s what we can control', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:39:12'),
(11185, 23, 'My relationship with Northeast Ohio is bigger than basketball. I didn\'t realize that four years ago. I do now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:39:20'),
(11186, 23, 'Be more concerned with your character than your reputation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:39:29'),
(11187, 23, 'Your defense will save you on the nights that your offense isn\'t working', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:39:38'),
(11188, 23, 'Defense is what matters. Scoring doesn\'t interest me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:40:10'),
(11189, 23, 'I have one thing to say to those non-believers. Don\'t ever underestimate the heart of a champion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:40:25'),
(11190, 23, 'Success is determined by your daily choices and habits', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:40:35'),
(11191, 23, 'I have seen countless people make a choice to be confident. If you don\'t naturally feel bold and confident, you can choose an attitude of confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:40:45'),
(11192, 23, 'A team should be an extension of a coach\'s personality. My teams are arrogant and obnoxious.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:41:04'),
(11193, 23, 'Practice to beat the best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:41:14'),
(11194, 23, 'Basketball is in my blood. It is my obligation to try.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:41:22'),
(11195, 23, 'I\'m not a role model... Just because I dunk a basketball doesn\'t mean I should raise your kids.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:41:31'),
(11196, 23, 'We overload in our workouts so that the game slows down in real life. It helps you become a smarter basketball player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:41:52'),
(11197, 23, 'I don\'t complain about playing time. My job is to play so well the coach can\'t sit me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:01'),
(11198, 23, 'The players I respected most were the toughest players, not those who talked a good game or blocked a shot and acted like a fool.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:09'),
(11199, 23, 'I told them not to worry about it, since we were going to play indoors.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:17'),
(11200, 23, 'Mental toughness is to physical as four is to one.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:25'),
(11201, 23, 'If you are afraid of failure, you don\'t deserve success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:33'),
(11202, 23, 'You don\'t play against opponents, you play against the game of basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:42'),
(11203, 23, 'Kobe always tried to be a hero. But you know, as the saying goes, a hero ain\'t nothing but a sandwich.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:50'),
(11204, 23, 'Basketball is just a platform for me to inspire people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:42:57'),
(11205, 23, 'I told him, \'Son, what is it with you? Is it ignorance or apathy?\' He said, \'Coach, I don\'t know and I don\'t care.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:05'),
(11206, 23, 'I\'ll never worry about not being successful. I\'ll just take it one day at a time, one season at a time. And play as hard as I can.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:18'),
(11207, 23, 'One score makes happy ONE player, one assist makes happy TWO.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:26'),
(11208, 23, 'You can always tell the Catholic schools by the length of the cheerleaders\' skirts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:34'),
(11209, 23, 'Sport is the best means of communication between people from different religions and countries.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:42'),
(11210, 23, 'I don\'t try to change myself to impress anybody. I\'m just who I am.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:50'),
(11211, 23, 'You always have to be on edge. You always have to take every practice, every game, like it is your last.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:43:57'),
(11212, 23, 'People ask me if I could fly, I said, \'yeah....\' for a little while.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:44:06'),
(11213, 23, 'Defense doesn\'t break down on the help, it breaks down on the recovery.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:44:23'),
(11214, 23, 'People think that I\'m some tough renegade, black-hearted being, evil, but that ain\'t me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:44:35'),
(11215, 23, 'I always wanted to be a basketball player. Nothing more, nothing less.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:44:43'),
(11216, 23, 'Picking an assistant coach, the first thing I was interested in was the man\'s character.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:45:51'),
(11217, 23, 'For five years I\'ve felt like the best prostitute in a high-class whorehouse. But all the other girls get paid more than I do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:04'),
(11218, 23, 'If the waitress has dirty ankles, the chili is good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:12'),
(11219, 23, 'I know that the hard work got me here. And the day I stop working hard, this can all go away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:20'),
(11220, 23, 'It is foolish to expect a young man to follow your advice and to ignore your example.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:28'),
(11221, 23, 'I\'ve been playing youth basketball ever since I was in sixth grade; I\'ve been traveling ever since I was in sixth grade, so I\'m used to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:38'),
(11222, 23, 'I can get better. I haven\'t reached my ceiling yet on how well I can shoot the basketball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:46:49'),
(11223, 23, 'The most important thing in good leadership is truly caring.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:03'),
(11224, 23, 'In all my years one thing has never changed; You win with serious, tough-minded players. That never changes', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:12'),
(11225, 23, 'If you want it you must obtain it by great labor.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:22'),
(11226, 23, 'If you are a good team, your offense is born on the defensive end.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:32'),
(11227, 23, 'What does politically correct mean? If you\'re fat, don\'t ask me if you\'re fat, because I\'m gonna tell you the truth. You\'re fat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:40'),
(11228, 23, 'Basketball is my refuge, my sanctuary. I go back to being a kid on the playground. When I get here, it\'s all good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:50'),
(11229, 23, 'One man cannot make a team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABasketball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 16:47:58'),
