(11287, 22, 'The NFL draft is going to be this Thursday. That\'s a huge night for college players. That\'s the night they start being paid over the table.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:12:26'),
