(11317, 22, 'It\'s not whether you get knocked down, it\'s whether you get up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:19:22'),
(11318, 22, 'Nobody who ever gave his best regretted it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:19:29'),
(11319, 22, 'Some people are born on third base and go through life thinking they hit a triple.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:19:37'),
(11320, 22, 'The man on top of the mountain didn\'t fall there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:19:44'),
(11321, 22, 'There is a difference between conceit and confidence. Conceit is bragging about yourself. Confidence means you believe you can get the job done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:19:52'),
(11322, 22, 'If you\'re willing to put yourself and your dreams on the line, at the very least you\'ll discover an inner strength you may not have known existed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:00'),
(11323, 22, 'The more honor and self-respect among players, the greater the team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:07'),
(11324, 22, 'Winning means being unafraid to lose.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:14'),
(11325, 22, 'Most of us are in this more than just for playing soccer. We\'re in it for the bigger goal - to move it along for the next generation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:21'),
(11326, 22, 'Yes, I thought I was joining Manchester United, I was misled by all involved. I wasnt aware of another Manchester team', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:33'),
(11327, 22, 'Being an England supporter is like being the over-optimistic parents of the fat kid on sports day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:46'),
(11328, 22, 'If I ever wear a Chelsea shirt, you have permission to kill me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:20:59'),
(11329, 22, 'Messi is class. There is him, and then there is the rest. What he does is extraordinary.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:21:09'),
(11330, 22, 'Build up your weaknesses until they become your strong points.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:21:56'),
(11331, 22, 'If you aren\'t going all the way, why go at all?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:03'),
(11332, 22, 'There\'s two times of year for me: Football season, and waiting for football season.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:10'),
(11333, 22, 'I\'d catch a punt naked, in the snow, in Buffalo, for a chance to play in the NFL.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:17');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(11334, 22, 'When all is said and done, more is said than done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:24'),
(11335, 22, 'Writing is like a contact sport, like football. You can get hurt, but you enjoy it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:31'),
(11336, 22, 'Football is a more beautiful game in high definition.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:38'),
(11337, 22, 'Football is all very well as a game for rough girls, but is hardly suitable for delicate boys.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:51'),
(11338, 22, 'I love playing football, being out on the pitch with a ball, and I will be a little sad when that ends.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:22:59'),
(11339, 22, 'Going to college offered me the chance to play football for four more years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:06'),
(11340, 22, 'That lad must have been born offside.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:13'),
(11341, 22, 'It takes sacrifice as well as talent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:20'),
(11342, 22, 'You can always become better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:27'),
(11343, 22, 'Every football coach worries about every football game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:33'),
(11344, 22, 'I take football as an avenue to different opportunities. Football is not using me; I\'m using football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:41'),
(11345, 22, 'I\'ve played everything - baseball, football, basketball. I can still swim a mile a day. That\'s why I can\'t walk.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:49'),
(11346, 22, 'Football is a simple game. It\'s just very hard to play it simple.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:23:58'),
(11347, 22, 'The same thing I applied to football, I applied to trying to be an actor and hopefully it came off well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:24:05'),
(11348, 22, 'Keeping fit is really important as playing football is all I\'ve ever wanted to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:24:35'),
(11349, 22, 'Baseball is not like football, basketball where a momentum is something made. You don\'t really have that kind of momentum in baseball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:24:44'),
(11350, 22, 'There\'s just a big, empty football field that\'s supposed to be filled with monsters that I haven\'t even thought of.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:24:56'),
(11351, 22, 'I love football. I really love football, As far as I\'m concerned, it\'s the second best thing in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:25:04'),
(11352, 22, 'There are visible and invisible dictators. The power structure of world football is monarchical. It\'s the most secret kingdom in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:25:18'),
(11353, 22, 'I like to read the papers. I make my living from football, and I like to know what\'s going on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:15'),
(11354, 22, 'If you dont live, eat, breathe, football, then youre not a true football player. You just wear the jersey.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:25'),
(11355, 22, 'Football players are misunderstood. They arent the dumb jocks people think they are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:32'),
(11356, 22, 'Football is the No. 1 sport in America.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:39'),
(11357, 22, 'Football is a violent game. We are violent men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:49'),
(11358, 22, 'I hate perception. There\'s far too much of it in football', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:26:56'),
(11359, 22, 'Jonny Evans plays sort of international football with Northern Ireland', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:27:04'),
(11360, 22, 'Messi is much more than being clever. He is a genius who reserves all his expressiveness for football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:27:11'),
(11361, 22, 'Im a huge Rugby Union fan, which is a bit like American football - but tougher.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:27:38'),
(11362, 22, 'When I\'m done playing football, I just might be the couch potato dad.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:27:47'),
(11363, 22, 'Football is pretty much played 16 times a year, where training is kind of a year-round thing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:27:55'),
(11364, 22, 'I play American football every Saturday, which I find calming.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:14'),
(11365, 22, 'What matters to me more than anything is that when all of this is over, football is the winner.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:22'),
(11366, 22, 'We cannot allow the reputation of football and FIFA to be dragged through the mud any longer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:31'),
(11367, 22, 'I played football and ran track in junior high, but by high school I was getting serious about my studies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:38'),
(11368, 22, 'Football makes nonsense of class. It may make nonsense of colour in some circumstances.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:48'),
(11369, 22, 'There\'s only one plan in football: win you next match.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:28:56'),
(11370, 22, 'I grew up in Tennessee where you either play football or you don\'t do anything at all. So I was a bit of loner, being interested in music.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:29:34'),
(11371, 22, 'That\'s often the best place to beat a goalkeeper, isn\'t it, between the legs?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:29:44'),
(11372, 22, 'A full-blooded encounter for a number of reasons, many of them illegitimate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:29:51'),
(11373, 22, 'It\'s not just a football club. Celtic means so much to so many people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:29:59'),
(11374, 22, 'Football is not a game for the weak of heart, because every day you\'ve got a hundred reasons to take all those pads off and say, \'F-k it.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:30:33'),
(11375, 22, 'Football, like life, is about change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:30:45'),
(11376, 22, 'The issue that a political campaign would make a human life into - you know - a political football, is unsettling.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:30:55'),
(11377, 22, 'I\'ve lived most people\'s dream by playing football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:31:12'),
(11378, 22, 'I can never hope to find words to express my feelings at becoming a member of the Celtic Football Club.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:31:28'),
(11379, 22, 'Some people wouldn\'t say I coached in the National Football League. I coached with the Raiders, right?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:31:47'),
(11380, 22, 'Being a running back helped me tremendously. It taught me judgement in the defense and how to judge the football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:32:35'),
(11381, 22, 'I was a pretty good soccer player, but it just wasn\'t for me. I thrive in the intensified atmosphere on a football field.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:32:42'),
(11382, 22, 'I was never someone who had a lot of confidence in anything that had to do with using your brain. I really was lost in my life after football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:36:26'),
(11383, 22, 'I am gagged and imprisoned. I can\'t even speak. I want to kick a football in a park with my son. Ordinary, banal life: my impossible dream.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:36:37'),
(11384, 22, 'Once I started taking drama classes, I asked myself why I had ever wasted so much time on a football team.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:36:46'),
(11385, 22, 'I\'m not pro-life, and I\'m not pro-choice. I\'m pro-football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:36:54'),
(11386, 22, 'I love football and I love winning, and when things aren\'t going right I get annoyed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:01'),
(11387, 22, 'I hope I have a lot more football left.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:09'),
(11388, 22, 'I love playing football. I love playing for the Patriots.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:19'),
(11389, 22, 'I love football. I\'ll watch the NFL before I watch any NBA.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:28'),
(11390, 22, 'I am more mature. I\'m a better football player. I just feel like this is my time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:36'),
(11391, 22, 'Football is my job, not my life, but it\'s a job I\'m going to give my all for as long as I\'m in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:37:49'),
(11392, 22, 'I don\'t care if it\'s politics, religion or football. I believe you have to keep opening your mind. And shut your mouth sometimes!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:38:17'),
(11393, 22, 'I was awful at football when I was a little kid. I didn\'t have the aggressiveness. I was just a nice kid. I didn\'t want to hurt anyone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:38:44'),
(11394, 22, 'Football comes naturally to me, but basketball is a challenge, that\'s why I like it so much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:38:52'),
(11395, 22, 'I love football. The games are a pure rush. By the time I\'m done playing, I want to be among the best tight ends ever to play the game.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:00'),
(11396, 22, 'It doesn\'t matter that I play football. Anybody can make a difference in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:11'),
(11397, 22, 'Football is my love. Football is what I\'m going to do. I\'m a football player first.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:18'),
(11398, 22, 'Football is my life. There is no question about that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:26'),
(11399, 22, 'I take pride in my life-my wife, my family. I try my best not to have football define the person that I am.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:37'),
(11400, 22, 'The greatest thing for me football-wise is that it\'s a test of will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:39:44'),
(11401, 22, 'America needs football. It\'s a real blue-collar sport; it\'s played with a blue-collar mentality, a mentality that\'s the backbone of this country.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:40:02'),
(11402, 22, 'I have a great family. I can call them and they don\'t want to talk just football They want to find out how my day went outside of football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:40:10'),
(11403, 22, 'Basketball was always my first love, but once I had a good year as a senior, I figured the next step was to play college football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:40:19'),
(11405, 22, 'I know I probably never will win the league MVP or passing title. That is not why I play the game. I try to win football games and championships.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:40:53'),
(11406, 22, 'All I have to do is play football now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:01'),
(11407, 22, 'Trust me-the day I\'m not into football, I\'ll walk away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:10'),
(11408, 22, 'Football is more important to me than money right now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:22'),
(11409, 22, 'Football is what I love, and I know I can do it, too.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:30'),
(11410, 22, 'I\'m not the prototype wide receiver. But I like to think I\'m one hell of a football player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:40'),
(11411, 22, 'At Texas, I was a football player playing baseball. And the way I play I think I still am.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:41:48'),
(11412, 22, 'I love football in the rain. That is what it\'s all about.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:42:22'),
(11413, 22, 'I like to think of myself as a regular guy, except I play football for a living. I try not to be an arrogant turd out there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:42:30'),
(11414, 22, 'I want to be remembered as a championship football player.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:42:58'),
(11415, 22, 'I like to watch good football so I like to watch good players. I like Cristiano Ronaldo, Andres Iniesta, Xavi and Wayne Rooney.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:43:08'),
(11416, 22, 'The stronger women get, the more men love football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:43:17'),
(11417, 22, 'If I had stayed with football in college, I probably would have been a first-round pick.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:43:26'),
(11418, 22, 'High school football in Detroit was not easy at all. There were talented players everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:43:35'),
(11419, 22, 'The stuff I went through at Auburn? It didn\'t matter anymore. I just wanted to play football.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:44:12'),
(11420, 22, 'I fought as a kid. But football is what kept me out of trouble. You could always fight, whether you\'re in trouble or not', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:44:44'),
(11421, 22, 'I don\'t take a day off. I don\'t slack. All I know is hard-nose football. There ain\'t no breaks or vacations for me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:44:54'),
(11422, 22, 'It was fun, having speed and being able to jump. Especially playing football. I played wide receiver and defensive back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:01'),
(11423, 22, 'A lot of people wanted me to play college football, but I wanted to get started playing pro baseball.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:09'),
(11424, 22, 'Kicking the football and the soccer ball is all the same, just a different shape, like an egg. It doesn\'t make any difference.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:23'),
(11425, 22, 'I\'m a selfish football player. Each time the ball is snapped, I tell myself that I want to make that tackle, make that big play.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:31'),
(11426, 22, 'I\'m a guy here to play football. I\'m not here for photos or newspapers or TV shows or trophies or awards. I\'m not into all that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:40'),
(11427, 22, 'Excluding nobody, I\'m the best player in the National Football League.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:47'),
(11428, 22, 'I was a college football fanatic, and I wanted to play, not sit on the sidelines. It\'s tough when you know you\'re just a project.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:45:56'),
(11429, 22, 'There\'s more to me than football. It\'s just part of my life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:46:03'),
(11430, 22, 'I believe that if I committed to basketball, I could make an impact in the NBA. I now see football as my job and my greatest challenge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:48:05'),
(11431, 22, 'I approach football like a street-ball game, like I\'m playing with the fellas in the yard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 17:48:14'),
