(11544, 22, 'My days are so busy with school and football, it\'s not often that I get out, anyway. But when I do, I like to meet people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:10:58'),
(11545, 22, 'Is [football] for everybody? Of course not. But it is a meaningful contribution beyond, I think, other alternatives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:11:11'),
(11546, 22, 'I take a good feeling away from what football brings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:11:19'),
(11547, 22, 'Football is my first passion. I\'ve played it since I was a little kid.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:11:31'),
(11548, 22, 'You have to sometimes shoot from the second row, that\'s all football. So you have to be a bit more flexible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:12:24'),
(11549, 22, 'I think my boys handled it pretty much the same way with their children, but my grandsons all ended up playing football or lacrosse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:12:42'),
(11550, 22, 'When I look back on when I grew up, not even football players lifted weights. That was back 50 years ago.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:12:52'),
(11551, 22, 'Look at football, where you still have injuries no matter how much they improve the helmets and other equipment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:02'),
(11552, 22, 'If I wasn\'t playing football, I\'d be a juvenile probation officer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:11'),
(11553, 22, 'The world is changing isn\'t it? So you\'re not allowed to pray before a football game. I thought it was horrible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:27'),
(11554, 22, 'I\'m a football coach. I\'m not a doctor ... They don\'t call plays, I don\'t do surgeries. We have a great deal here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:36'),
(11555, 22, 'I was a football player and competitor in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:45'),
(11556, 22, 'I like watching sports. I like going to sports games and that\'s kind of my life during football season for sure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:13:52'),
(11557, 22, 'You can\'t control some things in football, but you can control how we view things and how we work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:14:00'),
(11558, 22, 'I\'ve played rugby at school a bit. I didn\'t play football at school; I played football after school.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:14:10'),
(11559, 22, 'Chess isn\'t football or hockey.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAFootball', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-27 18:14:20'),
(11560, 21, 'One reason cats are happier than people is that they have no newspapers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:16:40'),
(11561, 21, 'Now you people have names. That\'s because you don\'t know who you are. We know who we are, so we don\'t need names.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:16:48'),
(11562, 21, 'I usually just have one cat. It is difficult, but I have my one cat that he\'ll travel with me if it\'s appropriate, if I\'m not going overseas.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:16:59'),
(11563, 21, 'We are the ones who have high blood pressure, ulcers, and heart attacks, not cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:18:41'),
(11564, 21, 'But thousands die without or this or that, Die, and endow a college or a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:18:50'),
(11565, 21, 'Cats names are more for human benefit. They give one a certain degree more confidence that the animal belongs to you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:19:48'),
(11566, 21, 'Cats do not keep the mice away; it is my belief that they preserve them for the chase.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:19:57'),
(11567, 21, 'There is no \'cat language.\' Painful as it is for us to admit, they don\'t need one!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:21:22'),
(11568, 21, 'If cats were double the size they are now, they\'d probably be illegal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:21:30'),
(11569, 21, 'Many cats are the death of the mouse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:21:40'),
(11570, 21, 'You have learned enough to see that cats are much like you and me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:21:48'),
(11571, 21, 'I had the X rating on my films. Now they do as much on The Simpsons as I got an X rating for Fritz the Cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:21:57'),
(11572, 21, 'I cant swing a dead cat without hitting a reporter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:22:23'),
(11573, 21, 'For every house is incomplete without him, and a blessing is lacking in the spirit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:22:33'),
(11574, 21, 'It\'s still about the women. It\'s not called Desperate Plumber. People are more interested in cat fights.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:22:41'),
(11575, 21, 'We [journalists] tell the public which way the cat is jumping. The public will take care of the cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:24:21'),
(11576, 21, 'What I used to do between writing fits was feed my kids, ride my horse and go shopping for cat and dog food.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:24:28'),
(11577, 21, 'I can\'t have cats around me because they try to steal my energy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:24:36'),
(11578, 21, 'I also believe, without any supporting evidence, that cats are evil.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:24:43'),
(11579, 21, 'Persian pussy from over the sea demure and lazy and smug and fat none of your ribbons and bells for me ours is the zest of the alley cat', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:24:52'),
(11580, 21, 'One small cat changes coming home to an empty house to coming home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:25:07'),
(11581, 21, 'A cat\'s rage is beautiful, burning with pure cat flame, all its hair standing up and crackling blue sparks, eyes blazing and sputtering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:25:20'),
(11582, 21, 'Like all pure creatures, cats are practical.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:07'),
(11583, 21, 'I am fond of pigs. Dogs look up to us. Cats look down on us. Pigs treat us as equals.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:13'),
(11584, 21, 'Prose books are the show dogs I breed and sell to support my cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:21'),
(11585, 21, 'Cats are connoisseurs of comfort.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:29'),
(11586, 21, 'Cats are intended to teach us that not everything in nature has a function.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:37');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(11587, 21, 'I kind of imagine myself at eighty, a cat lady.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:44'),
(11588, 21, 'I care not much for a man\'s religion whose dog and cat are not the better for it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:27:51'),
(11589, 21, 'I have a lot of very close girlfriends and sisters - I\'m from an all female family. My father often quips that even the cat was neutered!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:04'),
(11590, 21, 'Never wear anything that panics the cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:15'),
(11591, 21, 'God is really only another artist. He invented the giraffe, the elephant and the cat. He has no real style, He just goes on trying other things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:22'),
(11592, 21, 'A man who carries a cat by the tail learns something he can learn in no other way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:29'),
(11593, 21, 'If man could be crossed with the cat, it would improve man but deteriorate the cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:37'),
(11594, 21, 'One of the most striking differences between a cat and a lie is that a cat has only nine lives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:45'),
(11595, 21, 'If a dog jumps into your lap, it is because he is fond of you; but if a cat does the same thing, it is because your lap is warmer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:52'),
(11596, 21, 'Curiosity killed the cat, but for a while I was a suspect.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:28:59'),
(11597, 21, 'Winners are different. They\'re a different breed of cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:29:08'),
(11598, 21, 'I\'ve met many thinkers and many cats, but the wisdom of cats is infinitely superior.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:29:16'),
(11599, 21, 'A cat is the only domestic animal I know who toilet trains itself and does a damned impressive job of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:29:25'),
(11600, 21, 'I am as vigilant as a cat to steal cream.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:29:33'),
(11601, 21, 'By and large, people who enjoy teaching animals to roll over will find themselves happier with a dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:30:55'),
(11602, 21, 'The cat could very well be man\'s best friend but would never stoop to admitting it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:09'),
(11603, 21, 'Cat said, \'I am not a friend, and I am not a Servant. I am the Cat who walks by himself, and I wish to come into your Cave.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:16'),
(11604, 21, 'For me, one of the pleasures of cats company is their devotion to bodily comfort.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:23'),
(11605, 21, 'Nobody who is not prepared to spoil cats will get from them the reward they are able to give to those who do spoil them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:31'),
(11606, 21, 'The only mystery about the cat is why it ever decided to become a domestic animal.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:38'),
(11607, 21, 'You cannot look at a sleeping cat and feel tense.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:45'),
(11608, 21, 'It always gives me a shiver when I see a cat seeing what I can\'t see.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:31:53'),
(11609, 21, 'Always the cat remains a little beyond the limits we try to set for him in our blind folly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:00'),
(11610, 21, 'Cats are smarter than dogs. You can\'t get eight cats to pull a sled through snow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:08'),
(11611, 21, 'Even the stupidest cat seems to know more than any dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:16'),
(11612, 21, 'Intelligence in the cat is underrated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:24'),
(11613, 21, 'A little drowsing cat is an image of perfect beatitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:31'),
(11614, 21, 'A cat improves the garden wall in sunshine, and the hearth in foul weather.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:39'),
(11615, 21, 'A dog, I have always said, is prose; a cat is a poem.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:47'),
(11616, 21, 'The cat is, above all things, a dramatist.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:32:58'),
(11617, 21, 'The cat is the only animal without visible means of support who still manages to find a living in the city.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:33:07'),
(11618, 21, 'Cats are dangerous companions for writers because cat watching is a near-perfect method of writing avoidance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:33:15'),
(11619, 21, 'Don\'t think that I\'m silly for liking it, I just happen to like the simple little things, and I love cats!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:33:24'),
(11620, 21, 'If the claws didn\'t retract, cats would be like Velcro', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:33:32'),
(11621, 21, 'It was so cold today that I saw a dog chasing a cat, and the dog was walking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:33:40'),
(11622, 21, 'As every cat owner knows, nobody owns a cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:08'),
(11623, 21, 'Dogs have owners, cats have staff.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:16'),
(11624, 21, 'Only very brave mouse makes nest in cat\'s ear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:23'),
(11625, 21, 'Cat people are different, to the extent that they generally are not conformists. How could they be, with a cat running their lives?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:31'),
(11626, 21, 'Actually, cats do this to protect you from gnomes who come and steal your breath while you sleep.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:38'),
(11627, 21, 'Cats possess so many of the same qualities as some poeple that it is often hard to tell the people and the cats apart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:45'),
(11628, 21, 'Cats are autocrats of naked self-interest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:34:53'),
(11629, 21, 'Cats aren\'t really friendly, they\'re just cozying up to the dominant life-form as a hedge against extinction.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:02'),
(11630, 21, 'A mathematician is a blind man in a dark room looking for a black cat which isn\'t there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:09'),
(11631, 21, 'I am the Cat who walks by himself, and all places are alike to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:17'),
(11632, 21, 'How you behave toward cats here below determines your status in Heaven.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:24'),
(11633, 21, 'If you try and take a cat apart to see how it works, the first thing you have on your hands is a nonworking cat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:31'),
(11634, 21, 'My cat is not insane, she\'s just a really good actress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:38'),
(11635, 21, 'When Rome burned, the emperor\'s cats still expected to be fed on time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:45'),
(11636, 21, 'When addressed, a Gentleman Cat does not move a muscle. He looks as if he hasn\'t heard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:52'),
(11637, 21, 'The cat, having sat upon a hot stove lid, will not sit upon a hot stove lid again. Nor upon a cold stove lid.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:35:59'),
(11638, 21, 'To assume a cat\'s asleep is a grave mistake. He can close his eyes and keep both his ears awake.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:06'),
(11639, 21, 'A kitten is chiefly remarkable for rushing about like mad at nothing whatever and generally stopping before it gets there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:14'),
(11640, 21, 'The cat has complete emotional honesty - an attribute not often found in humans.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:22'),
(11641, 21, 'If you want to write, keep cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:29'),
(11642, 21, 'Artists like cats; soldiers like dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:37'),
(11643, 21, 'Sleeping together is a euphemism for people, but tantamount to marriage with cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:36:44'),
(11644, 21, 'Cat: a soft indestructible automaton provided by nature to be kicked when things go wrong in the domestic circle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'Cat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 16:37:11'),
(11695, 21, 'No matter how hard you try to teach your cat general relativity, you\'re going to fail.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:02:29'),
(11696, 21, 'Know yourself. Don\'t accept your dog\'s admiration as conclusive evidence that you are wonderful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:02:39'),
(11697, 21, 'I happen to think that computers are the most important thing to happen to musicians since the invention of cat-gut which was a long time ago', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:02:48'),
(11698, 21, 'Cats are a tonic, they are a laugh, they are a cuddle, they are at least pretty just about all of the time and beautiful some of the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:02:56'),
(11699, 21, 'You know what I should do?\" Hoshino asked excited. \"Of course,\" the cat said. \"What\'d I tell you? Cats know everything. Not like dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:04'),
(11700, 21, 'I used to love dogs until I discovered cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:13'),
(11701, 21, 'Little girls are like old cats. If they don\'t like you nothing on Earth will make them pretend to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:21'),
(11702, 21, 'Dogs have their day but cats have 365.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:30'),
(11703, 21, 'Unlike cats dogs never scratch you when you wash them. They just become very sad and try to figure out what they did wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:42'),
(11704, 21, 'Teenagers are like cats - they have important business that doesn\'t involve mere humans.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAACat love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 17:03:50'),
