(12041, 19, 'Oh love will make a dog howl in rhyme.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:38:57'),
(12042, 19, 'I love dogs because they\'re so adaptable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:39:07'),
(12043, 19, 'My wife and I love to read. We\'re going to have to move out to make room for the books! And we have our dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:39:17'),
(12044, 19, 'I love a Hebrew National hot dog with an ice-cold Corona - no lime. If the phone rings, I won\'t answer until I\'m done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:39:28'),
(12045, 19, 'People always say that, like, you\'re a dog person or a cat person. I just love animals. I\'m not a dog person or a cat person.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:39:38'),
(12046, 19, 'Loving dogs is a question of anthropomorphism. We become attached to dogs because of the feelings we project on them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:39:49'),
(12047, 19, 'I love pets, especially dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:41:09'),
(12048, 19, 'I love my dog unconditionally, but never the man I\'m sleeping with.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:43:57'),
(12049, 19, 'I love it when dogs yawn. Especially when it\'s in the middle of another dog\'s speech.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:44:26'),
(12050, 19, 'I love my dog, but since the kids came along, the petting has gone out of our relationship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:44:35'),
(12051, 19, 'You know what I love best about baseball? The pine tar, the resin, the grass, the dirt - and that\'s just in the hot-dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:44:44'),
(12052, 19, 'I watch movies and hang with my family, go shopping, love to cuddle with my dog, Happy, & write songs with my guitar!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:44:54'),
(12053, 19, 'Doubt, if you will, the being who loves you, Woman or dog, but never doubt love itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:45:03'),
(12054, 19, 'I petted the dogs who didn\'t argue with me ever. All dogs love God. They\'re wiser than their masters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:45:12'),
(12055, 19, 'I\'m actually more of a cat guy than a dog person because I travel so much. I love cats.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:45:30'),
(12056, 19, 'Free, open love I have looked upon as dog\'s love. Secret love is, besides, cowardly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:45:41'),
(12057, 19, 'I\'ve always loved dogs. I grew up with them and I love working with them. They\'re really fun.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:45:50'),
(12058, 19, 'Dogs want only love but cats demand worship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:46:51'),
(12059, 19, 'I love my job but it takes a lot for me to leave my kids, leave my husband and leave my dogs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:47:07'),
(12060, 19, 'A dog pours a pitcher of love into the lonesome spots of your life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:48:04'),
(12061, 19, 'Loving and parenting a dog as a single parent can create all sorts of new and unusual problems, but also new sources of joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:48:29'),
(12062, 19, 'The world has been fair cruel if you\'ve never known the love of a dog!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:48:41'),
(12063, 19, 'Love never forgets; or if it does, it is an imperfect love, like the beautiful love of a dog, faithful and unreasoning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:48:52'),
(12064, 19, 'Love never forgets; or if it does, it is an imperfect love, like the beautiful love of a dog, faithful and unreasoning.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:48:52'),
(12065, 19, 'Be patient. Your future will come to you and lie down at your feet like a dog who knows and loves you no matter what you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:49:06'),
(12066, 19, 'Love is a Dog from Hell.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:50:04'),
(12067, 19, 'Love\'s a dog in a manger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:50:13'),
(12068, 19, 'I know I\'d rather have any amount of time with a dog I love and suffer the mourning than not have the time at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:50:27'),
(12069, 19, 'Actually, my dog I think is the only person who consistently loves me all the time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:50:49'),
(12070, 19, 'The love of a dog is a pure thing. He gives you a trust which is total. You must not betray it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:52:23'),
(12071, 19, 'In harmony with cosmic sea, true love needs no company. It can cure the soul, it can make it whole, if dogs run free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:52:47'),
(12072, 19, 'What I love doing is taking my dog for runs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:53:23'),
(12073, 19, 'I love dogs, but dogs, you have to be in the country with dogs. I cannot walk a dog on the street.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:53:59'),
(12074, 19, 'I am a dog that loves my fleas.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:54:09'),
(12075, 19, 'My songs are like a three-legged dog - you have to get to know them to have any love for them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:54:20'),
(12076, 19, 'I have three dogs, a cat, fish. I\'m a huge animal lover. They\'re amazing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:54:30'),
(12077, 19, 'I don\'t smoke, I try to eat right, and I love doing yoga and going for hikes with my dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:54:41'),
(12078, 19, 'I would love for the world to have a dog psychology center everywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:54:51'),
(12079, 19, 'Think about a dog’s ability to forgive. This to me is love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:55:02'),
(12080, 19, 'There\'s nothing that I love more than predawn. I\'m with the dogs, I make coffee, and there\'s no one up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:55:16'),
(12081, 19, 'If you treat your feelings with as much love as you treat your dog or your cat or your child you\'ll feel as if you were living in heaven.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:55:37'),
(12082, 19, 'We expressed love for this dog by ... knowing without showing that we cared for him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:55:52'),
(12083, 19, 'They give unconditional love and undying loyalty in return for regular meals and an occasional pat on the head.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:56:01'),
(12084, 19, 'Like many other much-loved humans, they believed that they owned their dogs, instead of realizing that their dogs owned them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:56:28'),
(12085, 19, 'Dogs love to go for rides. A dog will happily get into any vehicle going anywhere.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:56:49'),
(12086, 19, 'I am misanthropos, and hate mankind, For thy part, I do wish thou wert a dog, That I might love thee something.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:56:59'),
(12087, 19, 'It is scarcely possible to doubt that the love of man has become instinctive in the dog.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAADog love', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-08-30 18:57:10'),
(12088, 50, 'Be patient. Do the best with what you know. When you know more, adjust the trajectory.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:09'),
(12089, 50, 'Some of your greatest blessings come with patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:17'),
(12090, 50, 'The people who test your patience are a blessing.. Without them, you can\'t practice patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:33'),
(12091, 50, 'Patience is the companion of wisdom.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:41'),
(12092, 50, 'Patience, persistence and perspiration make an unbeatable combination for success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:49'),
(12093, 50, 'Patience is not simply the ability to wait - it\'s how we behave while we\'re waiting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:17:57'),
(12094, 50, 'Have patience. All things are difficult before they become easy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:13'),
(12095, 50, 'Patience and time do more than strength or passion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:22'),
(12096, 50, 'Above all, trust in the slow work of God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:30'),
(12097, 50, 'He who has infinite patience and infinite energy at his back, will alone succeed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:36'),
(12098, 50, 'Adopt the pace of nature: her secret is patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:44'),
(12099, 50, 'Patient waiting is often the highest way of doing God\'s will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:51'),
(12100, 50, 'The trees that are slow to grow bear the best fruit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:18:59'),
(12101, 50, 'Everything comes gradually and at its appointed hour.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:07'),
(12102, 50, 'Be content to progress in slow steps until you have legs to run and wings with which to fly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:14'),
(12103, 50, 'Patience is not passive; on the contrary, it is active; it is concentrated strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:22'),
(12104, 50, 'The principle part of faith is patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:29'),
(12105, 50, 'Patience is the ability to idle your motor when you feel like stripping your gears.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:38'),
(12106, 50, 'Endurance is patience concentrated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:46'),
(12107, 50, 'The two most powerful warriors are patience and time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:19:53'),
(12108, 50, 'If I have ever made any valuable discoveries, it has been due more to patient attention, than to any other talent', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:10'),
(12109, 50, 'To lose patience is to lose the battle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:18'),
(12110, 50, 'He that can have patience can have what he will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:25'),
(12111, 50, 'There is something good in all seeming failures. You are not to see that now. Time will reveal it. Be patient.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:33'),
(12112, 50, 'We have to slow the rhythm of rush in our lives so that the best of who are can emerge.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:40'),
(12113, 50, 'We could never learn to be brave and patient, if there were only joy in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:20:49'),
(12114, 50, 'If you would know strength and patience, welcome the company of trees.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:04'),
(12115, 50, 'All men commend patience, although few are willing to practice it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:12'),
(12116, 50, 'Purity, patience and perseverance overcome all obstacles. All great things must of necessity be slow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:20'),
(12117, 50, 'Knowing trees, I understand the meaning of patience. Knowing grass, I can appreciate persistence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:31'),
(12118, 50, 'Hope is patience with the lamp lit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:38'),
(12119, 50, 'It\'s not that I\'m so smart, it\'s just that I stay with problems longer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:48'),
(12120, 50, 'Only those who have the patience to do simple things perfectly will acquire the skill to do difficult things easily.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:21:56'),
(12121, 50, 'Have patience with all things, But, first of all with yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:22:05'),
(12122, 50, 'It is easier to find men who will volunteer to die, than to find those who are willing to endure pain with patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:22:16'),
(12123, 50, 'Patience wins the race.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:22:37'),
(12124, 50, 'Patience is not a virtue. It is an achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:22:44'),
(12125, 50, 'A wise man is superior to any insults which can be put upon him, and the best reply to unseemly behavior is patience and moderation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:22:53'),
(12126, 50, 'Seek patience and passion in equal amounts. Patience alone will not build the temple. Passion alone will destroy its walls.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:12'),
(12127, 50, 'Abused patience turns to fury.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:20'),
(12128, 50, 'A moment of patience in a moment of anger prevents a thousand moments of regret.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:28'),
(12129, 50, 'Good ideas are not adopted automatically. They must be driven into practice with courageous impatience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:40'),
(12130, 50, 'He who was living is now dead We who were living are now dying With a little patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:47'),
(12131, 50, 'Patience is also a form of action.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:23:56'),
(12132, 50, 'Never make your most important decisions when you are in your worst moods.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:04'),
(12133, 50, 'Education is the ability to listen to almost anything without losing your temper or your self-confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:14'),
(12134, 50, 'Never speak out of anger, Never act out of fear, Never choose from impatience, But wait... and peace will appear.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:23'),
(12135, 50, 'Let him that hath no power of patience retire within himself, though even there he will have to put up with himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:31'),
(12136, 50, 'Purity, patience and perseverance are the three essentials to success and above all love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:41'),
(12137, 50, 'It is hard! But what can not be removed, becomes lighter through patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:24:53'),
(12138, 50, 'I am patient with stupidity but not with those who are proud of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:04'),
(12139, 50, 'Patience is necessary, and one cannot reap immediately where one has sown.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:13'),
(12140, 50, 'Patience and fortitude conquer all things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:21'),
(12141, 50, 'The greatest art is to sit, and wait, and let it come.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:29'),
(12142, 50, 'Our patience will achieve more than our force.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:44'),
(12143, 50, 'Endurance is the crowning quality, And patience all the passion of great hearts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:25:52'),
(12144, 50, 'Who ever is out of patience is out of possession of their soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:00'),
(12145, 50, 'It is strange that the years teach us patience; that the shorter our time, the greater our capacity for waiting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:08'),
(12146, 50, 'Of all manifestations of power, restraint impresses men most.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:16'),
(12147, 50, 'Patience is the best remedy for every trouble.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:24'),
(12148, 50, 'Patience is a necessary ingredient of genius.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:35'),
(12149, 50, 'Genius is eternal patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:42'),
(12150, 50, 'The strongest of all warriors are these two — Time and Patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:26:50'),
(12151, 50, 'Don\'t try to rush things: for the cup to run over, it must first be filled.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:00'),
(12152, 50, 'It is in length of patience, endurance and forbearance that so much of what is good in mankind and womankind is shown.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:08'),
(12153, 50, 'The more patient we are, the more understanding we become.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:17'),
(12154, 50, 'I have declared that patience is never more than patient. I too have declared, that I who am not patient am patient.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:25'),
(12155, 50, 'Humility is attentive patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:33'),
(12156, 50, 'Genius is nothing but a greater aptitude for patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:50'),
(12157, 50, 'There art two cardinal sins from which all others spring: Impatience and Laziness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:27:58'),
(12158, 50, 'Patience can\'t be acquired overnight. It is just like building up a muscle. Every day you need to work on it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:07'),
(12159, 50, 'Don\'t cross the bridge til you come to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:15'),
(12160, 50, 'It is not necessary for all men to be great in action. The greatest and sublimest power is often simple patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:23'),
(12161, 50, 'To know how to wait. It is the great secret of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:32'),
(12162, 50, 'If patience is worth anything, it must endure to the end of time. And a living faith will last in the midst of the blackest storm.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:48'),
(12163, 50, 'Patience and Diligence, like faith, remove mountains.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:28:57'),
(12164, 50, 'He who says patience, says courage, endurance, strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:29:32'),
(12165, 50, 'Patience is so like fortitude that she seems either her sister or her daughter.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:29:37');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(12166, 50, 'Patience is the support of weakness; impatience the ruin of strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:29:54'),
(12167, 50, 'All things come to him who waits - provided he knows what he is waiting for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:03'),
(12168, 50, 'The test of good manners is to be patient with the bad ones.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:11'),
(12169, 50, 'Patience is the greatest of all virtues.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:18'),
(12170, 50, 'Patience is the art of hoping.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:25'),
(12171, 50, 'How poor are they that have not patience! What wound did ever heal but by degrees?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:40'),
(12172, 50, 'Nothing is so bitter that a calm mind cannot find comfort in it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:49'),
(12173, 50, 'The pursuit, even of the best things, ought to be calm and tranquil.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:30:56'),
(12174, 50, 'In any contest between power and patience, bet on patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:04'),
(12175, 50, 'Patience has its limits. Take it too far, and it\'s cowardice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:11'),
(12176, 50, 'Infinite patience, infinite purity, and infinite perseverance are the secret of success in a good cause.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:19'),
(12177, 50, 'All things come round to him who will but wait.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:34'),
(12178, 50, 'Possess your soul with patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:42'),
(12179, 50, 'The fates have given mankind a patient soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:31:49'),
(12180, 50, 'All men are made one for another: either then teach them better or bear with them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:32:10'),
(12181, 50, 'With love and patience, nothing is impossible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:33:05'),
(12182, 50, 'Patience is the best medicine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:33:38'),
(12183, 50, 'All great achievements require time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:33:56'),
(12184, 50, 'Endurance is nobler than strength, and patience than beauty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:34:09'),
(12185, 50, 'If I have done the public any service, it is due to my patient thought.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:34:37'),
(12186, 50, 'Heaven grant us patience with a man in love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:34:55'),
(12187, 50, 'Know full well that patience is the best means of succeeds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:35:03'),
(12188, 50, 'I am extraordinarily patient, provided I get my own way in the end.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:35:17'),
(12189, 50, 'No, I will be the pattern of all patience; I will say nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:35:33'),
(12190, 50, 'Patience is not just about waiting for something... it\'s about how you wait, or your attitude while waiting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:35:52'),
(12191, 50, 'I\'m a slow walker, but I never walk back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:36:00'),
(12192, 50, 'You must first have a lot of patience to learn to have patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:36:15'),
(12193, 50, 'Lack of pep is often mistaken for patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:36:25'),
(12194, 50, 'The bigger the dam of patience, the worse the flood when the dam breaks.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:36:34'),
(12195, 50, 'Patience is the most necessary quality for business, many a man would rather you heard his story than grant his request.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:37:12'),
(12196, 50, 'I learn it every day of my life, learn it with pain I am grateful for: patience is everything!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:37:21'),
(12197, 50, 'All things are difficult before they are easy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:37:30'),
(12198, 50, 'The two powers which in my opinion constitute a wise man are those of bearing and forbearing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:37:39'),
(12199, 50, 'Patience patience quotes is bitter, but its fruit is sweet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:37:55'),
(12200, 50, 'Perhaps then, some day far in the future, you will gradually, without even noticing it, live your way into the answer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:38:06'),
(12201, 50, 'Accustom yourself to that which you bear ill, and you will bear it well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:38:38'),
(12202, 50, 'Right actions in the future are the best apologies for bad actions in the past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:38:46'),
(12203, 50, 'Patience ornaments the woman and proves the man.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:38:59'),
(12204, 50, 'Patience is the analogue of God\'s serenity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:39:15'),
(12205, 50, 'Fortune knocks but once, but misfortune has much more patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:39:25'),
(12206, 50, 'All things come to him who mates.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:39:32'),
(12207, 50, 'Why is patience so important?\" \"Because it makes us pay attention.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:03'),
(12208, 50, 'Genius is only a greater aptitude for patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:12'),
(12209, 50, 'Patience is the panacea; but where does it grow, or who can swallow it?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:27'),
(12210, 50, 'To hear complaints with patience, even when complaints are vain, is one of the duties of friendship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:36'),
(12211, 50, 'Infinite Patience brings Immediate Results.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:46'),
(12212, 50, 'Patience is sorrow\'s salve.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:40:53'),
(12213, 50, 'Great patience is called for on the hard path that I have entered on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:41:04'),
(12214, 50, 'Waiting and hoping is a hard thing to do when you\'ve already been waiting and hoping for almost as long as you can bear it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:41:24'),
(12215, 50, 'I can imagine few things more trying to the patience than the long wasted days of waiting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:41:39'),
(12216, 50, 'Nothing else is necessary but these - love, sincerity, and patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:41:47'),
(12217, 50, 'Purity, perseverance, and energy- these three I want.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:41:55'),
(12218, 50, 'If you have infinite patience and perseverance, success is bound to come. No mistake in that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:42:04'),
(12219, 50, 'Patience is the mother of will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:42:12'),
(12220, 50, 'Be patient and understanding. Life is too short to be vengeful or malicious.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:42:21'),
(12221, 50, 'A healthy male adult bore consumes each year one and a half times his own weight in other people\'s patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:43:00'),
(12222, 50, 'Let the gentle bush dig its root deep and spread upward to split the boulder.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:43:07'),
(12223, 50, 'Everything comes in time to him who knows how to wait. There is nothing stronger than those two: patience and time, they will do it all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:04'),
(12224, 50, 'Wise to resolve, and patient to perform.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:12'),
(12225, 50, 'All\'s well in the end, if you\'ve only the patience to wait.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:20'),
(12226, 50, 'They also serve who only stand and wait.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:29'),
(12227, 50, 'All commend patience, but none can endure to suffer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:38'),
(12228, 50, 'He preacheth patience that never knew pain', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:45'),
(12229, 50, 'Everything comes if a man will only wait.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:44:52'),
(12230, 50, 'Better to complete a small task well, than to do much imperfectly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:02'),
(12231, 50, 'Only those who will risk going too far can possibly find out how far one can go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:10'),
(12232, 50, 'Though patience be a tired mare, yet she will plod.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:17'),
(12233, 50, 'Teach us, O Lord, the disciplines of patience, for to wait is often harder than to work.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:24'),
(12234, 50, 'Patience and shuffle the cards.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:32'),
(12235, 50, 'By time and toil we sever What strength and rage could never.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:40'),
(12236, 50, 'O gentle son, Upon the heat and flame of thy distemper, sprinkle cool patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:48'),
(12237, 50, 'It takes patience to appreciate domestic bliss; volatile spirits prefer unhappiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:45:57'),
(12238, 50, 'Arm the obdured breast with stubborn patience as with triple steel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:05'),
(12239, 50, 'It is by attempting to reach the top at a single leap that so much misery is caused in the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:14'),
(12240, 50, 'Patience is the art of caring slowly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:21'),
(12241, 50, 'Do not lose courage in considering your own imperfections.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:42'),
(12242, 50, 'You cannot swim for new horizons until you have courage to lose sight of the shore.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:50'),
(12243, 50, 'Things may come to those who wait, but only the things left by those who hustle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:46:57'),
(12244, 50, 'I learned patience, perseverance, and dedication. Now I really know myself, and I know my voice. It\'s a voice of pain and victory.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:05'),
(12245, 50, 'The cart before the horse is neither beautiful nor useful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:13'),
(12246, 50, 'Affliction is the wholesome soil of virtue, where patience, honor, sweet humility, and calm fortitude, take root and strongly flourish.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:26'),
(12247, 50, 'We shall sooner have the fowl by hatching the egg than by smashing it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:35'),
(12248, 50, 'Rule by patience, Laughing Water!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:42'),
(12249, 50, 'If we could have a little patience, we should escape much mortification; time takes away as much as it gives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:50'),
(12250, 50, 'But there are times when patience proves at fault.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:47:57'),
(12251, 50, 'Many a man thinks he is patient when, in reality, he is indifferent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:05'),
(12252, 50, 'We usually learn to wait only when we have no longer anything to wait for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:12'),
(12253, 50, 'That which in mean men we entitle patience is pale cold cowardice in noble breasts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:19'),
(12254, 50, 'Patience means self-suffering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:27'),
(12255, 50, 'Patience makes a woman beautiful in middle age.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:34'),
(12256, 50, 'Love conquers in the long run. It won\'t do to become impatient - wait, wait - patience is bound to give success. . . .', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:43'),
(12257, 50, 'My advice to someone to follow in my footsteps is to have patience. I\'ve been doing this for twelve years.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:52'),
(12258, 50, 'When you feel gloomy, think what has been done within the last year. How, rising from nothing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:48:59'),
(12259, 50, 'Deliberately seek opportunities for kindness, sympathy, and patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:49:22'),
(12260, 50, 'And sure enough, even waiting will end...if you can just wait long enough.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:49:31'),
(12261, 50, 'I believe there\'s too little patience and context to many of the investigations I read or see on television.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:49:38'),
(12262, 50, 'Who can be patient in extremes?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:49:44'),
(12263, 50, 'Is the patience of the American people that long suffering? Is there no outrage left in the country?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:49:53'),
(12264, 50, 'Patience, n. A minor form of dispair, disguised as a virtue.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:01'),
(12265, 50, 'Patience may be a virtue, but quitting is an art.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:17'),
(12266, 50, 'I worked with patience which means almost power.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:28'),
(12267, 50, 'A high hope for a low heaven: God grant us patience!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:36'),
(12268, 50, 'We have no patience with other people\'s vanity because it is offensive to our own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:46'),
(12269, 50, 'The worst speak something good; if all want sense, God takes a text, and preacheth patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:50:54'),
(12270, 50, 'For patience, sov\'reign o\'er transmuted ill.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:01'),
(12271, 50, 'Time can but make it easier to be wise / Though now it seems impossible, and so / All that you need is patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:26'),
(12272, 50, 'Openness, patience, receptivity, solitude is everything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:33'),
(12273, 50, 'Wait long enough and people will surprise and impress you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:41'),
(12274, 50, 'Sad Patience, too near neighbour to despair.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:48'),
(12275, 50, 'It\'s easy finding reasons why other folks should be patient.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:51:58'),
(12276, 50, 'Patience is the courage of virtue.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:05'),
(12277, 50, 'Your passion must be tempered with patience. Maybe long-suffering patience would be a better word.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:11'),
(12278, 50, 'Patience has tender feet.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:20'),
(12279, 50, 'Patient endurance / Attaineth to all things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:29'),
(12280, 50, 'He who rides the sea of the Nile must have sails woven of patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:39'),
(12281, 50, 'God, teach me to be patient, teach me to go slow', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:45'),
(12282, 50, 'Patience is the key of content.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:52:52'),
(12283, 50, 'Sometimes things aren\'t clear right away. That\'s where you need to be patient and persevere and see where things lead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:00'),
(12284, 50, 'Don\'t get impatient when it takes too long.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:07'),
(12285, 50, 'Patience is the mother of joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:26'),
(12286, 50, 'Learn to wait; invariably either things will change or your heart will.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:35'),
(12287, 50, 'Be patient. Relax and trust. Let go. Then, let go some more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:42'),
(12288, 50, 'Great towers take time to construct.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:49'),
(12289, 50, 'With patience everything comes in due season.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:53:57'),
(12290, 50, 'Patience is the virtue of an ass, who treads beneath his burden and complains not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:04'),
(12291, 50, 'Patience is the direct antithesis of anger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:12'),
(12292, 50, 'Let nothing disturb thee; Let nothing dismay thee; All things pass; God never changes. Patience attains All that it strives for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:21'),
(12293, 50, 'Keep your friendships in repair.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:28'),
(12294, 50, 'He surely is most in need of another\'s patience, who has none of his own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:41'),
(12295, 50, 'Strength comes from waiting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:49'),
(12296, 50, 'If you’re walking down the right path and you’re willing to keep walking, eventually you’ll make progress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:54:58'),
(12297, 50, 'We must be careful not to let our current appetites steal away any chance we might have for a future feast', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:55:15'),
(12298, 50, 'Avoiding the temptation to sin and being patient upon that, is greater than being patient whilst being afflicted with trials.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:55:23'),
(12299, 50, 'Waiting is still an occupation. It is having nothing to wait for that is terrible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:55:44'),
(12300, 50, 'When a friend is in trouble, don\'t annoy him by asking if there is anything you can do. Think up something appropriate and do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:55:55'),
(12301, 50, 'Friendship is the inexpressible comfort of feeling safe with a person, having neither to weigh thoughts nor measure words.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:56:03'),
(12302, 50, 'The disciples of a patient Saviour should be patient themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:56:10'),
(12303, 50, 'When a train goes through a tunnel and it gets dark, you don\'t throw away the ticket and jump off. You sit still and trust the engineer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:56:17'),
(12304, 50, 'Only a burning patience will lead to the attainment of a splendid happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:56:27'),
(12305, 50, 'Face your deficiencies and acknowledge them; but do not let them master you. Let them teach you patience, sweetness, insight.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:56:38'),
(12306, 50, 'Character never quits; and with patience and persistence; Dreams do come true!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:12'),
(12307, 50, 'No man can be patient who has not strong passions, for patience is passion tamed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:21'),
(12308, 50, 'I think patience is a skill and I wish I had it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:30'),
(12309, 50, 'Patience is nobler motion than any deed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:37'),
(12310, 50, 'In order to make friends you must first be friendly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:47'),
(12311, 50, 'Friendship is the only cement that will ever hold the world together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:57:57'),
(12312, 50, 'Friendship is the only cement that will ever hold the world together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:58:04'),
(12313, 50, 'A true friend is someone who is there for you when he\'d rather be anywhere else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:58:12'),
(12314, 50, 'Great men wait for the right moment to abandon caution. The rest of us abandon it when impatience becomes too much for us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:58:20'),
(12315, 50, 'What may not be altered is made lighter by patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:58:35'),
(12316, 50, 'Patience is an integral part of talent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:06'),
(12317, 50, 'You can tell the size of a man by the size of the thing that makes him mad.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:14'),
(12318, 50, 'The poison leaves bit by bit, not all at once. Be patient. You are healing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:25'),
(12319, 50, 'It is patience that reveals every grace to you, and it is through patience that the saints received all that was promised to them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:33'),
(12320, 50, 'Dear parents, have great patience, and forgive from the depths of your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:41'),
(12321, 50, 'A good Muslim is not one who is strictest in his judgment, but who is most patient in listening.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:48'),
(12322, 50, 'Be patient toward all that is unsolved in your heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 16:59:59'),
(12323, 50, 'Sufferance is the badge of all our tribe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:06'),
(12324, 50, 'Patience leads to power; but eagerness in greed leads to loss.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:15'),
(12325, 50, 'Hopelessness has surprised me with patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:23'),
(12326, 50, 'Patience is like ice cold water running through your veins, but our love will be immense', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:39'),
(12327, 50, 'Patience is like ice cold water running through your veins, but our love will be immense', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:50'),
(12328, 50, 'Patience, the beggar\'s virtue, shall find no harbor here.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:00:59'),
(12329, 50, 'Hold on; hold fast; hold out. Patience is genius.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:07'),
(12330, 50, 'I work with patience, which is almost power.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:18'),
(12331, 50, 'My three Ps: passion, patience, perseverance. You have to do this if you\'ve got to be a filmmaker.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:26'),
(12332, 50, 'All things pass... Patience attains all it strives for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:35'),
(12333, 50, 'Talent is a long patience, and originality an effort of will and intense observation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:43'),
(12334, 50, 'Patience means restraining one\'s inclinations.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:01:55'),
(12335, 50, 'Everything comes to him who hustles while he waits.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:02:33'),
(12336, 50, 'The world is full of magical things patiently waiting for our wits to grow sharper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:02:40'),
(12337, 50, 'Like Patience gazing on kings\' graves, and smiling Extremity out of act.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:02:48'),
(12338, 50, 'If I could have one prayer answered, I would pray for patience. I move so fast sometimes. I try to slow down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:02:56'),
(12339, 50, 'I have just three things to teach: simplicity, patience, compassion. These three are your greatest treasures.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:03:13'),
(12340, 50, 'Temperamentally I\'m not a natural producer, because I don\'t have the patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:03:33'),
(12341, 50, 'Dispose thyself to patience rather than to comfort, and to the bearing of the cross rather than to gladness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:04:10'),
(12342, 50, 'Even a snail will eventually reach its destination.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:04:19'),
(12343, 50, 'Patience serves as a protection against wrongs as clothes do against cold.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:04:28'),
(12344, 50, 'Constant repetition of tongue-twisters was like lifting weights for me, but patience and persistence have paid off.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:05:02'),
(12345, 50, 'The real secret of patience is to find something to do in the meantime.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:05:38'),
(12346, 50, 'The real secret of patience is to find something to do in the meantime.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:05:52'),
(12347, 50, 'Waiting does not exist in the experience of those who recognize the presence of love wherever they are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:06:01'),
(12348, 50, 'Whether it\'s marriage of business, patience is the first rule of success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:06:09'),
(12349, 50, 'Never a tear bedims the eye that time and patience will not dry.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:06:29'),
(12350, 50, 'All things come to him who waits - even justice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:07:25'),
(12351, 50, 'If you pray about it don\'t worry about it. If you\'re going to worry about it don\'t pray about it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:07:50'),
(12352, 50, 'Faith is taking the first step even when you don\'t see the whole staircase.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:08:01'),
(12353, 50, 'Boredom is the feeling that everything is a waste of time; serenity, that nothing is.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:08:12'),
(12354, 50, 'Never cut a tree down in the wintertime. Never make a negative decision in the low time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:08:23'),
(12355, 50, 'Good things come to those who hustle', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:08:32'),
(12356, 50, 'Patience is God\'s nature.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:08:44'),
(12357, 50, 'You can learn many things from children. How much patience you have, for instance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:09:02'),
(12358, 50, 'Everything is out there if you know how to find it, and have the patience. I don\'t and haven\'t, but that\'s my problem', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:09:25'),
(12359, 50, 'I have all the patience in the world about Sirens. For me it\'s not a Grateful Dead project, it\'s a Me project.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:09:40'),
(12360, 50, 'You must grow in patience when you meet with great wrongs, and they will then be powerless to vex your mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:09:54'),
(12362, 50, 'So it\'s been a slow process and it\'s taken some patience. That\'s why patients are called patients I think - patience is required.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:10:25'),
(12363, 50, 'Be worthy love, and love will come.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:10:43'),
(12364, 50, 'The balance you have between drive and patience may be your master key to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:10:51'),
(12365, 50, 'That\'s why I never became a director. I never had patience with people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:11:01'),
(12366, 50, 'Listen. Pay attention. Treasure every moment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:11:15'),
(12367, 50, 'As any gardener will tell you, the cycles of nature require patience...Even a fast-growing vegetable like a radish requires time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:11:33'),
(12368, 50, 'I\'ve done an awful lot of stuff that\'s a monument to public patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:11:45'),
(12369, 50, 'A man without patience is a lamp without oil.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:12:03'),
(12370, 50, 'She will never submit to any thing requiring industry and patience, and a subjection of the fancy to the understanding.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:12:59'),
(12371, 50, 'Patience is the art of concealing your impatience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:14:06'),
(12372, 50, 'Patience attains All that it strives for. He who has God Finds he lacks nothing: God alone suffices.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:14:15'),
(12373, 50, 'The strong manly ones in life are those who understand the meaning of the word patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:14:23'),
(12374, 50, 'Bear patiently with a rival.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:15:17'),
(12375, 50, 'A mule will labor ten years willingly and patiently for you, for the privilege of kicking you once.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:15:30'),
(12376, 50, 'I haven\'t been given many things, but I\'ve been given ample, limitless patience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:15:42'),
(12377, 50, 'All things come to those who wait.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:15:51'),
(12378, 50, 'There is no well-doing, no Godlike doing, that is not patient doing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:16:30'),
(12379, 50, 'I\'ve learned the importance of loving what you do. I have also learned more patience due to the nature of the music business.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:16:39'),
(12380, 50, 'Any methodology for developing patience requires a multi-tiered approach.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:17:01'),
(12381, 50, 'Sometimes you just have to be patient and brave and strong. If you don\'t know how, just make it up as you go along.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:17:21'),
(12382, 50, 'Patience is the key to content.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:17:28'),
(12383, 50, 'Patience is supported & nurtured by a quality of forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:17:37'),
(12384, 50, 'We must accept the reality that the causes of impatience travel a two-way street.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:17:49'),
(12385, 50, 'Slow down. Calm down. Don\'t worry. Don\'t hurry. Trust the process.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:18:22'),
(12386, 50, 'Good things come to those who initiate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:18:32'),
(12387, 50, 'Patience is moral elasticity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAPatience', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-04 17:18:44'),
(12389, 51, 'We cannot become what we need by remaining what we are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:13:41'),
(12390, 51, 'Don\'t try to rush progress. Remember -- a step forward, no matter how small, is a step in the right direction. Keep believing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:13:49'),
(12391, 51, 'Don\'t let yesterday use up too much of today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:13:58'),
(12392, 51, 'Nothing can drag you down if you\'re not holding on to it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:14:06'),
(12393, 51, 'In order to move on, you must understand why you felt what you did and why you no longer need to feel it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:14:13'),
(12394, 51, 'Ups and downs in life are very important to keep us going, because a straight line even in an ECG means we are not alive', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:14:20'),
(12395, 51, 'You may have a fresh start any moment you choose, for this thing that we call \'failure\' is not the falling down, but the staying down.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:14:28'),
(12396, 51, 'You are responsible for your life. You can\'t keep blaming somebody else for your dysfunction. Life is really about moving on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:03'),
(12397, 51, 'Courage isn\'t having the strength to go on - it is going on when you don\'t have strength.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:10'),
(12398, 51, 'On your journey to your dream, be ready to face oasis and deserts. In both cases, don\'t stop', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:20'),
(12399, 51, 'You don\'t drown by falling in the water; you drown by staying there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:27'),
(12400, 51, 'When you lose what you love remember to stay strong. Look out the window and remember life goes on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:38'),
(12401, 51, 'Sometimes, carrying on, just carrying on, is the superhuman achievement.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:48'),
(12402, 51, 'Life is like riding a bicycle. To keep your balance, you must keep moving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:15:56'),
(12403, 51, 'Many of us crucify ourselves between two thieves - regret for the past and fear of the future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:16:04'),
(12404, 51, 'As you move toward a dream, the dream moves toward you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:16:13'),
(12405, 51, 'The only way to define your limits is by going beyond them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:17:00'),
(12406, 51, 'You can\'t keep the birds of sadness from flying over your head, but you can keep them from nesting in your hair.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:17:21'),
(12407, 51, 'Never mind what others do; do better than yourself, beat your own record from day to day, and you are a success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:17:39'),
(12408, 51, 'When you hear that something can’t be done, ignore that advice and push forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:17:48'),
(12409, 51, 'Life can only be understood backwards; but it must be lived forwards.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:17:57'),
(12410, 51, 'Don\'t watch the clock; do what it does. Keep going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:07'),
(12411, 51, 'We are not a failure just because we fail at something. Nobody is a failure unless they quit trying!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:15'),
(12412, 51, 'Often we look so long at the closed door that we do not see the one that has been opened for us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:23'),
(12413, 51, 'I demolish my bridges behind me - then there is no choice but forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:31'),
(12414, 51, 'It\'s not what happens to you, but how you react to it that matters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:39'),
(12415, 51, 'Today will never happen again. Don\'t waste it with a false start or no start at all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:46'),
(12416, 51, 'When life takes the wind out of your sails, it is to test you at the oars.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:18:54'),
(12417, 51, 'It\'s not whether you get knocked down, it\'s whether you get up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:01'),
(12418, 51, 'Part of growing up is just taking what you learn from that and moving on and not taking it to heart.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:09'),
(12419, 51, 'Letting go has never been easy, but holding on can be as difficult. Yet strength is measured not by holding on, but by letting go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:25'),
(12420, 51, 'Regret of neglected opportunity is the worst hell that a living soul can inhabit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:35'),
(12421, 51, 'Never confuse a single defeat with a final defeat.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:42'),
(12422, 51, 'You gotta know when to hold \'em, know when to fold \'em, know when to walk away, know when to run.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:50'),
(12423, 51, 'All the art of living lies in a fine mingling of letting go and holding on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:19:57'),
(12424, 51, 'Never give up. When your heart becomes tired, just walk with your legs - but move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:04'),
(12425, 51, 'Success is a pile of failure that you are standing on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:16'),
(12426, 51, 'Don\'t cry because it\'s over. Smile because it happened.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:23'),
(12427, 51, 'All experience is an arch wherethrough gleams that untravelled world whose margin fades for ever and for ever when I move.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:31'),
(12428, 51, 'Self-pity is our worst enemy and if we yield to it, we can never do anything wise in this world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:40'),
(12429, 51, 'Anybody can quit. Only a real champion and a person of character and strength can keep going and refuse to give up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:48'),
(12430, 51, 'Today is the first day of the rest of your life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:20:55'),
(12431, 51, 'It took me a long time to learn that mistakes aren\'t good or bad, they\'re just mistakes, and you clean them up and go on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:03'),
(12432, 51, 'Every day is a new day, and you\'ll never be able to find happiness if you don\'t move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:13'),
(12433, 51, 'People can be more forgiving than you can imagine. But you have to forgive yourself. Let go of what\'s bitter and move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:25'),
(12434, 51, 'If you\'re going through hell, keep going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:32'),
(12435, 51, ' Forgive yourself for your faults and your mistakes and move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:49'),
(12436, 51, 'Just because you miss someone doesn\'t mean you need them back in your life. Missing is just a part of moving on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:21:56'),
(12437, 51, 'I\'m at the point where going forward is easier than going back.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:03'),
(12438, 51, 'One must always maintain one\'s connection to the past and yet ceaselessly pull away from it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:18'),
(12439, 51, 'Never give up, for that is just the place and time that the tide will turn.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:27'),
(12440, 51, 'Every setback might be the very thing that makes you carry on and fight all the harder and become much better.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:34'),
(12441, 51, 'The only conquests that are permanent and leave no regrets are our conquests over ourselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:41'),
(12442, 51, 'You quit, you lose. You keep going, you may still lose. But, your ambition will never die.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:49'),
(12443, 51, 'Success ... seems to be connected with action. Successful men keep moving. They make mistakes, but they don\'t quit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:22:57'),
(12444, 51, 'Vitality shows in not only the ability to persist but the ability to start over.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:24:40');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(12445, 51, 'Hanging onto resentment is letting someone you despise live rent-free in your head.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:26:21'),
(12446, 51, 'If everyone is moving forward together, then success takes care of itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:26:32'),
(12447, 51, 'And there are people that will stand in your corner and convince you to stand up for another round no matter what.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:26:42'),
(12448, 51, 'You can\'t look back - you just have to put the past behind you, and find something better in your future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:26:51'),
(12449, 51, 'People have a hard time letting go of their suffering. Out of a fear of the unknown, they prefer suffering that is familiar.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:01'),
(12450, 51, 'If there is no struggle, there is no progress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:10'),
(12451, 51, 'Often the thought of pain is actually worse that the pain itself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:18'),
(12452, 51, 'I don\'t want to lose you, but I don\'t want to use you just to have someone by my side.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:25'),
(12453, 51, 'Even if you fall on your face, you\'re still moving forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:32'),
(12454, 51, 'Man maintains his balance, poise, and sense of security only as he is moving forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:27:50'),
(12455, 51, 'When I let go of what I am, I become what I might be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:28:08'),
(12456, 51, 'Loving someone is setting them free, letting them go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:28:16'),
(12457, 51, 'You can only lose what you cling to.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:28:27'),
(12458, 51, 'The secret of our success is that we never, never give up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:28:52'),
(12459, 51, 'Notice that the stiffest tree is most easily cracked, while the bamboo or willow survives by bending with the wind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:29:48'),
(12460, 51, 'When you hit a wall – of your own imagined limitations – just kick it in.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:29:57'),
(12461, 51, 'The price of inaction is far greater than the cost of making a mistake.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:07'),
(12462, 51, 'Laughter gives us distance. It allows us to step back from an event, deal with it and then move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:14'),
(12463, 51, 'Those who don\'t know how to weep with their whole heart, don\'t know how to laugh either.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:21'),
(12464, 51, 'Moving on, is a simple thing, what it leaves behind is hard.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:30'),
(12465, 51, 'Forget the past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:37'),
(12466, 51, 'Worry never robs tomorrow of its sorrow, it only saps today of its joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:47'),
(12467, 51, 'We are set in our ways, bound by our perspectives and stuck in our thinking.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:30:59'),
(12468, 51, 'I won\'t let the sun go down on me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:06'),
(12469, 51, 'It is only through labor and painful effort, by grim energy and resolute courage, that we move on to better things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:16'),
(12470, 51, 'I chose and my world was shaken. So what? The choice may have been mistaken; the choosing was not. You have to move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:33'),
(12471, 51, 'What surrounds us we endure better for giving it a name - and moving on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:42'),
(12472, 51, 'Goals give you more than a reason to get up in the morning; they are an incentive to keep you going all day.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:50'),
(12473, 51, 'You can fall, but you can rise also.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:31:57'),
(12474, 51, 'The secret of joy is the mastery of pain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:04'),
(12475, 51, 'I postpone death by living, by suffering, by error, by risking, by giving, by losing.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:12'),
(12476, 51, 'Don\'t cry over spilled milk', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:20'),
(12477, 51, 'He\'s a million rubber bands in his resilience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:28'),
(12478, 51, '80% of people\'s problems are about how they feel about themselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:35'),
(12479, 51, 'The final wisdom of life requires not the annulment of incongruity but the achievement of serenity within and above it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:43'),
(12480, 51, 'Faith doesn\'t mean that you don\'t have doubts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:32:53'),
(12481, 51, 'Curiosity keeps leading us down new paths.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:01'),
(12482, 51, 'I realize I waited too long but please don\'t move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:13'),
(12483, 51, 'Out of difficulties grow miracles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:20'),
(12484, 51, 'Beginners are many; finishers are few.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:27'),
(12485, 51, 'Motivation is what gets you started. Habit is what keeps you going.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:34'),
(12486, 51, 'My heart is broke, but I have some glue, help me inhale and mend it with you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:41'),
(12487, 51, 'Letting go. Everyone talks about it like it\'s the easiest thing. Unfurl your fingers one by one until your hand is open.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:33:55'),
(12488, 51, 'Nothing is impossible', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:17'),
(12489, 51, 'Every setback means you\'re one step closer to seeing the dream come to pass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:25'),
(12490, 51, 'I haven\'t slept in days. And me and my latest girl agreed to go our separate ways.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:33'),
(12491, 51, 'Successful people don\'t have fewer problems. They have determined that nothing will stop them from going forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:41'),
(12492, 51, 'I can tell that you been crying all night, drinking all summer, praying for your happiness, hope that you recover', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:48'),
(12493, 51, 'Problems are guidelines, not stop signs!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:34:56'),
(12494, 51, 'Winners never quit and quitters never win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:07'),
(12495, 51, 'We go forward with our heads held high, but look back and remember where we come from.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:21'),
(12496, 51, 'If you fall behind, run faster. Never give up, never surrender, and rise up against the odds.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:30'),
(12497, 51, 'Patience, persistence and perspiration make an unbeatable combination for success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:38'),
(12498, 51, 'I keep going because if you stop, you stop. Why retire? Inspire.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:47'),
(12499, 51, 'Be patient. Relax and trust. Let go. Then, let go some more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:35:54'),
(12500, 51, 'Life is movement. Once you stop moving, you\'re dead. Choose life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:12'),
(12501, 51, 'If you fell down yesterday, stand up today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:22'),
(12502, 51, 'Year\'s end is neither an end nor a beginning but a going on, with all the wisdom that experience can instill in us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:30'),
(12503, 51, 'Have a dream, make a plan, go for it. You\'ll get there, I promise.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:40'),
(12504, 51, 'Mistakes and errors are the discipline through which we advance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:48'),
(12505, 51, 'We are all failures - at least the best of us are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:36:57'),
(12506, 51, 'In the theater, it\'s about taking time in a musical segment, a pause in a musical way and then moving on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:37:05'),
(12507, 51, 'Change is the law of life. And those who look only to the past or present are certain to miss the future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:37:13'),
(12508, 51, 'Happiness is not something ready made. It comes from your own actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:37:21'),
(12509, 51, 'With the new day comes new strength and new thoughts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:37:29'),
(12511, 51, 'There is no greater agony than bearing an untold story inside you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:38:10'),
(12512, 51, 'When your own mind tells you to quit, you must ignore your negative thoughts and press on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:38:18'),
(12513, 51, 'Be willing to move forward and find out what happens next.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:38:26'),
(12514, 51, 'Once I slow down because I think I have reached my peak, then my skills will go nowhere but down', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:38:48'),
(12515, 51, 'I give myself the green light to move forward, and to joyously embrace the new.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:39:01'),
(12516, 51, 'In a time of rapid change, standing still is the most dangerous course of action.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:39:10'),
(12517, 51, 'When you feel stuck and can\'t seem to move ahead, always remember that you don\'t have to get it right, you just have to get it going!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:39:23'),
(12518, 51, 'There is no point at which you can say, \"Well, I\'m successful now. I might as well take a nap.\"', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:39:33'),
(12519, 51, 'Anytime you suffer a setback or disappointment, put your head down and plow ahead.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:39:58'),
(12520, 51, 'Living is a constant process of deciding what we are going to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:40:20'),
(12521, 51, 'I tell people this: It\'s hard to write about walking in the park, but it\'s easy to write about a breakup.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:40:37'),
(12522, 51, 'The future depends entirely on what each of us does every day; a movement is only people moving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:40:44'),
(12523, 51, 'I never see what has been done; I only see what remains to be done.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:40:53'),
(12524, 51, 'Not knowing a thing is not ignorance. Feigning knowledge you don\'t have can be--Sholto', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:14'),
(12525, 51, 'I was young and felt like it was opportunity \'cause they were moving units back then on the underground scene.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:23'),
(12526, 51, 'Nothing makes one feel so strong as a call for help.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:30'),
(12527, 51, 'Our state\'s strategy on methamphetamine, and any other issue, is going to be a moving target.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:38'),
(12528, 51, 'I am pretty embroiled in moving on and moving forward with music.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:46'),
(12529, 51, 'Our national security is at risk when we rely on foreign oil to keep our economy moving forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:41:53'),
(12530, 51, 'Any time I\'m in a moving thing, like an airplane, I\'m usually asleep before we even get on our way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:42:00'),
(12532, 51, 'I can see that if this was an album done 10 or 15 years ago we could see we were moving on to some place else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:42:30'),
(12533, 51, 'I can see that if this was an album done 10 or 15 years ago we could see we were moving on to some place else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:42:50'),
(12534, 51, 'Never regret. If it\'s good, it\'s wonderful. If it\'s bad, it\'s experience.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:45:31'),
(12535, 51, 'Life moves forward. The old leaves wither, die and fall away, and the new growth extends forward into the light.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:45:53'),
(12536, 51, 'Go as far as you can see; when you get there you\'ll be able to see farther.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:03'),
(12537, 51, 'Every failure is a step to success.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:11'),
(12538, 51, 'If you do not create your destiny, you will have your fate inflicted upon you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:21'),
(12539, 51, 'Patience is key for getting over a breakup. That, and trailing off your interaction after the breakup.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:32'),
(12540, 51, 'In the process of letting go you will lose many things from the past, but you will find yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:40'),
(12541, 51, 'I just wanted to tell you that I understand if you go. It’s okay if you have to leave us. It’s okay if you want to stop fighting.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:47'),
(12542, 51, 'The only way to make sense out of change is to plunge into it, move with it, and join the dance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:46:56'),
(12543, 51, 'See every difficulty as a challenge, a stepping stone, and never be defeated by anything or anyone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:47:06'),
(12544, 51, 'What great thing would you attempt if you knew you could not fail?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:47:15'),
(12545, 51, 'It is our attitude at the beginning of a difficult task which, more than anything else, will affect its successful outcome.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:47:24'),
(12546, 51, 'I break up very well. I am a good breaker-upper.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:47:34'),
(12547, 51, 'Forgiveness means letting go of the past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:47:43'),
(12548, 51, 'Breathe. Let go. And remind yourself that this very moment is the only one you know you have for sure.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:04'),
(12549, 51, 'If you don\'t hurry up and let life know what you want, life will damned soon show you what you\'ll get.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:12'),
(12550, 51, 'You alone are enough. You have nothing to prove to anybody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:21'),
(12551, 51, 'If you love somebody, let them go, for if they return, they were always yours. And if they don\'t, they never were.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:30'),
(12552, 51, 'Nothing will work unless you do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:38'),
(12553, 51, 'We must let go of the life we have planned, so as to accept the one that is waiting for us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:48:48'),
(12554, 51, 'The act of laughing releases some nice chemical into your brain, you feel good and it\'s free.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:07'),
(12555, 51, 'Our whole economy is based on planned obsolescence, and anyone who can read without moving his lips should know it by now.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:14'),
(12556, 51, 'Well I certainly have learned and I hope I\'m moving on and certainly two years of prison was a terrible punishment.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:23'),
(12557, 51, 'There is one thing I would break up over, and that is if she caught me with another woman. I won\'t stand for that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:35'),
(12558, 51, 'Cry me a river, build a bridge, and get over it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:46'),
(12559, 51, 'Learn your lessons quickly and move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:49:53'),
(12560, 51, 'When lifes seems hopeless, rearrange things for a dose of dopeness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:51:36'),
(12561, 51, 'The weak can never forgive. Forgiveness is the attribute of the strong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:51:50'),
(12562, 51, 'It\'s time to move on to the next step in the psychedelic revolution. We\'ve reached a certain point, but we\'re not moving any more.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:06'),
(12563, 51, 'Cowards die many times before their actual deaths.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:13'),
(12564, 51, 'The world hates change, yet it is the only thing that has brought progress.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:21'),
(12565, 51, 'Some people will dream big dreams while others will wake up and do them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:31'),
(12566, 51, 'A bend in the road is not the end of the road…Unless you fail to make the turn.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:39'),
(12567, 51, 'Sooner or later we\'ve all got to let go of our past.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:46'),
(12568, 51, 'We delight in the beauty of the butterfly, but rarely admit the changes it has gone through to achieve that beauty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:52:55'),
(12569, 51, 'Things do not change; we change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:04'),
(12570, 51, 'Always forgive your enemies - nothing annoys them so much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:12'),
(12571, 51, 'She took a step and didn\'t want to take any more, but she did.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:19'),
(12572, 51, 'Change has to come for life to struggle forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:36'),
(12573, 51, 'Not to engage in this pursuit of ideas is to live like ants instead of like men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:44'),
(12574, 51, 'Let go of your attachment to being right, and suddenly your mind is more open.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:51'),
(12575, 51, 'Insanity: doing the same thing over and over again and expecting different results.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:53:58'),
(12576, 51, 'Any change, even a change for the better, is always accompanied by drawbacks and discomforts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:54:07'),
(12577, 51, 'It is not enough just to wish well; we must also do well.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:54:44'),
(12578, 51, 'Open your arms to change but don\'t let go of your values.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:54:55'),
(12579, 51, 'Life moves on and so should we', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:02'),
(12580, 51, 'It is foolish to tear one\'s hair in grief, as though sorrow would be made less by baldness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:09'),
(12581, 51, 'Because things are the way they are, things will not stay the way they are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:17'),
(12582, 51, 'Never make someone a priority when all you are to them is an option.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:25'),
(12583, 51, 'Bitter experience has taught us how fundamental our values are and how great the mission they represent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:34'),
(12584, 51, 'You\'ve got to make a conscious choice every day to shed the old - whatever \"the old\" means for you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:43'),
(12585, 51, 'Intelligence is not to make no mistakes, but quickly to see how to make them good', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:55:50'),
(12586, 51, 'I began writing a book on love because I felt that the United States is moving away from love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:04'),
(12587, 51, 'My great hope is to laugh as much as I cry; to get my work done and try to love somebody and have the courage to accept the love in return.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:13'),
(12588, 51, 'I\'ve always believed that if you don\'t stay moving, they will throw dirt on you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:20'),
(12589, 51, 'It\'s the possibility that keeps me going, not the guarantee.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:28'),
(12590, 51, 'It is not death that a man should fear, but he should fear never beginning to live.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:36'),
(12591, 51, 'All experience is an arch, to build upon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:43'),
(12592, 51, 'Surround yourself with only people who are going to lift you higher.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:56:53'),
(12593, 51, 'Have enough courage to trust love one more time and always one more time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:57:29'),
(12594, 51, 'I will continue my path, but I will keep a memory always.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:57:38'),
(12595, 51, 'It was strange, really. A couple months ago, I had thought I couldn’t live without him. Apparently I could.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:57:46'),
(12596, 51, 'Nothing can dim the light which shines from within.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:57:53'),
(12597, 51, 'Never fall out of love with life', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:03'),
(12598, 51, 'I think that you never fall out of love with somebody, you just let go and move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:10'),
(12599, 51, 'Ignore reality, there\'s nothing you can do about it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:18'),
(12600, 51, 'Nothing in the universe can stop you from letting go and starting over.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:26'),
(12601, 51, 'There is nothing you can do about the past except keep it there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:36'),
(12602, 51, 'When you are through changing, you are through.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:43'),
(12603, 51, 'Success is liking yourself, liking what you do, and liking how you do it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:58:53'),
(12604, 51, 'If you love someone, set them free. If they come back they\'re yours; if they don\'t they never were.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:00'),
(12605, 51, 'When someone shows you who they are, believe them the first time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:08'),
(12606, 51, 'Ask for what you want and be prepared to get it!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:15'),
(12607, 51, 'Man never made any material as resilient as the human spirit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:38'),
(12608, 51, 'If you don\'t like something, change it. If you can\'t change it, change your attitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:45'),
(12609, 51, 'I can be changed by what happens to me. But I refuse to be reduced by it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 16:59:54'),
(12610, 51, 'Life shrinks or expands in proportion to one\'s courage.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:00:44'),
(12611, 51, 'You can love someone so much...But you can never love people as much as you can miss them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:00:52'),
(12612, 51, 'There\'s always something to suggest that you\'ll never be who you wanted to be. Your choice is to take it or keep on moving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:01:00'),
(12613, 51, 'Getting over a painful experience is much like crossing monkey bars. You have to let go at some point in order to move forward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:01:16'),
(12614, 51, 'Get mad, then get over it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:01:33'),
(12615, 51, 'Be miserable. Or motivate yourself. Whatever has to be done, it\'s always your choice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:01:47'),
(12616, 51, 'Some of us think holding on makes us strong; but sometimes it is letting go.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:01:58'),
(12617, 51, ' Forgive yourself and move on, mistakes are irreversible but the future can be changed to the best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:05:45'),
(12618, 51, ' The best revenge is just moving on and getting over it. Don\'t give someone the satisfaction of watching you suffer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:05:57'),
(12619, 51, ' Maturity is learning to walk away from situations that threatens your peace of mind, self respect, values, moral or self worth. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:06:11'),
(12620, 51, ' Don\'t throw money at the problem - walk away from it. You\'ll be wealthier from it down the road.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:06:27'),
(12621, 51, ' Sometimes its better to leave your ex in the past than to bring the same mistake to your future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:06:41'),
(12622, 51, ' It is important that we forgive ourselves for making mistakes. We need to learn from our errors and move on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:07:01'),
(12623, 51, ' Move on! Move on! Don\'t let anything Stop you. Go on and make your Dreams come true.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:07:21'),
(12624, 51, 'After a breakup realize that you had a life BEFORE them and you can still have a life AFTER them you just have to find yourself again.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:07:55'),
(12625, 51, ' Never cry for someone who hurts you, Just smile and say thanks for giving me a chance to find someone better than you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:08:10'),
(12626, 51, ' I am learning to love the sound of my feet walking away from things not meant for me. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:08:25'),
(12627, 51, ' One of the best feelings is finally losing your attachment to somebody who\'s always hurt you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:08:39'),
(12628, 51, 'Walk away from things that aren\'t encouraging you to excel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:08:53'),
(12629, 51, ' Hope allows you to live on long after battles have been fought and long after the dust has settled and the sun has set.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:09:05'),
(12630, 51, ' It\'s hard sometimes to just walk away, but if and when you go, it is one of the most rewarding things you will ever do. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:09:43'),
(12631, 51, ' The more time you spend contemplating what you should have done, you lose valuable time planning what you can and will do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:09:58'),
(12632, 51, ' Farewell is not the end of life. But the first step to how strongly we survive without someone. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:10:25'),
(12633, 51, 'One of the best feelings in the world is when you stop caring about things that used to bother you. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:10:37'),
(12634, 51, ' Rest is essential if you want to move on and attain objectives. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:10:53'),
(12635, 51, ' Leave your bad past memories behind, or it can destroy your future. Live life for tomorrow, not for yesterday.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:11:08'),
(12636, 51, ' Let Go of the past and forgive yourself! It was teaching moment to become a better person. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:11:20'),
(12637, 51, ' Learn to surrender, because sometimes, when there is no way, surrender is the way. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:11:33'),
(12638, 51, ' Wisdom teaches you to walk away than fight for what isn\'t worth your fight ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:11:47'),
(12639, 51, ' Success is your journey through life everyday with lessons learned, mistakes altered and moving on. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:12:01'),
(12640, 51, ' Learn to move on from the people and memories that only cause you pain and suffering.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:12:14'),
(12641, 51, ' Learn to walk away from those who cause harm to you . ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:12:27'),
(12642, 51, ' I am done with the past, the future has plenty of room for change. Be the change you wish to see. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:12:39'),
(12643, 51, ' Life is like a moving car. It\'s okay to look behind you sometimes but keep looking straight because life goes on ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:13:18'),
(12644, 51, ' No matter what you do, never go back to what broke you. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:13:33'),
(12645, 51, ' Letting go is the toughest thing to do in life but sometimes it can turn out to be the best thing you ever done ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:13:46'),
(12646, 51, ' Divorce the past to marry the present and be blessed with a lovely child of future.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:13:59'),
(12647, 51, ' The truth is, unless you let go, unless you forgive yourself, unless you forgive the situation is over, you cannot move forward. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:14:16'),
(12648, 51, ' I separate myself from people who do not want to see me for who I am, so that I can make enough space for those who do. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:14:29'),
(12649, 51, ' Your best teacher will always be our last mistake. Learn from it, and move on with knowledge. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:14:45'),
(12650, 51, ' Sometimes it\'s very hard to move on, but once you move on, you\'ll realize it was the best decision you\'ve ever made.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:14:59'),
(12651, 51, ' You cant move forward until you learn to accept it ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:15:13'),
(12652, 51, ' Focus on what to do next instead of worrying about what went wrong. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:15:24'),
(12653, 51, ' I know it\'s hard and I know it\'s taking too long but don\'t give up on yourself. Stay strong and keep fighting!  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:15:36'),
(12654, 51, ' If you were strong enough to survive your past circumstances you are strong enough to survive your present circumstances. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:15:50'),
(12655, 51, ' Make life yours. Get past your mistakes of the past by learning from them and moving forward in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:16:07'),
(12656, 51, ' Letting go is beautiful but you have to let it be and find someone who appreciates who you are. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:16:49'),
(12657, 51, ' Moving on becomes so painful when our other half is still held by our past. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:17:02'),
(12658, 51, ' You can\'t move forward if your past is holding you back. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:17:14'),
(12659, 51, ' When people walk away, let them. Your future is not about those who walk away but those who stay in for the ride.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:17:29'),
(12660, 51, ' Sometimes things don\'t go the way we plan them, sometimes we just have to accept them and prepare for the next day. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:17:39'),
(12661, 51, ' It is better to take many small steps in the right direction than to make a great leap forward only to stumble backward.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:17:51'),
(12662, 51, ' Life is about accepting what you\'ve got. And moving on ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:18:13'),
(12663, 51, ' Sometimes you need to walk away to be appreciated.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:18:41'),
(12664, 51, ' Nobody\'s perfect, we all make mistakes. Forgive yourself, learn the lesson and move on. Something better is just around the corner.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:18:53'),
(12665, 51, ' Once you realize your worth, letting go will become the best decision you would ever make. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:19:07'),
(12666, 51, ' When the wrong people leave your life, the right things start. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:19:19'),
(12667, 51, ' Sometimes we need to let go of something that makes us happy for us to become happier in the future.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:19:30'),
(12668, 51, ' At some point you just have to let go of what you thought should happen and live in what is happening.   ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:19:45'),
(12669, 51, ' Letting go does not mean you stop caring. It means you stop trying to force others to ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:20:08'),
(12670, 51, ' The best can\'t find you until you put the worst behind you.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:20:21'),
(12671, 51, ' Life will became so easy if you stop looking back in the past and worrying about the future', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:20:34'),
(12672, 51, 'The sooner you realize things will never be the same again the sooner you can move on.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:20:46'),
(12673, 51, ' Moving on doesn\'t mean you forget about things. It just means you have to accept what\'s happened and continue living. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:21:19'),
(12674, 51, ' I can choose to let it define me, confine me, refine me, outshine me or I can choose to move on and leave them behind me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:22:03'),
(12675, 51, 'To truly love is to have the courage to walk away and let the other person who wishes to be free go no matter how much it hurts ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:22:17'),
(12676, 51, ' I am going to hold on to the times that we had, and find a way to make it without you.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:22:29'),
(12677, 51, ' Before a new chapter is begun, the old one has to be finished', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:22:45'),
(12678, 51, 'Every heartache will fade away. Just like every storm runs out of rain. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:23:37'),
(12679, 51, ' Just because you miss them, that doesn\'t mean you need them back in your life. Missing them is a part of moving on ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:24:55'),
(12680, 51, ' If I cut you off, chances are, you handed me the scissors. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:25:08'),
(12681, 51, ' Sometimes you just need to put the past away and move on with your life', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:25:28'),
(12682, 51, ' I never stopped caring, but you did, and thats why Ive moved on. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:25:44'),
(12683, 51, ' Sometimes you have to let go and be free. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:25:57'),
(12684, 51, ' There\'s so much more to life than a heart which does not beat for you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:26:12'),
(12685, 51, ' Just because your life story has a horrible beginning it doesn\'t mean that it can\'t have a happy ending. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:26:23'),
(12686, 51, ' If they keep hurting you, love them and stay or love yourself and leave. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:26:36'),
(12687, 51, ' When guilt rears its ugly head, confront it, discuss it and let it go. The past is over. Forgive yourself and move on', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:26:52'),
(12688, 51, ' I don\'t forget, I choose to forgive. I don\'t regret, I choose to move on. I don\'t hate, I choose to Love. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:27:06'),
(12689, 51, ' Worrying does not empty tomorrow of its troubles, it empties today of its strength. Stop worrying and let life go on, happily. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:27:20'),
(12690, 51, ' Moving on is made a lot easier when you accept that some people are seasonal. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:27:33'),
(12691, 51, ' Don\'t waste your time getting hurt by someone when there\'s someone else out there waiting to make you happy.  ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:27:48'),
(12692, 51, ' It might hurt when you move on, but then it will heal. And with each passing day, you will get stronger and life will get better. ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAMoving On', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-05 17:28:02'),
(12693, 49, 'Heal me, O Lord, and I shall be healed; save me, and I shall be saved, for you are my praise. Jeremiah 17:14', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 17:06:08'),
