(12837, 49, 'He shall call upon Me, and I will answer him; I will be with him in trouble; I will deliver him and honor him. Psalm 91:15', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:00:43'),
(12838, 49, 'Whenever I am afraid, I will trust in You. In God I have put my trust; I will not fear. What can flesh do to me?. Psalm 56:3-4', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:01:20'),
(12839, 49, 'The Lord is on my side; I will not fear. What can man do to me? . Psalm 118:6', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:01:43'),
(12840, 49, 'You will keep him in perfect peace, Whose mind is stayed on You, Because he trusts in You.  Isaiah 26:3', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:02:04'),
(12841, 49, 'So we may boldly say: \'The Lord is my helper; I will not fear. What can man do to me?\' .Hebrews 13:6', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:02:21'),
(12842, 49, 'But the Lord is faithful, who will establish you and guard you from the evil one .2 Thessalonians 3:3', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:02:43'),
(12843, 49, 'From the end of the earth I will cry to You, When my heart is overwhelmed; Lead me to the rock that is higher than I. Psalm 61:2', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:07:06'),
(12844, 49, 'Trust in Him at all times, you people; Pour out your heart before Him; God is a refuge for us. Selah. Psalm 62:8', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:07:24'),
(12845, 49, 'Be my strong refuge, To which I may resort continually; You have given the commandment to save me, For You are my rock and my fortress. Psalm 71:3', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:07:57'),
(12846, 49, 'The Lord is good, A stronghold in the day of trouble; And He knows those who trust in Him. Nahum 1:7 ', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAABiblical Verses', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-09-09 18:08:11'),
(12847, 43, 'Kindness is ever the begetter of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:23:49'),
(12848, 43, 'If you want others to be happy, practice compassion. If you want to be happy, practice compassion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:02'),
(12849, 43, 'Real generosity is doing something nice for someone who will never find out.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:10'),
(12850, 43, 'Ask yourself: Have you been kind today? Make kindness your daily modus operandi and change your world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:19'),
(12851, 43, 'Whenever you are confronted with an opponent. Conquer him with love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:29'),
(12852, 43, 'We\'re here for a reason. I believe a bit of the reason is to throw little torches out to lead people through the dark.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:37'),
(12853, 43, 'Ignorant kindness may have the effect of cruelty; but to be angry with it as if it were direct cruelty would be an ignorant unkindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:47'),
(12854, 43, 'Kindness in giving creates love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:24:55'),
(12855, 43, 'For attractive lips, speak words of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:04'),
(12856, 43, 'Getting money is not all a man\'s business: to cultivate kindness is a valuable part of the business of life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:14'),
(12857, 43, 'Everyone responds to kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:22'),
(12858, 43, 'The greatest good you can do for another is not just to share your riches but to reveal to him his own.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:31'),
(12859, 43, 'When we know ourselves to be connected to all others, acting compassionately is simply the natural thing to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:39'),
(12860, 43, 'He that has done you a kindness will be more ready to do you another, than he whom you yourself have obliged.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:25:47'),
(12861, 43, 'Great people are those who make others feel that they, too, can become great.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:00'),
(12862, 43, 'They who sow courtesy reap friendship, and they who plant kindness gather love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:19'),
(12863, 43, 'We think too much and feel too little.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:30'),
(12864, 43, 'Shall we make a new rule of life from tonight: always to try to be a little kinder than is necessary?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:38'),
(12865, 43, 'If a man be gracious and courteous to strangers, it shows he is a citizen of the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:45'),
(12866, 43, 'Practice random acts of kindness and senseless acts of beauty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:26:53'),
(12867, 43, 'Showing kindness to others is one of the nicest things we can do for ourselves.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:27:03'),
(12868, 43, 'As far as we can discern, the sole purpose of human existence is to kindle a light in the darkness of mere being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:27:12'),
(12869, 43, 'To make one good action succeed another, is the perfection of goodness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:27:21'),
(12870, 43, 'There are no traffic jams when you go the extra mile.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:27:42'),
(12871, 43, 'Service is the rent we pay for being. It is the very purpose of life, and not something you do in your spare time.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:27:49'),
(12872, 43, 'People just take your kindness for weakness sometimes, and that\'s just the bottom line.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:28:02'),
(12873, 43, 'For lovely eyes, seek out the good in people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:28:12'),
(12874, 43, 'You can accomplish by kindness what you cannot by force.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:28:46'),
(12875, 43, 'Kindness in thinking creates profoundness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:28:56'),
(12876, 43, 'Don\'t be yourself - be someone a little nicer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:04'),
(12877, 43, 'Never look down on anybody unless you\'re helping him up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:12'),
(12878, 43, 'The catch phrase for the day is \'Do an act of kindness. Help one person smile.\'', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:25'),
(12879, 43, 'That which you give to another will become your own sustenance; if you light a lamp for another, your own way will be lit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:34'),
(12880, 43, 'What I regret most in my life are failures of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:42'),
(12881, 43, 'Do good by stealth, and blush to find it fame.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:49'),
(12882, 43, 'Oh worse than everything, is kindness counterfeiting absent love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:29:57'),
(12883, 43, 'You cannot do a kindness too soon.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:06'),
(12884, 43, 'Kindness, I\'ve discovered, is everything in life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:14'),
(12885, 43, 'Being considerate of others will take your children further in life than any college degree.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:25'),
(12886, 43, 'Kindness makes a fellow feel good whether it\'s being done to him or by him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:41'),
(12887, 43, 'Without kindness there can be no true joy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:49'),
(12888, 43, 'Act with kindness but do not expect gratitude.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:30:56'),
(12889, 43, 'Real kindness seeks no return.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:04'),
(12890, 43, 'One\'s life has value so long as one attributes value to the life of others, by means of love, friendship, indignation and compassion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:13'),
(12891, 43, 'Goodness is achieved not in a vacuum, but in the company of other men, attended by love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:20'),
(12892, 43, 'We are made kind by being kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:28'),
(12893, 43, 'When your suffering is a little greater than my suffering I feel that I am a little cruel.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:36'),
(12894, 43, 'If compassion was the motivating factor behind all of our decisions, would our world not be a completely different place?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:45'),
(12895, 43, 'Illness is the doctor to whom we pay most heed; to kindness, to knowledge, we make promise only; pain we obey.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:31:56'),
(12896, 43, 'Our own brain, our own heart is our temple; the philosophy is kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:04'),
(12897, 43, 'The everyday kindness of the back roads more than makes up for the acts of greed in the headlines.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:12'),
(12898, 43, 'The best practical advice I can give to the present generation is to practice the virtue which the Christians call love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:19'),
(12899, 43, 'Men are more prone to revenge injuries than to requite kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:28'),
(12900, 43, 'He who waits to do a great deal of good at once will never do anything.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:36'),
(12901, 43, 'Kindness refreshes and restores the tired and broken.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:44'),
(12902, 43, 'Kindness in words creates confidence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:32:54'),
(12903, 43, 'Kindness is the music of Good Will to men, and on this harp the smallest fingers may play heaven\'s sweetest tunes on earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:33:02'),
(12904, 43, 'The more sympathy you give, the less you need.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:33:11'),
(12905, 43, 'Be Somebody who makes Everybody feel like a Somebody.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:33:37'),
(12906, 43, 'There\'s no dearth of kindness In the world of ours; Only in our blindness We gather thorns for flowers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:33:46'),
(12907, 43, 'A word of kindness is seldom spoken in vain, while witty saying are as easily lost as the pearls slipping from a broken string.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:33:54'),
(12908, 43, 'Kindness in women, not their beauteous looks, Shall win my love.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:02'),
(12909, 43, 'Unseasonable kindness gets no thanks.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:10'),
(12910, 43, 'We have committed the Golden Rule to memory; let us now commit it to life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:18'),
(12911, 43, 'I have always held firmly to the thought that each one of us can do a little to bring some portion of misery to an end.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:26'),
(12912, 43, 'Scatter seeds of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:35'),
(12913, 43, 'Did universal charity prevail, earth would be a heaven, and hell a fable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:42'),
(12914, 43, 'People are governed with the head; kindness of heart is little use in chess.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:50'),
(12915, 43, 'Constant Kindness can accomplish much.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:34:59'),
(12916, 43, 'My Brain and My Heart are my Temples. My true Religion is Kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:08'),
(12917, 43, 'Kindness is the power that moves us to support and heal someone who offers nothing in return.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:16'),
(12918, 43, 'I always say that kindness is the greatest beauty that you can have.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:24'),
(12919, 43, 'Neither genius, fame, nor love show the greatness of the soul. Only kindness can do that.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:31'),
(12920, 43, 'Only your compassion and your loving kindness are invincible, and without limit.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:41'),
(12921, 43, 'Charity begins at home, but should not end there.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:48'),
(12922, 43, 'One man cannot hold another man down in the ditch without remaining down in the ditch with him.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:35:55'),
(12923, 43, 'We hate the kindness which we understand.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:36:03'),
(12924, 43, 'Be thoughtful of others and you will not be shy, for they are incompatible addictions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:36:54'),
(12925, 43, 'When you are young you take the kindness people show you as your right.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:02'),
(12926, 43, 'It is difficult to tell how much men\'s minds are conciliated by a kind manner and gentle speech.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:10'),
(12927, 43, 'There are eight rungs in charity. The highest is when you help a man to help himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:18'),
(12928, 43, 'The greater the kindred is, the lesse the kindnesse must bee.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:29'),
(12929, 43, 'Giving connects two people, the giver and the receiver, and this connection gives birth to a new sense of belonging.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:37'),
(12930, 43, 'It is not only for what we do that we are held responsible, but also for what we do not do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:44'),
(12931, 43, 'For the cause that lacks assistance, The wrong that needs resistance, For the future in the distance, And the good that I can do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:37:53'),
(12932, 43, 'Complete possession is proved only by giving. All you are unable to give possesses you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:01'),
(12933, 43, 'Recompense injury with justice, and recompense kindness with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:09'),
(12934, 43, 'Have you had a kindness shown? Pass it on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:17'),
(12935, 43, 'A word spoken in loving kindness is worth far more than any gift.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:25'),
(12936, 43, 'Kindness is wisdom. There is none in life But needs it and may learn.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:33'),
(12937, 43, 'It is the characteristic of the magnanimous man to ask no favor but to be ready to do kindness to others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:44'),
(12938, 43, 'If what must be given is given willingly the kindness is doubled.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:38:52'),
(12939, 43, 'What this world needs is a new kind of army - the army of the kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:00'),
(12940, 43, 'Kindness is gladdening the hearts of those who are traveling the dark journey with us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:14'),
(12941, 43, 'You can\'t live a perfect day without doing something for someone who will never be able to repay you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:23'),
(12942, 43, 'The daisy, by the shadow that it casts, Protects the lingering dewdrop from the sun.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:31'),
(12943, 43, 'Yet do I fear thy nature; It is too full o\' the milk of human kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:40'),
(12944, 43, 'God loves each of us as if there were only one of us.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:50'),
(12945, 43, 'And Heaven, that every virtue bears in mind, E\'en to the ashes of the just is kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:39:57'),
(12946, 43, 'Compassion is not weakness, and concern for the unfortunate is not socialism.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:05'),
(12947, 43, 'If you stop to be kind, you must swerve often from your path.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:12'),
(12948, 43, 'Great persons are able to do great kindnesses.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:20'),
(12949, 43, 'Life is short but there is always time for courtesy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:29'),
(12950, 43, 'Love and kindness are never wasted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:36'),
(12951, 43, 'When you\'re a kid it\'s people\'s cruelty that makes you cry, then when you\'re an adult it\'s their kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:40:57'),
(12952, 43, 'My religion is kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:09'),
(12953, 43, 'Seek not good from without; seek it within yourselves, or you will never find it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:17'),
(12954, 43, 'There is one word which may serve as a rule of practice for all one\'s life -reciprocity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:25');
INSERT INTO `tbl_gallery` (`id`, `cat_id`, `quote`, `image`, `view_count`, `download_count`, `image_url`, `type`, `featured`, `tags`, `image_name`, `image_resolution`, `image_size`, `image_extension`, `last_update`) VALUES
(12955, 43, 'There\'s no use doing a kindness if you do it a day too late.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:34'),
(12956, 43, 'More than cleverness, we need kindness and gentleness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:43'),
(12957, 43, 'A little thought and a little kindness are often worth more than a great deal of money.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:41:53'),
(12958, 43, 'Kindness is like snow-it beautifies everything it covers.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:42:00'),
(12959, 43, 'The first thing a kindness deserves is acceptance, the second, transmission.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:42:28'),
(12960, 43, 'One good turn asketh another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:42:38'),
(12961, 43, 'It is easy to perform a good action, but not easy to acquire a settled habit of performing such actions.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:42:47'),
(12962, 43, 'Life is just a short walk from the cradle to the grave - and it sure behooves us to be kind to one another along the way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:42:56'),
(12963, 43, 'Perfect kindness acts without thinking of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:43:06'),
(12964, 43, 'By the accident of fortune a man may rule the world for a time, but by virtue of love and kindness he may rule the world forever.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:43:24'),
(12965, 43, 'Persistent kindness conquers the ill-disposed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:43:32'),
(12966, 43, 'We cannot possibly let ourselves get frozen into regarding everyone we do not know as an absolute stranger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:43:42'),
(12967, 43, 'I have found that among its other benefits, giving liberates the soul of the giver.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:08'),
(12968, 43, 'Kindness in ourselves is the honey that blunts the sting of unkindness in another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:17'),
(12969, 43, 'Kindness is the velvet of social intercourse.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:25'),
(12970, 43, 'When giving comes directly from the heart, it can never disappoint or embarrass.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:33'),
(12971, 43, 'Do your little bit of good where you are; its those little bits of good put together that overwhelm the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:48'),
(12972, 43, 'Compassion is the chief law of human existence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:44:56'),
(12973, 43, 'Reversing your treatment of the man you have wronged is better than asking his forgiveness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:06'),
(12974, 43, 'Even small acts of kindness can make a profound difference to somebody else.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:21'),
(12975, 43, 'Service to others is the rent you pay for your room here on earth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:30'),
(12976, 43, 'Nothing teaches character better than generosity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:40'),
(12977, 43, 'Be silly. Be honest. Be kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:49'),
(12978, 43, 'Compassion will cure more sins than condemnation.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:45:58'),
(12979, 43, 'Kindly words do not enter so deeply into men as a reputation for kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:46:06'),
(12980, 43, 'Friendship is a living thing that lasts only as it is nourished with kindness, sympathy, and understanding.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:46:15'),
(12981, 43, 'Simplification is one of the most difficult things to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:46:24'),
(12982, 43, 'If you want to give the devil a nervous breakdown, just get up every day and see how much good you can do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:46:33'),
(12983, 43, 'So many gods, so many creeds, so many paths that wind and wind while just the art of being kind is all the sad world needs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:46:44'),
(12984, 43, 'Make it a practice to judge persons and things in the most favorable light at all times and under all circumstances.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:02'),
(12985, 43, 'A disciple having asked for a definition of charity, the Master said LOVE ONE ANOTHER.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:09'),
(12986, 43, 'No matter how little you have, you can always give some of it away.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:18'),
(12987, 43, 'Keep doing good deeds long enough, and you\'ll probably turn out a good man in spite of yourself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:26'),
(12988, 43, 'Let us choose life and love, and happily use our selves up in loving service to one another.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:44'),
(12989, 43, 'Kindness’ covers all of my political beliefs.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:47:52'),
(12990, 43, 'Kindness can turn the bad man\'s heart, and fools convert to wise, Make poison into nectar-juice, and friends of enemies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:00'),
(12991, 43, 'In the end only kindness matters.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:09'),
(12992, 43, 'To give and then not feel that one has given is the very best of all ways of giving.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:17'),
(12993, 43, 'You can tell by the kindness of a dog how a human should be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:27'),
(12994, 43, 'Be good, be kind, be humane, and charitable; love your fellows; console the afflicted; pardon those who have done you wrong.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:35'),
(12995, 43, 'The center of human nature is rooted in ten thousand ordinary acts of kindness that define our days.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:43'),
(12996, 43, 'Truth is a deep kindness that teaches us to be content in our everyday life and share with the people the same happiness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:51'),
(12997, 43, 'Kindness goes a long ways lots of times when it ought to stay at home.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:48:59'),
(12998, 43, 'It is kindness immediately to refuse what you intend to deny.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:08'),
(12999, 43, 'Always stop to think whether your fun may be the cause of another\'s unhappiness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:16'),
(13000, 43, 'Always carry with you a little reasonable doubt, should you meet someone who needs to be found innocent.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:24'),
(13001, 43, 'Kurds are like fire, if approached kindly they will warm you, if approached badly they will burn you', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:34'),
(13002, 43, 'The good deed you do today, for a brother or sister in need will come back to you some day, for humanity\'s a circle in deed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:41'),
(13003, 43, 'Kindness eases everything almost as much as money does.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:49:57'),
(13004, 43, 'A life of kindness is the primary meaning of divine worship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:05'),
(13005, 43, 'A life of kindness is the primary meaning of divine worship.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:13'),
(13006, 43, 'An enemy to whom you show kindness becomes your friend.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:21'),
(13007, 43, 'The true measure of a man is how he treats someone who can do him absolutely no good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:31'),
(13008, 43, 'Kindness will always attract kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:39'),
(13009, 43, 'There is only one way of not hating those who do us wrong, and that is by doing them good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:50'),
(13010, 43, 'The creed of a true saint is to make the best of life, and to make the most of it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:50:58'),
(13011, 43, 'Kindness is no virtue, but a common duty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:05'),
(13012, 43, 'Human kindness is like a defective tap, the first gush may be impressive but the stream soon dries up.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:13'),
(13013, 43, 'Love thy neighbor, and if it requires that you bend your understanding of the truth, the Truth will understand.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:21'),
(13014, 43, 'Adversity has the effect of eliciting talents which, in prosperous circumstances, would have lain dormant.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:29'),
(13015, 43, 'True popularity comes from acts of kindness rather than acts of stupidity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:37'),
(13016, 43, 'Together we are creating a more peaceful, just and sustainable world through kindness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:46'),
(13017, 43, 'Life is not so short but that there is always time enough for courtesy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:51:55'),
(13018, 43, 'Don\'t ever underestimate the importance of treating others with respect and kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:52:02'),
(13019, 43, 'Our kindness may be the most persuasive argument for that which we believe.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:52:10'),
(13020, 43, 'Not always actions show the man; we find who does a kindness is not therefore kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:52:47'),
(13021, 43, 'The cheapest gift I have to give is kindness, and it is the best.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:07'),
(13022, 43, 'Eradicating a religion of kindness is, I think, a terrible thing for the Chinese to attempt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:15'),
(13023, 43, 'Life is given to us, we earn it by giving it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:23'),
(13024, 43, 'Treat everyone with kindness, dignity, compassion and respect, irrespective of whether you think they understand or not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:32'),
(13025, 43, 'Even a little gift may be vast with loving kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:39'),
(13026, 43, 'Surely it is the maxim of loving-kindness: Do not unto others that you would not have them do unto you.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:47'),
(13027, 43, 'Divine opportunities are all around you every day. Make a conscious effort today to show kindness to someone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:53:55'),
(13028, 43, 'It is God\'s kindness to terrify you in order to lead you to safety.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:03'),
(13029, 43, 'Man is born for deeds of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:10'),
(13030, 43, 'How wonderful it is that nobody need wait a single moment before starting to improve the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:21'),
(13031, 43, 'If you haven\'t got any charity in your heart, you have the worst kind of heart trouble.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:29'),
(13032, 43, 'I always prefer to believe the best of everybody, it saves so much trouble.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:41'),
(13033, 43, 'No one is more worthy of your kindness and compassion than you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:51'),
(13034, 43, 'If you can be kind and considerate for one day, then you can be for another. It won\'t cost you a penny in the world. Begin today.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:54:59'),
(13035, 43, 'The truest greatness lies in being kind, the truest wisdom in a happy mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:55:07'),
(13036, 43, 'Be kind whenever possible. It is always possible.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:55:15'),
(13037, 43, 'If life becomes hard, soften it with random acts of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:55:48'),
(13038, 43, 'Kindness is the key to peace and harmony in family life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:55:56'),
(13039, 43, 'And you can always, always, give kindness', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:04'),
(13040, 43, 'Unless someone like you cares a whole awful lot, nothing is going to get better. It\'s not.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:11'),
(13041, 43, 'Its unfortunate and I really wish I wouldn\'t have to say this, but I really like human beings who have suffered. They\'re kinder.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:20'),
(13042, 43, 'You is kind. You is smart. You is important.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:28'),
(13043, 43, 'If we will have the kindness of others, we must endure their follies.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:36'),
(13044, 43, 'Man is kind enough when he is not excited by religion', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:56:48'),
(13045, 43, 'The short way to happiness is through kindness and sensitivity.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:57:05'),
(13046, 43, 'If you\'re naturally kind, you attract a lot of people you don\'t like.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:57:16'),
(13047, 43, 'If I can stop one heart from breaking, I shall not live in vain.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:57:36'),
(13048, 43, 'If we always helped one another, no one would need luck.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:57:43'),
(13049, 43, 'A grateful heart is like a sponge that soaks up God\'s goodness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:57:54'),
(13050, 43, 'A gentle answer turns away wrath, but a harsh word stirs up anger.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:58:01'),
(13051, 43, 'Let us learn from Christ how to pray, to forgive, to sow peace, and to be near those in need.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:58:09'),
(13052, 43, 'One person can stop a great injustice. One person can be a voice for truth. One person’s kindness can save a life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:58:18'),
(13053, 43, 'When people are mean to you, win them over with kindness. If it doesn\'t work, you still win.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:58:25'),
(13054, 43, 'Courage and clemency are equal virtues.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:58:34'),
(13055, 43, 'But remember, boy, that a kind act can sometimes be as powerful as a sword.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:59:01'),
(13056, 43, 'We have two ears and one mouth so that we can listen twice as much as we speak.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:59:11'),
(13057, 43, 'Do one act of kindness each day of the year and change 365 lives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:59:19'),
(13058, 43, 'If you set out to do a good deed, you may do a hundred small kindnesses on the way.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:59:26'),
(13059, 43, 'I\'m a kind person, I\'m kind to everyone, but if you are unkind to me, then kindness is not what you\'ll remember me for', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 04:59:49'),
(13060, 43, 'True kindness is rooted in a deep sense of abundance, out of which flows a sense that even as I give, it is being given back to me.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:02'),
(13061, 43, 'Cruelty hardens and degrades, kindness reforms and ennobles.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:10'),
(13062, 43, 'Kindness has no religion. It is like an open sky.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:18'),
(13063, 43, 'When people are serving, life is no longer meaningless.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:26'),
(13064, 43, 'He who distributes the milk of human kindness cannot help but spill a little on himself.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:32'),
(13065, 43, 'Random acts of kindness and the desire to do the best job possible lead to trust.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:41'),
(13066, 43, 'Kindness is not an act, it\'s a lifestyle.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:48'),
(13067, 43, 'I think your heart needs to be broken, and broken open, at least once to have a heart at all or to have a heart for others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:00:58'),
(13068, 43, 'Saints are the great teachers of the loving-kindness and fascination with God.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:05'),
(13069, 43, 'The two wings of mindfulness and kindness will begin to open the heart to more connection with our world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:11'),
(13070, 43, 'Kindness is a language herd by deaf men and felt by blind men.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:20'),
(13071, 43, 'Kindness should become the natural way of life,not the exception.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:38'),
(13072, 43, 'Remember that the biggest thing you could do today is a small act of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:45'),
(13073, 43, 'Hatred and anger are powerless when met with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:01:52'),
(13074, 43, 'In the end, what really matters? Only kindness. Only making somebody a little happier for your presence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:02:00'),
(13075, 43, 'My message is always the same: to cultivate and practice love, kindness, compassion and tolerance.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:02:15'),
(13076, 43, 'I think we ought to have a kindness year, or a kindness century.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:02:23'),
(13077, 43, 'Kindness is a highly underrated quality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:03'),
(13078, 43, 'Kindness which is bestowed on the good is never lost.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:11'),
(13079, 43, 'With Kindness 1+1 always equals more than 2', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:18'),
(13080, 43, 'If you can\'t go where people are happier, try to make people happier where you are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:26'),
(13081, 43, 'Sometimes it takes only one act of kindness and caring to change a person\'s life.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:35'),
(13082, 43, 'There is nothing more powerful than kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:42'),
(13083, 43, 'Kindness to self will put you in the perfect attitude and position to be kind to others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:03:51'),
(13084, 43, 'Kindness and consideration of somebody besides yourself. I think that keeps you feeling young. I really do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:00'),
(13085, 43, 'I prefer to make a mistake because I am too kind than to perform miracles without any kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:16'),
(13086, 43, 'Is base in kind, and born to be a slave.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:23'),
(13087, 43, 'The universe is made of one kind of what-ever-it-is, which cannot be defined.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:30'),
(13088, 43, 'Actions determine what kind of characteristics are developed.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:46'),
(13089, 43, 'We are a kind of posterity in respect to them.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:04:52'),
(13090, 43, 'An epic is the easiest kind of picture to make badly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:05:01'),
(13092, 43, 'Things that have a common quality ever quickly seek their kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:05:38'),
(13093, 43, 'Paradise is open to all kind hearts.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:06:09'),
(13094, 43, 'It takes all sorts of in and outdoor schooling To get adapted to my kind of fooling.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:06:25'),
(13095, 43, 'The British like any kind of music so long as it is loud.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:06:33'),
(13096, 43, 'Respect kindly all religions that teach loving kindness, and have no respect for envy and jealousy. Never follow hate.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:06:41'),
(13097, 43, 'I want to have thoughts of abundance. I want to have thoughts of love, of kindness, of beauty.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:12'),
(13098, 43, 'Cruel birds, ravens, but wise. And creatures should be loved for their wisdom if they cannot be loved for kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:19'),
(13099, 43, 'Great people create great acts of kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:28'),
(13100, 43, 'A brush of kindness can paint a smile on a face.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:35'),
(13101, 43, 'Bitterness is repaid more often than kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:46'),
(13102, 43, 'I think true success is intrinsic... It\'s love. It\'s kindness. It\'s community.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:07:58'),
(13103, 43, 'If God is Love, He is, by definition, something more than mere kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:08:07'),
(13104, 43, 'You have the absolute power to change someone\'s life with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:08:20'),
(13105, 43, 'May our memories of kindness be long and of offenses be short.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:08:28'),
(13106, 43, 'You can never go wrong with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:08:41'),
(13107, 43, 'Genuine kindness is not what we do, it is what we are.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:02'),
(13108, 43, 'A man needs the feelings of kindness to think great than thinking of the greatness to feel good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:13'),
(13109, 43, 'You can be rich in spirit, kindness, love and all those things that you can\'t put a dollar sign on.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:20'),
(13110, 43, 'Kindness is a calling. Caring about people is powerful. Love changes lives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:28'),
(13111, 43, 'The world tells us to be mean and bitter to survive. But I believe kindness is the very thing that makes us thrive.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:36'),
(13112, 43, 'To eliminate the inner turmoil we must focus our attention inward and act with loving kindness to ourselves—and each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:45'),
(13113, 43, 'Praise will come to those whose kindness leaves you without debt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:09:54'),
(13114, 43, 'People pay the doctor for his trouble; for his kindness they still remain in his debt.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:10:00'),
(13115, 43, 'Spontaneous kindness is to hipsters as high beams are to deer.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:10:22'),
(13116, 43, 'To a well deserving person God will show favor. To an ill deserving person He will simply be just.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:10:36'),
(13117, 43, 'One of the ultimate things a human can learn is kindness for their fellow humans', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:10:44'),
(13118, 43, 'Kindness is the golden thread that holds society together.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:17'),
(13119, 43, 'Our friends are generally ready to do everything for us, except the very thing we wish them to do.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:25'),
(13120, 43, 'Often what we take for a kindness is just someone acting in their capacity as a human being.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:32'),
(13121, 43, 'There\'s a lot of not caring that goes under the name of minding your own business.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:40'),
(13122, 43, 'Loving-kindness is required, but a follower of Christ-just like the Master-will be firm in the truth.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:47'),
(13123, 43, 'Do not ask me to be kind; just ask me to act as though I were.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:11:55'),
(13124, 43, 'Requite injury with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:12:02'),
(13125, 43, 'Loving-kindness is the better part of goodness. It lends grace to the sterner qualities of which this consists.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:12:11'),
(13126, 43, 'When you confer a benefit on those worthy of it, you confer a favor on all.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:12:19'),
(13127, 43, 'Nature, in giving tears to man, confessed that he Had a tender heart; this is our noblest quality.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:12:28'),
(13128, 43, 'Kindness acts Not always as you think; a hated hand Renders it odious.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:12:45'),
(13129, 43, 'An inherent kindness exists in the process of aging ... we are allowed to move along gradually.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:13:13'),
(13130, 43, 'Kindness and patience were always called for.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:13:18'),
(13131, 43, 'Do not feel badly if your kindness is rewarded with ingratitude; it is better to fall from your dream clouds than from a third-story window.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:13:35'),
(13132, 43, 'Always radiate positive currents of... Light, Goodness, Love, Kindness, Hope and Determination.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:15:48'),
(13133, 43, 'In times of tragedies, our duty is to lend a helping hand to those in grief and thus light lamps of kindness and compassion.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:15:58'),
(13134, 43, 'For your kindness, I\'m in debt to you. For your selflessness, my admiration.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:16:07'),
(13135, 43, 'Being part of an agenda beyond ourselves liberates us to complement each other rather than compete with each other.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:16:18'),
(13136, 43, 'I don\'t worry about people misinterpreting my kindness for weakness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:16:27'),
(13137, 43, 'I am a little bit of a softie, yes. Actually I don\'t think it\'s softness, I think it\'s kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:16:35'),
(13138, 43, 'There are people who have lost every trace of human kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:16:53'),
(13139, 43, 'Kindness is something that I feel is leaving us a little bit - people are getting more self-involved.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:03'),
(13140, 43, 'Kindness and love open the doors to one\'s soul.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:14'),
(13141, 43, 'There is no small act of kindness. Every compassionate act makes large the world.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:21'),
(13142, 43, 'Kindness causes us to learn, and to forget, many things.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:33'),
(13143, 43, 'I\'m always impressed by confidence, kindness and a sense of humour.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:42'),
(13144, 43, 'I value humor, kindness, and the ability to tell a good story far more than money, status, or the kind of car someone drives.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:51'),
(13145, 43, 'I believe that in the end that it is kindness and accommodation that are all the catalysts for real change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:17:59'),
(13146, 43, 'We\'re all mankind and humankind - so just be one and show kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:18:07'),
(13147, 43, 'To rankling poison hast thou turned in me the milk of human kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:18:27'),
(13148, 43, 'Let the man, who would be grateful, think of repaying a kindness, even while receiving it.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:18:57'),
(13149, 43, 'Wit is an intermittent fountain; kindness is a perennial spring.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:07'),
(13150, 43, 'Let us open up our natures, throw wide the doors of our hearts and let in the sunshine of good will and kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:18'),
(13151, 43, 'Be prudent, diligent, temperate and discreet. Remember that every human being has a claim upon your kind offices.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:25'),
(13152, 43, 'We really want to thank everyone for their kindness and generosity, even those who aren\'t helping us directly.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:39'),
(13153, 43, 'No act of kindness is wasted.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:47'),
(13154, 43, 'The more kindness shown to an envious man, the worse he becomes.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:19:56'),
(13155, 43, 'Life is a blend of laughter and tears, a combination of rain and sunshine.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:20:17'),
(13156, 43, 'Maturity is the ability to live in peace with that which we cannot change.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:20:28'),
(13157, 43, 'Only kindness matters. We are God\'s hands.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:20:36'),
(13158, 43, 'It is not the things you have that make you happy. It is love and kindness and helping each other and just plain being good.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:20:45'),
(13159, 43, 'Rigorous authority and justice are the kindness of kings.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:20:55'),
(13160, 43, 'The secret to enlightenment is kindness and selfless giving. Without that, it\'s just words, isn\'t it?', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:21:10'),
(13161, 43, 'Kindness is one of the best gifts you can bestow... We know that inherently that feels great.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:21:17'),
(13162, 43, 'The world is full of love and pity, I say. Had there been less suffering, there would have been less kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:21:27'),
(13163, 43, 'Justice for some people is an evil for others. Good intentions, kindness, and hope will not necessarily make people happy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:21:35'),
(13164, 43, 'A god of kindness would be charitable to all. Your god of wrath and punishment is but a monstrous phantasy.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:21:59'),
(13165, 43, 'For whoever knows how to return a kindness he has received must be a friend above all price.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:22:07'),
(13166, 43, 'Those who return evil for good should not expect the kindness of others to last long.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:22:29'),
(13167, 43, 'The greatest kindness will not bind the ungrateful.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:22:37'),
(13168, 43, 'All is well, practice kindness, heaven is nigh.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:22:47'),
(13169, 43, 'Take a month and show some kindness for the folks who thought that blindness was an illness that affected eyes alone.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:23:07'),
(13170, 43, 'I\'m more interested in plot than theme, but I hope my values find their way into my stories: kindness, sympathy, effort, and humor!', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:23:20'),
(13171, 43, 'In our interactions with others, gentleness, kindness, respectare the source of harmony', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:23:31'),
(13172, 43, 'The real index of civilization is when people are kinder than they need to be.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:23:38'),
(13173, 43, 'I am vulnerable, starved for kindness. And when I receive it, I lose my mind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:23:51'),
(13174, 43, 'Kindness which is not inexhaustible does not deserve the name.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:24:16'),
(13175, 43, 'Kindness, so far as we can return it, is agreeable.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:24:27'),
(13176, 43, 'God wishes to exhaust all means of kindness before His hand takes hold on justice.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:24:36'),
(13177, 43, 'It is not without a purpose when a rich man greets a poor one with kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:24:42'),
(13178, 43, 'I have sped by land and sea, and mingled with much people, but never yet could find a spot unsunned by human kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:24:52'),
(13179, 43, 'There are always a few people you do a lot for, and a few who do a lot for you, but they\'re not the same people.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:25:03'),
(13180, 43, 'To a haughty belly, kindness is hard to swallow and harder to digest.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:25:15'),
(13181, 43, 'Friendship is infinitely better than kindness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:30:01'),
(13182, 43, 'No thanks attach to a kindness long deferred.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:30:13'),
(13183, 43, 'Surely there is no road of effort so steep but a loving deed may soften its hardshness.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:30:25'),
(13184, 43, 'The same quickness which makes a mind buoyant in gladness often makes it gentlest and most sympathetic in sorrow.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:30:45'),
(13185, 43, 'There is a vast deal of vital air in loving words.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:30:55'),
(13186, 43, 'A little praise is good for a shy temper; it teaches it to rely on the kindness of others.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:02'),
(13187, 43, 'Everyone, to those weaker than themselves, is kind.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:11'),
(13188, 43, 'To be civilized is to be incapable of giving unnecessary offense, it is to have some quality of consideration for all who cross our path.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:24'),
(13189, 43, 'When the milk of human kindness turns sour, it is a singularly unpalatable draught.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:32'),
(13190, 43, 'It is kindness that makes one strong and brave; and so we are kind to our prisoners.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:40'),
(13191, 43, 'A small unkindness is a great offence.', '', 0, 0, '', 'upload', 'no', 'AAAKindness', 'none', '0', '0', '', '2023-10-05 05:31:47'),
